NK125(co)003:1: // gu ru dwi t+ai ya bu d+d+ha pa d+ma sam
NK125(co)003:2: b+ha s+ya bi mo k+sha ma no n+d+ha k+aa ra
NK125(co)003:3: pa na ya n+aa ma bi ha ra ti sma
NK125(co)003:4: //// slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma 'byung gnas
NK125(co)003:5: kyi rnam par thar pa yid kyi mun sel zhes
NK125(co)003:7: na mo gu ru bud+d+ha bo d+hi sat+wa d+aa ki
NK125(co)003:8: ni sam+b+ha ra b+h+yah phyi ltar rgya gar pan chen
NK125(co)003:9: sprul pa'i sku // nang ltar khyab bdag rgyal ba rdo rje 'chang //
NK125(co)003:10: gsang ba chos sku kun bzang 'od dpag med //
NK125(co)003:11: sangs rgyas kun bdag de la bdag phyag 'tshal //
NK125(co)003:12: don dam shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK125(co)003:13: zag med bde ba chen po'i ngang //
NK125(co)003:14: rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NK125(co)003:15: ye shes mtsho rgyal des bdag skyongs //
NK125(co)003:16: zhes mchod par brjod nas 'dir rang gi 'dod pa brjod pa ni /
NK125(co)003:17: slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa 'di nyid kyi bka' las /
NK125(co)003:18: bdag ni sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas te //
NK125(co)003:19: gang la gang 'dul sku ru snang na yang //
NK125(co)003:20: zhing 'dir bardzusa skyes mon bu a tsa ra //
NK125(co)003:22: lung bstan bka' rgya can las /
NK125(co)003:23: rang byung pad+ma zhes byar grags pa bdag /
NK125(co)003:24: sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas thugs las brdol //
NK125(co)003:25: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang gsung las sprul //
NK125(co)003:26: mkha' 'gro yongs kyi ming po dpa' bo rgyal //
NK125(co)003:27: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las bdag /
NK125(co)003:28: mnyam med kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen po //
NK125(co)003:29: sprul pa'i skur snang thugs rje chen por ldan //
NK125(co)003:30: gang la gang 'dul phrin las rlabs po che //
NK125(co)003:31: sems can kun gyi re 'dod yid bzhin skong //
NK125(co)003:33: ye nas yin pa'i sangs rgyas gcig /
NK125(co)003:34: smon lam dbang gis bod du 'ong //
NK125(co)003:35: zhes sogs gsungs pas de ni /
NK125(co)003:36: sangs rgyas kun bas sngar sangs rgyas //
NK125(co)003:37: zhes pa ltar 'khor 'das thams cad kyi snga rol du /
NK125(co)003:38: slob dpon nyid chos kyi sku kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar sangs rgyas pa yin pas /
NK125(co)003:39: ye nas yin pa'i sangs rgyas gcig /
NK125(co)003:40: zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa yin la /
NK125(co)003:41: chos sku de las ma g.yos bzhin du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhi ba dang /
NK125(co)003:43: zhi drag phyed ma'i tshul can de snyed du skur bzhengs /
NK125(co)003:44: de dag gi zhing khams dang /
NK125(co)003:47: 'dul byed kyi mdzad pa phrin las bsam gyis mi
NK125(co)003:48: khyab cing mtha' yas pa dag gis sa chen po
NK125(co)003:49: la bzhugs pa'i byang sems 'phags pa rnams kyi don
NK125(co)003:50: mdzad / yang ma dag pa byis pa so so skye bo'i snang ngo la /
NK125(co)003:51: bzo dang skye ba byang chub che //
NK125(co)003:52: mya ngan 'das pa rtag ston pa //
NK125(co)003:53: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku 'di ni //
NK125(co)003:54: zhes de lta bu'i sprul sku'i snang tshul bye brag
NK125(co)003:55: brjod kyis mi langs shing bsam gyis mi khyab ste
NK125(co)003:56: / gdul bya so so'i bsam pa mtha' yas par mthun par /
NK125(co)003:57: 'dul byed kyi sprul sku gzugs mtha' yas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:58: sgra skad mtha' yas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:59: mdzad pa dang phrin las thabs tshul mi 'dra ba mtha' yas pa ste /
NK125(co)003:60: mdor na sangs rgyas kyi rnam par sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK125(co)003:61: de bas na 'di nyid kyi rnam par thar pa'i
NK125(co)003:62: tshul yongs su rdzogs par ni dus gsum sangs rgyas
NK125(co)003:63: thams cad kyis ji srid 'khor ba ma stong gi
NK125(co)003:64: bar du gsungs kyang rdzogs mtha' mi mngon pa yin
NK125(co)003:65: no // 'di ltar zung 'jug thob pa rnams dang /
NK125(co)003:66: 'phags pa byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK125(co)003:67: rgya bod kyi grub thob chen po dag gi rnam
NK125(co)003:68: par thar pa yang gdul bya'i snang ngor cha tsam
NK125(co)003:69: las yongs su rdzogs par ni su zhig gis 'chad
NK125(co)003:70: par nus / 'jag ma'i srin bu dag gi mig
NK125(co)003:71: gis ri bo mthong ba ma yin pa dang mtshungs
NK125(co)003:72: par nus / so // de ltar rgya bod gnyis
NK125(co)003:73: su grags par gyur pa'i slob dpon 'di'i rnam par
NK125(co)003:74: thar pa mi 'dra ba stong phrag gcig dang dgu
NK125(co)003:76: de dag kyang dper na nyi ma'i 'od kyis stong khams kun la khyab kyang /
NK125(co)003:77: de dag tu grags pa dag ni skar khung gi nyi zhur tsam mam /
NK125(co)003:78: rgya mtsho las chu thig gcig blangs pa tsam du zad do //
NK125(co)003:79: de bas 'di ltar slob dpon chen po 'di nyid sangs rgyas kho nar blta bar bya yi /
NK125(co)003:80: bod kha cig ltar pan+di ta'am /
NK125(co)003:81: rim skyes kyi grub thob rang rgyud pa zhig tu blta bar mi bya'o //
NK125(co)003:82: sangs rgyas kyi rnam par 'phrul pa gang du yang snang bar de ma go bar /
NK125(co)003:83: slob dpon nyid pad+ma las rdzus te skyes so zhes dang /
NK125(co)003:84: ma yin te mngal las skyes pa'o zhes phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa byis pa'i blo ste /
NK125(co)003:85: gdul bya'i snang ngo la gang yang mi 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK125(co)003:86: de ltar slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar bsam gyis mi
NK125(co)003:87: khyab na khyod 'dir bri ba de yang don med
NK125(co)003:88: do snyam na / ma yin te /
NK125(co)003:90: rgyal ba'i yon tan mtha' mi 'tshal bas gal te gsang sngags mi brjod na //
NK125(co)003:91: 'ga' yang khyod bstod mi bgyid khyod kyi 'byor pa 'gro bas rtogs pa mchis //
NK125(co)003:92: gang slad 'gro 'dis khyod la bstod pa bgyis kyang nongs pa ma mchis pas //
NK125(co)003:93: de slad don 'dir bdag ni blo gros rab tu chung yang brtson pa lags //
NK125(co)003:94: zhes slob dpon rta dbyangs kyis sangs rgyas la bstod
NK125(co)003:95: pas yon tan mtha' yas pa nyid du gsungs te
NK125(co)003:97: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan mtha' yas pa mi rnyed do //
NK125(co)003:98: zhes btang snyoms su byas nas /
NK125(co)003:99: 'gro ba dag gis sangs rgyas kyi yon tan mi rtogs /
NK125(co)003:100: de ma rtogs pas dad par mi 'gyur /
NK125(co)003:101: ma dad pas bstod cing bkur ba'i gnas su mi 'dzin no //
NK125(co)003:102: gal te sangs rgyas kyi yon tan thos par gyur na /
NK125(co)003:103: 'gro ba so so rang rang gi ji ltar shes
NK125(co)003:104: pa'i sgo nas bstod cing basngagasa pa brjod na phan
NK125(co)003:106: skyon gyi rnam pa gang yang med do zhes dgongs pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:107: phan yon gzhan yang skyes rabs las /
NK125(co)003:108: grags pa'i mtshan mar gyur pa bzang po 'di rnams kyi //
NK125(co)003:109: bde bar gshegs gyur lam rnams gang yin bsten par 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:110: yid la dad pa med pa rnams kyang dad par 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:111: chos dang ldan pa'i gtam gyis rab tu dga' bar 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:112: zhes skyes bu chen po'i mdzad pa 'jig rten du grags pa dag brjod pa la bsten nas /
NK125(co)003:113: rigs can gsum gyi gdul bya lam du zhugs pa
NK125(co)003:114: rnams kyis ni gong ma rnams kyi rjes su bsgrub
NK125(co)003:115: pa'i phyir / de dag gi lam gang yin pa
NK125(co)003:116: yang bde blag tu rtogs nas theg pa gsum la
NK125(co)003:117: pa'i phyir / spyod par 'gyur / khyim pa la
NK125(co)003:118: sogs pa lam du ma zhugs pa dag gis thos
NK125(co)003:120: dad pa skyes phyin chad thar pa'i sa bon thebs pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:122: dad pa med pa'i mi rnams la //
NK125(co)003:123: dkar po'i chos rnams mi 'byung ste //
NK125(co)003:124: sa bon me yis tshig pa la //
NK125(co)003:125: myu gu sngon po ji bzhin no //
NK125(co)003:127: lan gcig tsam yang dad pa skyes pa na //
NK125(co)003:128: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
NK125(co)003:130: don chen po dang ldan par 'gyur zhing /
NK125(co)003:131: chos dang ldan pa'i gtam gyis lha dang mir bcas
NK125(co)003:132: pa'i 'gro ba bstan pa la dad pa rnams rab
NK125(co)003:133: tu dga' zhing / de la brten nas dge ba bcu la gzhol bar 'gyur /
NK125(co)003:134: des lha dang mi thams cad gnas skabs dang mthar
NK125(co)003:135: thug gi bde ba thob par 'gyur ba la sogs
NK125(co)003:136: pa'i dgos pa rgya chen yod la /
NK125(co)003:137: khyad par du slob dpon gyi rnam thar thos nas sangs rgyas thob par gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:138: blon po bka' yi thang yig las /
NK125(co)003:139: u rgyan gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas de //
NK125(co)003:140: dus gsum 'jig rten khams 'dir mtshungs pa med //
NK125(co)003:141: rgyal ba'i bka' la rtsod med sprul skur grags //
NK125(co)003:142: 'jig rten khams 'dir mdzad pa ches mang bas //
NK125(co)003:143: de phyir rnam thar yongs rdzogs brjod dka' yang //
NK125(co)003:144: thos pas byang chub rnam thar mdor bsdus na //
NK125(co)003:145: rgyal sras mdzad pa bcu gcig 'di lta ste //
NK125(co)003:146: 'gro 'dul dgongs mdzad pad+ma'i lhums zhugs mdzad //
NK125(co)003:147: rang byung bltams mdzad rgyal sras rol rtsed mdzad //
NK125(co)003:148: rab tu byung mdzad dka' thub sna tshogs mdzad //
NK125(co)003:149: bdud dpung 'joms mdzad sangs rgyas byang chub mdzad //
NK125(co)003:150: chos 'khor bskor mdzad brtul zhugs spyod pa mdzad //
NK125(co)003:151: bstan pa mtha' rgyas mi nub gter sbas mdzad //
NK125(co)003:152: u rgyan rnam thar mdor bsdus mdzad pa ni //
NK125(co)003:153: su yis bris sam mthong thos gzhan la ston //
NK125(co)003:154: de dag bde ba can gyi zhing du skye //
NK125(co)003:155: 'di la dad cing mos pas spyod tshad rnams //
NK125(co)003:156: bla med byang chub sangs rgyas the tshom med //
NK125(co)003:157: de phyir mdzad pa bcu gcig 'dir bkod pas //
NK125(co)003:158: las 'phro can gyi re ba kun bskang 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:161: rnam thar stong phrag gcig dang brgya phrag dgu //
NK125(co)003:162: ma 'ongs dad ldan don du bkod nas sbas //
NK125(co)003:163: 'di thon mi la bsod nams snyan grags 'ong //
NK125(co)003:164: gu ru'i rnam thar rgyas bsdus gang 'thad pa //
NK125(co)003:165: mthong thos mos gus tshad med bya ba gces //
NK125(co)003:166: 'di la dad pas thar pa'i rgyal sa zin //
NK125(co)003:167: bla med byang chub 'tshang rgya the tshom med //
NK125(co)003:169: spyir rgya bod du grags pa'i rnam thar mi 'dra
NK125(co)003:170: ba stong phrag gcig dang dgu brgya mkha' 'gro ma
NK125(co)003:173: dus gsum mkhyen pa slob dpon pad+ma 'byung //
NK125(co)003:174: phyi rgyud dag pas sprul sku'i bstan pa 'dzin //
NK125(co)003:175: nang rgyud dag pas longs sku'i bstan pa 'dzin //
NK125(co)003:176: gsang rgyud dag pas chos sku'i bstan pa 'dzin //
NK125(co)003:177: zhes mkha' 'gro'i gtso mo ye shes mtsho rgyal bzhed pa ltar 'dus /
NK125(co)003:178: de la sprul sku'i bstan pa sde snod gsum /
NK125(co)003:179: longs sku'i bstan pa kri yog gsum /
NK125(co)003:180: chos sku'i bstan pa yo ga gsum /
NK125(co)003:181: de la sprul sku'i bstan pa bzung ba'i slad du /
NK125(co)003:182: bye ba brgyad cur rgyal ba nyid //
NK125(co)003:183: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK125(co)003:184: da dung chog pa'i 'du shes bsal //
NK125(co)003:185: byang chub mchog tu thugs kyang 'jug /
NK125(co)003:186: ces pa la sogs pa'i tshul gyis las dang po
NK125(co)003:187: pa ltar rim skyes pa'i tshul gyis 'gro ba rnams
NK125(co)003:188: byang chub la sbyor ba dang /
NK125(co)003:189: sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i tshul gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa dang /
NK125(co)003:190: de bzhin du nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyis
NK125(co)003:191: 'dul ba dag na nyan rang gi gtso bor sprul
NK125(co)003:193: bstan pa 'di la mtshon na yang /
NK125(co)003:194: rjes 'jug gi gdul bya drangs pa'i slad du /
NK125(co)003:196: thos bsam la sbyangs pa mdzad pa dang /
NK125(co)003:197: mu stegs kyi rtsod pa bzlog pa dang /
NK125(co)003:198: sgrub gnas rnams su bsgrub pa mdzad pa'i tshul dang /
NK125(co)003:199: bdud dang mu stegs btul ba dang /
NK125(co)003:200: mi ma yin dam 'og tu btags pa dang /
NK125(co)003:201: bka' dgongs pa 'grel pa'i bstan bcos /
NK125(co)003:202: 'dul ba la dge tshul gyi mdo dri ba la sogs pa du ma dang /
NK125(co)003:203: mdo sde la spyod phyogs thams cad btus pa'i tshom la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK125(co)003:204: bod du ma 'gyur yang mngon pa'i bstan bcos kyang mang du mdzad par grags /
NK125(co)003:205: gsang sngags la bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i rgyud
NK125(co)003:206: kyi 'grel pa gru rdzing la sogs pa mang po
NK125(co)003:208: sde dgon dang gtsug lag khang mang por tshogs kyi mkhan po mdzad de gzhung lugs mang du bshad /
NK125(co)003:210: rig pa glegs bam las blangs shing //
NK125(co)003:211: bla ma'i ngag la ma bslabs pa //
NK125(co)003:212: ngang pa'i dbus na chu skyar bzhin //
NK125(co)003:213: mang po'i khrod na de mi mdzes //
NK125(co)003:214: zhes klu sgrub kyis gsungs pa bzhin /
NK125(co)003:215: phyis kyi gang zag dge ba'i bshes gnyen la mi brten la rnams dgag pa'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:216: rang nyid gsang sngags kyi bdag po yin kyang rjes
NK125(co)003:217: 'jug sngags la rang gar 'jug pa dag bzlog pa'i
NK125(co)003:218: phyir du / pan grub dang mkha' 'gro ma la
NK125(co)003:219: sogs pa bla ma stong dang dgu brgya bsten tshul
NK125(co)003:220: phyir du / mdzad / bod du dge 'dun gyi sde tshugs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:221: slob dpon gyis lha srin dam la thogs /
NK125(co)003:222: bsam yas kyi gtsug lag khang mgyogs pa las byung ste /
NK125(co)003:223: slob dpon 'di kho na'i bka' drin yin /
NK125(co)003:224: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan dag tu /
NK125(co)003:225: zhing 'di nas shar phyogs su stong spyi phud kyi
NK125(co)003:226: 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag brgyad cu gnyis 'das
NK125(co)003:227: pa na / sangs rgyas kyi zhing dri ma med pa zhes bya ba yod de /
NK125(co)003:228: de na sh+aakya thub pa zhes gsungs pa dri med rnga sgra zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:229: gu ru pad+ma skyes bzang zhes bya ba bzhugs te /
NK125(co)003:230: mdo dang sngags kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ro //
NK125(co)003:231: zhing khams de'i phyogs mtshams brgyad du gu ru mtshan
NK125(co)003:232: brgyad kyis mdo sngags bstan gnyis ya ma zung gis
NK125(co)003:234: steng 'og phyogs bzhi'i 'jig rten drug tu gu ru
NK125(co)003:235: drug gis rigs drug so so'i don rang rang gi
NK125(co)003:236: skal pa dang 'tshams pa nyid du mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:237: de bzhin du zhing khams 'di nas lho dang nub dang byang dang /
NK125(co)003:238: shar lho la sogs pa mtshams bzhi dang /
NK125(co)003:239: gdung ba sel ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams zhes pa na /
NK125(co)003:240: 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed ces bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:241: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:242: gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas zhes bya bas mdo sngags kyi chos ston to //
NK125(co)003:243: de'i phyogs mtshams brgyad du gu ru mtshan brgyad dang /
NK125(co)003:244: 'jig rten drug tu gu ru drug gis rigs drug so so'i don mdzad tshul las /
NK125(co)003:245: re zhig gdul bya rang re rnams kyis thos pa'i tshul mdo tsam smos na /
NK125(co)003:246: slob dpon 'di nyid bde ba can na kha sbyor
NK125(co)003:247: yan lag bdun ldan gyi ngo bo nyid du bzhugs
NK125(co)003:248: pas / sangs rgyas rnams la chos sku dang /
NK125(co)003:249: byang sems rnams la longs spyod rdzogs sku dang /
NK125(co)003:250: nyan thos rnams la sprul sku 'od dpag med du snang ste /
NK125(co)003:251: theg pa rang rang dang mthun pa'i chos ston to //
NK125(co)003:252: der bde ba can na sangs rgyas 'od dpag tu
NK125(co)003:253: med pa'i sprul pa 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po
NK125(co)003:254: bzang po mchog ces bya ba la sras gcig byung
NK125(co)003:255: ba de / de bzhin gshegs pa tshe dpag med ces bya bar sangs rgyas te /
NK125(co)003:256: steng phyogs kyi zhing khams yon tan dpag tu med
NK125(co)003:257: pa zhes bya ba'i ston pa la gshegs te da
NK125(co)003:259: de'i rjes su btsun mo stong yod kyang sras mi mnga'/
NK125(co)003:261: lho nub 'o ma can gyi mtsho la pad+ma'i sdong po chen po zhig skyes te /
NK125(co)003:262: lo gcig tu kha ma bye /
NK125(co)003:263: de nas spre'u'i lo spre'u zla ba'i tshes bcu la kha bye ste /
NK125(co)003:264: dbus dang phyogs bzhi nas khye'u rigs lnga byung /
NK125(co)003:265: der rgyal pos 'od dpag med 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs mtsho 'gram du byon pas /
NK125(co)003:266: de rnams mthong nas ngo mtshar te bstod pa mdzad /
NK125(co)003:267: sangs rgyas kyis gsang sngags bla na med pa'i ston pa thod phreng rigs lnga ru lung bstan te /
NK125(co)003:268: pho brang du spyan drangs nas skal pa can gyi
NK125(co)003:269: 'khor tshogs rnams la gsang sngags zab mo'i chos kyi
NK125(co)003:270: 'khor lo rgyun mi chad par bskor ro //
NK125(co)003:271: de nas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku sa chen po
NK125(co)003:272: la bzhugs pa'i rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK125(co)003:273: kyi don mdzad pa yin la /
NK125(co)003:274: sprul pa'i skus don mdzad pa ni /
NK125(co)003:275: 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di nas stong gsum
NK125(co)003:276: gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag
NK125(co)003:278: sangs rgyas kyi zhing dri ma med pa zhes bya ba yod de /
NK125(co)003:279: de na thub dbang 'chi med rnga sgra zhes bya
NK125(co)003:280: bas phyi sde snod gsum gyi chos ston cing 'gro
NK125(co)003:282: slob dpon pad+ma skyes bzang zhes bya ba bzhugs te
NK125(co)003:283: nang gsang sngags kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te
NK125(co)003:284: sems can gyi don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:285: de'i steng 'og phyogs bzhi'i 'jig rten drug na /
NK125(co)003:286: sangs rgyas de las sprul pa thub pa drug /
NK125(co)003:287: slob dpon de las sprul pa gu ru drug dang /
NK125(co)003:288: phyogs mtshams brgyad du gu ru mtshan brgyad du sprul
NK125(co)003:289: nas mdo sngags chos kyis rigs drug so so'i don
NK125(co)003:290: mdzad do // de bzhin du 'di nas lho phyogs 'jig rten khams stong phrag brgya 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:291: 'jig rten khams yon tan 'byung gnas zhes bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:292: thub dbang dkon mchog sprin zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:293: slob dpon lhun grub 'od skor zhes bya bas mdo sngags kyi chos ston cing /
NK125(co)003:294: 'jig rten drug dang phyogs mtshams brgyad du /
NK125(co)003:297: sprul pa'i mtshan brgyad rnams kyis snga ma ltar 'gro ba'i don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:298: de bzhin du 'di nas nub kyi phyogs su 'jig rten gyi khams khri phrag gcig 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:299: sangs rgyas kyi zhing stong phrag bdun brgya pa bya
NK125(co)003:300: ba mi rnams bardzusa te skye zhing tshe lo brgyad
NK125(co)003:301: khri bzhi stong thub pa zhig yod de /
NK125(co)003:302: de na thub dbang yon tan 'byung gnas bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:303: slob dpon gar gyi dbang phyug bya bas /
NK125(co)003:305: phyogs mtshams brgyad dang bcas pa na thub pa drug /
NK125(co)003:307: mtshan brgyad rnams kyis don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:308: yang 'di nas byang gi phyogs su 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag sum cu 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:309: 'jig rten gyi khams bag tsha ba med pa zhes bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:310: thub dbang seng ge sgra bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:311: slob dpon ye grub mtha' bral bya ba bzhugs te /
NK125(co)003:312: 'jig rten drug tu thub pa drug dang /
NK125(co)003:314: phyogs mtshams brgyad du sprul pa mtshan brgyad kyis bstan pa gnyis la don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:315: 'di nas shar lho mtshams su 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:316: zhing khams rnam par mdzes pa zhes bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:317: thub dbang mdzes pa'i tog ces bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:318: slob dpon 'khrul zhig seng ge zhes bya ba bzhugs te /
NK125(co)003:319: de'i 'jig rten drug dang phyogs mtshams brgyad na /
NK125(co)003:322: mtshan brgyad dang bcas pas mdo sngags ji lta ba bzhin chos ston to //
NK125(co)003:323: 'di nas lho nub kyi phyogs mtshams su 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag bcu 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:324: 'jig rten gyi khams rab tu snang ba zhes bya bar /
NK125(co)003:325: thub dbang mdzes pas brjid pa zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:326: slob dpon 'dzum bzhad rtsal zhes bya ba bzhugs te /
NK125(co)003:327: snga ma bzhin du 'jig rten drug dang /
NK125(co)003:328: phyogs mtshams brgyad du thub pa dang gu ru sprul pa mtshan brgyad dang bcas pas don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:329: 'di nas nub byang gi phyogs mtshams su 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag drug cu 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:330: 'jig rten gyi khams rab tu snang ba zhes bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:331: thub dbang tsan dan dri mchog dpal dang /
NK125(co)003:332: slob dpon thugs rje 'gro 'dul bya bas /
NK125(co)003:333: 'jig rten drug dang phyogs mtshams brgyad du thub pa dang /
NK125(co)003:334: gu ru sprul pa dang bcas pas snga ma ltar don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:335: 'di nas byang shar mtshams su 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi 'das pa na /
NK125(co)003:336: gdung ba sel ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK125(co)003:337: thub dbang snying po'i rgyal po bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:338: slob dpon 'jig rten dbang phyug ces bya bas /
NK125(co)003:339: 'jig rten drug dang phyogs mtshams brgyad du thub pa
NK125(co)003:340: drug dang gu ru sprul pa mtshan brgyad snga ma
NK125(co)003:342: rnam par snang byed ces bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:343: thub dbang myur du 'dzin bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:344: slob dpon 'khor ba dong sprugs bya bas snga ma ltar don mdzad la /
NK125(co)003:345: de bzhin du rin chen bkod pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:346: thub dbang dga' ba'i spyan dang /
NK125(co)003:347: slob dpon rang byung ye shes dang /
NK125(co)003:348: rnam par bkram pa bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:349: thub dbang yongs su bkod pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:350: slob dpon bde ba gtsug phud bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:351: gser 'od dam pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:353: slob dpon chos dbyings dpal bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:354: bee d+aur+ya'i snying po bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:355: thub dbang gser gyi zla ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:356: slob dpon yang snying rang grol zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:357: rnam par zhi ba zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:358: thub dbang zhi ba'i dbang po zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:359: slob dpon zhing skyong chen po zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:360: sprin chen rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:361: thub dbang sprin gyi dpal zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:362: slob dpon gser gyi ri dbang zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:363: yid mngon par dga' ba zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:364: thub dbang yid dbyangs zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:365: slob dpon rgyal ba'i me long zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:366: me tog dpyangs pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:367: thub dbang me long 'od kyi snang ba bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:368: slob dpon mtho ris lhun grub zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:369: 'jig rten gyi khams zla bas brgyan pa bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:370: thub dbang zla ba'i 'od kyi dpal zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:371: slob dpon yid kyi snang ba'i cod pan zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:372: nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis brgyan pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:373: thub dbang nyi ma'i snying po'i dpal zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:374: slob dpon in+d+ra ne'u le'i dbang po zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:375: 'jig rten gyi khams spos kyi dri dang ldan pa na /
NK125(co)003:376: thub dbang spos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:377: slob dpon rnam dag ye shes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:378: 'jig rten gyi khams rnam par spras pa'i rgyan bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:379: thub dbang mngon par spro ba'i rgyal po bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:380: slob dpon phyag mtshan me tog bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:381: 'jig rten gyi khams rnam par spras pa bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:382: thub dbang rin chen rgyal po bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:383: slob dpon kul+la kul li bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:384: 'od zer 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:385: thub dbang 'od kyi bkod pa brgyan pa bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:386: slob dpon rab tu kun tu sbyor zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:387: dag pa kun nas sbyong ba zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:388: thub dbang dka' thub rgyal po bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:389: slob dpon g.yul las rgyal ba bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:390: 'jig rten gyi khams gtsug tor bkod pa bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:391: thub dbang gtsug tor snying po zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:392: slob dpon sa mkhan skyabs zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:393: nges pa can zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:394: thub dbang nges par song ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:395: slob dpon ko sha ni bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:396: 'jig rten khams nges par 'phags pa zhes pa na /
NK125(co)003:397: thub dbang nges par gsungs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:398: slob dpon lam ster bshes gnyen bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:399: bde ba sbyor ba zhes pa'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:400: thub dbang bde ba chen po dang /
NK125(co)003:401: slob dpon 'khor ba'i gcong 'byin bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:402: 'jig rten me tog bkram pa bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:403: thub dbang me tog dbang po'i dbyangs dang /
NK125(co)003:404: slob dpon 'dod dgu rang las 'byung ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:405: 'jig rten gyi khams yongs su grags pa bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:406: thub dbang grags pa'i dpal dang /
NK125(co)003:407: slob dpon 'dren pa'i dpa' bo bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:408: 'jig rten gyi khams rnam par 'phrul pa bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:409: thub dbang sprul pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:410: slob dpon bka' rtags rgyal po bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:411: rnam par dbyangs sa zhes pa'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:412: thub dbang sgra dbyangs mi zad pa dang /
NK125(co)003:413: slob dpon blo sbyangs dam pa bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:414: 'jig rten gyi khams sman gyi rgyan bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:415: thub dbang sman gyi rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:416: slob dpon spyod yul dag pa bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:417: gser 'od snang ba bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:419: slob dpon sna tshogs rin chen bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:420: 'jig rten gyi khams 'od zer bkod pa na /
NK125(co)003:421: thub dbang bkod pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:422: slob dpon rigs ldan bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:423: gser gyi 'byung gnas bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:424: thub dbang gser gyi gzungs zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:425: slob dpon 'byung ba chen po lhun gyis grub pa bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:426: dpal gyi 'byung gnas bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:427: thub dbang dpal gyi rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:428: slob dpon skye shi gnyis spangs bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:429: snang ba dam pa bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:430: thub dbang snang ba brtsegs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:431: slob dpon 'jigs par bde ba 'byin pa bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:432: dga' ba'i mdangs zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:433: thub dbang dga' mchog dpal dang /
NK125(co)003:434: slob dpon spyi chings nam mkha' bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:436: thub dbang gzi brjid dpal dang /
NK125(co)003:437: slob dpon mthu chen yak+sha bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:439: thub dbang dge rtsa dran pa dang /
NK125(co)003:440: slob dpon zla ba'i bu bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:441: yongs su sbyangs pa bya ba'i zhing na /
NK125(co)003:442: thub dbang ngan song sbyong ba dang /
NK125(co)003:443: slob dpon mi nub rgyal mtshan bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:444: tha dad spyod pa bya ba'i 'jig rten na /
NK125(co)003:445: thub dbang 'jig rten kun gyi slob dpon bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:446: slob dpon mi thub rgyal ba bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:447: 'jig rten gyi khams rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i dpung rgyan bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:448: thub dbang rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK125(co)003:449: slob dpon kun tu snang bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:450: me tog mdzes ldan gyi 'jig rten khams na /
NK125(co)003:451: thub dbang yon tan bkod pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:452: slob dpon me tri ko tsa bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:453: 'jig rten gyi khams mdzes par snang ba bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:454: thub dbang thams cad snang ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:455: slob dpon 'khor ba 'dul ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:456: 'jig rten gyi khams tsan dan bkod pa zhes bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:457: sh+aakya thub pa tsan+dana gyi dri zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:458: slob dpon pad+ma rol pa rnam par dag pa zhes bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:459: 'jig rten gyi khams seng ge'i 'byung gnas bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:460: sh+aakya thub pa seng ge 'bum gyi gzugs bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:461: slob dpon pad+ma tha mu ti tha bya bas mdo
NK125(co)003:462: dang sngags ji lta ba nyid du chos ston to
NK125(co)003:463: // da lta 'o skol gyi gnas stong gsum gyi
NK125(co)003:464: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed 'di
NK125(co)003:465: // na / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK125(co)003:466: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis mdo sde dang 'dul ba
NK125(co)003:468: kri ya dang u pa y+aa dang yo ga la sogs pa ji lta bar chos ston la /
NK125(co)003:469: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas bya bas /
NK125(co)003:473: spyi tig dang yang tig la sogs pa ji lta ba bzhin du chos ston /
NK125(co)003:474: phyogs mtshams brgyad du sprul pa mtshan brgyad kyis mdo sngags gnyis ldan du chos ston cing /
NK125(co)003:475: steng 'og phyogs bzhi'i 'jig rten gyi khams drug tu
NK125(co)003:476: gu ru drug gis rigs drug so so'i don mdzad
NK125(co)003:477: par gsungs shing / de ltar zhing khams lnga bcur
NK125(co)003:478: mdo sngags kyi bstan pa lnga bcu sprul pa dang
NK125(co)003:479: bcas pa 'di dag kyang mdo tsam zhig smos pa
NK125(co)003:480: yin gyi yongs su rdzogs pa ni 'chad mi nus
NK125(co)003:481: par gsungs shing / te / thang yig las /
NK125(co)003:482: de nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams dang 'jig rten gyi khams kyang bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK125(co)003:483: 'khor ba'i sems can dang nyon mongs pa yang bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK125(co)003:484: de thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen po sprul pa'i sku yang bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK125(co)003:485: grangs med brjod du med par yang sprul te /
NK125(co)003:487: de dag las sangs rgyas rnams kyis sprul pa'i sku'i bstan pa 'dzin la /
NK125(co)003:488: mtshan brgyad dang gu ru drug ni longs sku gsang
NK125(co)003:489: sngags kyi bstan pa 'dzin pa nyid du rig par
NK125(co)003:490: bya'o // gu ru drug la yang /
NK125(co)003:491: lha yi gu ru srid thub 'dzin las 'phros pa'i sprul sku /
NK125(co)003:498: dri med 'byung rnams kyis theg pa dbu sems kri yog sde drug la sogs pas /
NK125(co)003:499: mchog lha'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi don mdzad la /
NK125(co)003:500: lha phal pa dag la dngos dang brda'i sgo nas brtson 'grus kyi chos ston to //
NK125(co)003:501: 'pho ltung gi sdug bsngal sel ba la sogs pa mdzad pa mtha' yas so //
NK125(co)003:502: de bzhin du lha ma yin gyi gnas su gu ru rnam par rgyal ba /
NK125(co)003:503: de las 'phros pa'i sprul sku karma thod phreng rtsal /
NK125(co)003:504: sam b+ha wa thod phreng rtsal /
NK125(co)003:505: nir ma na thod phreng rtsal /
NK125(co)003:510: karma thod phreng rtsal la sogs pas byams pa dang /
NK125(co)003:512: sbyin sogs phar phyin drug dang /
NK125(co)003:513: nyon mongs pa ye shes su bsgyur ba sngags kyi lam la sogs pa bstan nas /
NK125(co)003:514: lha ma yin rab rnams kyi don dang /
NK125(co)003:515: phal pa dag la 'thab rtsod spangs pa'i chos dngos dang brda'i sgo nas ston pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:516: mi yi gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas las 'phros pa'i sku /
NK125(co)003:517: mtsho skyes rdo rjes dug lnga'i rtsa ba gcod //
NK125(co)003:518: pad+ma rgyal pos legs pa'i yon tan ster //
NK125(co)003:519: pad+ma sam b+has dad ldan byin gyis rlobs //
NK125(co)003:520: rdo rje gro lod gnod sbyin dregs pa 'dul //
NK125(co)003:521: nyi ma 'od zer gsang sngags snying po ston //
NK125(co)003:522: sh+aakya seng ges gdul bya thar lam 'dren //
NK125(co)003:523: seng ge sgra sgrogs phyi rgol mu stegs 'dul //
NK125(co)003:524: blo ldan mchog sred mdo sngags chos char 'bebs //
NK125(co)003:525: sku gcig mtshan brgyad 'gro ba'i gzhi rtsa gcod //
NK125(co)003:526: drang don rgyu 'bras spyod pas mas nas 'dzeg /
NK125(co)003:527: lta ba yas 'bub yin lugs thog tu 'bebs //
NK125(co)003:528: rig pa'i gnad gcun sgom pa sems la shar //
NK125(co)003:529: chos sku rang ngo 'phrod pas de yis ston //
NK125(co)003:530: zhes pa ltar mi rnams kyi don mdzad //
NK125(co)003:531: byol song gi gu ru seng ge rab brtan las 'phros pa'i sprul sku /
NK125(co)003:539: phrin las 'byung gnas la sogs pas rmig zlum /
NK125(co)003:545: shang shang la sogs pa sbrang bu'i rigs dang /
NK125(co)003:546: de ltar dud 'gro'i sde rigs lnga las /
NK125(co)003:547: blun shing rmongs pa zas skom yid la dran pa
NK125(co)003:548: tsam las ma mchis pa dag la bcud len sna
NK125(co)003:549: tshogs pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas don mdzad de
NK125(co)003:550: / mdor na brda'i sgo nas chos ston pa'o //
NK125(co)003:551: yi dwags kyi gu ru rnam par snang byed las 'phros pa'i sprul sku /
NK125(co)003:552: dbang po bde ba 'phags nor bdun la spyod //
NK125(co)003:554: shor ba gzhon nu gdung sems zhi bar mdzad //
NK125(co)003:555: pu ni ri yas 'dod dgu kun la ster //
NK125(co)003:556: pad+ma badz+ra phyi sgrib rnag khrag sel //
NK125(co)003:557: dom b+hi he rus yi dwags nang sgrib 'khru //
NK125(co)003:558: pad+ma dkar pos dkon mchog dkor 'bag sbyongs //
NK125(co)003:559: pad+ma b+hu tis spyi mthun sgrib pa sbyongs //
NK125(co)003:560: zhes sogs kyi sgo nas yi dwags kyi rang lo
NK125(co)003:561: khri dang lnga stong la sogs pa las sgrib ma
NK125(co)003:562: byang gi bar du don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:563: dmyal ba'i gnas su gu ru rnam par gnon de las sprul pa /
NK125(co)003:564: bde mchog dus kyi snying po /
NK125(co)003:571: sa ha ra la sogs pa dag gis /
NK125(co)003:574: nyi tshe ba la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal rgyu dang
NK125(co)003:575: bcas pa sbyongs shing rgyu 'bras ston pa'i chos bstan
NK125(co)003:577: de lta bu'i sprul sku de rnams la che ba'i
NK125(co)003:578: yon tan bzhi bcu mnga' bar lha 'dre bka' thang
NK125(co)003:580: sangs rgyas la che ba'i yon tan mtha' yas pa
NK125(co)003:581: mnga' ba'i rnam grangs ni sus kyang brjod par mi
NK125(co)003:582: nus pas smra ba po rang ngal ba nyid du
NK125(co)003:583: go'o // cha mthun pa'i sprul sku ni /
NK125(co)003:584: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can re re'i drung
NK125(co)003:585: na gang la gang gis 'dul ba de dang de'i
NK125(co)003:586: gzugs su bstan pa mtha' las 'das pa yod cing
NK125(co)003:587: / mchog dman gyi gzugs snang mtha' yas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:588: tshangs pas 'dul ba la tshangs pa'i gzugs dang /
NK125(co)003:589: de bzhin du brgya byin dang /
NK125(co)003:594: gnod sbyin gyi dbang po dang /
NK125(co)003:595: lha ma yin gyi dbang po dang /
NK125(co)003:596: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK125(co)003:607: tshos mkhan ma la sogs pa mtha' dag tu snang nas kyang don mdzad la /
NK125(co)003:612: gcan gzan gyi dbang po la sogs pa g.yo ba'i sems can gyi rigs ji snyed pa dag dang /
NK125(co)003:616: ri bo la sogs pa brtan pa'i gzugs sna tshogs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:617: mdor na sngon gyi smon lam las byung bas na /
NK125(co)003:618: sems can rnams la phan pa'i dngos po srid tshad du snang ba ste /
NK125(co)003:620: mu ge'i bskal pa bar ma'i tshe //
NK125(co)003:621: gang gi zas dang skom du gyur //
NK125(co)003:622: sems can phongs shing dbul ba la //
NK125(co)003:623: bdag ni mi zad gter gyur cig /
NK125(co)003:624: ces gsungs pa ltar 'byung ba yin pas /
NK125(co)003:625: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi rnam par 'phrul pa ni dpags par daka'o //
NK125(co)003:626: gzhan yang hor gyi yig tshang las /
NK125(co)003:627: hor gyi rgyal po la snga ba gnam gyi bu spor ba rta che /
NK125(co)003:628: de nas mi rabs bzhi pa la /
NK125(co)003:629: ji chi mer gan bya ba'i rgyal po byung /
NK125(co)003:630: de mngon par shes pa mnga' bas ma 'ong lung
NK125(co)003:631: bstan pa'i yi ge yang deng sang bar du yod
NK125(co)003:632: / 'di ma shi bar da lta lho nub srin
NK125(co)003:633: po'i kha gnon la yod pas pad+ma 'byung gnas yin
NK125(co)003:634: / zer ro // de bas na slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar dang mdzad pa ni mtha' yas shing /
NK125(co)003:635: yon tan dang phrin las dang gdul bya 'dul tshul ni bsam par mi nus pas /
NK125(co)003:636: 'di dag las kyang ches lhag pa'i ngo mtshar ba'i rnam thar mtha' yas pa zhig yod nges kyang /
NK125(co)003:637: gdul bya rnams kyi skal par ma 'tshams pa zhig gis deng sang mi snang ngo //
NK125(co)003:638: tshul de dag gis ni sprul sku'i bstan pa 'dzin tshul zur tsam smos pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:639: nang rgyud kyi bstan pa ji ltar bzung ba ni /
NK125(co)003:640: longs sku'i bstan pa ji lta ba nyid ni 'og min dang /
NK125(co)003:641: dag pa'i zhing khams lnga la sogs pa la yod la /
NK125(co)003:642: zhing de dag gi ston pa rdo rje 'chang chen po dang /
NK125(co)003:643: rigs lnga dang gangs chen mtsho la sogs pa de
NK125(co)003:644: dag kyang slob dpon nyid las gzhan ma yin pas
NK125(co)003:645: / de la dgongs pa yang yin cing /
NK125(co)003:646: rgyud sde drug gi chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun chad pa med par bskor zhing /
NK125(co)003:647: bstan pa mi nub pas rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor gnas pa nyid do //
NK125(co)003:648: bstan pa 'di la rgya bod gnyis su gsang sngags
NK125(co)003:649: longs sku'i bstan pa ji ltar bzung ba'i tshul ni
NK125(co)003:650: 'og tu 'chad pa las shes par bya'o //
NK125(co)003:651: gsang rgyud dag pa chos sku'i bstan pa ni /
NK125(co)003:652: chos sku'i chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK125(co)003:653: chos sku'i longs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga /
NK125(co)003:654: chos sku'i sprul sku rigs gsum mgon po rnams kyang
NK125(co)003:655: slob dpon kho na'i rnam par rol ba yin la
NK125(co)003:656: / chos sku snang ba mtha' yas /
NK125(co)003:657: longs sku thugs rje chen po /
NK125(co)003:658: sprul sku pad+ma 'byung gnas 'di gsum gnas skabs su
NK125(co)003:659: gdul bya la snang tshul so so ba yin kyang
NK125(co)003:660: / don du ngo bo gcig pa yin mod /
NK125(co)003:661: 'og min chos kyi dbyings dbus mtha' med pa'i zhing khams dang /
NK125(co)003:662: nub phyogs bde ba can la sogs par nyid las
NK125(co)003:663: mi gzhan pa'i 'khor tshogs rigs brgya la sogs par
NK125(co)003:664: rang rang gi ye shes kyi rang gdangs kun tu
NK125(co)003:665: bzang po dang / snang ba mtha' yas la sogs par shar nas /
NK125(co)003:666: chos rdzogs pa chen po klong dgu /
NK125(co)003:667: bam po nyi khri chig stong /
NK125(co)003:668: le'u 'bum phrag lnga la sogs pa'i sgo mtha' yas pa dag dang /
NK125(co)003:669: dgongs 'dus rtsa ba'i rgyud la sogs pa bya rtsol
NK125(co)003:670: las 'das pa'i chos theg pa'i rtse mo'i yang rtse
NK125(co)003:672: ston pas zhal nas ma gsungs par //
NK125(co)003:673: 'khor gyi rtogs dpyod blo la snang //
NK125(co)003:674: zhes gtso 'khor tha dad pa ma yin pa de'i phyir /
NK125(co)003:675: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor chu nang du gsal ba'am /
NK125(co)003:676: me long la gzugs brnyan shar ba lta bu'i dgongs pa la dus 'da' ba nyid do //
NK125(co)003:677: de ltar chos sku'i bstan pa dngos ni de nyid yin la /
NK125(co)003:678: cha mthun pa'i smin grol gyi lam cha lag dang bcas pa ston pa dang /
NK125(co)003:679: sems nyid chos skur ngo sprod pa dang /
NK125(co)003:680: gzhan du ngo sprod nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK125(co)003:681: brda don rtags dang bcas pa ston pa la bya ste /
NK125(co)003:682: de'i tshul rgyas pa ni bdag lta bu'i rigs can
NK125(co)003:683: don la rmongs pa dag gis gtam du bya bar
NK125(co)003:684: dka' bas de tsam gyis mtshon no //
NK125(co)003:685: tshul gzhan yang phar phyin theg pa nas gsungs pa'i
NK125(co)003:686: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zhes grags
NK125(co)003:687: pa de yang ji lta ba bzhin du ston pa'i
NK125(co)003:688: dge ba'i bshes gnyen de dag chos sku'i bstan 'dzin
NK125(co)003:689: nyid du gor ma chag go //
NK125(co)003:690: de yan chad kyi ma bsdus pa dang ma 'dus pa zhig med do //
NK125(co)003:691: 'on kyang sangs rgyas rnams kyi rnam par thar pa'i
NK125(co)003:692: mchog tu gyur pa 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i tshul
NK125(co)003:693: yin la / de la rang gi thos shing go
NK125(co)003:694: ba rnams rags rim sa bon tsam du brjod na
NK125(co)003:695: yin la / / slob dpon 'dis chos sku spros
NK125(co)003:696: pa med pa'i ngang nas rdo rje 'chang du sprul
NK125(co)003:697: yin la / / / bskal pa thog mar mngon
NK125(co)003:698: par dga' ba zhes bya ba la sangs rgyas sum
NK125(co)003:700: de 'og bskal pa rgyan shin tu bkram pa bya ba la sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po byung /
NK125(co)003:701: de'i yon bdag 'khor los sgyur rgyal gyi sras lngar 'khrungs /
NK125(co)003:702: de lnga pos rang rang gi sprul gzhi rdo rje 'chang la dbang zhus /
NK125(co)003:703: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su lung bstan te sangs rgyas so //
NK125(co)003:704: de nas slob dpon rdo rje 'chang des sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po'i bstan zhabs la /
NK125(co)003:705: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na gsang sngags 'byung ba'i rgyu rkyen la dgongs nas /
NK125(co)003:706: dge slob thub dka' gzhon nur skye ba bzung /
NK125(co)003:707: dus der mdo sngags gnyis skyong dgongs nas gsang sngags 'dzin pa'i khyim pa gcig tu'ang sprul /
NK125(co)003:709: de las dan phag lta spyod 'brel bas lag na rdo rjer sangs rgyas /
NK125(co)003:710: dge slong thar pa nag po lta spyod log pas
NK125(co)003:711: ru trar skyes pa yang phyis su thar pa thob
NK125(co)003:712: / kho la brten nas gsang sngags 'byung ba'i rten 'brel 'grigs /
NK125(co)003:713: de nas bskal pa mang po 'das pa'i 'og tu /
NK125(co)003:714: srin yul lang ka pu ri'i rgyud du ru tra byung /
NK125(co)003:716: sngon gyi dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu rdo rje
NK125(co)003:717: sems dpar sangs rgyas pa de nyid bcom ldan 'das
NK125(co)003:719: dan phag lag na rdo rje yang rdo rje phur pa'i skur bzhengs /
NK125(co)003:720: gzhan yang khro bo'i dmag tshogs kyis ru tra btul /
NK125(co)003:721: kho'i las nyon sbyangs te chos skyong mgon po legs
NK125(co)003:722: ldan du dbang bskur nas mthar sangs rgyas su lung
NK125(co)003:723: bstan / ru tra'i lus kyi tshal pa gnas brgyad
NK125(co)003:724: du bor ba las gsang sngags 'byung ba'i gnas brgyad
NK125(co)003:725: bstan / byung / zag pa rgya mtsho la dor
NK125(co)003:726: ba tsan+dana du skyes te bdud rtsi'i rtsa ba brgyad
NK125(co)003:727: bstan / byung / byung / de la sogs pa
NK125(co)003:728: 'di ni gsang sngags 'byung ba'i gzhi yang dag pa
NK125(co)003:730: de'i sngon du thub dka' gzhon nu ni slob dpon nus ldan rdo rjer sprul /
NK125(co)003:731: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po yul 'khor srung ba'i sras stong dang /
NK125(co)003:732: bardzusa skyes gnyis la dbang bskur te /
NK125(co)003:733: bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid kyi sangs rgyas stong dang /
NK125(co)003:734: sems dpa' gnyis su lung bstan to //
NK125(co)003:735: de nas rgyal po spyi bo skyes kyi dus su /
NK125(co)003:736: slob dpon pad+ma'i bla ma bzhi dang /
NK125(co)003:737: drag po'i bla ma gnyis su sku sprul /
NK125(co)003:738: rgyal po dgra 'dul ba'ang gdul byar gyur /
NK125(co)003:739: gsang sngags yo ga gsum gyi sgo nas gdul bya smin grol la bkod /
NK125(co)003:740: sangs rgyas mar me mdzad dang dus mtshungs so //
NK125(co)003:741: de nas bskal pa rdzogs ldan la sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs /
NK125(co)003:742: sum ldan man la sangs rgyas gser thub dang /
NK125(co)003:744: sngar gyi slob dpon gnyis kyis /
NK125(co)003:745: bde skyong rdo rje zag med 'od /
NK125(co)003:747: yon tan 'od ldan gsum du sprul nas gsang sngags
NK125(co)003:748: rgya mtsho lta bus 'gro ba'i don rgya chen po
NK125(co)003:749: mdzad do // de nas sprul pa gsum po bsdus nas go'u ta mar skye ba bzhes /
NK125(co)003:750: g.yo can pad+ma'i rtsa lag gis bzang mo bsad pa'i
NK125(co)003:751: ral gri khrag can mdun du bor ba la rgyal
NK125(co)003:752: pos gsal shing gi rtse la bskyon /
NK125(co)003:753: der mkhan po drang srong mdog nag lhags pa las /
NK125(co)003:754: bden tshig brjod pas mkhan po gser mdog tu bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:755: bar snang gi lhas pad+ma'i rtsa lag bsad /
NK125(co)003:756: der mkhan pos rdzi char phab nas 'dod chags sgom byas pa las /
NK125(co)003:757: khu khrag thig pa de nags su drod gsher gyis smin pa bu ru song ste /
NK125(co)003:758: 'di ni rgyal rabs chad na rgya gar du phan
NK125(co)003:759: bde'i rgyun chad par 'gyur ba las de la dgongs
NK125(co)003:760: pa yin la / go'u ta ma ni sangs rgyas
NK125(co)003:761: ston pa kun tu 'chang du bzhengs te dga' ldan
NK125(co)003:762: du lha rnams la chos bstan nas rdo rje 'chang
NK125(co)003:764: khyad par du dam pa tog dkar po la yongs su 'dzin pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi dbang /
NK125(co)003:765: chos bka' gtad pa po ti glegs bam gyi dbang /
NK125(co)003:768: yongs rdzogs phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dbang /
NK125(co)003:770: phyi yi dbang bcu la sogs pa bskur /
NK125(co)003:771: de nas bdud rtsi thob phyir tshe la dbang ba /
NK125(co)003:772: sems shes pa'i phyir sems la dbang ba /
NK125(co)003:773: rat+na nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyir spyod pa rnyed pa /
NK125(co)003:774: de nas bag chags dang bcas pa'i las kyi lam
NK125(co)003:775: gcod pa la yas dbang 'dzin pa ting nge 'dzin
NK125(co)003:776: gyi dbang bskur / bsam gtan brnyes phyir skye ba'i dbang /
NK125(co)003:777: lhun grub 'jug pa thob phyir rdzu 'phrul gyi dbang /
NK125(co)003:778: zad par skye mched thob phyir mos pa'i dbang /
NK125(co)003:779: bsod nams thob phyir smon lam gyi dbang /
NK125(co)003:780: sgo gsum gyi las thob pa'i phyir ye shes kyi dbang /
NK125(co)003:781: chos dbyings rnam par dag pa'i chos dbang dang bcu bskur /
NK125(co)003:782: khyad par spyi dbang nyi shu rtsa lnga bskur te mi yul du bskul /
NK125(co)003:783: dam pa tog dkar gyis rang gi dbu rgyan byams
NK125(co)003:784: pa la bskon nas lha rnams kyi ston par dbang
NK125(co)003:785: bskur nas / dam pa tog dkar ni lha mo sgyu 'phrul gyi lhums su gshegs so //
NK125(co)003:786: de nas ston pa kun tu 'chang gis mi yul du yo ga gsum gyis 'dul bar gzigs nas /
NK125(co)003:787: o rgyan gyi rgyal po gtsug phud ris bzang gi
NK125(co)003:788: sras su sprul nas rgyal srid ma thob pas thang
NK125(co)003:790: ming sh+aan+ta rak+shi ta ru grags /
NK125(co)003:791: der rgyal srid la gnod pa byas pas dur khrod so sa gling du spyugs /
NK125(co)003:792: der 'od ma'i mda' gzhu bzung nas pho byung tshad bsad cing zos /
NK125(co)003:793: mo byung tshad sbyor nas spyad /
NK125(co)003:794: 'khor du mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs dpag med 'dus te /
NK125(co)003:795: der ting 'dzin bskyang nas lo brgya dang bcu dgu bzhugs so //
NK125(co)003:796: 'di ni phur pa pa dag slob dpon mngal skyes
NK125(co)003:797: su byed pa'i lo rgyus de yin pa 'dra ste
NK125(co)003:798: / mthun mi mthun cung zad 'dug pas thang yig bzhin bris pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:799: de'i 'og tu gu ru rnam shes rtsad gcod du
NK125(co)003:800: sprul nas sprin ldan gyi rgyal khams bskyed rdzogs gsum
NK125(co)003:801: gyis btul lo // de dang dus mtshungs su sde snod 'dzin pa'i dge slong re dang /
NK125(co)003:802: gsang sngags bstan pa'i sngags pa re ru sprul nas /
NK125(co)003:803: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams gzhan mang po dag tu
NK125(co)003:804: 'gro don mdzad pa yin kyang brjod par ga la
NK125(co)003:805: nus / de nas sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa la
NK125(co)003:806: rigs gsum mgon pos 'dul ba'i zhing khams zhes bya
NK125(co)003:807: nus / ste / rgya dkar po phyag na rdo rje'i 'dul zhing /
NK125(co)003:808: rgya nag po 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi 'dul zhing /
NK125(co)003:809: bod kha ba na spyan ras gzigs kyi 'dul zhing /
NK125(co)003:810: zhing de gsum 'dul ba'i dus mkhyen nas ji ltar 'khrungs ba ni /
NK125(co)003:816: sangs rgyas rnams kyi rnam 'phrul ni gang du yang snang bas so //
NK125(co)003:817: 'dir bardzusa skyes su yongs la grags pa'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:818: gdul bya mi ma yin mngal skyes kyis 'dul dka' bas de'i ched du dang /
NK125(co)003:819: bla med don rdzogs 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK125(co)003:821: lo ni bcu ru gnyis chad na //
NK125(co)003:822: 'jig rten kun las rgyal ba mchog /
NK125(co)003:823: o rgyan yul du nga nyid 'byung //
NK125(co)003:826: gsang sngags ston pa ngas lung bstan //
NK125(co)003:827: zhes pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis bardzusa skyes su smra'o //
NK125(co)003:828: de yang o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi
NK125(co)003:829: bar ma la sras mi mnga' bas longs spyod thams
NK125(co)003:831: rang byung gzi'i mchod rten la mchod pa chen po byas /
NK125(co)003:832: chos kyi sprin zhes bya ba'i mdo yi dam du byas te bton pa na /
NK125(co)003:833: bardzusa skyes khye'u zhig gis sras byed pa'i ltas shar /
NK125(co)003:834: da rung sbyin pa btang ba'i slad du rgya mtsho
NK125(co)003:835: nas nor bu blangs pas de'i mthus rgyal po spyan
NK125(co)003:836: long ba phyed / tshur lam d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho las khye'u rnyed zer /
NK125(co)003:837: yang blon po krish+na 'dzin mngags nas btsal bas d+ha
NK125(co)003:838: na ko sha'i pad sdong las khye'u rnyed kyang zer
NK125(co)003:839: / gang ltar pad sdong las khye'u blangs nas sa la bzhag pa na /
NK125(co)003:841: de nas phab pas yang gdan gyi pad+ma gcig skyes /
NK125(co)003:842: de 'dra ba kho na byung ste /
NK125(co)003:843: de ni bcom ldan 'das lum+bi'i tshal du sku bltams
NK125(co)003:844: pa'itshe phyogs bzhir gom pa bdun bdun bor ba na
NK125(co)003:845: gang du bor ba de dang der pad+ma skyes pa
NK125(co)003:846: ltar / sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku rnams la de
NK125(co)003:847: lta bu'i pad+ma 'byung ba srol yin yang de ltar
NK125(co)003:848: ma go bas blon po na re /
NK125(co)003:849: khye'u 'di ni pad+ma 'byung gnas su 'dug go byas nas pad sdong dang bcas pa khyer te 'ongs /
NK125(co)003:850: phyis mtshan yang pad+ma 'byung gnas su grags /
NK125(co)003:851: rgyal pos dri ba lnga byas te /
NK125(co)003:857: nga yi pha ni rig pa'i ye shes yin /
NK125(co)003:858: ma ni dbyings phyug kun tu bzang mo yin /
NK125(co)003:860: zas su gnyis snang rtog pa za /
NK125(co)003:861: las su nyon mongs 'dul ba yin /
NK125(co)003:862: zer bas rgyal po ngo mtshar skyes te sras su bzung nas rgyal srid gtad /
NK125(co)003:863: rgyal bus dge ba bcu'i khrims bcas /
NK125(co)003:865: de nas rgyal srid spangs nas rab tu byung bar 'dod kyang yab rgyal pos ma gnang bas /
NK125(co)003:866: sngon pho brang na 'byon pa'i lam na pha ma
NK125(co)003:867: gnyis kyi bu gcig yod pa des byis pa zla'o
NK125(co)003:869: pha mas bu de khyim du mi 'jug pa'i brda de dgongs nas /
NK125(co)003:870: pho brang gi yang rtser gar mdzad pas kha t+w+aam
NK125(co)003:871: ka shor ba ltar byas nas sdig blon ka ma
NK125(co)003:872: ta'i bu la phog nas bsad pas /
NK125(co)003:873: rgyal khrims gnyan pas sras dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal du spyugs /
NK125(co)003:874: de'i nub mo lnga ldan yul gyi brag phug bka' skyong du bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:875: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes te sgrub
NK125(co)003:876: pa zhag bdun nas zhi ba'i lha tshogs rnams zhal
NK125(co)003:878: de nas bsil ba'i tshal du brtul zhugs kyi spyod
NK125(co)003:879: pa mdzad pas srin po sh+aan+ta rak+shi ta zhes grags
NK125(co)003:880: / yul mi rnams kyi bsad par byas pas ma zin te /
NK125(co)003:881: bdud shor ba gzhon nur grags /
NK125(co)003:882: de nas sh+aakya srid sgrub las rtsis bslab /
NK125(co)003:883: za hor gyi dur khrod dga' ba'i tshal du mkha' 'gro bdud 'dul mas dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs /
NK125(co)003:884: o rgyan gyi lho phyogs kyi dur khrod so sa
NK125(co)003:885: gling du mkha' 'gro ma zhi ba mtshos byin gyis
NK125(co)003:886: brlabs / 'khrungs yul d+ha na ko shar byon nas
NK125(co)003:887: gsang sngags mkha' 'gro'i brda skad kyis bsgrubs pas rgya
NK125(co)003:888: mtsho gling gi mkha' 'gro ma dbang du 'dus /
NK125(co)003:889: phag mos byin gyis brlabs so //
NK125(co)003:890: de nas rdo rje gdan du sprul pa glang po
NK125(co)003:891: che brgya stong du byas nas rten la mchod pa
NK125(co)003:893: res 'ga' rnal 'byor pa brgya stong du sprul nas spyod pa sna tshogs byas pas /
NK125(co)003:894: mi rnams kyis khyod kyi slob dpon su yin zer /
NK125(co)003:896: nga ni rang byung sangs rgyas yin byas pas /
NK125(co)003:897: slob dpon med pa'i brtul zhugs can bdud ma yin nam zer ba byung /
NK125(co)003:898: de nas 'tsho byed gzhon nu las sman bslab /
NK125(co)003:899: a tsar+y+aa kun gyi bshes gnyen bya ba zhig las rtsis dang yi ge bslab /
NK125(co)003:900: bi shwa karma las bzo bslab /
NK125(co)003:901: phyi nang gi pan+di ta rnams las tshad ma bslab ste rig pa'i gnas lnga sbyong tshul bstan /
NK125(co)003:903: gnas brtan nyi ma gung pa dang lhan cig par
NK125(co)003:904: g+aang+ga'i dbus su 'phags pa kun dga' bo las rab
NK125(co)003:906: rnam thar gzhan du slob dpon pra b+ha hasti las rab tu byung /
NK125(co)003:907: slob dpon de las yo ga'i chos rnams rdzogs par
NK125(co)003:908: zhus nas bsgrub pa byas pas yo ga'i lha tshogs
NK125(co)003:910: 'phags pa kun dga' bo las 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa thams cad rdzogs par gsan /
NK125(co)003:911: de nas b+he ta'i dur khrod sku la rdzogs su lo lnga bcur mkha' 'gro ma la chos gsungs /
NK125(co)003:912: mtshan nyi ma 'od zer du grags /
NK125(co)003:913: sras mo g+ho ma de wi sa nags tshal d+r+wa ba can du phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang bskur /
NK125(co)003:914: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi zhing khams su byon
NK125(co)003:915: nas bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po las rdzogs
NK125(co)003:916: pa chen po'i rgyud ma lus pa thob /
NK125(co)003:917: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi spyan sngar byon nas chos zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:918: ngas khyod 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab /
NK125(co)003:919: dge slong kun dga' mo la dbang nos shig gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:920: mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba ye shes de dge slong
NK125(co)003:921: mar sprul pa der mjal ba na h+aum yig tu
NK125(co)003:922: bsgyur / zhal du mid nas gsang bar phyungs nas dbang gnang /
NK125(co)003:923: snang ba mtha' yas kyi sgo nas phyi tshe'i rig 'dzin /
NK125(co)003:924: spyan ras gzigs kyi sgo nas nang phyag chen gyi rig 'dzin /
NK125(co)003:925: gsang ba rta mgrin gyi sgo nas dregs pa can thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang thob /
NK125(co)003:934: bud+d+ha gup+ta la sogs pa las gsang sngags phyi nang gsan /
NK125(co)003:935: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams slar bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' dngos las gsan te /
NK125(co)003:936: mtshan blo ldan mchog sred du grags /
NK125(co)003:937: de nas bya rgod phung po'i ri la bzhugs te 'byung ba lnga'i bcud len mdzad /
NK125(co)003:938: mtshan pad+ma sam b+ha war grags /
NK125(co)003:939: ma g+ha d+har mu stegs kyi ston pa lnga brgya'i rtsod pa las slob dpon rgyal /
NK125(co)003:940: mu stegs kyi gnas su mthu byas pa la slob
NK125(co)003:941: dpon gyis thog phab pas mu stegs mang po shi
NK125(co)003:942: / lhag ma sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la btsud /
NK125(co)003:943: mtshan seng ge sgra sgrog tu grags /
NK125(co)003:944: de nas slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje las rdzogs pa chen po gsan pa'i tshul mdzad /
NK125(co)003:945: sh+r+ai seng+ha las rdzogs chen sems mchog zhus /
NK125(co)003:946: de nas zhing khams bkod pa lhun grub tu byon
NK125(co)003:947: nas bcom ldan 'das kun tu 'chang chen po las
NK125(co)003:948: spyi tig yo ga'i rgyud sde bye ba phrag bcu
NK125(co)003:949: dang stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gcig zhus /
NK125(co)003:950: de nas rigs ngan pa shan pa'i grong khyer 'dul ba'i dus mkhyen te /
NK125(co)003:951: rigs ngan gyi bu ka ti zhes par sprul nas
NK125(co)003:952: gsod gcod las kyis thams cad mtho ris su drangs
NK125(co)003:953: / dur khrod phung lung nag por byon nas phyi
NK125(co)003:954: nang gsang ba'i lha ma srin sde brgyad thams cad
NK125(co)003:955: dam la btags nas chos skyong du bskos /
NK125(co)003:956: sems can la gnod pa mi byed pa'i dam baca'i bka' la btags /
NK125(co)003:957: slar yang bsil ba tshal du byon nas bdud dang bgegs rigs thams cad btul /
NK125(co)003:958: de nas za hor gyi rgyal khams lha lcam man+d+ha
NK125(co)003:959: ra ba la brten nas btul te chos la bcug
NK125(co)003:960: / man+d+ha ra bas sgrub sde mo byas te m+aa
NK125(co)003:961: ra ti ka'i brag phug tu tshe'i rig 'dzin thob
NK125(co)003:962: / / o rgyan gyi yul 'dul ba'i dus la bab pas der byon /
NK125(co)003:963: bsod snyoms byas pas ngo shes te man+d+ha ra ba dang yab yum gnyis ka mer bsregs pas /
NK125(co)003:964: me nang du pad+ma'i sdong po la yab yum 'khril
NK125(co)003:965: sbyor sems can 'khor ba las sgrol ba mtshon byed
NK125(co)003:967: pad+ma thod phreng rtsal du grags /
NK125(co)003:968: o rgyan gyi rgyal khams thul te rgyal po 'khor 'bangs dang bcas pa 'od lus su yal /
NK125(co)003:969: rgya bal gyi sa mtshams su yang le shod du
NK125(co)003:970: bal mo sh+aakya de bas sgrub sde mo mdzad de
NK125(co)003:971: dpal yang dag gi sgo nas mchog gi dngos grub
NK125(co)003:972: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin bsgrub pas /
NK125(co)003:975: byi thur glog ma sprin gsum gyis bar gcod byas /
NK125(co)003:976: lo gsum char pa ma bab nad dang mu ge btang bas /
NK125(co)003:977: rgya gar du bla ma rnams la bar chad 'dul ba'i chos bardzonga dgos byas pas /
NK125(co)003:978: phur pa bi to ta ma la pusti mi khur gnyis bskur bas bar chad zhi /
NK125(co)003:980: nad dang mu ge rgyun chad /
NK125(co)003:981: yang dag mchog gi dngos grub thob /
NK125(co)003:982: yang dag dngos grub che yang tshong pa dang 'dra bas /
NK125(co)003:983: bar chad mang ba la skyel ma dang 'dra ba'i
NK125(co)003:984: phur pa dgos par gzigs nas yang phur sbrag ma'i
NK125(co)003:985: sgrub skor mdzad / phur srung dang /
NK125(co)003:986: rgya bal gyi lha 'dre dregs pa can thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:987: de nas rgya gar yul du byon nas ti ra hu ti la sogs pa tha ru'i yul dang /
NK125(co)003:988: karma ru la sogs pa rnams su gser 'gyur dang /
NK125(co)003:989: bcud len la sogs pas sems can mang po'i tshe bsring /
NK125(co)003:991: chu med pa rnams la chu gter bton /
NK125(co)003:992: chu ches pa rnams sa 'og tu bcug ste /
NK125(co)003:995: kha s+ya zhes pa'i yul phyogs dag na slob dpon 'dis bton pa'i chu mang du yod la /
NK125(co)003:996: chu sa 'og tu bcug pa yang du ma yod do //
NK125(co)003:997: tsam pa kha zhes bya ba'i yul na b+ha rmo
NK125(co)003:998: zhes pa'i chu chen po gtsang po rgyas pa tsam
NK125(co)003:999: zhig sa'i sbugs su nyin lam tsam zhig bcug pa
NK125(co)003:1000: dang / tsha lam gcig tsam zhig bcug pa gnyis yod /
NK125(co)003:1001: rgya gar lho phyogs tri ling ga dang nye ba
NK125(co)003:1002: na sh+r+ai b+aar+tha na bya bar dbang phyug gi ling
NK125(co)003:1003: ga khru gang pa rang byung du byung ste /
NK125(co)003:1004: nyin re bzhin srog chags brgya stong mang po bsad nas mchod pa byed de /
NK125(co)003:1005: mu stegs pa dag gis der mos pa byas pas
NK125(co)003:1006: nang ba'i sde la nad yams la sogs pa mi
NK125(co)003:1007: rung ba sha stag yong ba yin /
NK125(co)003:1008: yul de bzang bas o tan+ta pu ri'i gtsug lag
NK125(co)003:1009: khang gi mchod pa phal cher ba yang yul de
NK125(co)003:1011: rang byung gi ling ga des gnod pa zhig byung /
NK125(co)003:1012: shar na len+d+ra'i lho nub b+ha ga la bya bar
NK125(co)003:1013: mtsho chung zhig gsar du byung nas mu stegs la
NK125(co)003:1015: mtsho de la mu stegs pas mchod pa byas pas rims nad mang po yong /
NK125(co)003:1016: de la brten nas shar phyogs kyi yul so sor
NK125(co)003:1017: mu stegs kyi sde mang po 'phel te nang pa
NK125(co)003:1019: klu des nang pa la cho 'phrul shin tu che zhing gnod /
NK125(co)003:1020: ma ga d+har shel gyi pha bong zhig la 'byung
NK125(co)003:1021: po mang po gnas pas de bsgrub mi dgos par
NK125(co)003:1022: mig mthong dang mngon shes mang po dngos su ston
NK125(co)003:1024: 'dul ba'i dus mkhyen nas skabs zhig la tri ma
NK125(co)003:1025: la yar byon nas ling ga dang nye ba'i shing
NK125(co)003:1026: sdong la phur pa btab pas nags mes tshig /
NK125(co)003:1027: ling ga phyed thal phung du zhig nas de phyin chad gnod pa ma byung /
NK125(co)003:1028: o tan+ta bu ri'i mchod pa yang lon /
NK125(co)003:1029: dkyil 'khor gyi gzungs ma byas pa'i rnal 'byor ma
NK125(co)003:1030: zhig la phur pa gtad de mtsho de la 'debs
NK125(co)003:1031: su bcug pas klu 'khor bcas shi ste zhag bdun
NK125(co)003:1032: nas mtsho skam / mu stegs kyi sde rnams zhig /
NK125(co)003:1033: phur pa gcig sgrub g.yog la bskur nas ma ga d+ha'i shel gyi pha bong la 'debs su btang /
NK125(co)003:1034: de phye mar song nas nang pa la phan cher byung /
NK125(co)003:1035: kalatsa&a&a&azhesa pa'i yul na nang ba'i chos dar ba la /
NK125(co)003:1036: du ru ka'i rgyal pos dmag drangs byung ste ni
NK125(co)003:1037: la zhes pa'i chu klu la grur zhugs pa dang
NK125(co)003:1038: / slob dpon gyis sdigs mdzub mdzad pas gru lnga
NK125(co)003:1039: brgya lhag tsam chur bying ste du ru ka'i dpa'
NK125(co)003:1040: bo thams cad shi nas dmag bzlog pa sogs kyi
NK125(co)003:1042: mtshon pa tsam las brjod par mi nus so //
NK125(co)003:1043: skabs gzhan yang sangs rgyas mya ngan 'das nas byon
NK125(co)003:1044: pa'i chos rgyal mya ngan med 'dul ba'i dge tshul
NK125(co)003:1045: de dang / dge slong dbang po'i sde yang slob dpon gyi sprul pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:1046: spyod yul rnam par dag pa'i mdo las /
NK125(co)003:1047: nga mya ngan las 'das nas ma skyes dgra'i skal
NK125(co)003:1048: pa'i ring bsrel dang mdo 'di lhan cig tu rgyal
NK125(co)003:1049: po'i khab kyi lho phyogs su ma 'ongs pa na
NK125(co)003:1050: rgyal po mya ngan med ces bya ba 'byung ba
NK125(co)003:1051: de'i don du sbed par 'gyur la /
NK125(co)003:1052: de'i tshe dge slong dbang po'i sde zhes bya ba
NK125(co)003:1053: 'byung ste mdo sde des rgyal po de 'dul zhing
NK125(co)003:1054: / rgyal po des ring bsrel can gyi mchod rten brgyad khri bzhi stong byed par 'gyur zhing /
NK125(co)003:1055: dge slong des mdo sde 'di byang phyogs su 'jog
NK125(co)003:1056: par 'gyur mod kyi sus kyang shes par mi 'gyur
NK125(co)003:1058: mdo sde de dge slong des bod yul du gter sbas par yang lung bstan to //
NK125(co)003:1059: gzhan yang bde mchog dus kyi snying po bya bar
NK125(co)003:1060: sprul nas rdo rje gdan du mu stegs kyi rgyal
NK125(co)003:1062: mu stegs kyi ston pa thams cad mer bsregs te nang pa'i bstan pa la bya ba cher mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1063: mu stegs kyi rgyal po nor bu 'od ldan gnas
NK125(co)003:1064: spar te ro la grong 'jug byas te rgyal po
NK125(co)003:1065: mdzad nas b+ha ga la btul /
NK125(co)003:1066: grub chen dom bi he ru ka yang o rgyan gyi yul 'dul ba'i phyir skur sprul pa yin /
NK125(co)003:1068: gser gling gnyis su mu stegs btul nas de'i blon 'bangs thams cad nang pa la bkod /
NK125(co)003:1069: rgya gar du byon nas sa dang /
NK125(co)003:1082: grub thob la sogs pa snang zhing srid tshad du
NK125(co)003:1083: sprul nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad tshul ni bsam las
NK125(co)003:1084: 'das kyang / thang yig tu mdo tsam smos pa las shes so //
NK125(co)003:1085: de nas rgyal po nyi ma seng ges rdo rje
NK125(co)003:1086: gdan du spyan drangs te thams cad smin grol du
NK125(co)003:1087: bkod do // de ltar lo sum stong drug brgya ru bzhugs nas bstan pa bskyangs so ////
NK125(co)003:1088: de nas bod du spyan ji ltar drangs pa ni /
NK125(co)003:1090: spyan drangs tshul dngos gnyis las /
NK125(co)003:1092: slob dpon chen po 'di bod du zla ba gsum bzhugs zer ba dang /
NK125(co)003:1095: 'ga' zhig las lo drug bzhugs par 'chad de /
NK125(co)003:1096: phal cher sba bzhed kyi rjes su 'brang ba las /
NK125(co)003:1097: rnam thar dang mdzad phreng rgya cher ma mthong bas yun ring thung gi rtog pa zhugs par mngon /
NK125(co)003:1098: 'dir kha cig gtsug lag khang bzhengs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1100: gter sba ba la sogs pa mdzad pa sna tshogs mi tshar ro snyam du mi bsam ste /
NK125(co)003:1101: mtha' yas pa'i rdzu 'phrul mnga' bas so //
NK125(co)003:1103: de ltar na slob dpon la bskal pa skad cig ma dang /
NK125(co)003:1104: skad cig bskal par bsgyur ba'i rdzu 'phrul mnga' ba yin pas /
NK125(co)003:1105: bod yul du skad cig ma gcig gi yun las ma bzhugs zhes zer ram ci /
NK125(co)003:1106: yang sba bzhed kyi yi ge gcig na lo bcu gsum bzhugs pa 'chad de /
NK125(co)003:1107: bsam yas me mo yos la brtsam /
NK125(co)003:1109: rab gnas slob dpon pad+mas mdzad zer /
NK125(co)003:1110: bu ston chos 'byung du yang 'di ltar drangs 'dug /
NK125(co)003:1111: yang kha cig bsam yas su lo brgyad /
NK125(co)003:1112: sgrub gnas rnams su bcu gcig ste /
NK125(co)003:1113: brgya dang bcu gcig ma dag /
NK125(co)003:1114: brgyad dang bcu gcig yin zhes 'chad /
NK125(co)003:1115: de lta bu gong gi 'dod tshul de kun kyang
NK125(co)003:1116: so so rang rang gi snang ngo la 'byung ba
NK125(co)003:1117: yin pas so sor bden cing mi 'gal ba yin
NK125(co)003:1118: mod / 'on kyang snga phyi bar gsum thams cad
NK125(co)003:1119: du 'byung ba'i tshul mthun snang du grub pa zhig
NK125(co)003:1120: brjod dgos pas na 'di ltar yin te /
NK125(co)003:1121: rnying ma ba kha cig sba ye shes dbang po
NK125(co)003:1122: slob dpon la mi dad pas de ltar bris pa
NK125(co)003:1123: yin / sba bzhed ma dag zer ro //
NK125(co)003:1124: sba bzhed ni rgyal blon gyis skrag gis te /
NK125(co)003:1125: gcig rje'i phyag sbal du bzhag /
NK125(co)003:1126: gcig zhang blon rnams la bzhag /
NK125(co)003:1127: gcig mchod gnas dge 'dun rnams la bzhag go zhes 'dug pas /
NK125(co)003:1128: sba ye shes dbang po'i don ni mi snang /
NK125(co)003:1129: 'dir ha shang sun phyungs pa'i lo rgyus de yang 'dug pas /
NK125(co)003:1130: byung ba'i dus de yang b+ho d+hi sa t+wa gshegs nas byung bar mngon /
NK125(co)003:1131: slob dpon bod yul du yun ring bzhugs kyang sba
NK125(co)003:1132: rnams kyi snang ngo la ma bzhugs par mngon pas
NK125(co)003:1133: / ming yang sba bzhed zhes grags pa yin mod /
NK125(co)003:1134: lo rgyus de 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan sdig blon rnams slob dpon gyi mthu stobs la skrag nas /
NK125(co)003:1135: rgyal po la dbang ma byung bar slob dpon 'byon par bcug /
NK125(co)003:1136: lkog tu mchod yon bka' bgros mdzad nas rgyal po ma grong bar du bzhugs par chad /
NK125(co)003:1137: slob dpon la sdig blon gyis mi tshugs mod kyi
NK125(co)003:1138: bod spyi'i bsod nams la ma shong bas sprul pa
NK125(co)003:1139: rang 'dra ba gcig sprul te gung thang la kha
NK125(co)003:1141: sku dngos sgrub gnas rnams su bzhugs pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:1142: 'og tu 'chad pa las shes par 'gyur ro //
NK125(co)003:1143: sba bzhed ma dag pa yang ma yin te /
NK125(co)003:1144: bsam yas kyi lo rgyus sba bzhed las khungs btsun pa med pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1145: slob dpon pad+ma'i chos 'phro lus pa la bi ma
NK125(co)003:1146: las spyan drangs pa'i chos 'khor ji tsam zhig 'dug
NK125(co)003:1147: / sba rnams slob dpon la mi mos pa ni
NK125(co)003:1148: rmongs gtam yin gyi khung thub pa'i lo rgyus med
NK125(co)003:1149: / pas so // de bas na sba bzhed dang /
NK125(co)003:1150: bka' ma'i lo rgyus thang yig rnams gung sgrig shes nas thams cad mthun te /
NK125(co)003:1151: bka' ma'i yig cha khungs ma rnams su bsam yas
NK125(co)003:1152: kyi rab gnas slob dpon pad+mas mdzad par bshad pa
NK125(co)003:1153: kho na yod / yang gsar ma 'ga' zhig sba
NK125(co)003:1154: bzhed kho na'i rjes su 'brang ba ni lo rgyus
NK125(co)003:1155: de'i gras gzhan ma mthong bas bden mod /
NK125(co)003:1156: kha cig slob dpon yun ring ma bzhugs pa'i gtam
NK125(co)003:1157: la brten nas rnying ma chos log tu 'dod pa
NK125(co)003:1158: la / sprul sku gtsug lag phreng bas 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:1159: gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi phyogs la 'gos khug pa
NK125(co)003:1160: lhas btsas la sogs pas mdzad do bar grags pa'i
NK125(co)003:1161: sngags log sun 'byin 'dod pa du mar bka' bstan
NK125(co)003:1162: bcos khungs ma mchis par smra ba po byung ba
NK125(co)003:1163: rnams la ni / bdag gis kyang gzhan du lan btab zin cing /
NK125(co)003:1164: spyir lo chen rin chen bzang po'i sngags log sum 'byin dang /
NK125(co)003:1165: zhi ba 'od kyi 'byams yig la sogs pa ni gsar rnying gang gi'ang rung ste /
NK125(co)003:1166: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa sngags spyod so skyes sgra ji bzhin du spyod pa 'gog pa yin gyi /
NK125(co)003:1167: gsang sngags rnying ma rtsa ba nas 'gog pa ma yin la /
NK125(co)003:1168: jo bo rje la sogs pa rgya gar gyi pan+di
NK125(co)003:1169: ta ji tsam zhig bod du byon pa de dag
NK125(co)003:1170: gis ma bkag pa'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:1171: gal te klu skar rgyal gyi bka' bardzusa ma bstan
NK125(co)003:1172: pa lta bu yin na bstan pa la shin tu
NK125(co)003:1173: sel che bas / lo chen rin bzang gis klu skar rgyal btul ba ltar /
NK125(co)003:1174: rnying ma 'dul byed kyi skyes bu dam pa rdzu
NK125(co)003:1175: 'phrul dang nus pa ldan pa byon nas btul te
NK125(co)003:1176: / phyin chad thams cad kyis yang dag pa ma
NK125(co)003:1177: yin pa shes nas su yang ma 'jug pa zhig
NK125(co)003:1179: de lta bu ma byung ba'i tshul dang /
NK125(co)003:1180: gal te bka' bardzusa ma yin na pan+di ta mkhas
NK125(co)003:1181: pa bod du byon pa rnams kyis mi mkhyen mi
NK125(co)003:1182: gzigs cing / mkhyen na bstan pa'i dbyen de lta
NK125(co)003:1183: bu btang snyoms su 'jog pa ga la srid pa'i
NK125(co)003:1184: gzigs cing / phyir dang / bka' gdams glegs bam tshad mar byed na /
NK125(co)003:1185: de nas jo bo rje nyid sngon slob dpon pad+mas
NK125(co)003:1186: mdzad de bod kyi lha srin btul ba'i chos rnams
NK125(co)003:1187: da lta sngags pa rnams la dar ba 'di yin
NK125(co)003:1188: gsungs pa dang / pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai dang khro
NK125(co)003:1189: phu lo ts+aa ba chen pos gsang snying gi rgya
NK125(co)003:1191: lcam dral bas gsang snying rnam dag tu bsgrub pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1192: rdzogs chen sems klong man ngag gi sde rnams ni
NK125(co)003:1193: rgya gar nyid du yang spyod pa blang dor med
NK125(co)003:1194: par bstan pa'i don ma rtogs na chad lta dang
NK125(co)003:1195: nye bar 'gyur bas shin tu sbas te /
NK125(co)003:1196: sngags la mkhas pa'i pan+di ta rnams dang rgyal pos rgyas btab ste longs spyod du med pas /
NK125(co)003:1197: sh+r+ai seng+ha dang bi ma la mi tras bee ro
NK125(co)003:1198: tsa na dang gtsang legs grub la lkog tu bshad
NK125(co)003:1199: pas / pan+di ta thams cad rmi lam 'khrugs te
NK125(co)003:1200: man ngag gi chos bod du shor bar shes nas
NK125(co)003:1201: pas / / slar dpe rnams rdo rje gdan du
NK125(co)003:1202: sbas nas mi thon par byas pa bee ro'i 'dra
NK125(co)003:1203: 'bag ba slad med rnams su mthong bas /
NK125(co)003:1204: da lta rgya gar na pan+di ta rnams la ma grags pa yin la /
NK125(co)003:1205: jo bo rjes bsam yas su rgya dpe'i dkor mdzod gcig kha phyes nas gzigs pas /
NK125(co)003:1206: sngar gsan rgyus med pa'i rgyud shin tu mang ba gzigs te /
NK125(co)003:1207: ngas 'dzam gling na grags pa'i rgyud yongs su rdzogs
NK125(co)003:1208: pa ma zad mkha' 'gro mas bstan pa kho na
NK125(co)003:1209: yang mtha' yas pa mthong ste /
NK125(co)003:1210: de kun la yang rgyud 'di rnams mi gda'/
NK125(co)003:1211: phal cher slob dpon pad+mas rdzu 'phrul gyis srin po'i yul nas blangs pa yin mchi /
NK125(co)003:1212: theg pa chen po gsang sngags 'di la mtha' mngon rgyu yod yod mi 'dra /
NK125(co)003:1213: zhes sngags la mkhas pa'i thugs rgyal der chags par bshad pas /
NK125(co)003:1214: de kun kyang phal cher rdzogs chen gyi rgyud du gor ma chags la /
NK125(co)003:1215: 'dus pa mdo ni lhas zhus pa'i mado'am /
NK125(co)003:1216: mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal po zhes grags pa /
NK125(co)003:1217: rgyu la mos pa rgyu chos kyis sogs khungs de
NK125(co)003:1218: nyid yin par 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal la sogs
NK125(co)003:1219: 'chad do // spyir sangs rgyas kyi chos bsam gyis
NK125(co)003:1220: mi khyab pa rnams gtso bor lha klu sogs 'gro
NK125(co)003:1221: ba'i gnas gzhan kho nar bzhugs pa las /
NK125(co)003:1222: sher phyin 'bum sogs 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis klu'i yul nas blangs /
NK125(co)003:1223: mdo sde sa bcu pa sogs mang zhig 'phags pa
NK125(co)003:1224: thogs med kyis dga' ldan nas blangs te dar ba
NK125(co)003:1225: na / nyan thos ba kun gyis bskur pa btab pas bkar bsgrub /
NK125(co)003:1226: gsang sngags rnying ma rnams slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje dang /
NK125(co)003:1227: slob dpon chen po pad+ma la sogs pas 'og min dang srin yul sogs nas spyan drangs /
NK125(co)003:1228: dgyes rdor bde mchog 'dus pa la sogs pa 'phags pa klu sgrub /
NK125(co)003:1229: rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi dang /
NK125(co)003:1230: slob dpon la ba pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1231: rta mchog bi na pa la sogs pas spyan drangs te dar ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:1232: mtshan nyid theg pa ba rnams kyis sgro skur btab
NK125(co)003:1233: pa na gsang sngags pas bkar bsgrub dgos pa byung
NK125(co)003:1234: ba yin / dper na bod pa dag rgya dpe yod na yang dag pa yin la /
NK125(co)003:1235: med na yang dag pa ma yin par 'chad pa
NK125(co)003:1236: 'di la yang de tsam gyis snying po ci yod
NK125(co)003:1237: de / rgya dpe rgyangs 'phen gyi gzhung la sogs
NK125(co)003:1238: pa mu stegs kyi chos rnams la yang yod la
NK125(co)003:1239: de / / dga' ldan dang 'og min dang klu
NK125(co)003:1240: la sogs pa'i gnas nas blangs pa'i glegs bam rnams
NK125(co)003:1241: rgya gar gyi ta la'i lo ma kho na la
NK125(co)003:1242: lo pan la grags pa'i yi ge kho na yod
NK125(co)003:1243: de / / pa dka' ste / de rnams kyi
NK125(co)003:1244: bris gzhi sna tshogs gzugs sogs gang du yod shes
NK125(co)003:1245: de / / pa dka' ste / dka' bas /
NK125(co)003:1246: gal te mthong na khyed cag yang dag pa ma
NK125(co)003:1247: yin pa'i blo yang skye srid pas /
NK125(co)003:1248: yang sangs rgyas kyi chos bsam gyis mi khyab kyang
NK125(co)003:1249: yul dus kyi gdul bya'i khams dang dbang por 'tshams
NK125(co)003:1251: tshig tu go bar 'byung ba ltar /
NK125(co)003:1252: zhing gzhan nas sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi glegs bam
NK125(co)003:1253: byung ba na yang yul dus de'i skad dang yi
NK125(co)003:1255: slob dpon pad+ma lta bus bod kyi gdul bya'i don
NK125(co)003:1256: dang 'og min sogs nas glegs bam spyan drangs pa
NK125(co)003:1257: na yang bod kyi skad dang yig gzugs su mi
NK125(co)003:1259: nyan rang dang byang sems kyis kyang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas 'di dag la /
NK125(co)003:1260: bdag cag byis pa rnams kyis tshad 'dzin pa'i ngal bas ci bya ste bag yod par dpyod cig /
NK125(co)003:1261: de don rgyal ba byams pas /
NK125(co)003:1262: sngar lung ma bstan lhan cig byung //
NK125(co)003:1263: spyod yul ma yin grub pa dang //
NK125(co)003:1264: yod pa med dang yod med dang //
NK125(co)003:1265: gnyen po dang ni sgra gzhan phyir //
NK125(co)003:1266: zhes theg chen bkar bsgrub pa'i rig pa 'di kho
NK125(co)003:1267: nas gsang sngags rnying ma yang bkar bsgrub nus te
NK125(co)003:1268: / gal te rnying ma bka' min na ma 'ongs
NK125(co)003:1269: pa na gsang sngags rnying ma'i rdzogs chen bya ba
NK125(co)003:1270: bka' ma yin pa bka' ltar bcos pa 'byung zhes
NK125(co)003:1271: lung ston par rigs pa las /
NK125(co)003:1272: de ltar bstan pa mi snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:1273: de lta bur byung ba mi mkhyen pa yang mi rigs te /
NK125(co)003:1274: sangs rgyas rnams ni mngon sum gyi spyan can yin la /
NK125(co)003:1275: dus la'ang ye shes mi sgrib pa'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:1276: mkhyen kyang ma bstan pa mi rigs te /
NK125(co)003:1277: bstan pa dag kyang bsrung bar mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:1278: bde dgyes la sogs pa'i rgyud rgyas pa 'bum bdun
NK125(co)003:1279: dang 'bum lnga 'bum pa chen po sogs rnams dang
NK125(co)003:1280: / snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sde chen po 'di rnams
NK125(co)003:1281: ni sngon rdzogs ldan la sogs pa'i dus su mtshungs
NK125(co)003:1282: par gsungs pas rgyud sde de dag lhan cig tu
NK125(co)003:1284: de la mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi rgyud bslad med
NK125(co)003:1285: 'di lta bu rtog ge ba la sogs pas brtsam
NK125(co)003:1287: 'di lta bu ni nyan rang gis yang spyod yul
NK125(co)003:1288: ma yin na gzhan gyis lta ci smos pa'i phyir
NK125(co)003:1289: / gal te ston pa las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas
NK125(co)003:1290: zhig gis gsungs so snyam nas de ltar na bka'
NK125(co)003:1292: yang gsar ma'i rgyud sde 'di dag las gzhan zhig yod dam med /
NK125(co)003:1293: med na ni gsang sngags mtha' mi mngon par bshad pa dang 'gal zhing /
NK125(co)003:1294: yod na snga 'gyur 'di dag kyang yang dag pa'i gsang sngags ci'i phyir ma yin /
NK125(co)003:1295: slob dpon pad+ma la chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan
NK125(co)003:1296: gyis btsun mo mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal phul ba
NK125(co)003:1297: bzhes pas / blon po rnams btsun mo yang 'phrog /
NK125(co)003:1298: rgyal srid 'phrog nges zer nas gshegs par gsol ba btab snang bas /
NK125(co)003:1299: rgyal po la ma rgyud kyi gdams pa gnang bar gdon mi za la /
NK125(co)003:1300: dge slong lus la phyag rgya bsten //
NK125(co)003:1301: zhes slob dpon pad+ma dngos rigs kyi lam par yang
NK125(co)003:1302: snang bas de dus bde dgyes sogs ni ma bsgyur
NK125(co)003:1303: / rnying ma bka' brgyad sogs slob dpon pad+mas rgyal po la gsungs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1304: nam mkha'i snying po las rgya las sgrub pa mdzad
NK125(co)003:1305: par gsungs pa'i lam de dag gzhan gang zhig yin
NK125(co)003:1306: te / gsang sngags rnying ma las 'os ci mchis /
NK125(co)003:1307: gal te gsar ma'i rgyud dang mi mtshungs pa du ma yod pas so zhe na /
NK125(co)003:1308: 'o na rgyun mi chad pas rgyud du bshad pa sogs mtshungs pa de bas kyang mang bas /
NK125(co)003:1309: des yang dag tu cis bsgrub mi nus /
NK125(co)003:1310: rdzogs chen du las 'bras med pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1311: 'khor 'das gang yang med pa'i snga rol tu kun
NK125(co)003:1312: tu bzang po sangs rgyas pa sogs bshad pas yang
NK125(co)003:1313: dag pa ma yin snyam na /
NK125(co)003:1314: las 'bras med pa ni las 'bras la rtag tu
NK125(co)003:1315: zhen pa'i gnyen po'i 'dzin pa gzhig pa'i ched de
NK125(co)003:1316: / mdo las kyang mtshon cha thogs pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs bshad pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1317: rgyal la sogs pa chags pa phra //
NK125(co)003:1318: zhes bshad pa ltar yin gyis /
NK125(co)003:1319: gnas skabs gzhan du ma yin la /
NK125(co)003:1320: 'khor 'das gang yang med pa'i sngon ni chos kyi
NK125(co)003:1321: dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid la 'khor 'das gang yang
NK125(co)003:1323: de ngo shes pas kun tu bzang po tshogs ma
NK125(co)003:1324: bsags sgrib pa ma sbyangs par sangs rgyas pa ni
NK125(co)003:1325: / skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK125(co)003:1326: skad cig gcig gis bye brag phyed //
NK125(co)003:1327: ces pa ltar chos dbyings rang ngo shes nas de nyid grol ba dang /
NK125(co)003:1328: de'i 'od lnga ye shes lnga shar ba sogs ni
NK125(co)003:1329: lhan cig skyes kyi sku 'od gsal de nyid longs
NK125(co)003:1330: sprul gyi rnam pa thams cad du 'char zhing /
NK125(co)003:1331: sems nyid dri ma med pa 'di las ci yang
NK125(co)003:1332: snang du rung ba'i don la sogs pa gleng gzhi
NK125(co)003:1333: lta bu'i sgo nas gzhi lam 'bras gsum brjod pas
NK125(co)003:1334: sgra gzhan du bstan par bya ba yin gyi lo
NK125(co)003:1336: 'di ni gsar ma'i rgyud sde la yang /
NK125(co)003:1337: 'di skad bdag thos la sogs yi ge'i don du tshigs 'di skad ston pas gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:1338: sdud pa pos bdag gis dus der 'khor de dag
NK125(co)003:1339: dang lhan cig par dus gcig na zhes lo rgyus
NK125(co)003:1341: sbas don du e yig dmar cha dang wam yig
NK125(co)003:1342: dkar cha dang a yig bar srid gsum tshogs pa
NK125(co)003:1343: / e wam gnyis med las bskyed rim gyi sbyangs gzhi lus grub pa sogs su 'chad cing /
NK125(co)003:1344: mthar thug gi don du e shes rab dang wam
NK125(co)003:1345: yig thabs kyi yi ge gnyis su med pa ste
NK125(co)003:1346: / gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos thams cad thabs shes dbyer med du ston pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:1347: des na gsar rnying brgyud 'dzin pa su yin yang rung ste /
NK125(co)003:1348: rgyud kyi gleng gzhi dang 'khor 'das byung tshul 'di
NK125(co)003:1349: dag sngon byung gi lo rgyus kho nar ni rtogs
NK125(co)003:1351: lo rgyus kyi tshul gyis nyams su blang bya'i chos kyi rnam grangs ston par rig par bya'o //
NK125(co)003:1352: 'o na rdzogs chen las 'khor 'das kyi thog ma'i mtha' bshad do snyam na /
NK125(co)003:1353: nges pa'i don 'di mtshon byed yin gyi /
NK125(co)003:1354: bskal pa chags 'jig bshad pa lta bu zhig ma yin no //
NK125(co)003:1355: nyon mongs pa'i gnyen po yang byed de /
NK125(co)003:1356: bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim chags lam dang grol lam
NK125(co)003:1357: gnyis kyi lam sbyor bar gsar ma'i bla med rnams
NK125(co)003:1358: dang tha mi dad pa'i phyir ro //
NK125(co)003:1359: des na bskyed rdzogs kyis nyon mongs rang rgyud pa
NK125(co)003:1360: 'dul bas rdo rje theg pa'i 'dul ba la snang
NK125(co)003:1361: / dbyings rig gnyis su med pa'i rang gi sems
NK125(co)003:1362: nyid 'od gsal ba la 'jug pas sngags kyi mdo
NK125(co)003:1363: / sde la 'jug / chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK125(co)003:1364: gang du yang ma grub cing cir yang 'char rung
NK125(co)003:1365: ba dang mi 'gal bas mngon pa'i chos nyid dang
NK125(co)003:1366: mi 'gal ba'i phyir bka' yang dag pa ste /
NK125(co)003:1367: ston pa nyid kyis nga mya ngan las 'das nas 'dul ba la snang /
NK125(co)003:1369: chos nyid dang mi 'gal na bka' yin par zung zhig /
NK125(co)003:1370: de las ldog pa ma yin par zung zhig /
NK125(co)003:1373: rang gi 'dul la snang phyir dang //
NK125(co)003:1374: zhes theg chen nyid la sbyar ba yin no //
NK125(co)003:1375: 'di skad bdag gis bstan pa'i dus gcig na //
