NK125(co)003:1377: rdzogs pa'i don du nam yang ma rdzogs so //
NK125(co)003:1378: zhes 'byung ba sogs kyang brtag pa gnyis par /
NK125(co)003:1379: 'chad pa po nga chos kyang nga //
NK125(co)003:1380: rang gi tshogs ldan nyan po nga //
NK125(co)003:1381: 'jig rten ston pa bsgrub bya nga //
NK125(co)003:1382: zhes chos thams cad ston pa nyid du gsungs pa dang khyad med la /
NK125(co)003:1383: rjod byed tshig gi rgyud kyi mtha' rdzogs so sbyar
NK125(co)003:1384: ba ni re zhig glegs bam de rdzogs pa'i don
NK125(co)003:1385: yin gyi / rgyud rdzogs pa'i don min la /
NK125(co)003:1386: brjod bya don gyi rgyud las btsal na nam yang
NK125(co)003:1387: ma rdzogs par rgyun chad med pa zhig la ma
NK125(co)003:1388: bzhag na rgyud du ji ltar 'jog /
NK125(co)003:1389: des na don la rton par bya yis /
NK125(co)003:1390: tshig tsam la rtsod pas ci zhig bya /
NK125(co)003:1391: dus thams cad kyi mchog ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa chos nyid kyi dus yin la /
NK125(co)003:1392: dus gsum ni 'jig rten gyi rnam btags tsam ste /
NK125(co)003:1393: des na dus bzhir bshad pa la 'gal ba ci yod /
NK125(co)003:1394: rdor sems lha gtso bor mi rigs na sam b+hu
NK125(co)003:1395: tar rdor sems gtsor byas pa yang 'dor dgos so
NK125(co)003:1396: // spyir rdor sems kyi mtshan rigs drug pa rdo rje 'chang la 'jug pa'i skabs dang /
NK125(co)003:1397: rigs lnga pa'i mi bskyod pa la 'jug pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1398: gsang sngags kyi byang chub sems dpa' spyi la 'jug pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1399: rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' spyi la 'jug pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1400: rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa'i nang tshan rnal 'byor
NK125(co)003:1401: rgyud kyi shar gyi sems dpa' bzhi'i dang po la
NK125(co)003:1402: 'jug pa sogs mang bas skabs thob ma phye bar
NK125(co)003:1403: ming tsam la rtsod pa ni bod phyi rabs pa
NK125(co)003:1404: rnams kyis mkhas nyams byed par snang mod /
NK125(co)003:1405: dpyod ldan gyi mdun du brin par bya ba ma yin no //
NK125(co)003:1406: btags grol mthong grol myong grol sogs kyang gdul bya
NK125(co)003:1407: de dang der rigs sad pa las 'phro bzhag pa
NK125(co)003:1408: kha cig la ni de dag de ma thag tu
NK125(co)003:1410: spyir phan yon gyi sgo nas dus gzhan la dgongs pa yang yin /
NK125(co)003:1411: gang zag de da lta nyid la gnas 'gyur ba'i rgyur gyur pa'ang yin la /
NK125(co)003:1412: za ma tog gi mdor yi ge drug pa'i phan yon bshad pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1413: so sor 'brang mar gzungs de lus la bcang ba'i
NK125(co)003:1414: phan yon bshad pa la sogs gsar ma'i mdo rgyud
NK125(co)003:1416: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'i mtshan thos pa tsam gyis
NK125(co)003:1417: phyir mi ldog par gsungs pa dang yang mtshungs so
NK125(co)003:1418: // lung rigs kyis grub pa ma zad /
NK125(co)003:1419: dam pa rgya gar gyis rdzogs chen yang dag tu gsungs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1420: dam pa'i pha rgyud bla med yo ga rlung gi
NK125(co)003:1421: rnal 'byor gyi bla ma bcu gcig gi nang nas
NK125(co)003:1422: yo ga la mkhas pa gsum gyi gcig bud+d+ha gu
NK125(co)003:1423: h+ya ste sangs rgyas gsang ba yin la /
NK125(co)003:1424: de'i skabs su rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK125(co)003:1425: ba'i rgyud 'di la rtsa rgyud gsang snying sogs rgyud
NK125(co)003:1426: 'grel gdams pa lag len dang bcas pa dpag med
NK125(co)003:1427: bzhugs kyang nyams len tshigs gsum po 'dis chog ste
NK125(co)003:1428: / dag snang yid la byas pas dngos 'dzin sems
NK125(co)003:1429: kyi spu ris bsub nas snang ba sprul skur 'char
NK125(co)003:1430: ba 'di ni bud+d+ha gu h+ya'i gdams pa yin /
NK125(co)003:1431: zhes sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rnam thar dang bcas te gsungs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1432: pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai'i khyad par gyi gdams pa bzhi'i
NK125(co)003:1433: gcig slob dpon pad+mas rdo rje phur pa'i dbang rgyud
NK125(co)003:1434: man ngag gsan pa la gnas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1435: rje mi la sogs mar ba bka' brgyud kyi grub
NK125(co)003:1436: chen phal cher gyis phyag rdzogs gcig tu sbyor zhing
NK125(co)003:1438: thams cad mkhyen pa rang byung rdo rje sogs kyis
NK125(co)003:1439: rtsa 'khor lnga la sgrub pa bka' brgyad kyi rigs
NK125(co)003:1440: lnga dang / rtsa phran la gzhan gsum bkod pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1441: rje rgod tshangs pas dza lan d+ha rar byon nas
NK125(co)003:1442: dus de skor du rdzogs chen gyi grub thob mang
NK125(co)003:1444: rje yang dgon pa'i thugs dam rdzogs chen las 'khrungs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1445: zhang g.yu brag gis mchim phu rgya ma zhes pa
NK125(co)003:1446: der slob dpon pad+ma bo d+hi sat+wa bi ma la
NK125(co)003:1447: mi tra rnams la dngos su gsan pa'i rdzogs chen
NK125(co)003:1448: gyi dbang gdams ngag yod pa sogs gsar ma nyid
NK125(co)003:1449: kyi skyes chen mtha' dag gis mngon du mdzad cing
NK125(co)003:1450: / grub chen karma pak+shi rdzogs ldan gyi tha ma
NK125(co)003:1451: mang bkur rgyal po'i dus rdo rje 'chang in+d+ra bo
NK125(co)003:1452: d+hi ye shes dri ma med pa'i skur bstan pa'i
NK125(co)003:1453: / tshe / sh+aakya'i rigs mthong na yid 'ong gi
NK125(co)003:1454: mdun kho bo yang rnal 'byor nam mkha' 'od ye
NK125(co)003:1456: rgyal po dza yi khab tu chos kyi char babs pa'i tshe rgyal po badz+ra sh+r+ai ru gyur /
NK125(co)003:1457: lha'i bu kun dga' snying po dga' rab rdo rjer
NK125(co)003:1458: byas te rdzogs pa chen po ston pa'i tshe tog
NK125(co)003:1459: rtse rnal 'byor du gyur nas rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK125(co)003:1460: rgyud 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi rtogs pa nas
NK125(co)003:1461: da lta'i bar gsang sngags gsar rnying thams cad ji
NK125(co)003:1462: lta ba mngon du gyur ces sngon gnas rjes su
NK125(co)003:1463: dran pa gsal bar bstan cing /
NK125(co)003:1464: phyag rdzogs dbyer med pa'i sku bzhi gnad kyi ngo sprod gdams ngag gi snying por mdzad pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1465: rje rang byung bas bi ma la rang gi mdzod
NK125(co)003:1466: spur thim pas snying thig gi don ji lta ba
NK125(co)003:1467: mngon du gyur te yig cha mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1468: rje rol pa'i rdo rje karma sgar du bzhugs dus
NK125(co)003:1469: kun bzang gi dgongs pa mthar thug rdzogs pa chen
NK125(co)003:1470: po thod rgal gyi rtogs pa mngon du gyur nas
NK125(co)003:1471: / rang gsal snying po stong gsal kun tu bzang //
NK125(co)003:1472: gdod nas dag pa rdzogs pa chen po'i dbyings //
NK125(co)003:1473: gzhi nyid gdod nas ma 'gag rang gsal ba //
NK125(co)003:1474: 'od lnga'i gdangs las ma bcos mnyam par bzhag /
NK125(co)003:1475: zhes sogs kyi rdo rje'i mgur mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1476: rgyal ba mi bskyod rdo rjes gu ru mtshan brgyad
NK125(co)003:1477: zhang sku brgyad karma rabs brgyad rang gsal kun tu
NK125(co)003:1478: khyab rnams dbyer med du gzigs nas de'i bla ma
NK125(co)003:1479: sgrub thabs mdzad / skyer sgang pa mnal lam bzung
NK125(co)003:1480: nas slob dpon pad+ma la rta mgrin gyi man ngag
NK125(co)003:1481: sgrub thabs mdzad / zhus tshe / slob dpon nyid rta mgrin du bzhengs nas gnang /
NK125(co)003:1482: rta mgrin sgrub thabs brgya rtsa brgyad kyi nang nas
NK125(co)003:1483: mchog tu gyur pa ngas bod du gter du sbas
NK125(co)003:1484: pa de da lta snye mor sngags pa zhig gis
NK125(co)003:1485: thon nas yod pas de la zhus shig gsungs /
NK125(co)003:1486: phyis slob dpon gyi drung du zhus dag byas pas /
NK125(co)003:1487: da dung 'khor lo ma byin par 'dug pa zhus shig gsungs /
NK125(co)003:1488: slar 'bul ba byas nas zhus pas 'khor lo byin zhes bshad /
NK125(co)003:1489: zhang rin po ches 'phrang po'i brag nas lung bstan
NK125(co)003:1490: gyi shog ser rnyed pa la sogs pa'i yang dag
NK125(co)003:1491: pa'i shes byed grangs las 'das pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:1494: sngags kyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas gshegs khar brag
NK125(co)003:1495: dmar 'om bu'i tshal du btsan po rje 'bangs nyi
NK125(co)003:1496: shu rtsa gcig la man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba
NK125(co)003:1497: bshad nas / rgyal po chen po /
NK125(co)003:1498: nga'i gsang sngags 'di lta ba chos sku dang bstun
NK125(co)003:1499: la spyod pa byang chub kyi phyogs dang bstun cig
NK125(co)003:1500: / spyod pa'i phyogs su lta ba ma shor bar mdzod /
NK125(co)003:1501: de shor na dngos po dang mtshan mas bcing nas grol bar mi 'gyur /
NK125(co)003:1502: lta ba'i phyogs su spyod pa ma shor bar mdzod /
NK125(co)003:1503: de shor na dge med sdig med du song /
NK125(co)003:1504: chad ltar skyes na phyis gsor mi rung /
NK125(co)003:1506: nga'i gsang sngags 'di lta ba shas che ste /
NK125(co)003:1507: ma 'ongs pa na tshig gi lta ba shes /
NK125(co)003:1508: rgyud la khel ba'i lta ba'i gding ni ma rnyed nas /
NK125(co)003:1509: mang po zhig ngan song du 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
NK125(co)003:1510: lta spyod ya bral ba'i 'dra min 'gas sems can mang po'i don byed pa yong ste /
NK125(co)003:1511: gang zag gis bcos pa'i 'dra min mang bas byin rlabs nyams te rtogs pa can nyung /
NK125(co)003:1512: ma bslad pa 'di kun sbas nas nam zhig na
NK125(co)003:1513: las can mang po'i don du 'gyur gsungs nas dpe
NK125(co)003:1514: cha mang po zhig rdza la sbas so //
NK125(co)003:1515: zhes 'byung bas gter gyi khungs 'di las bzang ba ci zhig dgos /
NK125(co)003:1516: slob dpon bod du yun ji tsam bzhugs pa yang
NK125(co)003:1517: lo brgya dang bcu gcig gi phyogs 'di dag la
NK125(co)003:1518: yin te / mnga' bdag myang gi gter kha bde
NK125(co)003:1519: gshegs 'dus pa'i lo rgyus bee ro tsa nas mdzad
NK125(co)003:1520: yin te / pa las / bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK125(co)003:1521: sku mnyam pa nyid du bzhugs pa la yum kun
NK125(co)003:1522: tu bzang mos dbyings rnam dag gi klong nas rdo
NK125(co)003:1523: rje'i dam tshig chen po'i glus bskul nas /
NK125(co)003:1524: longs sku zhi bar bzhengs te zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bstan no //
NK125(co)003:1525: zhi bas mi thul ba rnams la khro bo che mchog tu bzhengs nas khro bo'i dal gsungs so //
NK125(co)003:1526: de yang bde gshegs 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK125(co)003:1527: phyi ma mngon par 'byung ba'i rgyud /
NK125(co)003:1528: phyi ma'i phyi ma sngags kyi rgyud /
NK125(co)003:1529: ma tshang ba kha bskang ba'i rgyud /
NK125(co)003:1530: 'byed par byed pa lde mig gi rgyud /
NK125(co)003:1532: de rnams kyi rtsa rgyud gsang 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa /
NK125(co)003:1533: che mchog 'dus pa sogs brgyad dang /
NK125(co)003:1534: zhi khro lhan cig pa rig 'dzin 'dus pa ste bye brag gi rtsa rgyud bcu /
NK125(co)003:1535: de nas 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed la sogs pa
NK125(co)003:1536: so so'i gtso 'khor sprul te gsungs pa yan lag
NK125(co)003:1537: gi rgyud la / 'jam dpal gsang rgyud /
NK125(co)003:1539: bstod pa glur blangs sogs dang /
NK125(co)003:1542: gshed dmar nag dang bcas te 'jam dpal sku'i rgyud so bzhi /
NK125(co)003:1544: rngog ma le brgan la sogs pad+ma gsung gi rgyud bcu gnyis /
NK125(co)003:1545: he ru ka gal po che chung /
NK125(co)003:1547: mnyam sbyor gsang snying ma bu drug la sogs yang dag thugs kyi rgyud bco brgyad /
NK125(co)003:1549: bam po brgyad pa sogs bdud rtsi yon tan gyi rgyud dgu /
NK125(co)003:1550: phur pa'i rgyud la bi to ta ma la 'bum sde /
NK125(co)003:1551: pha rgyud rnal 'byor dam pa gsang chen /
NK125(co)003:1552: ma rgyud k+ai la ya bcu gnyis /
NK125(co)003:1553: gnyis ka'i rgyud sde phur pa spyi rgyud dang /
NK125(co)003:1554: bye brag tu phur pa pha rgyud la /
NK125(co)003:1555: rdo rje ye shes sangs rgyas rnal 'byor rtse mo ste rtse mo bzhi /
NK125(co)003:1556: de'i yang dag phur zlog bcu gnyis /
NK125(co)003:1558: srung ma bcu gnyis kyi rgyud do //
NK125(co)003:1560: yang snying sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud lnga /
NK125(co)003:1562: yan lag khro bo bcu'i rgyud bcu /
NK125(co)003:1566: kha bskang ba'i rgyud lnga ste /
NK125(co)003:1567: rtsa ba'i rgyud gsum la yan lag gi rgyud mtha'
NK125(co)003:1568: yas pa ni phur pa phrin las kyi rgyud do
NK125(co)003:1570: ma mo gsang ba gtan tshigs kyi rgyud srid pa'i
NK125(co)003:1571: klong chen po 'bum phrag gcig ste rtsa rgyud le'u
NK125(co)003:1572: brgyad / phyi rgyud le'u gcig dang /
NK125(co)003:1573: bye brag shel mtsho dwangs ma la sogs pa dkar mo sku'i rgyud dgu /
NK125(co)003:1574: tsit+ta gdong bzlog sogs smug mo gsung gi rgyud bzhi /
NK125(co)003:1575: smug nag 'khyil ba sogs nag mo thugs kyi rgyud bdun /
NK125(co)003:1576: ser mo yon tan dang ljang mo phrin las kyi rgyud re re /
NK125(co)003:1577: gzhan mkha' 'gro dgongs rgyud mtha' yas pa'o //
NK125(co)003:1579: dregs pa 'dul ba sogs sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud lnga /
NK125(co)003:1580: yan lag gi rgyud sde dpal mgon sum cu'i sgos rgyud sogs dang /
NK125(co)003:1582: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud lnga dang /
NK125(co)003:1583: sde dpon bco brgyad so so'i sgos rgyud sogs mang ba'o //
NK125(co)003:1584: de ltar rgyal ba dgongs brgyud la bka' stsal pa
NK125(co)003:1585: de kun tu bzang po nyid dang tha mi dad
NK125(co)003:1586: pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje chos /
NK125(co)003:1589: rdo rje drag rtsal lam mi'i thod pa can zhes kyang bya ba des /
NK125(co)003:1590: tshom bu dgu'i dal du rang nyid ston pa po dang /
NK125(co)003:1591: rig 'dzin gzhan rnams la 'khor du byas te rang
NK125(co)003:1592: nyid kyis bstan pa la mtshams sbyar nas bsdus te
NK125(co)003:1593: / gser gyi glegs bu la beed+aur+ya'i zhun mas bris nas /
NK125(co)003:1594: kun tu bzang mo'i thugs kyis sprul pa mkha' 'gro
NK125(co)003:1595: ma thams cad kyi gtso mo las kyi dbang mo
NK125(co)003:1597: khyod kyis spyi dang bye brag gi rgyud rnams tha
NK125(co)003:1598: dad du phyes la rin po che'i sgrom so sor
NK125(co)003:1599: zhog la skal ldan rjes su zungs shig par gdams
NK125(co)003:1600: so // mkha' 'gro des spyi rgyud lnga bye brag
NK125(co)003:1601: gi rgyud bcu gnyis rnams rin po che sna tshogs
NK125(co)003:1603: yan lag gi bka' brgyad so so rnams lcags zangs
NK125(co)003:1604: dngul g.yu mchong gzi rnams kyi sgrom bu so sor
NK125(co)003:1606: dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal gyi mchod rten gyi drung
NK125(co)003:1607: du phyi mchod rten la nang gzhal med khang du
NK125(co)003:1608: byas te der bzhugs nas rgyas btab ste mchod do
NK125(co)003:1609: // dur khrod de yang nyin mo thog ser 'beb cing mtshan mo me 'od du 'bar ba /
NK125(co)003:1610: mkha' 'gro dang lha srin gyis mchod pa'i glu dang rol mo rtag tu 'byung ba las /
NK125(co)003:1611: phyis zhig na grub chen brgyad dur khrod brgyad re
NK125(co)003:1612: re na so sor bzhugs pa las thugs kyis gzigs
NK125(co)003:1613: te dus gcig tu mchod rten de'i rtsa bar 'dus
NK125(co)003:1615: zhag bdun nas mkha' 'gro las kyi dbang mo che
NK125(co)003:1616: 'khor dang bcas pa dbang du 'dus te bka' ci
NK125(co)003:1618: khyed rnams kyis mchod pa'i sgrom 'di nged rnams la byin cig gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:1619: mkha' 'gro ma des rgya bkrol nas slob dpon brgyad la sgrom so sor gtad la /
NK125(co)003:1620: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la 'jam dpal sku /
NK125(co)003:1621: n+aa gardzu na la pad+ma gsung /
NK125(co)003:1622: h+aum ka ra la yang dag thugs /
NK125(co)003:1623: bi ma la mi tra la bdud rtsi yon tan /
NK125(co)003:1624: slob dpon pad+ma la phur pa phrin las /
NK125(co)003:1625: d+ha na sam kri ta la ma mo /
NK125(co)003:1626: gu h+ya de wa la mchod bstod /
NK125(co)003:1627: shin+tam gar+b+ha la drag sngags gtad de so sor bka' bab tha dad du byon pa las /
NK125(co)003:1628: slar slob dpon pad+ma byon nas mkha' 'gro dbang du 'dus te /
NK125(co)003:1629: dbus kyi rin po che'i thod pa'i sgrom bu nas
NK125(co)003:1630: rgyud man ngag thams cad phyungs gtad rgya bkrol te
NK125(co)003:1631: skal ldan la ston cig bar rjes su gnang ngo
NK125(co)003:1632: // de nas yang le shod du byon /
NK125(co)003:1633: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub pas rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK125(co)003:1634: lha tshogs thams cad zhal mngon sum du gzigs te
NK125(co)003:1636: de nas khro bo rol pa bsgrub pas bdag nyid
NK125(co)003:1637: dang gnyis su mi phyed par grub ste phyag chen
NK125(co)003:1639: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis bod du spyan
NK125(co)003:1640: drangs nas lha srin btul te bsam yas kyi rab
NK125(co)003:1641: gnas mnga' gsol ba'i bar mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1642: rgyal po dka' ba med par myur du sangs rgyas pa'i gdams pa zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:1643: mchims phu gre gur rje 'bangs brgyad la phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang rdzogs par bskur ba las /
NK125(co)003:1644: gser srang bcu las byas pa'i me tog re re so sor gtor bas /
NK125(co)003:1645: rgyal po nyid dbus che mchog la babs /
NK125(co)003:1646: nam mkha'i snying po badz+ra he ru ka /
NK125(co)003:1647: sangs rgyas ye shes 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed /
NK125(co)003:1648: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs rta mgrin dbang chen la /
NK125(co)003:1649: mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal phur pa /
NK125(co)003:1650: dpal gyi ye shes bla med he ru ka /
NK125(co)003:1651: rlangs dpal gyi seng ge dregs pa kun 'dul /
NK125(co)003:1652: bdag bee ro tsa na stobs ldan nag po'i dal la babs so //
NK125(co)003:1653: de nas khro bo'i lha tshogs bdun brgya nyi shu zhal me long la gzugs brnyan ltar bstan nas /
NK125(co)003:1654: dbang phyi nang gsang gsum lta ba spyi 'byams dang
NK125(co)003:1655: dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs par bskur zhing ngo sprad
NK125(co)003:1656: / sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs su gnas 'gyur zhing smin par mdzad pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:1657: de nas bdag cag rnams la rgyud sde yang so sor bshad de /
NK125(co)003:1658: mkhas pa mi bzhis gdams ngag dbang dang bcas pa
NK125(co)003:1659: ni rgyal po nyid dang gnyags la gnang ba yin
NK125(co)003:1660: no // rgyal po sku tshe de la nyams su ma longs kyang sku tshe phyir bsrings /
NK125(co)003:1661: nam mkha'i snying po nyi zer la zhon /
NK125(co)003:1662: sangs rgyas ye shes nam mkha' la 'phur /
NK125(co)003:1663: ngan lam gyi spyi gtsug tu rta mgos rta skad phyungs /
NK125(co)003:1664: mkhar chen bzas bsad pa gso nus /
NK125(co)003:1665: 'brog mi dpal gyi ye shes kyis ma mo dngos su rbad /
NK125(co)003:1666: rlangs dpal gyi seng ges sde brgyad bran du khol /
NK125(co)003:1667: bdag gis kyang 'jig rten gyi dregs pa dbang du 'dus shing las la 'chol bar nus /
NK125(co)003:1668: gzhan yang drag po mthu yi skor mtha' yas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1671: bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa'i gting phyungs pa
NK125(co)003:1672: rnams kyang rgyal po'i don du zhus shing bdag la
NK125(co)003:1673: gnang / gdams pa 'di rnams gang zag la brgyud
NK125(co)003:1674: cing bka' mang po zhig chos nub pa'i tshe nyams
NK125(co)003:1675: gnang / par 'gyur bas / rgyal po nyid kyi
NK125(co)003:1676: phyir lo brgya dang bcu gcig bod yul du bzhugs
NK125(co)003:1677: gnang / par 'gyur bas / nas / zhabs kyis bcags pa'i gtsug lag khang dang /
NK125(co)003:1678: brag dang sa rdo mtshan ma can rnams la mi brlag pa'i chas kyis bsdom /
NK125(co)003:1679: mi shigs pa'i rgyas thob la brag dmar mgrin bzang la gter du sbos shig /
NK125(co)003:1680: ces gsungs shing brag dmar mgrin bzang la sbas so //
NK125(co)003:1681: ma 'ongs pa na dbon sras kyis chos bsnubs pa'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:1682: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis khyer te mtha' 'dul gyi
NK125(co)003:1683: rnam snang gi sku la gter du sbas shing rgyal
NK125(co)003:1686: chos dbang rin po che'i gter kha las kyang de ltar byung /
NK125(co)003:1687: 'on kyang lo grangs 'di bgrod pa re la lo re ru byas pa 'dra ste /
NK125(co)003:1688: de ltar na lo hril po lnga bcu nga lnga dang zla ba drug yin te /
NK125(co)003:1689: chos rgyal khri srong dgung lo nyer gcig pa la slob dpon bod du phebs /
NK125(co)003:1690: rgyal po drug cu rtsa dgu la gshegs /
NK125(co)003:1691: de nas lo gcig lhag tsam zhig bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:1692: lho nub la theg dus mu khri btsad po byis pa lo bcu gsum lon yang zer /
NK125(co)003:1694: gang ltar sku na gzhon te skyel thung la byon dus /
NK125(co)003:1695: yab gcig rgyal po dgung du gshegs //
NK125(co)003:1696: gu ru o rgyan yul du gshegs //
NK125(co)003:1697: yab rgyal po sku tshe thung lags so //
NK125(co)003:1698: bod 'bangs skyid pa zad lags so //
NK125(co)003:1699: yab dang gu ru bzhugs ring la //
NK125(co)003:1700: mu khri btsan po mi 'gum par //
NK125(co)003:1701: zhes smre sngags ston pa las shugs kyis go'o ////
NK125(co)003:1702: bod du spyan drangs tshul yang /
NK125(co)003:1703: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan rta lo la 'khrungs /
NK125(co)003:1704: dbang thang shing dang sa ru 'dod pa mi mthun kyang /
NK125(co)003:1705: bcu gnyis lo la yab gshegs /
NK125(co)003:1706: bco lnga la rgyal srid bzung nas lo bdun gyi
NK125(co)003:1707: bar la dmag la sogs pas phyi'i so kha bsrung
NK125(co)003:1709: dgung lo bcu bdun pa khyi'i lo la yab myes kyi thang yig gzigs pas /
NK125(co)003:1710: sngon gyi las 'phro sad de chos kyi bsam pa 'khrungs /
NK125(co)003:1711: sdig blon rnams dbang che bas chos kyi bstan pa mi tshugs dgongs nas /
NK125(co)003:1712: 'gos dang mchims la sogs pa bka' bgros te /
NK125(co)003:1713: blon 'bangs bsdus te gtsang po sbubs su 'jug gam /
NK125(co)003:1714: has po ri rtser shel mkhar rgya yul mthong ba brtsig gam /
NK125(co)003:1715: wa lung grog po gser phyes 'gengs sam /
NK125(co)003:1716: lha khang bre gu lta bu gcig brtsegs kyi 'dems kha bzhi btang bar /
NK125(co)003:1717: blon 'bangs kyis gong ma gsum mi 'grub /
NK125(co)003:1718: lha khang bre tsam byed par 'chad /
NK125(co)003:1719: der rgyal pos sbas rgyal gyi blon po dpon g.yog
NK125(co)003:1720: gsum btang nas za hor nas mkhan po bo d+hi
NK125(co)003:1721: sat+wa spyan drangs / pho brang klu tshugs kyi yang
NK125(co)003:1722: thog tu dar dkar gyi gur phub ste bzhugs nas
NK125(co)003:1723: sat+wa spyan drangs / / zla ba bzhir dge ba
NK125(co)003:1724: bcu rten 'brel bcu gnyis khams bco brgyad rnams las
NK125(co)003:1725: brtsams te slob dpon gyis chos bshad /
NK125(co)003:1726: bsam yas kyi rmangs bting bas /
NK125(co)003:1727: bod kyi lha srin kun khros te nyin mo brtsigs pa nub mo bshigs /
NK125(co)003:1728: has po ri la thog brgyab /
NK125(co)003:1730: sad ser dang mi nad phyugs nad byung bas /
NK125(co)003:1731: der bod 'bangs thams cad kyis chos byas pas lan zer /
NK125(co)003:1733: rgyal po dang sba gsal snang sogs chos la dad pa 'gas bgros nas /
NK125(co)003:1734: slob dpon la gser phye bre gang ba re 'bul
NK125(co)003:1735: theng gsum byas pa'i rting ma'i tshe bka' bgros byas
NK125(co)003:1736: te / slob dpon bal por re zhig bskyal /
NK125(co)003:1737: de bar zhang blon 'bangs thams cad la rgyal pos barngana pa byin /
NK125(co)003:1738: thabs brid nas thams cad blo phyogs pa dang slob dpon spyan 'dren par byas pa na /
NK125(co)003:1740: bod kyi lha srin 'dul ba la slob dpon pad+ma
NK125(co)003:1741: 'byung gnas bya ba da lta 'dzam bu'i gling na
NK125(co)003:1742: mthu che ba gcig yod pas de spyan drongs /
NK125(co)003:1743: gser phye 'di nas khyor ba gang bal po'i rgyal po la sbyin dgos gsungs nas bsnams /
NK125(co)003:1744: lhag ma rgyal po la gtad /
NK125(co)003:1745: bskrad pa ltar byas te yar bzhud /
NK125(co)003:1747: gsal snang gnyis kyis bal yul du bskyal /
NK125(co)003:1748: rgya gar du gru gu e bag sha chos dang slob dpon tshol ba la btang /
NK125(co)003:1749: de'i bar du zhang blon thams cad bsdus nas thabs kyis brid de chos byed pa'i chad so grub /
NK125(co)003:1750: de'i sang phod gru gu e bag sha la rgya
NK125(co)003:1751: nag po'i rgyal pos gsung rab po ti mang po
NK125(co)003:1752: dang gos dar yug khri phrag gi skyes bzang po
NK125(co)003:1753: bskur nas rgyal po la phul /
NK125(co)003:1754: sba bzhed las sba gsal snang rgya nag nas 'khor zer to //
NK125(co)003:1755: gsal snang mang yul du so kha bsrung bcug par bshad pas /
NK125(co)003:1756: thang yig las gru gu yin par bshad pa 'di 'thad do ////
NK125(co)003:1757: de nas slob dpon pad+ma spyan 'dren pa la /
NK125(co)003:1764: blon po stag sna gdong gzigs dang bdun btang /
NK125(co)003:1765: de'i tshe slob dpon rgya gar d+ha hu la'i gtsug
NK125(co)003:1766: lag khang du bzhugs pa las mkhyen te bal por
NK125(co)003:1767: byon / bal yul nyi ma khud kyi mtsho 'gram du gdan 'dren pa rnams dang mjal /
NK125(co)003:1768: bod du byon par zhal gyis bzhes /
NK125(co)003:1770: bal yul e yi lha khang /
NK125(co)003:1772: yang le shod la sogs par gter kha brgya rtsa brgyad sbas /
NK125(co)003:1773: shing kun dang ri brag mang po la gter kha stong rtsa sbas /
NK125(co)003:1776: shud bu gsum slar bal yul du slob dpon gdan 'dren pa la btang /
NK125(co)003:1777: sba gsal snang bo d+hi sat+wa spyan 'dren par btang bas /
NK125(co)003:1780: sa brtags pa'i ph+y+wa mkhan dang bcas pa sta gon mdzad 'dug /
NK125(co)003:1781: de ma thag lam du zhugs pas /
NK125(co)003:1782: bal bod kyi lha 'dre kun kha mthun par /
NK125(co)003:1783: a tsar+ya 'di bod du shor na rang cag lha
NK125(co)003:1784: srin gyi bstan pa mi yong bas bar chad bya'o
NK125(co)003:1785: zhes bgros te / shing kun gyi sa bdag sbrul
NK125(co)003:1786: lto nag pos nyi phyed la nam sros su bcug
NK125(co)003:1787: zhes bgros te / pas / slob dpon gyis bsnyen
NK125(co)003:1788: phur 'phangs pas sa phyogs der pha wang bdun dang
NK125(co)003:1789: zhes bgros te / pas / / de'i rtse na'ang
NK125(co)003:1790: gshin rje nag po'i rdo sku gcig yod pa rnams
NK125(co)003:1792: da lta rdo sku de sa la thim pas mos pa byed pa zhig yod /
NK125(co)003:1793: slar yang a su ra'i brag phug tu phur srung bcu gnyis dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1794: yang bod 'dre rnams kyis bal 'dre sbran te kha ba 'phangs thog tshad tsam phab /
NK125(co)003:1795: ri phan tshun gyi bar du slob dpon rnams bcar
NK125(co)003:1796: bar byas pas phyag mtshan rdo rje 'phangs pas ri
NK125(co)003:1797: la bug pa thal byung du byung nas /
NK125(co)003:1798: dpon g.yog rnams de'i nang la byon /
NK125(co)003:1799: ming rdo rje phug lam du grags /
NK125(co)003:1801: de nas rting wi ru phebs pas te'i mtsho bdag mos ser ba phabs pa la /
NK125(co)003:1802: mo gzir bas skrag ste srog snying phul /
NK125(co)003:1803: chos byed kyi grogs byed par khas blangs so //
NK125(co)003:1804: de nas bar ko ru jo mo ngo sprod dwangs ma'i thad du phebs /
NK125(co)003:1805: mos thog ser btang bas thog chu ru bzhus /
NK125(co)003:1807: de nas mo ko'i brag la gnas pa'i dug sbrul
NK125(co)003:1808: chen po zhig gis sems can la gnod pa cher
NK125(co)003:1809: byed pa yod pa de btul /
NK125(co)003:1810: de nas mun la ru mang yul gyi srin mo
NK125(co)003:1811: spun bdun gyi sems can der byung ba thams cad
NK125(co)003:1812: smyor 'jug pa der byon pa dang de dag gis
NK125(co)003:1814: sgrub pa zhag bdun mdzad de btul nas phyin chad
NK125(co)003:1815: gnod pa mi byed pa'i dam bca' mang po mdzad
NK125(co)003:1816: / de nas tshong dus kyi gong gi gnod sbyin mo des mi rnams la yi mug btang nas /
NK125(co)003:1817: sna khrag phru le gsod pas yid mug 'phrang zhes rdo sbrul rgyug pa 'dra ba der byon /
NK125(co)003:1818: dpon g.yog rnams la yi mug btang bas /
NK125(co)003:1819: phur pa btab pas rdo de dum bu gsum du song ba la /
NK125(co)003:1820: mo la cho 'phrul gsum yod pas de'i gnyen po
NK125(co)003:1821: sbrul du sprul nas gnod pa byed pa la rigs
NK125(co)003:1822: gsum mgon po bzhengs te yid bde lha khang du
NK125(co)003:1823: ming btags / rus sbal du sprul nas bros song
NK125(co)003:1824: bas khog pa'i steng du rtsa brgyad mchod rten bzhengs
NK125(co)003:1825: ming btags / / ra ru sprul nas pha bong
NK125(co)003:1826: zhig la thim song ba la seng ldeng gi phur
NK125(co)003:1827: pa btab pas ra skad sla zer te phur pa
NK125(co)003:1828: bton pa'i shul nas khrag thig bu btang ba ltar
NK125(co)003:1829: ming btags / / byung / kha gnon la rdo'i mchod rten chen po gcig mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:1830: srog snying 'phrog nas dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1831: de rnams zhog phyed pa nas tsha gong tshun la rdzu 'phrul gyis mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1832: de nas slob dpon bo d+hi sat+wa bsam yas su sngon la gshegs /
NK125(co)003:1833: sa mkhan dang bal po'i lha bzo ba dang gsum bzhugs nas /
NK125(co)003:1834: mang yul byams sprin la rab gnas mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1835: chos nor gyi gter ka mang du sbas /
NK125(co)003:1836: de nas os spor gyi lung par bsgrub pa mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1837: klu bdud rdo rje spun bdun dang /
NK125(co)003:1838: lha mo rdo rje rab brtan ma dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1839: lha khang gi srung mar bskos so //
NK125(co)003:1840: de nas rag mo'i smyo thang du mong gi gong
NK125(co)003:1841: btsan dang gnod sbyin mo gnyis kyis bar chad byas
NK125(co)003:1842: pas / slob dpon gyis khro bo bcur sprul pas kho rang gnyis smyo ste /
NK125(co)003:1843: kha gnon la smyo thang gshis su rtsa brgyad mchod rten bzhengs so //
NK125(co)003:1844: de nas mtshams kyi thad du phebs /
NK125(co)003:1845: rdo gru bzhi la zhabs rjes bzhag ste /
NK125(co)003:1846: lan gcig dus kyi tha ma la //
NK125(co)003:1847: nga yi khro bo'i lha tshogs 'di //
NK125(co)003:1848: sangs rgyas bstan pa stong dus su //
NK125(co)003:1849: mtshon char bcas nas 'gro gyur cig /
NK125(co)003:1850: ces smon lam btab ste bzhag go //
NK125(co)003:1851: da lta'ang mtshams kyi zhabs rjes grags so //
NK125(co)003:1852: de la mos pa byas na rkyen ngan bar chad glo bur bas mi tshugs pa yin /
NK125(co)003:1853: de nas yar byon nas gung thang rgyun mda' ru /
NK125(co)003:1854: gung thang btsan dang sku lha dpal zung gis rlung dang shwa 'ud btang bas /
NK125(co)003:1855: chos gos kyis bskyil bas sha 'ud yar la ldog /
NK125(co)003:1856: kha gnon du rgyun mda' mchod rten nag po bzhengs /
NK125(co)003:1857: drag las kyis gzir nas dam la btags so //
NK125(co)003:1858: de nas ling pa rong du de'i klu des brag
NK125(co)003:1859: bsnyil ba'i bar du slob dpon bcar bar byas pas
NK125(co)003:1860: / ting nge 'dzin gyi me btang ste kho'i gnas bsregs pas skrag ste srog snying phul /
NK125(co)003:1861: de nas mthong ba dug can gyi chu de mthong ba dang dri tshor ba tsam gyis 'chi bas /
NK125(co)003:1862: de'i steng du sman chu bton nas dug chu sman
NK125(co)003:1863: chur bsgyur te da lta tshe chu phug tu grags
NK125(co)003:1864: so // ling pa'i brag dmar po de de dus mes tshigs pa yin zer /
NK125(co)003:1865: spyir gung thang du zla ba gsum bzhugs nas ri klung kun tu gter mang du sbas /
NK125(co)003:1866: de nas gdan 'dren pa'i mi gsum gyis slebs /
NK125(co)003:1867: lam gyi lha 'dre rnams 'dul zhing byon /
NK125(co)003:1868: zhang zhung dgra bla mun rje bya bas ri gnyis kyi bar du slob dpon bcar ba la /
NK125(co)003:1869: 'khor dang bcas pa bar snang la byon pas mo skyengs te srog snying phul /
NK125(co)003:1870: de nas gnam thang mkhar nag la khar byon pa na gangs dkar mas thog phab /
NK125(co)003:1871: slob dpon gyis phyag mthil du blug ste bzed pas
NK125(co)003:1872: thog ser sgra dang bcas te der song nas sran
NK125(co)003:1874: slar thog mda' bdun du byas nas phyag mdzub la
NK125(co)003:1875: dkris te 'phangs pas mo gnas pa'i gangs la phog
NK125(co)003:1877: der mo skrag ste dpal mtsho'i nang du bros /
NK125(co)003:1878: slob dpon gyis mtsho me dpung du bsgom /
NK125(co)003:1879: mtsho khol te mo sha rus phyes te mtsho'i khar thon pa la /
NK125(co)003:1880: phyag mtshan rdo rje 'phangs pas mig ya gcig bcar /
NK125(co)003:1881: srog 'phrog dam la btags te gangs dkar sha med ma'o //
NK125(co)003:1882: de nas ru lag la sogs par rim gyis lha srin dam la 'dogs shing gtsang gzhung la byon /
NK125(co)003:1883: stag gi thad nas 'o yug la byon /
NK125(co)003:1885: lha 'dre bka' thang las ni byang lam brgyud 'o yug la dmar la phebs zer /
NK125(co)003:1886: gang ltar sprul bsgyur mdzad pas mi 'gal lo //
NK125(co)003:1887: 'o yug bre mo sna ru bstan ma bcu gnyis kyis thog mda' bcu gnyis phab /
NK125(co)003:1888: ri bar du bcar bar byas pa la /
NK125(co)003:1889: sdigs mdzub mdzad pas thog sol dum bcu gnyis su song /
NK125(co)003:1890: skrag nas ri rtse la bros /
NK125(co)003:1891: slob dpon gyis ded pas ri bsnyil nas byung /
NK125(co)003:1892: da lta yang rang thag sna'i rgyab ri bsnyil ba'i rjes yod pa de yin /
NK125(co)003:1893: srin mo chos la gnag pa gcig yod pa de
NK125(co)003:1894: bsgral nas kha gnon gyi mchod rten mdzad pa da
NK125(co)003:1895: lta yang srin mo brag khung bya ba yod /
NK125(co)003:1896: brtan ma'i gnas thams cad me dpung dang thog gis bsdigs pas skrag ste /
NK125(co)003:1900: 'khor dang bcas pas srog snying phul /
NK125(co)003:1904: bod khams skyong bar bka' bsgos /
NK125(co)003:1906: rdo rje legs pa mched 'khor dang bcas pas bsu ba dang bsnyen bkur byas /
NK125(co)003:1907: gos sngon lha khang du rdo rje legs pa'i 'dra 'bag zhig kyang mdzad /
NK125(co)003:1908: yang lha sham pos g.yag dkar po kha rlangs sprin /
NK125(co)003:1912: de nas slob dpon gyis lcags kyus sna nas bzung nas /
NK125(co)003:1913: phyag mtshan gyis btsogs pas khye'u dar dkar gyon pa zhig tu gyur te srog 'phrog dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1914: de nas gya sa'i lam du byon nas gnam du phebs /
NK125(co)003:1915: chu du ba khar 'di na nyi tshe ba'i dmyal ba mang po yod pas snying rje gsungs /
NK125(co)003:1916: chu tshan drag tu khol ba'i nang na srog chags
NK125(co)003:1917: mang po 'dug pa la dgongs pa mdzad pas chu
NK125(co)003:1919: sems can rnams mtho ris su gnas spar /
NK125(co)003:1920: de nas thang lhas sbrul dkar po gru gu'i yul
NK125(co)003:1921: nas khams dbyar mo gong du sleb pa cig sprul
NK125(co)003:1923: slob dpon gyis phyag mkhar btsan gyis blangs nas 'phangs /
NK125(co)003:1925: zangs kyi nang lug thong zhig shi ba'i sha btsos te /
NK125(co)003:1926: gnod sbyin chen po dmar thabs 'tshal lo gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:1927: zangs la rdog pa brgyab nas thab btang /
NK125(co)003:1928: de nas thang lha khros te gangs la thug chom byung /
NK125(co)003:1929: 'brug dang sprin nag thog dang ser ba skye bo phal pas bzod mi nus pa byung /
NK125(co)003:1930: slob dpon sba dkar gyi phyag mkhar og tshugs mdzad
NK125(co)003:1931: de sdang mig gangs la gzigs pas gangs mer te
NK125(co)003:1932: zhu nas gang la zhur dod /
NK125(co)003:1934: thang lha skrag ste bsnyen bkur byas /
NK125(co)003:1936: de'i tshe thog gnas mtsho la lhung bas nya sbal
NK125(co)003:1937: lcong mo la sogs pa'i chu'i srog chags thams cad
NK125(co)003:1938: shi ba la / mtsho 'gram du dkyil 'khor bzhengs
NK125(co)003:1939: nas de dag gi sgribs pa sbyangs te dga' ldan
NK125(co)003:1940: shi ba la / du gnas spar / de nas snying drung du byon /
NK125(co)003:1941: 'dir chos byed du mi ster ba'i klu gdug pa
NK125(co)003:1942: can gcig 'dug gsungs nas 'dul bar dgongs pa la
NK125(co)003:1943: / klu de phyi'i rgya mtsho la bros /
NK125(co)003:1944: sa phyogs de'i phug zhig tu dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas /
NK125(co)003:1945: zhag gsum dgongs pa mdzad pa na klu de khug nas dam la thog /
NK125(co)003:1946: de nas yang thang lhas bsnyen bkur byas te chos skyong bar khas blangs so //
NK125(co)003:1947: de nas byang rgyud kyi lha 'dre mang po zhig dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1948: de nas yang le shod du byon /
NK125(co)003:1951: byang phug bstan ma bcu gnyis la sogs pas rlung
NK125(co)003:1952: thams cad dus gcig la btang bas 'khor thams cad
NK125(co)003:1953: 'khyag ste rengs / slob dpon kyang sku bsil ba tsam byung bas /
NK125(co)003:1954: sdigs mdzub mdzad pa'i rtse mo nas me dpung 'phros te /
NK125(co)003:1955: de rnams gnas pa'i gangs ri g.ya' ri thams cad las me 'bar te srog snying phul lo //
NK125(co)003:1956: gnam gyi shug thang glang phrom du byon /
NK125(co)003:1957: dge bsnyen nyer gcig srod la lhags te srog snying phul /
NK125(co)003:1959: de nas rdzu 'phrul gyis slob dpon gcig pus khams
NK125(co)003:1960: kyi gla ba rkang gcig tu byon nas the'u rang
NK125(co)003:1962: khams kyi wa seng ge brag phug tu ma sangs
NK125(co)003:1963: g.ya' spangs skyes gcig gis rgan mo mgo bo slob
NK125(co)003:1965: rkang pa dbyar mo thang la brkyang /
NK125(co)003:1966: lag pa gangs ti se la 'jug /
NK125(co)003:1967: lha 'dre bye ba stong phrag gcig gis mtshon char 'bebs su byung /
NK125(co)003:1968: slob dpon skad cig la stong khams gang ba'i khro bo'i skur bzhengs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:1969: skrag ste lha 'dre thams cad kyi srog snying phul lo //
NK125(co)003:1971: 'phan yul la rta ro dmar po kha phyes pa
NK125(co)003:1972: 'dra ste yul ngan gsungs nas sku dngos kyis ma
NK125(co)003:1973: byon / lha 'dre thams cad bkug nas dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1974: stod lung gi g.yas rol nas byon /
NK125(co)003:1975: ri nyil ba sdigs mdzub kyis bzlog /
NK125(co)003:1976: btsun mo 'phrang gi brag mu stegs ral can khros
NK125(co)003:1977: pa 'dra bas 'di'i gong ma bcad nas bod mu
NK125(co)003:1981: tshong pa 'ga' 'dug pas de rnams la gro thob gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:1983: gseg shing bye ma la tham tham lan bdun brgyab pa'i chu mig bdun byung /
NK125(co)003:1985: de nas mkhar nag 'dir klu btsan thu ba gcig 'dug pas 'dul byed ci bya gsungs /
NK125(co)003:1986: brag la rdo rje sems dpa'i sku zhig phyag gis
NK125(co)003:1987: 'dam pa la bzo ba ltar mdzad pas da lta
NK125(co)003:1988: 'jil le ba gcig yod pa yang de yin /
NK125(co)003:1989: bal po'i lha bzo bas bod kyi rdo la bzo
NK125(co)003:1990: i rung na zer te ste'usa brag la sha ba
NK125(co)003:1991: gcig brkos pa de cung sgros ga tsang ba da
NK125(co)003:1992: lta yang yod / de nas chu bo ri dang /
NK125(co)003:1994: ma mo dang srin mo thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1995: sil ma la khar sman mo thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1996: de nas dong rong lung du byon /
NK125(co)003:1997: ma yams thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1998: rong gi nags su srin po thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:1999: dbu ru mal gro lung par klu mal gro gzi
NK125(co)003:2000: chen la sogs pa klu thams cad dam la btags
NK125(co)003:2001: / g.yu 'dzin phug tu pho rgyud thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2002: dung tog brag dmar du dri za thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2003: gan pa la'i chu mig tu dge bsnyen thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2004: bye ma rab kha ru lha srin thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2005: gangs ti ser rgyu skar thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2006: glang chen sbas phug tu gter sbas /
NK125(co)003:2007: de nas byang rta rgod gangs su byon nas gza' chen po brgyad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2008: bu le gangs su byon pas der lha 'dre kun 'tshogs te tshogs 'khor zhus te dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2009: de nas gyo bor byon nas ldan ma spun gsum dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2010: de nas pho ma gangs rjes gdan drangs bsnyen bkur byas dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2011: de nas gangs lha bzang bos bsnyen bkur dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2012: de nas la yag gi sku lha mkha' ris spyan drangs dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2013: de nas e dang byar dang gnyal rnams su lha srin thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2014: de nas dwags po'i lha 'dre thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2015: de nas dwags lha sgam po'i rgyab ri rdzong rgyab la byon /
NK125(co)003:2016: rdzong mtsho spun gsum dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2019: nyin lung bya rgod rdzong ri zhes pa'i nang du lha srin thams cad btul ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:2020: srin mo 'jigs pa zhig gis pha wang g.yag che
NK125(co)003:2021: shos tsam zhig gi rbab slob dpon thog tu bsgril
NK125(co)003:2022: bas / slob dpon gyis sdigs mdzub mdzad pas rbad
NK125(co)003:2023: de gyen la log nas nam mkha' la yar ba
NK125(co)003:2025: rbab nag po gru gsum pa da lta yang ri'i
NK125(co)003:2026: rtse'i bar snang la 'dug pa dung mtsho ras pas
NK125(co)003:2027: gzigs zhes rnam thar na snang /
NK125(co)003:2028: de nas mar byon srin mo de gnas pa'i shar ri'i brag phug tu byon pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2030: der dgongs pa gtad pas mo brag ri la 'byar te 'gul ma nus pas /
NK125(co)003:2031: da lta yang bud med kyi gzugs nag po che
NK125(co)003:2032: ba gcig ri'i logs de la 'dug pa dung mtsho
NK125(co)003:2034: der srin mo log ma byung bas /
NK125(co)003:2035: srin mo'i bu ngu ba yin zer /
NK125(co)003:2036: shar ri'i brag phug de na bu chung ngu ba'i skad da lta yang 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2037: de nas nur tsam phyin pa'i sa la ma rmos
NK125(co)003:2038: pa'i lo thog rgya chung nge ba zhig la 'bras
NK125(co)003:2039: bu si le ba 'dug pa la srus yang zos
NK125(co)003:2040: / zhes dung mtsho ras pa'i rnam thar na snang /
NK125(co)003:2041: srin mo btul tshul gyi lo rgyus de tsho'ang dung
NK125(co)003:2042: mtsho ras pa'i gter nas bton pa'i lung byang gi
NK125(co)003:2043: shog dril lnga yod pa las gcig gi nang na
NK125(co)003:2045: de nas rgyal po'i bskyar shog bzhi pa byung ste /
NK125(co)003:2046: stod lung gram bu tshal du yon mchod 'dzom dus btab /
NK125(co)003:2047: kha la brag rir dgun thog gcig bzhugs nas btsan thams cad dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:2048: de nas zur bur byon nas zla ba gcig bzhugs te bdud dang gza' dang dam sri rnams btul /
NK125(co)003:2049: de nas yol ri sgang du bzhugs te /
NK125(co)003:2051: so sha gnyis dam la btags so //
NK125(co)003:2052: de nas lha sa ru phebs /
NK125(co)003:2053: de bsu ba la lha bzang klu dpal la sogs blon po rta pa lnga brgya slebs /
NK125(co)003:2054: rim gyis byon zur mkhar mda' ru bal po'i lha
NK125(co)003:2055: bzo bas mod la tshar bar byin gyis brlabs nas
NK125(co)003:2056: rdo'i mchod rten lnga bzhengs nas gter sbas rab gnas
NK125(co)003:2057: mdzad / thang yig las rgyal pos 'gyod bshags la bzhengs zer ba yod /
NK125(co)003:2058: de nas brag dmar 'om bu tshal du phebs /
NK125(co)003:2059: btsad po dang mjal ba la pho nyas brda sbyar te phyag bzhes zer la /
NK125(co)003:2061: nga'i phyag btsad pos mi thub gsungs nas pha bong zhig la phyag mdzad pas shigs kyis zhig /
NK125(co)003:2062: rgyal po'i na bza' phud pa la phyag mdzad pas thul gyis tshigs /
NK125(co)003:2063: thang yig ltar na de dag gi sngon du nga che nga btsan gyi mgur gsungs zer /
NK125(co)003:2064: rgyal pos slob dpon gyi zhabs la phyag phul lo //
NK125(co)003:2065: de nas brag dmar mgrin bzang rgya nag gi lha
NK125(co)003:2066: khang go'u de shan la dpe blangs pa zhig bzhengs
NK125(co)003:2067: / zhal bsro ma grub pa'i skabs yin pas /
NK125(co)003:2068: slob dpon chen po der gdan phebs par zhus nas phebs /
NK125(co)003:2069: rab gnas mnga' gsol gyi tshe /
NK125(co)003:2070: rgyal blon rnams ni ma byon /
NK125(co)003:2071: snang chen po gzim mal ba kun gyis /
NK125(co)003:2072: slob dpon gyis lha sku chen po thams cad la mi la bya ba bzhin du byas nas /
NK125(co)003:2073: ston mo byas pa'i sar spyan drangs song bas yid ma ches te /
NK125(co)003:2074: nam phyed nas mar me khyer te bltas pas /
NK125(co)003:2075: nang nas 'jim sku gcig kyang med par stong sang nge 'dug pa yid ches /
NK125(co)003:2076: nang par sgor song nas bltas pas /
NK125(co)003:2077: sku gzugs thams cad sngar bzhin 'khod pa la /
NK125(co)003:2078: slob dpon gyis mchod pa mdzad pas lha thams cad bshos gsol zhing gtam mdzad pa dngos su mthong /
NK125(co)003:2079: de'i nyin mo spos dang mar me thams cad rang 'bar /
NK125(co)003:2080: rol mo thams cad rang khrol /
NK125(co)003:2082: 'phan lnga brgya btags pa lnga brgyar 'phel /
NK125(co)003:2083: rgun 'bru snyim pa gang tsam yod pa der 'tshogs
NK125(co)003:2084: pa'i mi rnams ji tsam zos kyang nyung ngu ma
NK125(co)003:2085: song bas thams cad ngo mtshar skyes /
NK125(co)003:2086: de'i nang par gzim mal pa lha lung mtsho bzher legs bya ba de pra rten byas /
NK125(co)003:2087: lha mo 'od zer can ma'i pra phab tu bcug pas /
NK125(co)003:2088: bod kyi lha klu mi srun pa thams cad kyi ming smras /
NK125(co)003:2089: 'phang thang la chu thog 'bebs pa po sham po /
NK125(co)003:2090: dmar po ri la thog 'bebs pa po thang lha yin /
NK125(co)003:2091: mi nad phyugs nad btang ba brtan ma bcu gnyis /
NK125(co)003:2092: sad ser btang ba bod kyi lha gnyan dgu yin /
NK125(co)003:2094: de'i nang par nas bzung cho rigs bzang ba'i byis pa mang po la rgyal chen bzhi'i pra phab /
NK125(co)003:2095: gnod sbyin mo lhas zhal mngon sum du bstan /
NK125(co)003:2096: lha klu gdug pa can rnams kyi ming dang gnas dang spyod tshul smras /
NK125(co)003:2097: der rgyal blon yid ches pa'i phyir du lha 'dre
NK125(co)003:2098: ma rung ba rags rim zhig dngos su mi la
NK125(co)003:2099: phab nas bsdigs shing gzir ba dang /
NK125(co)003:2100: chos bshad nas dam 'og tu bcug /
NK125(co)003:2101: rang rang gi srog sngags cho ga rnams slob dpon la phul /
NK125(co)003:2102: des kyang ma thul ba rnams sbyin bsreg mdzad nas
NK125(co)003:2103: thabs sna tshogs pas btul te de 'dra ba lan
NK125(co)003:2104: gnyis mdzad / bod srin mo gan rkyal 'dra ba
NK125(co)003:2105: la me btsa' dgos pa rnams yab mes srong btsan
NK125(co)003:2107: da 'di rnams bya dgos gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:2108: srin mo'i mgo la de'u nag po dgos /
NK125(co)003:2109: rkang lag bzhi la mchod rten brgya rtsa brgyad dgos gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:2110: slob dpon gyis sprul pa bkyes nas mchod rten dgu bcu rtsa dgu grub /
NK125(co)003:2111: zangs kyi ga'u dgu bcu rtsa dgu ru bram ze
NK125(co)003:2112: skye ba bdun pa'i sha ril blug nas mchod rten
NK125(co)003:2114: zhes khyung drag gi gter rnam du bshad /
NK125(co)003:2115: de nas mal gro mdar byon nas 'khor ba dong sprugs kyi cho ga mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2116: mal gro'i sked par ngan song sbyong ba'i cho ga mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2117: mal gro'i phu ru zhi khro bskang bshags dang bcas pa mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2121: phyis klu yid dam la mi thog pa de mkhyen nas /
NK125(co)003:2122: de'i gnyen por glo bo dge dkar gyi gtsug lag khang bzhengs /
NK125(co)003:2123: bsam yas kyi sbas pa bzhi la gter kha bzhi /
NK125(co)003:2124: 'gram pa bzhi la me btsa' bzhi byas /
NK125(co)003:2125: rus sbal mgo la rta mgrin bzhengs shig gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:2126: has bo ri'i rtser byon nas gzi phor chung ngu zhig tu mtheb kyu gcig chus sbran /
NK125(co)003:2127: byin rlabs mdzad nas lha 'dre yongs la bsngosa /
NK125(co)003:2128: dregs pa zil gnon gyi mgur bzhengs te /
NK125(co)003:2129: khri srong lde'u btsan bsam pa sgrubs //
NK125(co)003:2130: lha khang rtsig cig lha 'dre rnams //
NK125(co)003:2131: gum gum chum chum las la 'dus //
NK125(co)003:2132: ces gsungs pas lha 'dre thams cad kyis de ltar khas blangs /
NK125(co)003:2133: rma chen spom ra las ma 'dod pa la /
NK125(co)003:2134: yang lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas bkug pas drung du lhags te /
NK125(co)003:2135: bdag kyang yal gam che ba gcig lags te /
NK125(co)003:2136: ban chung khyed kyi bka' nan che bas mi 'ong ba'i dbang ma byung nas 'dir mchis pa lags /
NK125(co)003:2137: da ci bgyi'i bka' stsol zer /
NK125(co)003:2139: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'di longs la mnga' bdag gi dgongs pa bsgrub cig /
NK125(co)003:2143: bdag sna gtod che ba gcig lags pas /
NK125(co)003:2145: zan shul la chu blugs pa'i gtor ma 'di mi 'tshal zer ba la /
NK125(co)003:2146: dngul phor gcig tu rin po che brdar nas byin
NK125(co)003:2147: rlabs mdzad nas byin pas kho dga' ste dam 'og
NK125(co)003:2148: tu 'dus so // der slob dpon gyis /
NK125(co)003:2149: slan chad lha chos ci bder mdzod /
NK125(co)003:2150: gtsug lag khang dgongs pa bzhin du brtsig cig /
NK125(co)003:2151: sngar lha klu dam 'og tu lan gnyis btsud lags te /
NK125(co)003:2152: da dung lan gcig bgyi ste 'tshal gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2153: zur phud rkyang bu tshal du phebs /
NK125(co)003:2155: mal gro gzi can na re /
NK125(co)003:2156: sa steng na btsad po khri srong lde'u btsan che /
NK125(co)003:2158: nged cag gnyis grogs po bya /
NK125(co)003:2159: rgyal pos lha khang bzhengs pa la gser phye dre'u khal bcu bzhi phul /
NK125(co)003:2160: gser khung glang po snar len du thong zer ba bzhin byung /
NK125(co)003:2161: dus de rang du gser dre'u khal bcu bzhi byung /
NK125(co)003:2162: dus der rgyal po pe dkar yang btul /
NK125(co)003:2163: de nas yang sham po slar 'dul dgos par dgongs nas /
NK125(co)003:2166: slob dpon gyis ber sna nas rdo rje gdengs pas
NK125(co)003:2167: chu gyen la log nas lha rdzing bam rdzing du
NK125(co)003:2168: 'khyil / der rdo rje 'phangs pas chu khol te sham po'i gangs sum cha tsam zhu /
NK125(co)003:2169: kho gangs rtse la bsdad nas nga la 'di tsam du tho 'tshams pa zer /
NK125(co)003:2170: slob dpon gyis khyod kyang nga la de tsam du tho 'tshams pa /
NK125(co)003:2171: da phyin chad dam 'og tu mi 'dzul na bsreg go gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:2172: der slob dpon gyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal bzhin du /
NK125(co)003:2173: bdag nag po'i rigs kyi lha yin pas /
NK125(co)003:2174: chos bgyi bar rngo mi thog /
NK125(co)003:2175: phyin chad gnod pa mi bgyid do //
NK125(co)003:2177: de nas bsam yas su phebs /
NK125(co)003:2178: phyag tu rdor dril bsnams nas h+aum h+aum zhes bar snang la gar mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2180: de nas rgyal srid dang bod 'bangs spyi la phan
NK125(co)003:2181: pa'i slad du sbyin sreg chen po gcig bya'o zhes
NK125(co)003:2182: gsungs so // de'i skabs shig tu dga' ston chen po zhig la /
NK125(co)003:2183: de ring btsan po dbu skra 'akhru'o zhes yod pa la /
NK125(co)003:2184: slob dpon bo d+hi sat+wasa ri rab kyi byang ngos
NK125(co)003:2185: na chu mig rtag tu snang ba bya ba yod
NK125(co)003:2186: de / de nas chab blangs te btsan po dbu bsil na sku tshe ring ba dang /
NK125(co)003:2188: chab srid chen po sha stag 'byung ba lags te /
NK125(co)003:2189: chab de sus len par rngo thogs sam gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:2190: slob dpon sngags mkhan gyis nus sam zer nas /
NK125(co)003:2192: rung gsungs nas gser gyi bum pa kha dar dkar gyis bcad /
NK125(co)003:2193: bum pa nam mkha' la 'phangs pas je mtho je mtho la mi snang bar song /
NK125(co)003:2195: bum pa de slob dpon gyi spyan sngar khrong gis byung /
NK125(co)003:2196: der btsan po dbu khrus shig byas nas blon po rnams la gtad pas /
NK125(co)003:2197: kha phyes pa'i nang na chu skya nyog ge 'dug pas /
NK125(co)003:2198: blon po kun tshogs pa'i mdun du brim pas /
NK125(co)003:2199: 'di mon gyi myos chu yin te 'ong /
NK125(co)003:2200: pho thong zer te phyir phos nas med par byas /
NK125(co)003:2201: des kyang don med chen po byung /
NK125(co)003:2202: gzhan yang slob dpon gyi bar snang khams nas 'brong kham pa'i rnga ma blangs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2203: gru gu rgyal po'i bang mdzod nas yum gyim shang
NK125(co)003:2204: kong jo'i bse'i me long bltas pas mngon shes gsal
NK125(co)003:2206: w+aa r+aa na s+ai'i mchod rten nas de bzhin gshegs
NK125(co)003:2207: pa'i ring bsrel rdzu 'phrul gyis skad cig la blangs
NK125(co)003:2208: nas rgyal po la gtad pa sogs mtha' yas pa
NK125(co)003:2209: yod de bri bar ma nus so //
NK125(co)003:2210: de nas rgyal po rje 'bangs las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams la dbang bskur te /
NK125(co)003:2211: bar chad bzlog pa'i phyir rdo rje phur ba /
NK125(co)003:2212: sgrib pa sbyong ba'i phyir rdo rje dbyings /
NK125(co)003:2213: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i phyir dpal yang dag gsum gyi dbang bskur /
NK125(co)003:2214: lo ts+aa ba rma gnyags gnyis kyis byas te /
NK125(co)003:2220: rdo rje phur ba'i rgyud rnams bsgyur ro //
NK125(co)003:2221: de'ang rong zom chos bzang gis /
NK125(co)003:2222: rig 'dzin gral thob pad+ma 'byung gnas de //
NK125(co)003:2223: rgyal bos spyan drangs chos 'khor sa gzhi btul //
NK125(co)003:2224: bod khams lha 'dre rnams kyang dam la btags //
NK125(co)003:2225: rgyal blon 'bangs rnams gzhan gyis 'dul dka' bas //
NK125(co)003:2226: bstan pa rin chen tshugs pa'i cha rkyen du //
NK125(co)003:2227: snying zhags ma gshin pad+ma phur pa bsgyur //
NK125(co)003:2228: de yi yan lag phrin las rnam bzhi la //
NK125(co)003:2229: 'jam dpal che mchog dbang chen phur bu bzhi //
NK125(co)003:2230: bstan pa bsrung shing las ka bzhi brgya dang //
NK125(co)003:2231: rtsa bzhi dag tu phyes nas bzhag pa yin //
NK125(co)003:2232: zhes gsungs pa ltar yin te /
NK125(co)003:2233: bod kyi rgyal po snyan khung srab /
NK125(co)003:2234: blon po gdug cing phrag dog che /
NK125(co)003:2235: 'bangs 'khor srin po gdong dmar gyi rigs yin pas /
NK125(co)003:2236: bstan pa mthus bsrung dgos par dgongs nas /
NK125(co)003:2237: sku 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed la brten nas 'khor lo nag po'i las brgya rtsa gcig /
NK125(co)003:2238: gsung pad+ma dbang chen la brten nas pho nya 'gugs 'dren gyi las brgya rtsa gcig /
NK125(co)003:2239: thugs rdo rje gzhon nu la brten nas phur bu gzir mnan gyi las brgya rtsa gcig /
NK125(co)003:2240: che mchog yon tan gyi khro bo la brten nas
NK125(co)003:2241: ma mo rbod gtong bzlog pa'i las brgya rtsa gcig
NK125(co)003:2242: ste / de ltar bzhi brgya dang rtsa bzhi mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2243: gzhan tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad las khol du byung ba'i man ngag kyang mang du bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2244: rgyud la ltos pa'i yi ge yang mang du mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2245: gdams ngag dad bskyed sgron ma zhes bya ba gcig mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:2246: de rnams zla ba drug gi khong du tshar bar mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2247: rje 'bangs rnams la dbang bskur ba'i skabs der /
NK125(co)003:2248: btsun mo tshe spong gza' me tog sgron dang /
NK125(co)003:2249: 'brog bza' khri rgyal btsun bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:2250: phyis rab tu byung ba'i mtshan jo mo byang chub
NK125(co)003:2251: rje zhes pa de la sogs pa btsun mo mchog
NK125(co)003:2252: rnams dkyil 'khor mchod pa'i gzungs ma byed par zhus
NK125(co)003:2253: pas / de kun skal pa dang ldan pa kho nar mi snang /
NK125(co)003:2254: mchims bza' lha mo btsan dang /
NK125(co)003:2255: mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal gnyis mchod pa'i gzungs ma byed pa'i skal ba can du lung bstan pas /
NK125(co)003:2256: de gnyis sa thag ring bas ji ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:2257: 'di la dka' ba med gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:2258: slob dpon dgongs pa la mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK125(co)003:2259: yud tsam zhig na de gnyis dkyil 'khor gyi mthar slebs /
NK125(co)003:2260: de gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i dgongs pa skyes te sgrub pa la zhugs so //
NK125(co)003:2261: bka' gtsigs kyi yi ge gsum las ni /
NK125(co)003:2262: de gnyis rgyal po'i btsun mo yin kyang gzhon nu
NK125(co)003:2263: la sgrub pa la gshegs pas phyag rjes kyi lha
NK125(co)003:2265: de nas dbang bskur grol ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:2266: rgyal po'i gzim mal pa sma co la bya bas
NK125(co)003:2267: lo rgyus de zhang blon rnams la bshad pas yid
NK125(co)003:2268: ma ches te / de tsam gyi nus pa rang
NK125(co)003:2269: med dam snyam pa'i skabs +aar+ya ba lo'i gling gi
NK125(co)003:2271: dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa la thig skud 'then pa'i bu
NK125(co)003:2272: mo yul khams na mtshar ba'i mthar thug pa gnyis
NK125(co)003:2274: bod tsam gyi yul khams che bar mtshar ba'i mthar thug pa su yod ma shes pa'i skabs der /
NK125(co)003:2275: sngags mkhan la de yi nus pa yod zer bas bden na 'gugs par zhu byas pas /
NK125(co)003:2276: slob dpon gyis dgongs pa la mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK125(co)003:2277: dar cig na lcog ro bza' bu chung sman dang /
NK125(co)003:2278: lcog ro bza' lha bu sman gnyis byung /
NK125(co)003:2279: de gnyis la ye shes kyi lha phab ste thig sna ba byas so //
NK125(co)003:2280: phyis bod 'bangs kyi mi thams cad 'dus pa'i tshe
NK125(co)003:2281: yang de gnyis las mtshar ba ye ma byung skad
NK125(co)003:2282: / +aar+ya pa lo'i gling gi rta mgrin gyi sku de /
NK125(co)003:2283: blon po khug stag sna la dpe gyis gsungs pa ltar bzhengs so //
NK125(co)003:2284: der blon po rnams kyi lkog tu smra bar /
NK125(co)003:2285: sngags mkhan 'dis bod khams kyi mtshan sdug can rnams
NK125(co)003:2286: dang nor bzang po thams cad rgya gar la gtod
NK125(co)003:2287: dam zer / de dus bsam yas nyin mo mis
NK125(co)003:2288: brtsigs pa las mtshan mo lha 'dres brtsigs pas mtho
NK125(co)003:2289: dam zer / / gza' dang rgyu skar dang /
NK125(co)003:2290: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs pa gnam
NK125(co)003:2291: sa bar gsum gyi lha srin kun gyis las byed
NK125(co)003:2294: rgyal chen bzhi la sogs pas kyang btang /
NK125(co)003:2295: rdo ring bzhi rgyal chen bzhis btsugs /
NK125(co)003:2296: slob dpon gyis mchims phu'i brag phug tu klu 'dul ba'i dgongs par bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:2297: dus der bsam yas shing gis 'thog /
NK125(co)003:2298: der klu des rgyal po la shing gang dgos ngas sbyin gyis /
NK125(co)003:2299: slob dpon dgongs pa klod zer te /
NK125(co)003:2301: mchims phur phyin pas slob dpon ma mthong /
NK125(co)003:2302: khyung sbrul bzung ba gcig 'dug pas slob dpon yin bsam dgongs pa klod /
NK125(co)003:2303: dngos grub chen po bdog go byas pas /
NK125(co)003:2304: khyung gi lag nas sbrul shor /
NK125(co)003:2305: dngos grub ci yod gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:2308: klu'i yid dam la ma thogs bas phyis bod du gnod pa cher 'ong gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2309: de'i klu 'dul bskyar ma ma zhus par slob dpon brag dmar du phebs /
NK125(co)003:2310: blon po khyung po stag rtse'i bsam pa la /
NK125(co)003:2311: brag dmar mgrin bzang 'di mes bsreg na sngags mkhan 'di gsod thub par 'dug bsam /
NK125(co)003:2312: lan gcig slob dpon gyi drung du phyin pa gcig la /
NK125(co)003:2313: khyod 'di lta bu sems zhes gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:2314: blon po dang mi mang po'i dbus der kho skyengs te phyir thon nas /
NK125(co)003:2315: matha'i mon bu 'dis ci yang shes par 'dug zer skad /
NK125(co)003:2316: der sbas gdong gzigs zer ba blon po shin tu
NK125(co)003:2317: chos la gnag pa de la 'di mi ring bar
NK125(co)003:2318: dbang che bar 'gyur te chos dar du mi ster
NK125(co)003:2319: ba gcig yong bar 'dug pas tshar bcad pa'i dus
NK125(co)003:2321: yud tsam zhig dgongs pa mdzad pas /
NK125(co)003:2322: kho de rang du lus la khrag zag ste shi /
NK125(co)003:2323: de ltar snga phyi mi dang mi ma yin pa rnams btul ba'i nus mthu mthong nas /
NK125(co)003:2324: blon po rnams rang rang gi byed spyod bsam pa ngan pa byed pa la /
NK125(co)003:2325: slob dpon bzhugs pas shin tu bag dog par gyur te /
NK125(co)003:2326: slob dpon rgya gar du bardzonga ba'i thabs kho nar sems shing yod pa la /
NK125(co)003:2328: btsad po khyod kyi yul 'di bzang por bya /
NK125(co)003:2329: dam shod bye ma'i tshal 'di ne'u sing du bya /
NK125(co)003:2330: gra dol dang stag la shar nub dang /
NK125(co)003:2331: yul pa che tshun gyi chab med pa rnams su chu 'byung ba dang /
NK125(co)003:2332: gram pa thams cad kyang zhing sar bsgyur nas bod kyi 'tsho ba bya /
NK125(co)003:2333: rnam thos sras las nor blangs nas dzam bu'i gling
NK125(co)003:2334: gi dkor nor yod do cog gi 'byung khung bod
NK125(co)003:2337: chab 'di bas kyang che ba gcig ngas rgya gar du sbubs su bcug pa yin /
NK125(co)003:2338: rgya dang hor la sogs pa'i rgyal po thams cad dbang du 'du bar bya'o //
NK125(co)003:2339: zhes sogs kyi bka' mchid rgya cher gsungs pa la /
NK125(co)003:2340: de ltar 'ong ngam mi 'ong nyams sad pa'i phyir mdzad par zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:2341: dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas snga dro gcig dgongs pa mdzad pas /
NK125(co)003:2342: brag dmar gyi skam sa gcig tu chu chen po gcig brdol /
NK125(co)003:2344: da dung mdzad dgos zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:2345: brag dmar mtsho mo 'gul sngar bye thang du yod pa la ne'u sing du sngo phyam gyis song /
NK125(co)003:2346: de'i phyi dro brag gla ba'i gdong du nags chen po skad cig la byung /
NK125(co)003:2347: ming gla ba'i tshal du btags /
NK125(co)003:2348: yang de'i sang snga dro dgongs pa mdzad pas /
NK125(co)003:2349: sngar zur mkhar la phu chu med pa la phu chu chen po nar gyis byung /
NK125(co)003:2350: da zhing sa gang du bya gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2351: stag la shar gyi yul sked der chu byung nas
NK125(co)003:2352: mdze pho zhig gis brgal bas mdze pho rab tu
NK125(co)003:2353: grags / de'i yul gyi phu zhig tu gtsang chu sbubs la drangs pas brag 'og zhig tu thon /
NK125(co)003:2354: slob dpon gyis dgongs pa la bar du ma bcad na der yang chu 'bad med 'byung rgyu la /
NK125(co)003:2355: blon po ngan pas bar chad byas pas ma byung kyang /
NK125(co)003:2356: da lta brag 'og gi chu der gtsang po'i mdog gang byung der 'ong ba zhig yod /
NK125(co)003:2357: de la brten nas yul gyi ming du chu sbubs gzhung du grags /
NK125(co)003:2358: yul po che ni lung pa chung bas chu 'bad med du byung /
NK125(co)003:2359: de ltar thams cad 'ong nges par 'dug pas /
NK125(co)003:2360: blon po rnams kyis 'dun pa chung ngur gros byas te /
NK125(co)003:2361: zhing dang na ba yar lung gis chog /
NK125(co)003:2362: sngags mkhan 'dis yul 'di bzang por btang nas rgya gar la gtad 'dod yin /
NK125(co)003:2363: da 'phro chod la matha'i mon bu 'di rang yul
NK125(co)003:2364: du bardzonga pa legs zhes dbang che che rnams kha
NK125(co)003:2367: matha'i mon bu 'di ni mthu rtsal che /
NK125(co)003:2368: btsad po'i thugs ni chos la gtad /
NK125(co)003:2369: chab srid rgya gar bas 'phrog te 'gro bar mchi /
NK125(co)003:2370: zhes sogs sngar gyi gsungs re re la de ltar
NK125(co)003:2371: bya mi rung ba'i rgyu mtshan log pa mang po
NK125(co)003:2372: bkod / slob dpon sngags mkhan rang la bya dga'
NK125(co)003:2373: cher byin te slar rgya gar la bzhud par zhu
NK125(co)003:2374: dgos zhes yang yang zhu ba phul /
NK125(co)003:2375: slob dpon nyid la'ang blon po rnams kyi de ltar zhu ba phul /
NK125(co)003:2376: btsan po thugs ma bde ste /
NK125(co)003:2377: slob dpon la gser phye bre gang phul /
NK125(co)003:2381: nga gser 'dod pas bod du 'ong ba min /
NK125(co)003:2382: bod khams mtha' 'khob kyi 'dre srin gdug pa can btul nas chos dar bar bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:2383: yul bzang por bsgyur nas bod rnams bde ba la bkod pa'i phyir 'ong ba yin /
NK125(co)003:2384: gser 'dod na 'di ltar byas pas 'ong gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:2385: mtha' bskor gyi bye ma dang rdo la phyag reg pas thams cad gser du song /
NK125(co)003:2386: 'on kyang btsan po'i ngo bsrung ba'i phyir du khyor
NK125(co)003:2387: ba gang blangs te rdo rje gdan du mchod pa
NK125(co)003:2388: gcig bya'o gsungs / lhag ma rnams btsad po nyid la gtad nas /
NK125(co)003:2389: bzang po byur gyi sna 'dren yin //
NK125(co)003:2390: snying rje rgas pa zhe sdang rgyu //
NK125(co)003:2391: rje yi kha lo blon gyis bsgyur //
NK125(co)003:2392: bod kyi 'dre blon gdug pa can //
NK125(co)003:2393: sems can las ngan spyod pa la //
NK125(co)003:2394: rgyal ba rnams kyi nus mathu'ang rdug /
NK125(co)003:2396: blon po rnams la zer ba'i stabs su btang /
NK125(co)003:2397: rgyal po la chos dang gdams pa mang du gnang /
NK125(co)003:2398: khyad par rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa gcig la man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2399: rgyal brgyud mnga' thang cher 'phel ba'i sbyin sreg dang /
NK125(co)003:2400: lha klu dam bzhag gsum pa yang ma grub /
NK125(co)003:2403: rgyal po 'gyod zer ba de dang mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:2404: 'on kyang ma 'ongs pa mkhyen pas slob ma rnams la drag sngags mang po gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2405: chos dang drag sngags kyi dpe mang po brag dang rdza la sbas /
NK125(co)003:2406: chos dang drag sngags sman rtsis nor gter la sogs
NK125(co)003:2407: pa gter kha chen po brgya rtsa brgyad sbas pa'i
NK125(co)003:2408: mthar / bdag dang gtan pa med pa'i sbyin bdag rnams //
NK125(co)003:2409: tshe rabs 'di dang tshe rabs gzhan yang rung //
NK125(co)003:2410: 'og min zhes bya'i gnas mchog dam pa ru //
NK125(co)003:2411: rnal 'byor theg chen 'bras bur spyod par shog /
NK125(co)003:2413: so so la zhal gyi gdams pa mang du gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:2414: glo bur du yar la gshegs te /
NK125(co)003:2415: yar lam ru lag brgyud nas phebs so //
NK125(co)003:2416: yar lam ru lag nas brgyud tshul rta mgrin yang
NK125(co)003:2417: gsang gi lo rgyus gter ma las kyang 'byung la
NK125(co)003:2419: lo ti dgu snang gong dang /
NK125(co)003:2420: zhang nyang bzang zhes bya ba'i blon po dad pa
NK125(co)003:2421: can gnyis kyis mang yul gung thang bar du bskyal
NK125(co)003:2423: sngags mkhan nus pa can de ma bsad na rang re rnams la mthu byed 'ong zer nas /
NK125(co)003:2424: gshed ma shin tu dpa' ba bco brgyad la rta dang bcas nas lkog tu btang ngo //
NK125(co)003:2425: slob dpon mang yul du byon pa na /
NK125(co)003:2426: nang par 'o cag la dgra 'ong gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2427: nang par sa dod bab kyi 'phrang na gshed ma
NK125(co)003:2428: bco brgyad po mtshon cha lag na gsor te slob
NK125(co)003:2430: der slob dpon gyis sdigs mdzub bstan pas thams cad kyi lus 'jim gzugs bzhin du rengs /
NK125(co)003:2432: slob dpon skyel mi dang bcas pa phar gshegs /
NK125(co)003:2433: de nas skyel ma rnams yul de'i la kha zhig
NK125(co)003:2434: nas tshur log skabs bod kyi 'dre srin lha klu
NK125(co)003:2435: bdud btsan rnams lan gsum 'dul dgos pa la gcig
NK125(co)003:2436: 'phro la lus / de ma lus na rgyal po sku tshe ring /
NK125(co)003:2438: rgyal po'i rigs brgyud kyang 'phel la mnga' thang che /
NK125(co)003:2439: chos yun ring du gnas pa la /
NK125(co)003:2440: da chos 'khor gcig dang 'byongs nas 'ong ste /
NK125(co)003:2441: der 'khrugs pa chen po zhig kyang 'ong /
NK125(co)003:2442: chos la sked nyag bag re 'ong /
NK125(co)003:2443: klu de yang rgyal po la phud zhe gnag par 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2444: rgyal brgyud kyang sil bur 'gro gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2445: khar sang gi 'tshe ba byed mi de rnams la
NK125(co)003:2446: 'di 'thor cig gsungs nas yungs dkar spar ba gang
NK125(co)003:2447: gtad / lho nub mtshams su srin po 'dul du 'gro gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:2448: chibs kyi kha nas chos gos spu re /
NK125(co)003:2449: gseg shang khrol le nam mkha' la 'phur te bzhud do //
NK125(co)003:2451: gshed ma rnams la yungs dkar gtor bas smra shes 'gro shes pa byung ngo //
NK125(co)003:2452: sngar slob dpon gyi gsungs rnams rgyal po'i snyan du gsol bas /
NK125(co)003:2453: rgyal po'i thugs la shin tu bcags pa byung ngo //
NK125(co)003:2454: zhes sogs sba bzhed nas byung ba 'di rnams mi bden zhes rnying ma 'ga' zhig smra /
NK125(co)003:2455: 'di dag kyang mi bden pa ni ma yin la /
NK125(co)003:2456: man ngag lta phreng gi lo rgyus dang /
NK125(co)003:2457: rgyal po'i bka' gtsigs kyi yi ge gsum dang /
NK125(co)003:2458: rta mgrin yang gsang khros pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK125(co)003:2459: bka' ma'i lo rgyus khung che ba mang por yang de lta bu byung zhing /
NK125(co)003:2460: 'o bran lugs kyi phur ba'i stong thun dang /
NK125(co)003:2463: jo lugs kyi phur pa'i stong thun rnams su lo
NK125(co)003:2464: rgyus gong dang mthun pa de ga ltar bshad pa
NK125(co)003:2465: dang / rje'i bka' chems kyi yi ge las kyang /
NK125(co)003:2466: yun ring por bzhugs nas bod khams thams cad bde
NK125(co)003:2467: skyid dang ldan par bya'o gsungs pa zhig yod pa
NK125(co)003:2468: la / phyis sems can spyi mthun gyi las kyis rgyu byas /
NK125(co)003:2469: nag phyogs kyi lha srin gdug pa can snying la
NK125(co)003:2470: zhugs pa blon po rnams kyis rkyen byas te ma
NK125(co)003:2472: 'o na ci ltar yin zhes na /
NK125(co)003:2473: mang yul la thog nas 'phur te gshegs pa de
NK125(co)003:2474: ni sdig blon rnams kyi ngor slob dpon gyis sprul
NK125(co)003:2476: yon mchod lkog tu bka' bgros te rgyal po ma
NK125(co)003:2477: grong bar du slob dpon bzhugs pa'i chad so yod
NK125(co)003:2478: pa bzhin slob dpon gyi sku dngos gzho stod ti
NK125(co)003:2479: sgror byon te mkha' 'gro ma ye shes mtsho rgyal
NK125(co)003:2480: la rdzogs pa chen po mkha' 'gro snying thig gsungs
NK125(co)003:2481: nas blun sgom yid byed dang phral nas sangs rgyas
NK125(co)003:2482: kyi dgongs pa mngon sum rang thog tu gtan la
NK125(co)003:2483: phab / bka' gtsigs kyi yi ge las /
NK125(co)003:2484: mchims bza' lha mo btsan dang /
NK125(co)003:2485: mkhar chen mtsho rgyal gnyis gzhon nu nas sgrub pa la gshegs pas phyag rjes kyi lha khang med /
NK125(co)003:2486: zhes gong du drangs pa'i rgyu mtshan yang de ltar yin /
NK125(co)003:2487: 'di bsam yas kyi sa 'dul ba la sogs pa'i
NK125(co)003:2488: sta gon stag lo la byas pa'i me pho stag
NK125(co)003:2490: thang yig las sa pho stag zhes bris pa ni yi ge nor /
NK125(co)003:2491: gang ltar mtsho rgyal la stag lor mkha' 'gro snying
NK125(co)003:2492: thig gnang tshul mkha' 'gro snying thig rang la gsal
NK125(co)003:2493: bar yod / de yan chad ni gsang sngags bab bdun byung ba las /
NK125(co)003:2494: bab dang po ni slob dpon pad+ma las byung ba'i tshul mdo tsam smos pa'o //
NK125(co)003:2495: de skabs rgyal pos bsam yas brtsig /
NK125(co)003:2496: dbu rtse rim gsum ri rab kyi tshul /
NK125(co)003:2498: lha khang gzhan thams cad gling bzhi gling phran gyi tshul /
NK125(co)003:2499: mtha' lcags ri rtsa brgyad mchod rten gyis bskor ba sogs byas te /
NK125(co)003:2500: thang yig ltar na lo lnga dang /
NK125(co)003:2501: sba bzhed ltar na lo bcu gsum la 'byongs /
NK125(co)003:2502: thog mar slob dpon bo d+hi sat+wasa rab gnas mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2503: kha cig shin+tam gar+b+hasa rab gnas mdzad zer /
NK125(co)003:2504: gang yang mi 'gal te dus der byon pa'i pan chen thams cad kyis rab gnas mdzad pas so //
NK125(co)003:2505: de skabs slob dpon pad+ma sgrub gnas rnams su bzhugs pa'i gtam mi mang pos gleng pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2506: rgyal pos kyang bden rdzun brtags pa ltar byas te gdan drangs /
NK125(co)003:2507: blon po rnams kyi bsam pa la 'byon rang mi nus sam snyam pa yod tshe /
NK125(co)003:2508: slob dpon byon te rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK125(co)003:2509: nam mkha' la mngon par sprul te rab gnas mdzad
NK125(co)003:2511: nang gi lha rnams phyir byung /
NK125(co)003:2512: dbu rtse'i lha rnams kyis phyag mtshan bskyur byung bas /
NK125(co)003:2513: rgyal po skrag ste da nang du mi tshud do dgongs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2514: lha rnams dbu rtse la bskor ba lan gsum byas nas nang du song /
NK125(co)003:2516: sgo srung khro bo la me dpung 'bar ba mi kun gyis mthong /
NK125(co)003:2517: bsam yas la me shor ram snyam du rgyal po yang skrag /
NK125(co)003:2518: jo mo gling gsum la me tog 'thor bas lha khang 'od kyis gang /
NK125(co)003:2520: sngar ma thos pa'i dri bzang 'thul /
NK125(co)003:2521: pad+ma'i sdong po skyes pa kun gyis mthong /
NK125(co)003:2522: +aar+ya pa lo'i gling na me tog 'thor bas /
NK125(co)003:2523: rta mgrin gyi sku des rta skad theng gsum bsgrags pa kun gyis thos /
NK125(co)003:2524: khor sa la sngar med pa'i smyug ma sngo shar gyis skyes /
NK125(co)003:2525: byams pa gling du me tog 'thor bas lha mang pos sprin gseb nas mchod pa 'bul du song /
NK125(co)003:2526: 'jam dpal gling du me tog gi char pa babs /
NK125(co)003:2527: bdud 'dul sngags pa gling du sangs rgyas nam mkha'
NK125(co)003:2528: ga nga ba kun gyis mthong bar byon nas nang
NK125(co)003:2530: khrus khang gling du me tog 'thor bas lha de rnams kyis chos gsungs pa kun gyis thos /
NK125(co)003:2531: bsam gtan gling du nyi zla gnyis dus gcig shar /
NK125(co)003:2532: sgra bsgyur gling du rol mo thams cad rang 'khrol /
NK125(co)003:2533: pe dkar gling du lha rnams phyir byon nas me tog blangs te nang du 'khod /
NK125(co)003:2534: mchod rten bzhi la gdugs dang /
NK125(co)003:2535: ba dan dang me tog phreng ba la sogs pa'i
NK125(co)003:2536: rgyan rnams ma btags pa la rang chas su byung
NK125(co)003:2537: / mgon khang bzhi la me tog 'thor bas 'od zer 'phros sku phyir thon pas khrom 'ur /
NK125(co)003:2538: rdo ring bzhi la me tog gtor bas zangs kyi khyi mo bzhi phyogs bzhir zug cing 'phyo /
NK125(co)003:2539: lcags ri la me tog gtor bas a ru ra
NK125(co)003:2540: rlon pa'i char chu tshod gsum gyi yun du babs
NK125(co)003:2541: pa rnams kun gyis mthun snang du grub /
NK125(co)003:2542: sba bzhed pas slob dpon bo d+hi sat+wasa mdzad dus byung zer /
NK125(co)003:2543: sba bzhed kyi yi ge gcig na slob dpon shin+tam
NK125(co)003:2544: gar+b+hasa rab gnas mdzad pa'i dus su de rnams 'byung
NK125(co)003:2545: bar bshad mod / de dus kyi rab gnas mdzad
NK125(co)003:2546: pa po thams cad ni 'phags pa sha stag yin
NK125(co)003:2547: pas thams cad de ltar 'byung bar gsal lo //
NK125(co)003:2548: de nas slob dpon gyis lha sa khra 'brug la
NK125(co)003:2549: sogs pa'i lha khang thams cad du sprul pa re
NK125(co)003:2550: byon te rab gnas bskyar te mdzad /
NK125(co)003:2551: dbu rtse rim gsum du lo pan brgya rtsa dang
NK125(co)003:2552: rje 'bangs grogs gsum la sogs pa la chos kyi
NK125(co)003:2553: 'khor lo rgya chen po bskor ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:2554: btsun mo tshe spong bza' dang blon po rnams snying rab tu na nas gros byas te /
NK125(co)003:2555: rgyal po khro chu gdong du spyan drangs nas /
NK125(co)003:2559: khri 'brang lha lod la sogs pas 'di skad du /
NK125(co)003:2561: bdag cag yid chad mchi ma bro /
NK125(co)003:2562: rgyal po'i thugs la nor ba 'di 'dra ba mchis lags so //
NK125(co)003:2563: yab kyi dkor nor rnams 'jim pa la byugs /
NK125(co)003:2564: nor med na rgyal po dmangs su 'bebs /
NK125(co)003:2565: lho bal gyi mtha' mi la thugs rtsis nan ltar che /
NK125(co)003:2566: mtha' mi ngan pas rgyal po'i sku tshe sdud /
NK125(co)003:2567: rab byung yin zer nas bran g.yog che sar 'don /
NK125(co)003:2568: rten 'brel 'chugs pas rgyal srid 'jig pa'i nyen che /
NK125(co)003:2569: chos khrims 'dzug pa yin zer nas mtha' mi'i spyod pa byed /
NK125(co)003:2570: bod 'bangs bde skyid la rang khar spyod pa'i dbang med /
NK125(co)003:2571: bdag cag blon po rnams la rtsis su mi byed /
NK125(co)003:2572: gros ma gsan na phyi yi dgra byung na chos kyis thul cig /
NK125(co)003:2573: nang gi so tshag rab byung btsun pas mdzod /
NK125(co)003:2574: nged cag blon po kun rang rang so sor gyes nas 'gro /
NK125(co)003:2575: sgo khyi ri la shor na spyang ku yin /
NK125(co)003:2576: yang rgyal blon 'dzom pa dpa' brjid che dgongs par gda' na /
NK125(co)003:2577: matha'i ban d+he 'di rnams chab gsol cig zer ro //
NK125(co)003:2580: rje yi thugs dgongs mtha' mis bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2581: blon po rnams yid chad pa yang shin tu bden /
NK125(co)003:2582: matha'i ngan sngags mkhan po 'dis 'o skol yab yum bar du dbyen 'dzud /
NK125(co)003:2583: rgyal po'i sku srog kyang bcad par mchi'o //
NK125(co)003:2584: sngar btsun mo mkhar chen bza' dang mchims bza' gnyis kyang 'phrog /
NK125(co)003:2585: da rgyal srid 'phrog par the tshom med /
NK125(co)003:2586: rje la blon po med na rgyal srid bzung thabs ga la yod /
NK125(co)003:2587: mtha' mi 'khyams po thams cad mtha' la spyugs la /
NK125(co)003:2588: rang re rgyal blon kun gros 'dun gcig tu mdzod zer ro //
NK125(co)003:2589: rgyal po thugs rab tu mug par gyur nas spyan chab shor /
NK125(co)003:2590: zhag gsum na lan btang gis gsungs nas bzhud /
NK125(co)003:2592: blon po med na phyi'i dgra mi thul zer ba bden /
NK125(co)003:2593: de min pa 'di lta bu chos la sdang snyam nas thugs ma bde /
NK125(co)003:2595: da ni slob dpon pad+ma lta bu bzhugs pa yin /
NK125(co)003:2596: btsun mo dang blon po'i bar chad kyis mi tshugs pa srid snyam nas /
NK125(co)003:2597: slob dpon gyi drung du byon nas sngar gyi lo rgyus zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:2600: ye shes dang ma rig pa'i rang mdangs las /
NK125(co)003:2601: sngon yang sangs rgyas re re'i drung du bdud re re lhan cig tu byung bar gda'/
NK125(co)003:2602: nyid chos skyong ba'i rgyal po yin pa'i phyir blon po bdud du babs par gda'/
NK125(co)003:2604: ye shes ni rig pa rang gsal nam mkha' dwangs pa'i klong lta bu yin /
NK125(co)003:2605: ma rig pa ni sprin dang na bun lta bu yin /
NK125(co)003:2606: don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi khyad par yod pas /
NK125(co)003:2607: bdud kyis sangs rgyas kyi yon tan sgrib par mi nus /
NK125(co)003:2608: de la rgyal po nyid rang thugs dgongs bzang po mi 'gyur ba rten 'brel du che /
NK125(co)003:2610: btsun mo la da ste zhag gsum nas lo pan rnams la ngas bsnyen bkur chen po bya yis /
NK125(co)003:2612: gal te gsod bar ma nus na /
NK125(co)003:2613: 'di rnams kyi ngan sngags kyis rang re rnams tshe srog bstung nges bas /
NK125(co)003:2614: phyin chad de lta bu mi byed pa'i bro skyol gsungs nas dam bdar mdzod /
NK125(co)003:2615: blon po rnams kyi bar chad bdag gis btul gyi gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:2616: de nas rgyal pos btsun mo dang blon po rnams la de skad gsungs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2617: khong rnams shin du dga' nas /
NK125(co)003:2618: rgyal pos ji skad gsungs pa ltar byas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2619: de nas zhag gsum na rgyal pos bu tshal gser
NK125(co)003:2620: khang gling du lo pan rnams spyan drangs te bsnyen
NK125(co)003:2621: bkur byas / btsun mo dang blon po rnams nyi ma shar ba dang gshed ma bkye bas /
NK125(co)003:2622: lo pan thams cad spyan ras gzigs su song ste /
NK125(co)003:2623: gshed ma rnams kyang gsod pa'i 'dun pa dor nas phyir log /
NK125(co)003:2624: de nas nyin dgung gshed ma bkye bas /
NK125(co)003:2625: thams cad rin chen 'bar ba de ru song /
NK125(co)003:2626: gshed ma rnams ltad mos g.yeng nas slar log song /
NK125(co)003:2627: nyi ma dgong mo bkye bas /
NK125(co)003:2628: lo pan rnams 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po re re ru gyur te /
NK125(co)003:2629: so so la btsun mo blon 'khor bsam gyis mi
NK125(co)003:2630: khyab pa sha stag tu gyur nas gsod par ma
NK125(co)003:2631: nus / de nas srod la blon po rnams rang
NK125(co)003:2632: rang gi mtshon cha dang bcas te gshed ma'i tshogs
NK125(co)003:2633: kyis bskor nas phyin te shin tu rngams pa'i nga
NK125(co)003:2634: ros rgyob gsod ces bsgrags shing rgyugs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2635: slob dpon pad+ma bzhengs te h+aum h+aum zhes gsungs shing khro bo mthing nag gcig tu song /
NK125(co)003:2636: bar snang sa gzhi thams cad ni khro bo dang
NK125(co)003:2637: mi'i dmag gis gang nas thams cad bsad song ba'i
NK125(co)003:2638: snang ba shar te blon po gshed ma de kun
NK125(co)003:2639: phyir bros nas bsam yas kyi lcags ri'i phyi rol
NK125(co)003:2641: thams cad 'gyel te rengs par gyur te /
NK125(co)003:2642: de'i tshe de dag gi bud med rnams kyis ma
NK125(co)003:2643: bzod nas nub zad la ku co di ri byung
NK125(co)003:2644: / nang par rgyal pos gzigs pas /
NK125(co)003:2645: gshed ma dang blon po rnams rgyangs grags re 'das
NK125(co)003:2646: pa'i sa na kha nas khrag skyugs te 'gyel 'dug
NK125(co)003:2647: / rgyal po dgyes te gu ru'i spyan sngar phyin phyag 'tshal /
NK125(co)003:2648: slob dpon gyis sa spar gang gnang nas 'di gshed ma dang blon po rnams la 'thor du thong /
NK125(co)003:2649: srog gcod na snying rje gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2650: der blon po rnams ga ler langs nas gyol gyol
NK125(co)003:2651: byung ste thams cad skyengs nas dpa' zhum mer 'dug
NK125(co)003:2652: / de nas bzung ste phyin chad btsun mo dang
NK125(co)003:2653: blon po'i tshogs kyis bod kyi bstan pa la rgol
NK125(co)003:2654: bar ma nus pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:2655: der rgyal po rab tu dad de /
NK125(co)003:2656: slob dpon gyi yon tan thams cad bstan dgos zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:2657: rgyal po chen po sangs rgyas kyi yon tan sems can gyis dpag par dka'/
NK125(co)003:2658: 'on kyang cung zad mthong yang srid /
NK125(co)003:2659: rdo rje 'di dbu sngas su thog la mos pa rtse gcig pas gzim zhig gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2660: de ltar byas pas rgyal po'i rmi lam na /
NK125(co)003:2661: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK125(co)003:2662: thams cad me long dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan shar ba
NK125(co)003:2664: snang srid thams cad 'ja' 'od du gsal /
NK125(co)003:2665: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i skar tshogs ltar bgrang las 'das pa 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2666: de rnams re re'i drung na slob dpon re re 'dug pa la /
NK125(co)003:2667: sangs rgyas byang sems rnams kyi thugs ka nas 'od
NK125(co)003:2668: zer sna lnga 'phros pas slob dpon gyi thugs kar
NK125(co)003:2670: sems can mang po'i don byas /
NK125(co)003:2671: bar snang khams thams cad me tog gis gang ba'i
NK125(co)003:2672: zhing khams mang po na mkha' 'gro ma dpag tu
NK125(co)003:2673: med pa 'dug / re re'i mdun na yang slob
NK125(co)003:2674: dpon re re 'od zer spro bsdu dang sems can
NK125(co)003:2675: gyi don snga ma lta byas pa 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2676: lho nub srin yul rnga yab gling dang zangs mdog dpal ri'i bkod pa yang gsal bar gzigs /
NK125(co)003:2677: der byon te rtse nas bltas pas /
NK125(co)003:2678: mi'i yul nas dmyal khams yan chad gsal bar mthong gin 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2679: ngan song gsum gyi sems can re re'i mdun na
NK125(co)003:2680: slob dpon re re bzhugs nas de dag gi don
NK125(co)003:2681: mdzad pa 'dug / zangs mdog dpal ri'i gzhal yas
NK125(co)003:2682: khang gi dbus na slob dpon sngar bas kyang gzi
NK125(co)003:2683: mdangs che ba zhal mngon du gzigs pa zhig 'khor
NK125(co)003:2684: rig 'dzin dpa' bo dpa' mos bskor ba 'ja' 'od
NK125(co)003:2685: kyi klong nas sku'i 'od zer 'phros pa'i sna la
NK125(co)003:2686: sangs rgyas byang sems mang po 'gro ba rigs drug
NK125(co)003:2687: gi gnas su 'gro don mdzad pa dpag tu med
NK125(co)003:2689: rgyal po rang gis bod 'bangs sum brgya tsam drongs /
NK125(co)003:2690: jo mo mtsho rgyal gyis dngos su mi lnga brgya
NK125(co)003:2691: dang shul na 'bum phrag lhag tsam 'dren par 'dug
NK125(co)003:2692: / nam mkha'i snying pos nyis 'bum sum stong 'dren pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2694: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la sogs pa lo
NK125(co)003:2695: ts+aa ba rnams kyis gdul bya khri phrag re re
NK125(co)003:2697: slar yang gsol ba btab pas /
NK125(co)003:2698: rgyal pos dngos su mu khri btsan po la sogs pa'i 'bum phrag brgya dang /
NK125(co)003:2699: brgyud nas bye ba phrag gsum 'dren par gzigs /
NK125(co)003:2700: de ltar slob dpon gyi ba spu gcig gi yon
NK125(co)003:2701: tan yang ma mthong yang yon tan gyi cha shas
NK125(co)003:2702: phra mo tsam zhig mnal lam du byung bas rgyal
NK125(co)003:2704: slob dpon nyid sangs rgyas thams cad las ches lhag pa'i mos pa thob /
NK125(co)003:2705: lo rgyus 'di rong zom gyi phyag dpe yin zer ba'i yig chung btab pa la /
NK125(co)003:2706: sngar dus lcags smyugs kyis bris pa'i shog 'khyar gnyis
NK125(co)003:2707: snar lce sna'i dape'u na 'khyar ba zhig la 'dug
NK125(co)003:2708: / byang gter thugs sgrub kyi lo rgyus de dang
