NK125(co)003:2709: bka' gter gyi khyad par 'dra min cung zad ma
NK125(co)003:2711: de nas rgyal pos dge ba bcu'i khrims bcas te /
NK125(co)003:2712: rgyal khrims gser gyi gnya' shing 'dra ste lji la sgroms /
NK125(co)003:2713: chos khrims dar gyi mdud pa 'dra ste 'jam la dam /
NK125(co)003:2714: bod yul bde skyid lha'i yul dang mnyam par mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:2715: de nas 'bangs blo rno ba dag la lo ts+aa bslab ste chos 'tshol du btang bar bzhed /
NK125(co)003:2717: lho brag pa gtsang legs grub gnyis rgya gar la btang /
NK125(co)003:2718: de la bee ro ni thang yig ltar na snye mor 'khrungs zhes dang /
NK125(co)003:2719: 'dra 'bag las nyang gtsang 'dzom pa lho brag shan du 'khrungs zer /
NK125(co)003:2721: bee ro ni sprul pa'i sku yin pas gang du yang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK125(co)003:2722: gzhan ni lo ts+aa rgan gsum gzhon gsum la sogs pa mang pos mdo sngags bsgyur te /
NK125(co)003:2723: rgan gsum la mi mthun pa mang /
NK125(co)003:2724: rta mgrin yang gsang las ni /
NK125(co)003:2727: 'ol g+hel gru'u byed lngas sgra bsgyur gyi lo ts+aa byas /
NK125(co)003:2732: shud bu a lo dang lngas mchan bu'i lo ts+aa byas zhes bshad /
NK125(co)003:2733: gang ltar na yang bsam yas rmang bting nas lo bcu gnyis pa me mo glang gi lor yin /
NK125(co)003:2734: rgyal po'i sku rim la dmigs te /
NK125(co)003:2735: shes rab snying po lta ba'i mdo /
NK125(co)003:2736: 'da' dka' ye shes sgom pa'i mdo /
NK125(co)003:2737: bzang po spyod pa smon lam gyi mdo /
NK125(co)003:2738: byang chub ltung bshags bshags pa'i mdo /
NK125(co)003:2739: gtsug tor dkar mo zlog pa'i mdo rnams bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2740: da lta'ang rgyal po mdo lnga zer ba de ltar yin /
NK125(co)003:2746: nang skong na rag dong sprugs cha lag dang bcas pa /
NK125(co)003:2747: gsang skong bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi rnams bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2748: rgyal po la sku tshe'i bar chad yod pa bzlog ste /
NK125(co)003:2749: de yang rgyal pos slob dpon nyid lta bu tshe
NK125(co)003:2750: la mnga' brnyes pa ji lta bu'i sgo nas lags
NK125(co)003:2752: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig bsgom pas 'khor 'das ru
NK125(co)003:2753: shan phye ste lus 'ja' ltar gyur nas thob pa
NK125(co)003:2754: yang yod / dbang po yang rab kyis lus gnad
NK125(co)003:2755: gzir nas bsgom pas sems rtags lus la shar nas
NK125(co)003:2756: lus rdo rje ltar gyur nas bgres rgud mi mnga'
NK125(co)003:2757: yang yod / ba yang yod / yi dam lha
NK125(co)003:2758: bsgrubs pas de dang gnyis su med par gyur te
NK125(co)003:2759: tshe la mnga' brnyes pa yang yod /
NK125(co)003:2760: bcud len la brten nas tshe nyi zla dang mnyam pa yang yod /
NK125(co)003:2761: mgon po tshe dpag med bsgrubs te dbang bskur bas tshe la dbang ba yang yod /
NK125(co)003:2762: yang de nyid la gsol ba btab pas lo lnga brgya la sogs pa thub pa yang yod /
NK125(co)003:2765: 'o na bdag la tshe dbang gcig bskur dgos zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:2767: jo mo 'khor 'bangs dkor mdzod mnga' ris dang bcas pa phul mdzod /
NK125(co)003:2768: rje nyid mi yul du lo stong phrag gsum bzhugs pa bdag gis dam baca'o gsungs /
NK125(co)003:2769: brag dmar g.ya' ma lung du tshe sgrub mdzad pas /
NK125(co)003:2770: zla ba gcig na tshe dpag med dngos su byon /
NK125(co)003:2771: bsam yas lung pa sman dris khengs /
NK125(co)003:2772: rgyal po'i mnal lam du tshe dpag med kyi phyag
NK125(co)003:2773: gis g.ya' ma lung gi tshe chu la reg pa
NK125(co)003:2774: rmis te dbang zhu bar chas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:2775: dbu rtse'i sgo drung du blon po klu dpal gyis blon po kun sbran te /
NK125(co)003:2781: khri bzang yab lhag sogs tshogs /
NK125(co)003:2782: klu dpal dang klu gong gnyis kyis /
NK125(co)003:2783: matha'i mon bu 'dod pa can 'dis rgyal po la dug gtong bar 'dug pas bshol thob zer /
NK125(co)003:2784: rang re rnams la yang yong nyen yod pas zon gyis lo /
NK125(co)003:2785: rdo rje spre'u chung dang shud bu na re /
NK125(co)003:2786: de 'dra mi srid slob dpon 'jig rten spangs ba'i skyes mchog la rgyal srid kyis ci bya zer /
NK125(co)003:2788: slob dpon rgyal po'i gdan sa la rings par 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2789: kha sang zla ba snga ma la g.ya' ma lung
NK125(co)003:2790: du rje 'bangs tshogs dus su yang rgyal po sku
NK125(co)003:2791: tshe ring bar 'dod na jo mo mnga' ris phul
NK125(co)003:2792: cig gsungs / nang rtags phyir shar shing gi yal ga 'dra zer /
NK125(co)003:2793: rgya tsha lha snang dang shud bu gnyis kyis /
NK125(co)003:2794: slob dpon 'phags pa'i nor gyis phyugs pa la /
NK125(co)003:2795: dkor mdzod mnga' ris kyis ci zhig bya /
NK125(co)003:2796: rgyal po tshe bsring na rang re kun bsam pa 'grub mod byas pas /
NK125(co)003:2798: tshe ring bar 'dod pas rang srog skyel /
NK125(co)003:2799: khyod tsho la de 'dra'i tshod med /
NK125(co)003:2800: zer te blon po kun rba mkhar gyis brdungs nas /
NK125(co)003:2801: rgyal po'i spyan sngar phyin te chibs mthur la bzung nas /
NK125(co)003:2803: tshe dbang zhu na sku srog 'dor ba'i nyen gada'o //
NK125(co)003:2804: matha'i mon bu 'dod pa can 'di rje'i gdan sa la rings par 'dug go //
NK125(co)003:2805: tshe chu bsgrub kyi yod skad de ni kha sang
NK125(co)003:2806: zla ba snga ma la rgya gar nas rtsi dug
NK125(co)003:2808: bla mchod pan+di ta gnyis kyis gser btsal nas khud du sbas pa mthong 'dug go //
NK125(co)003:2809: rtsi dug khur ba gnyis pos bzod pa gdong gi
NK125(co)003:2810: brag la yi ge bris nas dogs yod pas kun
NK125(co)003:2812: zer te chibs kha nang du slog /
NK125(co)003:2815: ci yin mi shes dgongs te nang du log /
NK125(co)003:2816: de slob dpon gyis mkhyen te /
NK125(co)003:2817: tshe chu cha brgyad du bgos te gter du sbas /
NK125(co)003:2818: rnam thar gser gyi phreng bar /
NK125(co)003:2819: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan nyid //
NK125(co)003:2820: mi yul tshe lo stong phrag gsum //
NK125(co)003:2821: bzhugs pa'i tshe chu ngas bsgrubs kyang //
NK125(co)003:2822: rgyal po bdud blon dbang du thal //
NK125(co)003:2823: 'on kyang lo skor gcig du bsrings //
NK125(co)003:2824: bod rnams spyi mthun bsod nams la //
NK125(co)003:2825: ma shong tshe chu gter du sbas //
NK125(co)003:2826: ma 'ongs dus kyi tha ma la //
NK125(co)003:2827: byang chub sems dpa' mi brgyad dbang //
NK125(co)003:2830: brag dmar 'dzam bu gling gong gi brag kho na la yod par bshad kyang /
NK125(co)003:2831: snga ma'i phyogs 'di dag pa 'dra ste /
NK125(co)003:2832: ye shes khyung grags dang zur pak+shi sh+aaka 'od kyis
NK125(co)003:2833: brag rdo rje tshe brtan nas tshe chu mu men
NK125(co)003:2834: gyi k+aa pa la gang thon pa se chen rgyal
NK125(co)003:2836: rgya nag gi rgyal po la se chen de sku tshe ring ste brgyad cu gya bzhi bzhugs so //
NK125(co)003:2837: zhes sa skya pa'i yig tshang las 'byung /
NK125(co)003:2838: de nas stag lo la yon mchod bka' bgros nas
NK125(co)003:2839: gsang ste tshe dbang bskur bas mi lo bcu gsum
NK125(co)003:2840: bsrings / slob dpon pad+ma dang bee ros gzi ldan 'bar ba mtshams kyi rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2841: zhi ba dam pa lha rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2842: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2845: lha mo go la ma'i rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2852: bdud rtsi rol pa che chung /
NK125(co)003:2854: phur pa bi to ta ma la'i cha lag sum cu so drug /
NK125(co)003:2857: shes pa sdong gis brgyan pa'i rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2861: stobs po che yongs sgrol gyi rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2862: thig le bde ba gnas rgyud /
NK125(co)003:2864: sbyin sreg gi rgyud za byed rol pa /
NK125(co)003:2867: zhing bcu rol pa'i rgyud rnams bsgyur ro //
NK125(co)003:2868: ma h+aa ya ga'i skor de rnams dang /
NK125(co)003:2869: a nu yo ga la kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo /
NK125(co)003:2871: dur khrod khu byug rol pa /
NK125(co)003:2872: sems lung chen mo ste mdo bzhi bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2873: gzhan yang sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK125(co)003:2885: de rnams kyi rgya dpe sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na bzhugs pa /
NK125(co)003:2886: slob dpon pad+mas rdzu 'phrul gyis skad cig gcig la blangs nas bsgyur te /
NK125(co)003:2887: dpe rnams bsam yas kyi ke tshang na bzhugs te rgya gar na med do //
NK125(co)003:2888: mkhan po bo d+hi sat+wasa mdo phyogs dang /
NK125(co)003:2889: sngags phyi pa mang du bsgyur ro //
NK125(co)003:2890: de nas mnga' bdag gis slob dpon gnyis kyis lung
NK125(co)003:2891: 'dren mdzad pa'i chos thams cad bod du dar bar
NK125(co)003:2892: bzhed de / de rnams len par btang ba ni /
NK125(co)003:2893: bee ro tsa na rdzogs pa chen po len par btang /
NK125(co)003:2898: 'bre rgyal ba'i blo gros dang lnga btang nas /
NK125(co)003:2899: slob dpon h'u ka ra las /
NK125(co)003:2900: dpal yang dag gi chos skor blangs /
NK125(co)003:2901: rlangs dpal seng lam du 'das kyang /
NK125(co)003:2902: dge slong mi bzhis grub pa thob /
NK125(co)003:2903: nam mkha'i snying pos rang gi brang kha gri gus
NK125(co)003:2904: phye nas khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs rgyal po la
NK125(co)003:2905: bstan pas / chos tshig dang don dang lha dang
NK125(co)003:2906: gsum mthun te rgyal pos dbang dang chos rnams zhus
NK125(co)003:2907: bstan pas / / skabs der blon po rnams kyis
NK125(co)003:2908: dge slong mi lngas rlangs dpal seng lam du bsad
NK125(co)003:2909: do zer phra mas nam mkha'i snying po lho brag
NK125(co)003:2911: dus der mkhan po bo d+hi sat+wa las sad mi
NK125(co)003:2912: mi bdun rab tu byung nas chos 'tshol bar btang
NK125(co)003:2913: zhes thang yig na bshad de /
NK125(co)003:2914: don du na rong zom gyi bzhed pa ltar bod
NK125(co)003:2915: du gsang sngags kyi babs bdun zhes pa'i babs gnyis
NK125(co)003:2916: pa ni sngar brjod pa'i dge slong nam mkha'i snying
NK125(co)003:2917: pos blangs pa'i yang dag gi chos skor yin /
NK125(co)003:2918: babs gsum pa slob dpon shit+nam gar+b+ha bsam yas kyi rab gnas la phebs dus /
NK125(co)003:2920: gzungs gtsug tor sde lnga sgrub thabs dang bcas pa bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2921: babs bzhi pa slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba gangs ti ser phebs /
NK125(co)003:2925: 'jam dpal go cha rnams btang nas spyan drangs pas /
NK125(co)003:2927: sba tshab kyis lo ts+aa byas nas /
NK125(co)003:2929: yo ga a ba ta ra /
NK125(co)003:2930: nang gi chos sgyu 'phrul lam rim /
NK125(co)003:2931: zhi ba d+r+wa chen d+r+wa chung /
NK125(co)003:2933: phreng lung rnams bsgyur te rgyal po la bskur ro //
NK125(co)003:2934: babs dang po ni sngar smos pa'i slob dpon pad+mas gsungs pa rnams so //
NK125(co)003:2935: babs lnga pa ni sh+r+ai seng+ha spyan drangs pas ma byon te /
NK125(co)003:2936: bee ro la gnang ba'i chos rnams yin /
NK125(co)003:2937: babs drug pa ni slob dpon bi ma la'i chos rnams yin /
NK125(co)003:2939: mnga' bdag mu ne btsan po gshegs pa'i rjes la
NK125(co)003:2940: slob dpon bi ma la mdo khams kyi thung byams
NK125(co)003:2941: chen nas spyan drangs te de dus gsungs pa rnams
NK125(co)003:2942: yin te / de'i chos kyi rnam grangs ni 'og tu 'chad do //
NK125(co)003:2943: de la bee ro tsa na rgya gar nas byon te rgyu 'bras kyi chos mang du bsgyur te /
NK125(co)003:2944: sher phyin 'bum la byams zhus rtag zhus dang mtshan 'bum bsdoms pas bam po dgu ma gtogs bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2945: po ti bcu gnyis la rgyal po'i bla 'bum sha sgro can du grags /
NK125(co)003:2946: lang kar gshegs pa bam po bco lnga pa /
NK125(co)003:2947: phal po che bam po brgyad /
NK125(co)003:2948: myang 'das la bam po nyis brgya dang sum cu kha ma long ste de rnams bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:2949: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po byang chub sems la rtsa ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK125(co)003:2950: yan lag gi rgyud sde bdun /
NK125(co)003:2951: bshad pa'i rgyud sde bzhi ste bcu drug /
NK125(co)003:2952: rtsa ba'i rgyud sde lnga nas gyes pa'i man ngag
NK125(co)003:2953: gi rgyud sde lnga ste nyi shu rtsa gcig bsgyur
NK125(co)003:2954: ro // de nas btsun mo dang sdig blon rnams gros mol te /
NK125(co)003:2955: rgyal po ni lho bal gyi skad kho na la
NK125(co)003:2956: dga' nas rgyal srid nyams te bod sil bur 'gro
NK125(co)003:2957: bas / ban+d+he bee ro tsa na rab tu bsad /
NK125(co)003:2958: tha ma spyugs zhes rgyal pos thabs mdzad kyang ma thub ste tsha ba rong du spyugs /
NK125(co)003:2959: bee ros tsha ba rong gi yul khams chos la bkod /
NK125(co)003:2960: g.yu sgra snying po gtsang legs grub kyi skye ba
NK125(co)003:2961: yin pas sngon gyi las 'phros mkhas grub chen por
NK125(co)003:2962: gyur to // de nas slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK125(co)003:2963: bee ro'i chos 'phro gsungs pa la bi ma la spyan drangs /
NK125(co)003:2969: la gsum rgyal ba byang chub dang lnga yin par byas 'dug /
NK125(co)003:2971: rgya gar gyi phra mas rgyal blon rnams kyis phyi nang gang yin the tshom pa la /
NK125(co)003:2972: lder so bshig gso'i rdzu 'phrul gyis yid ches nas dbu'i mchod gnas su bkur /
NK125(co)003:2973: pan+di ta phebs pa'i gtam de bee ros gsan nas /
NK125(co)003:2974: g.yu sgra la yog bsdur du btang /
NK125(co)003:2975: der bi ma las rtsod pa yang g.yu sgra rgyal ba ltar byas /
NK125(co)003:2976: rdzu 'phrul kyang g.yu sgra che ba ltar mdzad nas
NK125(co)003:2977: bee ro la basngagasa pa mang du mdzad pas rgyal
NK125(co)003:2978: blon 'gyod de bee ro spyan drangs /
NK125(co)003:2979: bi ma las nyin bzhin rgyu 'bras kyi chos /
NK125(co)003:2980: mtshan bzhin gsang sngags gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:2981: lo ts+aa ba ni rma gnyags gnyis dang ska cog gnyis so //
NK125(co)003:2982: de la sems phyogs la phyi 'gyur bcu gsum /
NK125(co)003:2986: phra mo sum cu rtsa gcig /
NK125(co)003:2987: lung phran bdun cu rtsa lnga la sogs pa bsgyur te /
NK125(co)003:2997: phra mo sum cu rtsa gcig ni sgyu 'phrul gyi cha lag ste /
NK125(co)003:2998: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las phye ba dang po
NK125(co)003:2999: de kho na nyid lta ba bstan pa'i man ngag
NK125(co)003:3003: la shan lta ba'i sgron ma /
NK125(co)003:3005: 'dzin chags med pa spyod pa'i man ngag ni /
NK125(co)003:3006: spyod pa bsdus pa'i sgron ma /
NK125(co)003:3011: rdo rje las rim gyi stod /
NK125(co)003:3016: gsal bkra nyi shu brgyad pa /
NK125(co)003:3020: lta ba'i khrus lung rgyal mtshan dang lnga'o //
NK125(co)003:3024: sku gdung las 'brel dang gsum mo //
NK125(co)003:3025: don du gnyer sgrub pa la /
NK125(co)003:3027: zhi ba las rim gyi skor d+r+wa ba che chung /
NK125(co)003:3030: khro bo dam pa rgyan dang /
NK125(co)003:3038: mi g.yo ba ting nge 'dzin bskyed rdzogs kyi khongs su 'adu'o //
NK125(co)003:3039: 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag rgya ni /
NK125(co)003:3041: zlos pa sngags te bskyed rim du 'adu'o //
NK125(co)003:3042: gnas su stob pa mchod pa ni /
NK125(co)003:3043: zhi khro'i phrin las kyi khongs su 'du ba'o //
NK125(co)003:3044: lung phran bdun cu rtsa lnga ni /
NK125(co)003:3045: mdo dgongs 'dus kyi cha lag ste /
NK125(co)003:3048: spyi mdo dgongs 'dus la 'grel pa bdun /
NK125(co)003:3049: mdo bzhi la 'grel pa re re'o //
NK125(co)003:3050: rtog dpyod kyi rjes la 'jug pa lta ba ston pa lung phran bcu /
NK125(co)003:3051: don gyi rjes su 'jug pa mi rtog pa bsgom
NK125(co)003:3052: pa bsam gtan gyi sgron ma las mi rtog pa
NK125(co)003:3053: bsgom pa'i thabs nyi shu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa
NK125(co)003:3054: bsdu na mdo phran rnam pa bcu ste nyi shu
NK125(co)003:3055: / yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa mtshan ma lha'i
NK125(co)003:3056: rnal 'byor bsgom pa la bcu gcig ste sum cu
NK125(co)003:3057: / so gcig / bkod pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa dgu ste bzhi bcu /
NK125(co)003:3058: rim pa bgrod pa dbang gi man ngag bco lnga ste nga lnga /
NK125(co)003:3059: mi 'da' ba dam tshig la bco lnga ste bdun cu /
NK125(co)003:3060: rol pa phrin las la lung phran bdun te /
NK125(co)003:3061: bdun cu rtsa bdun po a nu yo ga'i skor ro //
NK125(co)003:3062: rdzogs pa chen po man ngag gi sde ni /
NK125(co)003:3066: snying tig la sogs pa'i man ngag brgya bcu dgur mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:3067: nyang ting 'dzin bzang po la sogs pa la gnang /
NK125(co)003:3068: gzhan yang sems sde nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs pa bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:3069: rgyud bcu bdun gyi 'grel pa rnams kyang bsgyur te /
NK125(co)003:3070: da lta long po na 'dug pa la po ti bdun bzhugs zer ro //
NK125(co)003:3071: de nas slob dpon pad+mas bsam yas mchims phur rje
NK125(co)003:3072: 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga la sgrub pa bka' brgyad
NK125(co)003:3074: bka' babs kyi slob ma brgyad sgrub gnas brgyad du bsgrub pa la btang ste /
NK125(co)003:3075: sgrags yang rdzong du sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed bsgrubs pas /
NK125(co)003:3076: zhag nyer gcig na yi dam gyi zhal mthong ste /
NK125(co)003:3079: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyis bsam yas mchims
NK125(co)003:3080: phur dbang chen bsgrubs pas rang lus yi dam lha
NK125(co)003:3081: ru gyur te spyi gtsug gi rta mgos rta skad
NK125(co)003:3082: grags / dge slong nam mkha'i snying pos lho brag
NK125(co)003:3083: mkhar chur yang dag grub ste nyi zer la zhon
NK125(co)003:3084: grags / / gnyags dz+ny+aa nas che mchog grub pas
NK125(co)003:3085: yar lung shel brag tu brag la mdzub mos bdud
NK125(co)003:3086: grags / / rtsi bton / mkhar chen bza' mtsho
NK125(co)003:3087: rgyal gyis mon kha ne ring seng ge rdzong gsum
NK125(co)003:3088: du phur pa grub ste brag la phur pa btab
NK125(co)003:3089: grags / / rtsi bton / / der phur pa
NK125(co)003:3090: 'phur te song ba khang pa'i ltag na skyer phung
NK125(co)003:3091: gcig la pha mes kyi za 'dre zhig gnas pa
NK125(co)003:3092: grags / / rtsi bton / / de la zug
NK125(co)003:3093: / phur pa thon pa'i shul na khrag dmar tsar
NK125(co)003:3094: grags / / rtsi bton / / de la zug
NK125(co)003:3095: / gyis byung / za 'dre thul bas dbon brgyud
NK125(co)003:3096: rnams la'ang mkhar chen za 'dre 'dul gyi brgyud pa
NK125(co)003:3097: grags / / rtsi bton / / de la zug
NK125(co)003:3098: / gyis byung / zhes grags / 'brog mi dpal
NK125(co)003:3099: gyi ye shes kyis yar stod sham po gangs su
NK125(co)003:3100: ma mo grub pas las kyi ma mo dngos su
NK125(co)003:3101: grags / / rtsi bton / / de la zug
NK125(co)003:3102: / gyis byung / zhes grags / bran du 'khol
NK125(co)003:3103: / rlangs dpal gyi seng ge phyi mas spa gro
NK125(co)003:3104: stag tshang du dregs pa kun 'dul grub pas lha
NK125(co)003:3105: srin las la bcol tshad bsgrub pa byung /
NK125(co)003:3106: bee ro tsa nas brag dmar g.ya' ma lung du
NK125(co)003:3107: drag sngags grub ste dmod pa bor ba tsam gyis
NK125(co)003:3109: mnga' bdag gi ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag
NK125(co)003:3110: pas gang gis kyang g.yo bar mi nus pa thob
NK125(co)003:3112: g.yu sgra snying pos rtogs pa mngon du gyur /
NK125(co)003:3113: sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms nam mkha' la rlung ltar 'phyo /
NK125(co)003:3114: sba ye shes dbyangs kyis mkha' spyod 'grub /
NK125(co)003:3115: sog po lha dpal gyi ye shes kyis gcan gzan rnams gnya' ba nas 'dzin /
NK125(co)003:3116: ldan ma rtse mang gis mi brjed pa'i gzungs rnams thob /
NK125(co)003:3117: ska ba dpal brtsegs mngon shes dang ldan /
NK125(co)003:3118: shud bu dpal gyi seng ges gtsang po nyi ma
NK125(co)003:3119: phyed du gyen la slog /'bre rgyal ba'i blo gros
NK125(co)003:3120: kyis ro langs gser du bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:3121: khye'u chung lo ts+aa bas nam mkha' la bya 'phur pa phyag gis 'dzin /
NK125(co)003:3122: dran pa nam mkha' byang gi 'brong dgug /
NK125(co)003:3123: rma rin chen mchog gis pha bong zas su za /
NK125(co)003:3124: sna nam ye shes sdes nam mkha' la 'phur /
NK125(co)003:3125: 'o bran dbang phyug chu la nya ltar 'phyo /
NK125(co)003:3126: lha lung dpal gyi rdo rjes ri brag la thogs pa med par 'dzul /
NK125(co)003:3127: lang gro dkon mchog 'byung gnas kyis gnam lcags thog mda' 'phen /
NK125(co)003:3128: la gsum rgyal ba byang chub kyis nam mkha' la
NK125(co)003:3129: rdo rje skyil krung bca' ba la sogs pa so
NK125(co)003:3130: sos grub rtags mang du bstan te /
NK125(co)003:3131: sngar bsam yas sa 'dul mdzad pa'i skabs der rje 'bangs nyer gcig dang /
NK125(co)003:3132: dus 'dir nyi shu rtsa lnga byung yang /
NK125(co)003:3133: la la snga ma'i khrod nas 'dir byung ba'ang yod do //
NK125(co)003:3134: de nas 'chims phu'i sgrub phug tu nub gcig na
NK125(co)003:3135: pe har ru 'dren sde bzhi 'bag seng gar mkhan
NK125(co)003:3136: la sogs pa'i 'khor dang bcas pa lhags /
NK125(co)003:3137: phug pa'i steng du gnam rdo lug tsam zhig phab /
NK125(co)003:3140: slob dpon kyang ting nge 'dzin yud cig shor /
NK125(co)003:3141: jo mo mtsho rgyal la sogs pa 'khor rnams dran med du brgyal /
NK125(co)003:3142: der slob dpon gu ru drag por bzhengs nas kho 'khor bcas dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:3143: bod kyi lha khang thams cad kyi dkor bsrung ba'i gnyer gtad pa zhal gyis bzhes /
NK125(co)003:3144: de nas bsam yas su phebs /
NK125(co)003:3146: bsam yas kyi srung ma la /
NK125(co)003:3147: bdud ni srog gcod pa la dga'/
NK125(co)003:3155: rje la dbon sras bdud kyi sprul pa 'byung bas des chos bsnub /
NK125(co)003:3156: gdung rabs bcu nas hor gyi bstan pa dang dmag 'ong /
NK125(co)003:3157: pe har la gtad na lha khang mi 'jig pas /
NK125(co)003:3158: nga yis pe har gling du rten bya yi /
NK125(co)003:3159: 'ba' ta hor gyi sgom grwa choms la lha cha khyer 'ong dgos gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3160: pe har gyi 'dra 'bag kyang lha khang pe har gyi gling du mdzad /
NK125(co)003:3161: de'i skabs shed du mnga' bdag nyid zhang rgya tsha
NK125(co)003:3162: lha snang dang 'dzam gling sum gnyis dbang du bsdu
NK125(co)003:3163: ba'i bka' bgros mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:3164: lha sras mu rub btsan po yum gyis btang ngo yang zer /
NK125(co)003:3165: o rgyan gling pa'i zhi khro bka' brgyad 'dus pa nas ni /
NK125(co)003:3166: spyugs mkhan cher dge sbrang ma'i mchu can bya bas /
NK125(co)003:3167: rgyal bu rang la dug gtong ngam /
NK125(co)003:3169: gang rung gcig byed par 'dug pas rtog cig byas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3170: rgyal bus rgyal blon bka' gros kyi sar phyin /
NK125(co)003:3171: zhang gi bus sgo bsrung ste /
NK125(co)003:3172: rgyal blon bka' bgros bdog pas dar cig bzhugs byas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3174: pha'i gam du bu 'ong sa med dam zer te ral gri bsnun nas zhang gi bu bsad /
NK125(co)003:3175: bka' gros tshar nas zhang nang nas byung ste /
NK125(co)003:3176: bu'i mgo bregs te dkar zhal thang du sa la lan gsum brdab /
NK125(co)003:3178: bar snang la lan gsum skyogs pas /
NK125(co)003:3180: blon po byings kun rje blon 'khrugs pa chen po lang dogs nas skrag /
NK125(co)003:3181: de'i zhal lce gzhan sus kyang mi chod pas /
NK125(co)003:3182: blon po 'gos phag ri nas bos /
NK125(co)003:3183: 'gos rgan na so rgas pas drod mi la re
NK125(co)003:3184: ba'i tshul gyis bu mo gzhon nu ma gnyis kyi
NK125(co)003:3185: bar du sha drod la bcar te gzhung ko byas
NK125(co)003:3187: der zhal lce 'dar gsum dang dga' gsum byung ste /
NK125(co)003:3189: ngas de ring shar sgor phyin pas mi kun mthun
NK125(co)003:3190: par rjes 'bangs bsad na lang ba mi yong zer
NK125(co)003:3193: mi kun lab par rjes 'bangs bsad pa la sus ci bya zer byas pas blon po 'dar /
NK125(co)003:3194: 'bangs byings po 'khrug pa langs dogs pas 'dar /
NK125(co)003:3195: de nas skabs shig gi tshe sgo la yi ge sbyar te /
NK125(co)003:3196: ngas zhal lce mi chod par 'dug go //
NK125(co)003:3197: 'on kyang zur mkhar mad'i tho la dris zer /
NK125(co)003:3198: der rje 'bangs thams cad ha las te rgyugs pas /
NK125(co)003:3199: zur mkhar mad'i tho la rjes 'bangs bsad pa la sus ci bya zer bas rje dga'/
NK125(co)003:3200: 'on kyang tho gong ma la dris zer /
NK125(co)003:3201: tho de la rjes 'bangs bsad na lang ba mi yong /
NK125(co)003:3202: 'on kyang tho gong ma la dris zer bas zhang dga'/
NK125(co)003:3204: sras mu rub btsan po mtha' 'dul ba'i dmag la lo dgur thong /
NK125(co)003:3205: zhang gi bu'i stong la am bag gi wa chu gang sbyin /
NK125(co)003:3206: rje 'bangs byings rnams bder chug zer bas thams cad dga' ste /
NK125(co)003:3207: zhang gi bu'i stong la grwa dol gzhung gsum byin /
NK125(co)003:3208: grwa dol gzhung gsum la rje med zer ba'i gtam yang de yin zer /
NK125(co)003:3209: de nas sras mu rub btsan po byang phyogs kyi dmag la gtong ba'i dus su /
NK125(co)003:3213: ka ma la sh+ai la sogs bla mchod brgya dang lnga bcu /
NK125(co)003:3214: gu ru'i thugs kyi sras brgyad la sogs pa dbu rtse'i bar khang du spyan drangs /
NK125(co)003:3215: lha sras kyi mchod pa rgya chen po dang /
NK125(co)003:3216: bar khang gi rnga khang mdor tshogs gtor rgya chen po bshams /
NK125(co)003:3217: lha sras kyis lo pan rnams la zhus pa /
NK125(co)003:3218: bdag byang phyogs kyi yul khams khri don brgyad dang /
NK125(co)003:3219: phyogs thams cad du dmag dpon la gtong na /
NK125(co)003:3220: bdag dang dmag sde thams cad tshe srog la bar chad med par /
NK125(co)003:3221: phyogs kyi so kha thams cad thul nas yab rgyal po'i dgongs pa rdzogs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3222: sa phyogs thams cad du bde legs 'byung ba'i thabs dang rten 'brel mdzad dgos /
NK125(co)003:3224: yab rgyal pos thog drangs der 'dus pa thams cad
NK125(co)003:3225: kyis slob dpon pad+ma la de ltar du gsol ba
NK125(co)003:3227: rgyal po yab sras kyi thugs dgongs sgrub phyir de ltar bya'o gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3228: mdun gyi nam mkha' la rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras rta bdag brgyad /
NK125(co)003:3229: las sgrub par byed pa'i mgo brnyan sna tshogs dang
NK125(co)003:3230: bcas pa gnod sbyin thams cad nam mkhar bkug ste
NK125(co)003:3231: / yon mchod rnams la mngon sum du bstan nas bka' bsgos /
NK125(co)003:3232: rgyal bu 'di la lus dang grib ma ltar 'grogs
NK125(co)003:3233: nas ngas ji ltar bsgos pa ltar las gyis shig
NK125(co)003:3234: gsungs / de dus ji ltar gzigs pa bzhin mtha'
NK125(co)003:3235: mi mgon brtson gyis phyar dar chen mo 'di bris
NK125(co)003:3236: nas lo pan kun gyis rab gnas mdzad /
NK125(co)003:3237: rnam sras 'khor bcas kyis rgyal bu'i bzhed pa thams cad sgrub par khas blangs /
NK125(co)003:3238: de nas yab kyis phyogs thams cad du pho nya bkyes te /
NK125(co)003:3239: zla ba tshes grangs kyi dus btab nas dbyar mo thang du dmag thams cad 'dzoms par byas /
NK125(co)003:3240: me sgyogs chu sgyogs la sogs pa dmag chas thams cad gsar nas dbyar mo thang du tshogs /
NK125(co)003:3241: der rgya zam chen po gcig gi rngas su lcags
NK125(co)003:3242: phag gi made'u brtsigs te de'i steng du rgyal bu
NK125(co)003:3244: zhang blon chen po lha bzang klu dpal gyis rgya
NK125(co)003:3245: zam de la dmag rnams bshar nas grangs la btab
NK125(co)003:3246: pa'i dus der / shar phyogs bya khra'i rgyal khams
NK125(co)003:3247: kyi dmag yin zer ba lus po mi la bya
NK125(co)003:3248: khra'i gdong pa yod pa dar re'i shul la khri
NK125(co)003:3249: tsho re 'brang ba dar tsho dgu byung /
NK125(co)003:3250: lho phyogs grul bum rkang rtse'i rgyal khams kyi dmag
NK125(co)003:3251: yin zer ba ro stod mi la rta bong gi
NK125(co)003:3252: rkang sug yod pa dar re'i phyi la khri tsho
NK125(co)003:3253: re 'brang ba dar tsho bcu byung /
NK125(co)003:3254: nub phyogs byi la mjug ma can gyi dmag yin
NK125(co)003:3255: zer ba mi lus byi la'i mjug ma yod pa
NK125(co)003:3256: ko ba'i phub khyer ba gcer bu smyug mdung thogs
NK125(co)003:3257: pa dar re'i phyi la khri tsho re 'brang ba
NK125(co)003:3259: byang phyogs rna bo che bong bu'i rgyal khams nas
NK125(co)003:3260: yin zer ba mi lus bong bu'i rna ba can
NK125(co)003:3261: dar re'i phyi la khri tsho re 'brang ba dar
NK125(co)003:3263: de rnams mthong ba'i mod la rgyal bu gad mo shor /
NK125(co)003:3265: phyogs kyi dgra thams cad thul bar 'dug zer /
NK125(co)003:3266: de nas gru gu'i yul dang /
NK125(co)003:3267: rgya nag gi yul khams thams cad bcom /
NK125(co)003:3268: hor gyi sgom grwa bar pa bcom nas /
NK125(co)003:3270: shing dung dkar po rgyang grags dang /
NK125(co)003:3271: cha lang dang ba dre rdog la sogs pa dkor cha thams cad khyer /
NK125(co)003:3272: rgyal po pe har gyi sku dang /
NK125(co)003:3274: gnod sbyin tsi dmar gyi bswe 'bag smug chung gdan drangs /
NK125(co)003:3275: dmag rdzas chen po dang bcas te rgyal bu yar byon /
NK125(co)003:3276: blon chen po lha bzang klu dpal dmag sde 'ga' zhig dang bcas pa khri stan 'dul bar bkod /
NK125(co)003:3277: rgyal bus dmag rdzas rnams yab la phul /
NK125(co)003:3278: dmag la 'gro ba'i dus dgung lo nyer lnga yin /
NK125(co)003:3279: sum cu so lnga bzhes dus yar byon /
NK125(co)003:3280: mchims phur slob dpon pad+ma'i drung du sdig pa bshags /
NK125(co)003:3281: rdo rje phur pa'i zhal gzigs /
NK125(co)003:3282: yab rgyal po'i dgongs pa mthar phyin /
NK125(co)003:3283: so kha thams cad mu rub btsan pos btul ba'i
NK125(co)003:3284: lo rgyus 'dan ma rtse mang gis yi ger bkod
NK125(co)003:3285: ces rnam sras sprin gseb ma'i lo rgyus su 'byung
NK125(co)003:3286: la / ljang yul ma'i lo rgyus su /
NK125(co)003:3287: der rgyal po pe har skrag ste bya rgod thang
NK125(co)003:3288: dkar du sprul te nam mkha' la bros pa dang
NK125(co)003:3289: / rgyal chen rnam thos sras 'khor dang bcas pa'i dmag gis ded /
NK125(co)003:3290: gnod sbyin drag po zhig gis mda' 'phangs pas /
NK125(co)003:3291: bya rgod de'i gshog par la song nas sa la lhung nas /
NK125(co)003:3292: rnam sras 'khor dang bcas pas bsam yas su bskyal nas bzhag ces zer /
NK125(co)003:3293: de nas zhang rgya tsha lha snang 'phrul che bas
NK125(co)003:3294: rgyal bu bsad kyis dogs nas byang kong du spyugs
NK125(co)003:3295: / kong po'i mchims gad pa skya bor thugs dam
NK125(co)003:3296: gyi lha khang bzhengs pa ding sang yang yod la
NK125(co)003:3297: / / de dus kyi phyar dar de ni bsam
NK125(co)003:3298: yas kyi bang mdzod nas 'khyar te da lta chos
NK125(co)003:3300: bswe 'bag dang shing dung bsam yas la yod /
NK125(co)003:3301: rnam sras kyi 'chams sku ni da lta bya rgod gshongs na bzhugs pa 'di yin no //
NK125(co)003:3302: de nas ring por ma lon pa zhig na mdo
NK125(co)003:3303: khams smad kyi sde dpon 'u ra bkra shis bya
NK125(co)003:3304: ba dmag khri tsho lnga yod pa de rgya nag
NK125(co)003:3306: mnga' ris stod na zhang zhung ha la 'bar bya
NK125(co)003:3307: ba de bon po lnga brgya tsam gyi dpon yin
NK125(co)003:3308: pa mu stegs gu lang la ngo log /
NK125(co)003:3310: gzhan yang log pa byed pa 'ga' byung bas /
NK125(co)003:3311: mnga' bdag btsan po thugs ma bde ste /
NK125(co)003:3312: slob dpon pad+ma sgrags yang rdzong na bzhugs pas der byon nas /
NK125(co)003:3313: kyee slob dpon chen po lags /
NK125(co)003:3314: bdag rgyal pos mnga' thang chos bzhin bskyangs pas mi 'khyongs par /
NK125(co)003:3315: 'bangs blo log pas rgyal khrims dang srid 'jig par byed pa la ji ltar bgyi zhes zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:3316: mnga' bdag btsan po gson cig /'bangs ngo log byed pa rgyal po'i dgra /
NK125(co)003:3317: slob ma dam nyams byed pa slob dpon gyi dgra /
NK125(co)003:3318: ma rabs bdab gshog rgyas na ya rabs kyi dgra yin pas /
NK125(co)003:3319: de la gshed kyi thod pa 'tshal lo gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3320: kham pa ngo log gi ling+ga gri khrag gis bris nas spyang ki'i thod pa bcug /
NK125(co)003:3321: bon po'i ling ga ram gyis bris te khyi thod du bcug nas mkhar gyi rmangs su sbas /
NK125(co)003:3322: steng nas rgyal po'i phyags lhwam gyis mnan pas zla
NK125(co)003:3323: ba gsum song ba na de gnyis kas rgyal pos
NK125(co)003:3324: ci gsungs nyan pa'i khas len dang dam bca' byung
NK125(co)003:3325: / rgyal srid mtha' nas zags pa rang gi dbang du 'dus so //
NK125(co)003:3326: yang gnyal gyi yul du grags pa so yon dang /
NK125(co)003:3327: mgon po ngo ral bya ba spun gnyis pha'i nor gzhi la ma 'cham ste /
NK125(co)003:3329: rgyal pos chad pa 'bebs pa'ang dka' bar byung bas /
NK125(co)003:3330: de la ji ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:3331: pha dang bu 'thab ma dang bu mo 'thab //
NK125(co)003:3332: de ni phung srid khyim du zhugs pa yin //
NK125(co)003:3333: de la wa dar ma'i thod pa 'tshal lo gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:3334: gro ga la spun nang 'thab pa'i gzugs bris te /
NK125(co)003:3335: bung ba khyo shugs gnyis kyi rwa dang lhan du bstums te /
NK125(co)003:3336: ri rgyud bzang po'i sa 'jam po la sbas nas grogs mdza' mthun gyi gos blangs te mnan pas /
NK125(co)003:3337: gnyal pa spun gnyis 'thab pa'i dme shi la thug pa de sos /
NK125(co)003:3338: sngar 'thab pa la 'gyod de shin tu mdza' zhing mthun par gyur to //
NK125(co)003:3339: yang sngon bod kyi rgyal po'i so mtshams /
NK125(co)003:3340: shar rma ri smug po'i rgyud tshun chad /
NK125(co)003:3341: lho gangs ri brtsegs pa'i rgyud tshun chad /
NK125(co)003:3342: nub stag sha dung gi sgo mo man chad /
NK125(co)003:3343: byang chags po gangs kyi ra ba tshun chad yin pa la /
NK125(co)003:3344: dpal bsam yas mnga' gsol grub pa dang thams cad dad cing 'dun par gyur te /
NK125(co)003:3347: stag gzig la sogs pa mang po dbang du 'dus /
NK125(co)003:3348: yab mes kyi mnga' thang las bdun 'gyur du 'phel ba dang /
NK125(co)003:3349: byang ge sar dmar gi rgyal po li ha ra bya bas /
NK125(co)003:3350: 'dzam bu gling thams cad bod kyi rgyal pos mnga'
NK125(co)003:3351: 'og tu bsdus nas ge sar gyi yul 'joms su
NK125(co)003:3354: phyogs bzhir rkang mgyogs bkye bas rigs bzhi'i rgyal po
NK125(co)003:3355: dbang du ma 'dus pa shes nas so so la
NK125(co)003:3357: shar rgya nag rtsis kyi rgyal po /
NK125(co)003:3358: lho rgya gar chos kyi rgyal po /
NK125(co)003:3359: nub stag gzig nor gyi rgyal po /
NK125(co)003:3360: byang ge sar dmag gi rgyal po dang bzhi 'dzam bu gling na dbang che ba la /
NK125(co)003:3361: bod mtha' 'khob kha ba can gyi yul bya ba zhig chags /
NK125(co)003:3362: der glo brdol gyi mi gcig la rgyal po'i tha snyad du btags nas /
NK125(co)003:3363: da lta phyogs bzhi rgyal po'i mnga' thang 'phrog /'di myur du ma btul na /
NK125(co)003:3364: spre'u gar yan du btang ba dpa' bo stag gi
NK125(co)003:3365: gong du rgyug par 'dug pas phyogs bzhi nas dmag
NK125(co)003:3366: 'tshogs / zhes pa'i ngan bgros byas nas /
NK125(co)003:3367: shar tsong kha nas rgya nag gi dmag 'bum phrag brgyad 'jug pa /
NK125(co)003:3368: lho gnyal gyi gting nas rgya gar shar phyogs kyi dmag go rdol gsum 'jug pa /
NK125(co)003:3369: nub dmar ri nyal ba'i shar nas stag gzig gi dmag gar phrom gyi 'bum phrag brgyad 'jug pa /
NK125(co)003:3370: byang chags po ri gangs kyi ra ba'i 'dabs nas
NK125(co)003:3371: khrom ge sar gyi dmag dung phyur gcig 'jug pa
NK125(co)003:3373: der bya lo dpyid zla tha ma nas dmag skad kyis 'ur langs te /
NK125(co)003:3374: bsam yas su rgyal blon kun tshogs te bka' bgros
NK125(co)003:3375: pas blo 'tshabs nas gros sna tshogs su gyur te
NK125(co)003:3377: la la ngo phar lta zer /
NK125(co)003:3378: phal cher lho brag la 'bros zer /
NK125(co)003:3379: chos kyi blon po na re /
NK125(co)003:3382: 'bros pas mi thar stong 'bros sam khri 'bros /
NK125(co)003:3383: bod kyi rgyal khams kun 'bros dgos pa la /
NK125(co)003:3384: blo chung mi bcu lta bu'i gros kyis mi yong /
NK125(co)003:3385: bod rje 'bangs kyi 'dun ma dkon mchog gsum la dris zer ro //
NK125(co)003:3386: der bsam yas mchims phu na slob dpon pad+ma bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar byon te /
NK125(co)003:3387: gong gi lo rgyus zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:3389: mtha' bzhi dmag tu rgyug na dbus la ngan /
NK125(co)003:3390: gcan gzan dpung chen 'thab na sder chags thams cad brlag /
NK125(co)003:3391: mang po gros su mthun na ri bo rmangs nas bshig bya ba yin /
NK125(co)003:3393: sems can sna tshogs kyi thod pa tshol cig gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3394: phyogs bzhi'i dmag dpon dang dmag mi'i bla byang bris te /
NK125(co)003:3395: rgya mi mang bong bu gwa pa'i thod par bcug ste rabs chad kyi thod pas mnan /
NK125(co)003:3396: lho sog po gar log gi dmag dug sbrul gyi thod par bcug nas 'ug pa'i thod pas mnan /
NK125(co)003:3397: nub stag gzig klong brdol gyi dmag sa'i thod par bcug nas glag gi thod pas mnan /
NK125(co)003:3398: byang ge sar dpa' bo'i dmag gri rgod kyi thod
NK125(co)003:3399: par bcug nas dred kyi thod pas mnan te phyogs
NK125(co)003:3400: bzhi'i ngo lon chen po bzhi la sbas so //
NK125(co)003:3402: bod kyi rgyal po rigs gang yin /
NK125(co)003:3403: spyod pa ci byed dris pas /
NK125(co)003:3404: rigs rgya gar chos kyi rgyal po'i rigs nas chad /
NK125(co)003:3405: spyod pa dge ba'i las spyod zer ba thos pas /
NK125(co)003:3407: blo dkon mchog gsum la gtad yod /
NK125(co)003:3408: mnga' thang yang dpung dang gdug rtsub kyis ma bsdus /
NK125(co)003:3409: mos shing dad pas 'dus song bar 'dug pas gzhan gyis mi thub /
NK125(co)003:3410: da dmag rang sar gyes zer ro //
NK125(co)003:3411: de nas byi ba'i lo la 'dzam gling rgyal po rigs bzhis 'bul ba dang phyag mchod byung ste /
NK125(co)003:3412: 'dzam bu gling gi sum gnyis dbang du 'dus so //
NK125(co)003:3413: dus der ma 'ongs pa na bod la dgos par
NK125(co)003:3414: dgongs nas bod la phan pa'i man ngag brgya rtsa
NK125(co)003:3415: brgyad mdzad de gter du sbas so //
NK125(co)003:3416: skabs der rgyal pos chos dang bon gnyis ka dar bar mdzad pas /
NK125(co)003:3417: blon pos bon la gshin chog byas pas gshin po
NK125(co)003:3418: dngos su byung ba la sogs pa la rje 'bangs
NK125(co)003:3419: kun yid ches / der slob dpon pad+mas rgyal po la phyag mtshan gyi rdo rje bskur te /
NK125(co)003:3420: dbang bskur ba'i gsang mtshan drir bcug /
NK125(co)003:3422: rdo rje ston la 'byung po rang gzugs ston gyis shig gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3423: rgyal pos byon nas gsang mtshan dris pas /
NK125(co)003:3426: slob dpon pad+mas rgya mtsho pha rol du 'phangs pa yin /
NK125(co)003:3427: de min nga dang kho 'bral ma myong zer /
NK125(co)003:3428: der rgyal pos rdo rje bstan pas /
NK125(co)003:3429: de ma ston dang des nga brdung ba ci ka yin zer te /
NK125(co)003:3430: mtshan byang de rgad po slob hrul gyon pa zhig
NK125(co)003:3431: tu song nas blon po'i srog gcod pa'i gshed ma
NK125(co)003:3432: yin zer te / sbrul nag po zhig tu song ste lung pa'i phu la song /
NK125(co)003:3433: der rgyal po chos la yid ches /
NK125(co)003:3435: don mkhar thang la ban bon gnyis nus pa 'gran du bcug pas ban d+he bzang /
NK125(co)003:3436: bon pos cher ma byung kyang /
NK125(co)003:3437: ban d+hes rdzas ngan gyi dud pa btang bas nged kyi lha mnol pa yin zer /
NK125(co)003:3438: rtsod pa byed du bcug pas ban+d+he rgyal /
NK125(co)003:3441: gshen dran pa nam mkha' la sogs pa bon ston thams cad mtha' la spyugs /
NK125(co)003:3442: 'jig rten 'phral rkyen bzlog pa'i bon rnams bzhag /
NK125(co)003:3443: gzhan theg pa dgu'i dpe rnams sa la sbas /
NK125(co)003:3444: de nas bon ston rnams kyis bon gyi dpe rnams gter du sbas /
NK125(co)003:3445: dus lan gcig tsam na las 'phro dang skal ba ldan pa /
NK125(co)003:3446: blo la ye shes kyi me sbar ba /
NK125(co)003:3448: lce rno rkan drag gcig gis rnyed par shog /
NK125(co)003:3449: rnyed nas sems can gyi don byed par shog /
NK125(co)003:3453: ban d+he sha tshong byed cing glang dmar bsha'/
NK125(co)003:3455: rnal 'byor zhwa thul gyon par shog /
NK125(co)003:3456: ces sogs smon lam btab nas rgyal po la gter
NK125(co)003:3457: du sba bar zhus pas gnang ste bla chen khod
NK125(co)003:3458: spungs kyis bsam yas dbu rtse bskor khang dang /
NK125(co)003:3459: byang mi med kyi brag phug tu sbas /
NK125(co)003:3460: rgyal rabs bdun 'das pa dang bon gter thon te /
NK125(co)003:3461: bsam yas bskor khad nas a tsa ra gsum gyis rnyed /
NK125(co)003:3462: dbus kyi sri bya ba'i lung bar mtha' bzhi bon po la dbal phur gyi skor dpe bshur bcug /
NK125(co)003:3463: slar byang gi ldog tu khyer bas /
NK125(co)003:3466: 'o ma ti byang chub dang gsum gyis chos yin pa bsam ste nyos /
NK125(co)003:3467: bon yin pa shes pa dang gzhan gnyis pos dor /
NK125(co)003:3468: 'dar ban gyis rang gis tshag byas nas tsha bo gza' skyur bya ba la gtad /
NK125(co)003:3469: der 'dar ban la slob ma che ba bzhi ste /
NK125(co)003:3473: na ro ban chung ste bzhi /
NK125(co)003:3474: 'di rje btsun mi la dang dus mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:3475: de ltar deng sang bon dar ba rnams ni gter ma kho na yin la /
NK125(co)003:3478: khyad par bla na med pa'i theg pa dang dgur byed skad do //
NK125(co)003:3479: de nas slob dpon chen po bod du byon nas
NK125(co)003:3480: lo nyer bdun lon pa chu mo lug gi lo
NK125(co)003:3481: la bsam yas mchims phur rje 'bangs rnams 'tshogs pa
NK125(co)003:3482: la / sngon o rgyan gyi rgyal khams btul ba'i
NK125(co)003:3483: skabs der gshed mas tsan+dana gyi me dpung dbus su
NK125(co)003:3484: la / bsregs pa'i tshe / slob dpon nyid pad+ma
NK125(co)003:3485: badz+ra rtsal zhes bya ba drang srong khros pa'i he
NK125(co)003:3486: ru ka ru sku bzhengs te yum man+d+ha ra ba
NK125(co)003:3487: dang 'khril sbyor du bstan nas rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au
NK125(co)003:3488: ti 'khor dang bcas pa btul ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:3489: bde ba can gyi zhing khams su chos sku snang
NK125(co)003:3490: ba mtha' yas kyis 'dus pa'i 'khor la bka' stsal
NK125(co)003:3491: ba'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rtsa rgyud pad sdong
NK125(co)003:3492: brtsegs pa / sku rgyud shel gyi ri bo /
NK125(co)003:3496: phrin las kyi rgyud dang drug gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:3497: de'i tshe rgyud drug po de dag kyang dus mtshungs
NK125(co)003:3498: su o rgyan bkod pa'i zhing du pad+ma badz+ra gyis
NK125(co)003:3499: gsungs so // de bzhin du pad+ma badz+ra rtsal nyid las sprul pa'i lha tshogs ni /
NK125(co)003:3500: shar phyogs ri bo ta lar bud+d+ha thod phreng rtsal /
NK125(co)003:3501: lho phyogs gyad mkhar brtsegs pa'i dur khrod du mi bskyod rdo rje /
NK125(co)003:3502: nub phyogs so sa gling gi dur khrod du rta mgrin dang /
NK125(co)003:3503: byang phyogs ma g+ha d+har dpa' bo chen po rig 'dzin thod pa rtsal /
NK125(co)003:3504: shar lho bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod du gu ru drag po me lce'i phreng ba can /
NK125(co)003:3505: lho nub dga' ba tshal gyi dur khrod du sangs rgyas thod pa /
NK125(co)003:3506: nub byang rab tu rgyu ba'i dur khrod du dbang chen rta mgrin /
NK125(co)003:3507: byang shar lcang lo can du phyag na rdo rje /
NK125(co)003:3508: rang rang gi rig gdangs yum dang gtso 'khor du
NK125(co)003:3509: bcas pa'i sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po dgu ru
NK125(co)003:3511: gong du bshad pa'i rgyud sde drug gi sgo nas /
NK125(co)003:3515: mi rigs bzhi la sogs pa grangs med dpag tu med pa dag dang /
NK125(co)003:3516: khyad par gyi gdul bya mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK125(co)003:3519: 'byung po bye ba phrag brgya la sogs pa mi
NK125(co)003:3520: ma yin gyi gdul bya bgrang ba las 'das pa'i
NK125(co)003:3521: don rgya cher mdzad pa'i chos bla ma dgongs pa
NK125(co)003:3522: 'dus pa zhes bya ba de'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK125(co)003:3523: bskor te / smin byed kyi dbang bskur /
NK125(co)003:3524: grol byed kyi gdams pa bstan /
NK125(co)003:3527: man ngag gab pa mngon du bstan te /
NK125(co)003:3528: chos skor rnams kong yul gyi brag pu ri phug mo cher gter du sbas /
NK125(co)003:3529: sras mu rub btsan pos gter de 'don par lung bstan /
NK125(co)003:3530: 'dis ni bstan pa ma stong bar du 'gro don rgya chen po 'byung bar gsungs shing /
NK125(co)003:3531: bod kyi bstan pa stong nas 'bras mo ljongs su
NK125(co)003:3532: yang 'gro ba mang po 'di'i sgo nas smin grol
NK125(co)003:3533: la 'god do // zhes sogs rgya cher bshad la /
NK125(co)003:3534: sangs rgyas gling ba'i skye ba sprul sku slar yang 'byon par /
NK125(co)003:3535: gdul bya lhag ma skyong phyir slar yang 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3537: dgongs 'dus bar so'i bka' gdams 'byin par byed //
NK125(co)003:3539: smon lam dbang gis slar yang gter zhabs sdud //
NK125(co)003:3540: sprul sku sangs rgyas dpal ldan nor bu zhes sprul
NK125(co)003:3541: sku zhig po gling pa 'byon par lung bstan pa
NK125(co)003:3542: dang / dgongs 'dus la dbang ba'i gang zag lung
NK125(co)003:3543: bstan pa rnams dus gcig tu mi 'byung bar rim
NK125(co)003:3544: gyis 'byon pa ni lung bstan bka' rgya ma las
NK125(co)003:3545: dang / / la la 'gro ba'i don slad dang //
NK125(co)003:3546: la la smin dang ma smin dang //
NK125(co)003:3547: la la dus la ma bab phyir //
NK125(co)003:3548: thams cad dus gcig tshogs mi srid //
NK125(co)003:3549: snga phyi gang tshogs rim bzhin du //
NK125(co)003:3551: ces gsungs pa ni la la zhing gzhan du 'gro don spyod pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3552: la la rang smin kyang gzhan smin pa la de'i
NK125(co)003:3553: rgyu tshogs gnyis kyi 'phro bsags dgos pas de'i yun
NK125(co)003:3554: du sgug dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK125(co)003:3555: la la ni rang ma smin pas lam bsgom ste
NK125(co)003:3556: de nas rang nyid smin par gyur pa'i tshe gzhan
NK125(co)003:3558: rang smin kyang gzhan 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab pas /
NK125(co)003:3559: de ltar rgyu mtshan bzhi'i dbang gis gcig la mi 'dzom kyang /
NK125(co)003:3562: rje 'bangs rnams kyi smon lam gyi mthu las 'byung ba ste /
NK125(co)003:3563: la la skye thog de ru ma 'dzom kyang //
NK125(co)003:3564: slad mar 'dzom zhing chos kyis rjes su 'dzin //
NK125(co)003:3566: de ltar 'byung ba'i snga phyi'i grangs yang 'di skad du /
NK125(co)003:3567: gdul bya smin cing grol ba'i rnam grangs kyang //
NK125(co)003:3568: dus gcig ma yin brgyud mar rim bzhin du //
NK125(co)003:3569: bskyed rim brtan pa thob pa bye ba 'bum //
NK125(co)003:3570: mngon sum grub pa'i rtags thon 'bum phrag brgyad //
NK125(co)003:3571: zag med sgyu lus grol ba khri phrag dgu //
NK125(co)003:3572: dngos grub sna re thob pa dung phyur brgya //
NK125(co)003:3573: thar pa'i sa bon thebs pa rtsis las 'das //
NK125(co)003:3574: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos 'di ni nges par 'gro ba'i don chen po zhig go //
NK125(co)003:3575: gter chos gzhan dang bka' ma'i chos bka' gzhan rnams
NK125(co)003:3576: las kyang grol ba thob pa bsam las 'das pa
NK125(co)003:3577: de lta bu'i tshul byung ba ni /
NK125(co)003:3578: 'di ltar snga phyir byon pa'i bka' gter gyi grub thob mang du byon mod kyi /
NK125(co)003:3579: thams cad kyi cha rgyus mi 'tshal bas brjod par ma nus so //
NK125(co)003:3580: de nas mnga' bdag btsan pos lo pan rnams kyis
NK125(co)003:3581: bsgyur ba'i chos thams cad glegs bam du brir stsal
NK125(co)003:3582: te gtsug lag khang du bzhugs su gsol /
NK125(co)003:3583: bshad grwa dang sgom grwa btsugs /
NK125(co)003:3584: de thams cad la 'tsho ba dang na bza' bla nas sbyor /
NK125(co)003:3585: zhabs 'og gi rde'u bton nas dbu la 'jog /
NK125(co)003:3586: lha sa bsam yas mtha' 'dul yang 'dul la sogs
NK125(co)003:3587: pa'i lha khang thams cad du mchod pa chen po
NK125(co)003:3588: dang / dus bzang gsum gyi mchod pa rgya chen po mdzad /
NK125(co)003:3590: 'o yug nang khongs su mar me'i ru ba btsugs /
NK125(co)003:3591: lha khang re re la zhag re bzhin mar me
NK125(co)003:3592: brgya rtsa spor ba la sogs pa dkon mchog gsum
NK125(co)003:3593: gyi zhabs tog dpag tu med pa mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:3594: de dus kyi bstan pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3595: sbyin bdag de lta bu ni rgya gar du yang ma byung zhes jo bo rjes gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3596: de nas skabs shin tu mnga' bdag bsnyung nas sus kyang ma phan /
NK125(co)003:3597: mo dang ph+y+wa la nam mkha'i snying pos phan zer te /
NK125(co)003:3598: lho brag mkhar chu nas spyan drangs /
NK125(co)003:3599: nam mkha'i snying pos rgyal po rang da lta gang
NK125(co)003:3600: gsol ba'i 'tsho ba de drongs gsungs nas bzhes pa
NK125(co)003:3601: tsam gyis rgyal po bsnyung dwangs /
NK125(co)003:3603: 'di rgyal po nam mkha'i snying po dang 'phrad 'dod pa'i snyad yin 'ong zer /
NK125(co)003:3604: rgyal po nam mkha'i snying po la phyag 'tshal du ma ster /
NK125(co)003:3606: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la sogs pas mtshams sbyar te /
NK125(co)003:3607: nam mkha'i snying po la rgyal pos phyag byas pas /
NK125(co)003:3608: blon po rnams kyis nam mkha'i snying po bsad par brtsams te mtshon brdar bas /
NK125(co)003:3609: nam mkha'i snying pos mgon khang du byon /
NK125(co)003:3610: ma mgon gnyis kyi sku la rdog thos bsnun te
NK125(co)003:3611: 'dongs gsungs pas de gnyis phyir thon te sdig blon
NK125(co)003:3612: rnams bros / der nam mkha'i snying pos h'u h'u
NK125(co)003:3613: gsungs shing thog phab nas sdigs mdzub kyi rtse la
NK125(co)003:3614: rnams bros / dkris te / 'u shang rdo rje'i brag la brgyab nas brag bsnyil /
NK125(co)003:3616: gnam lcags thog bas kyang h'u sgra de 'jigs /
NK125(co)003:3617: blon po nag po 'di kun de re 'jebs //
NK125(co)003:3619: bod kyi ban+d+he dbu zlum ltag pa lcang lo can
NK125(co)003:3620: kun dbang cher drag she mong po yod du bcug
NK125(co)003:3621: go // de nas yang rgyal po la tshe dbang bskur /
NK125(co)003:3622: sku rim du bshags pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3623: sman gyi bcud len byed du bcug /
NK125(co)003:3624: lha 'dre dregs pa can rnams la /
NK125(co)003:3625: mdos lha 'dre stong gi d+r+wa ba dang /
NK125(co)003:3626: ma mo srid pa'i bem dang /
NK125(co)003:3627: srid pa mtsho bzhi la brten pa'i phyi mdos nang mdos dang /
NK125(co)003:3628: pho mdos dang byis pa chung gi mdos la sogs pa mdzad /
NK125(co)003:3629: khyad par du klus dbang du byed par gzigs nas /
NK125(co)003:3633: klu'i pho brang gso ba dang /
NK125(co)003:3635: byad dgrol la sogs pa'i cho ga mang du mdzad /
NK125(co)003:3637: bsod nams yang rab tu gyur pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3638: tshe mtha' phyin pa gnyis ka mi yong ste /
NK125(co)003:3639: rgyal po la gnyis ka 'dzoms pa yin zhes gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3640: skabs der gangs ti se nas bon po rnams kyis
NK125(co)003:3641: thog mda' stong rtsa brgyad phab byung ba de mkhyen
NK125(co)003:3642: nas phyag mtshan rdo rje 'phangs pa nam mkhar song
NK125(co)003:3643: ste nyang stod khu lo thang du thog gi rdza
NK125(co)003:3644: ma la phog pas thog mar du zhu bas sa
NK125(co)003:3645: gzhi gzhong pa ltar gyur pa'i nang khengs pas mar
NK125(co)003:3646: khu gzhong gang du grags te lung pa phyug pa'ang
NK125(co)003:3647: des yin / rdo rje'i rwa gcig thog gis zhu /
NK125(co)003:3648: rim pas brgyud de da lta yar rgyab pa la yod do //
NK125(co)003:3649: thang yig las mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal 'di'i dus
NK125(co)003:3650: su phul zer ba 'dug kyang thog ma nas phul
NK125(co)003:3651: bar mngon / skabs 'dir rgyal po rje 'bangs la sgrub pa bka' brgyad gnang zer ba yang 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3652: gang ltar slob dpon dang bee ro gnyis kyis chos
NK125(co)003:3653: dang drag sngags bstan srung mtha' dag rgyal po la
NK125(co)003:3654: gnang / rgyal pos sku yon 'bul ba cher byas pa la /
NK125(co)003:3655: slob dpon gyis dgyes tshul mdzad pas /
NK125(co)003:3656: rgyal po'i dgongs pa la slob dpon kyang lho bal gyi zhad kyis nor la dgyes snyam pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3657: slob dpon gyis rde'u gzhong pa gang gser du bsgyur nas rgyal po la gtad /
NK125(co)003:3658: der rgyal pos bshags pa byas /
NK125(co)003:3659: yang skabs shig tu mchims phur rje 'bangs la rdzogs pa chen po phung po zag med gnang dus /
NK125(co)003:3660: slob dpon gyi sku 'od lus yin zhes gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:3661: rgyal po the tshom du gyur /
NK125(co)003:3662: der slob dpon gyis rgyal po chen po bdag gi spyi bor khu tshur gcig bsnun 'tshal gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3663: de 'dra mi rung lags zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:3665: gsang sngags pas bla ma'i bka' ji skad gsungs pa bzhin sgrub dgos pa lags /
NK125(co)003:3667: der rgyal pos dbu la khu tshur bsnun pas thogs
NK125(co)003:3668: pa ci yang med par gdan gyi gab rtse la
NK125(co)003:3669: phog / de 'dra ba lan gsum byas pas kyang thogs rdugs ma byung bas /
NK125(co)003:3670: slob dpon gyi sku 'od lus su yid ches nas yang bshags pa byas so //
NK125(co)003:3671: de'i lo lha lcam pad+ma gsal tshe'i dus byas pas /
NK125(co)003:3672: slob dpon gyis ro la rnam shes bkug ste smra shes par byung ba la /
NK125(co)003:3673: dbang bskur dang gdams pa'i gtad rgya mang du gnang nas rjes su bzung /
NK125(co)003:3676: pad+ma gling pa la sogs par chos bdag 'gro don
NK125(co)003:3677: stobs chen yong bar byin gyis brlabs te lung bstan
NK125(co)003:3678: / gzhan yang rgyal po la ma 'ongs 'byung tshul gyi lung bstan mang du gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3679: mtha' dmag bzlog pa'i thabs dang /
NK125(co)003:3680: bod la phan pa'i man ngag mang po yang gnang nas /
NK125(co)003:3683: gtsang phung po ri bo che la sogs par gter du sbas /
NK125(co)003:3684: gzhan yang rgyal po glang dar gyis bstan pa bsnub par mkhyen pas /
NK125(co)003:3685: ma 'ongs pa'i skal ldan rnams kyi don du gter sbas te /
NK125(co)003:3687: ya thog ring mo ma thog ring mo dang //
NK125(co)003:3688: khug pa bco brgyad skyo shas can la gzigs //
NK125(co)003:3689: phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pa'i gter //
NK125(co)003:3690: gter gyi rtsa ba ma 'phyugs bzhir bsdus te //
NK125(co)003:3691: mes gter pha gter dbon gter yang gter bzhi //
NK125(co)003:3692: bzhi po re rer bco brgyad bco brgyad bsdus //
NK125(co)003:3693: bco brgyad re rer phun tshogs lnga lngas bstan //
NK125(co)003:3694: gter rgya sbas rgya zab rgya gsang rgya gtad rgya'o //
NK125(co)003:3695: gter rgya gter ston phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK125(co)003:3696: che ba'i yon tan bcu dang ldan pa ste //
NK125(co)003:3697: rigs kyi che ba rgyal rigs rje ru 'khrungs //
NK125(co)003:3698: sku yi che ba mtshan dang dpe byad ldan //
NK125(co)003:3699: yon tan che ba shes bya thams cad mkhyen //
NK125(co)003:3700: thos pas che ba mdo sngags thams cad mkhyen //
NK125(co)003:3701: bsam pas che ba tshig rjes don gyis bsob //
NK125(co)003:3702: bsgom pas che ba rtogs pa'i lta ba mtho //
NK125(co)003:3703: spobs pa che bas gzhan dag zil gyis gnon //
NK125(co)003:3704: rtsod blo che bas rgol ba'i tshigs kun 'joms //
NK125(co)003:3705: 'dzin blo che bas chos dang chos min 'byed //
NK125(co)003:3706: bsran thub rgyud dul che bas phun sum tshogs //
NK125(co)003:3707: sbas rgya dam chos phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK125(co)003:3708: rgyal ba'i bka' gnang 'phags pa'i lung gis grub //
NK125(co)003:3709: rig pas 'thad cing gtan tshigs rgyas thebs pa //
NK125(co)003:3710: mdo yin dgongs pa nyi shu rjes dran bcu //
NK125(co)003:3711: spyi mdo yin no sgos mdo khyad par mdo //
NK125(co)003:3712: rgyud yin dngos po bcu dang mtha' drug tshul bzhi bcas //
NK125(co)003:3713: lung yin mtha' bzhi man ngag dpe don rtags //
NK125(co)003:3714: gsang rgya gter slob dag pa'i yon tan bcu //
NK125(co)003:3715: rigs dag 'byor pa lang tsho 'bri klog mkhas //
NK125(co)003:3716: rgyud dag dad pa shes rab snying rje che //
NK125(co)003:3717: las dag chos phyir brtson 'grus dka' ba spyod //
NK125(co)003:3718: 'grus dag sgo gsum rkyen theg dam tshig gnad //
NK125(co)003:3719: rten dag gzhan dang ma 'khon sel ma zhugs //
NK125(co)003:3720: gtong ba dag pas bdag gzhan dge la bskul //
NK125(co)003:3721: sems bskyed dag pas lus srog don la ster //
NK125(co)003:3722: dngos po dag pas smar bzhun ser sna med //
NK125(co)003:3723: dbang po dag pas gzhan gyi sems mi dkrug /'dun pa dag pas zol 'grogs ngo zhal med //
NK125(co)003:3724: bcu po ma tshang kha ni thur la bub //
NK125(co)003:3725: stobs dang ldan yang dug gi me tog yin //
NK125(co)003:3726: zab rgya gter gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK125(co)003:3727: gnas kyis zab ste thun mong khyad par lnga //
NK125(co)003:3728: thun mong lnga ni sa la zab pa dang //
NK125(co)003:3729: de bzhin chu la zab dang brag la zab //
NK125(co)003:3730: gtsug lag khang dang shing la zab pa'o //
NK125(co)003:3731: khyad par lnga la dbus na zab pa dang //
NK125(co)003:3732: de bzhin shar nub lho dang byang gnas zab //
NK125(co)003:3733: gtad rgya 'don dus phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK125(co)003:3734: sa rtags g.yo 'gul skyo shas mar 'grib gsum //
NK125(co)003:3735: zhe sdang las gyur dmag 'khrug 'byung ba dang //
NK125(co)003:3736: 'dod chags las gyur mu ge 'byung ba dang //
NK125(co)003:3737: gti mug las byung nad yams 'byung ba dang //
NK125(co)003:3738: mi rnams skyo shas che bas 'dul ba'i zhing //
NK125(co)003:3739: mi 'dod bzhin du khab len rdos nyul bzhin //
NK125(co)003:3740: gtad rgya 'don pa'i gter ston gcig 'byung phyir //
NK125(co)003:3741: chos dang ngan sngags sman dang rtsis thams cad //
NK125(co)003:3742: dbus gter lho gter byang gter shar nub gter //
NK125(co)003:3743: gter kha brgya dang rtsa brgyad bod du sbas //
NK125(co)003:3745: gter sbas tshul ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK125(co)003:3746: mdo tsam mtshon na yang dbu rtse rim gsum la
NK125(co)003:3747: sogs pa bsam yas kyi lha khang rnams na rgyal
NK125(co)003:3749: slob dpon pad+ma'i thugs gter mang du yod la /
NK125(co)003:3750: bod yul gyi ri brag chu shing /
NK125(co)003:3759: sbas yul so so na sbas tshul mtha' yas shing /
NK125(co)003:3760: zab bu'i gnas yig tu bshad pa gcig pu la'ang
NK125(co)003:3761: mtha' mi 'dug pas rgyas par ni bri bar ma
NK125(co)003:3762: nus la / mdo tsam shes par 'dod na thang
NK125(co)003:3763: yig sde drug la sogs par blta bar bya zhing
NK125(co)003:3766: 'dzam gling spyi la dgos pa'i gter kha lnga /
NK125(co)003:3767: bod khams spyi la dgos pa'i gter kha lnga /
NK125(co)003:3768: sa yi bcud la dgos pa 'don du mi btub pa'i gter kha lnga /
NK125(co)003:3769: bton nas gter tshab 'jug dgos pa'i gter kha lnga /
NK125(co)003:3770: ma bton na dngos grub yal bar 'gyur ba'i gter kha lnga ste ming can nyer lnga yod la /
NK125(co)003:3771: ming med ni bgrang bar mi nus so //
NK125(co)003:3773: mnga' bdag nyang ral pa can dang /
NK125(co)003:3774: gu ru chos kyi dbang phyug /'jam dpal chos kyi
NK125(co)003:3775: bshes gnyen la sogs par skye ba bzhes pa'i tshe
NK125(co)003:3776: / zab mo'i gter la spyod pa dang /
NK125(co)003:3777: 'gro ba'i don mdzad par lung bstan /
NK125(co)003:3778: de nas slob dpon gyis zab bu lung du byon /
NK125(co)003:3779: rgyal yum ye shes mtsho rgyal dang /
NK125(co)003:3780: a tsar sa le bya ba bod pa gcig gis phyag phyi byas te /
NK125(co)003:3781: brag dkar bya tshang ma shel gyi yang rdzong bya ba na bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:3782: der jo mo la sngags srung mas lung bstan te /
NK125(co)003:3783: slob dpon la don tig zhus shig zer nas yal song /
NK125(co)003:3784: nang par slob dpon la zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:3785: bsgrub pa lo re dam bca' gyis zhes gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3787: a tsar sa les dbang nos pa'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:3788: slob dpon thugs rje chen po dngos su bzhengs /
NK125(co)003:3789: dbang zhu ba gnyis pos stong gsum bye ba phrag
NK125(co)003:3790: brgya dus gcig tu gsal bar mthong nas zhing khams
NK125(co)003:3791: de dag na rang rang gi ston pa sangs rgyas
NK125(co)003:3792: rnams kyis 'khor dpag tu med pa la chos ston
NK125(co)003:3793: pa dang sems can gyi don mdzad pa mthong /
NK125(co)003:3794: de slob dpon gyi yon tan las mthong bar yid ches te /
NK125(co)003:3795: da dung yon tan yongs su rdzogs pa bstan du gsol zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:3796: nga'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs pa sems can gyis mthong ba'i skal pa med /
NK125(co)003:3797: 'on kyang cha shas tsam bstan gyi gsungs /
NK125(co)003:3799: bdag cag gnyis la dag snang rgyun chad med par bstan du gsol /
NK125(co)003:3801: nges don du slob dpon gar bzhugs pa'i sa de ka 'og min yin mod kyi /
NK125(co)003:3802: snang tshul du khrid pa ltar mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:3803: khong gnyis la mig dar bkab /
NK125(co)003:3804: khong gnyis na bza' la 'jus pa de 'ub kyis 'then pas /
NK125(co)003:3805: skad cig la bde chen snying po bkod pa'i rgyan zhes bya ba'i zhing khams su slebs te /
NK125(co)003:3806: thig le dkar po 'od lnga'i mu khyud dang ldan pas yongs su gang ba la /
NK125(co)003:3807: thig le thams cad 'od zer gyis 'brel ba /
NK125(co)003:3808: thig le re re'i nang na longs sku'i zhing bye ba phrag brgya brgya /
NK125(co)003:3809: zhing khams re na slob dpon pad+ma longs spyod rdzogs sku gangs chen mtsho bye ba phrag brgya brgya /
NK125(co)003:3810: de re re la 'od zer gyi ba spu bye ba phrag brgya brgya /
NK125(co)003:3811: ba spu'i bu ga rer sprul sku'i zhing khams chen po bye ba phrag brgya brgya /
NK125(co)003:3812: zhing khams re re la stong gsum bye ba phrag brgya brgya /
NK125(co)003:3813: stong gsum re re la gling bzhi ri rab bye ba phrag brgya brgya /
NK125(co)003:3814: gling bzhi po re re na slob dpon pad+ma re /
NK125(co)003:3815: slob dpon re las sprul pa bye ba phrag brgya re /
NK125(co)003:3816: sprul pa re la gdul bya 'gro ba bye ba
NK125(co)003:3817: phrag brgya brgya re la sogs pa dpag tu med
NK125(co)003:3818: pa mthong / de nas skad cig la shar phyogs
NK125(co)003:3819: su zhing khams grangs med pa 'das pa'i pha rol
NK125(co)003:3820: pa mthong / tu slebs / bde chen rnam par
NK125(co)003:3821: bkod pa'i rgyan zhes bya ba'i zhing khams gong dang
NK125(co)003:3822: pa mthong / tu slebs / mtshungs pa la / thig le mthing ka /
NK125(co)003:3823: thig le re re'i nang na longs sku'i zhing khams bye ba phrag brgya /
NK125(co)003:3824: slob dpon pad+ma rdo rje gangs chen mtsho re re /
NK125(co)003:3826: gdul bya la sogs bye ba phrag brgya sngar ltar 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3827: de nas lho phyogs kyi zhing khams grangs med pa bgrod de /
NK125(co)003:3828: de na bde chen rin chen bkod pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK125(co)003:3829: thig le ser po bye ba phrag brgya /
NK125(co)003:3830: de re re na longs sku'i zhing dang slob dpon pad+ma bye ba phrag brgya /
NK125(co)003:3831: sprul pa gdul bya bye ba phrag brgya la sogs pa snga ma ltar 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3832: nub phyogs kyi zhing khams grangs med pa bgrod pa'i pha rol na /
NK125(co)003:3833: bde chen pad+ma bkod pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na thig le dmar po bye ba phrag brgya /
NK125(co)003:3834: re re'i nang na slob dpon pad+ma gangs chen mtsho re /
NK125(co)003:3835: sprul pa dang gdul bya bye ba phrag brgya gong ltar 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3836: de nas byang phyogs su zhing khams grangs med pa
NK125(co)003:3837: bgrod de bde chen las rab bkod pa zhes bya
NK125(co)003:3838: ba'i zhing khams thig le ljang khus gang ba /
NK125(co)003:3839: thig le re re'i nang na zhing khams bye ba phrag brgya la /
NK125(co)003:3840: slob dpon pad+ma karma gangs chen mtsho bye ba phrag brgya /
NK125(co)003:3841: sprul pa dang gdul bya bye ba phrag brgya brgya re snga ma dang 'dra bar 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3842: de nas bde chen 'khor ba yongs sgrol gyi dur khrod bya bar slebs /
NK125(co)003:3843: mi mgo brtsigs pa'i gzhal yas khang mi lpags kyis thog phub pa /
NK125(co)003:3845: thod pa'i ra bas bskor ba /
NK125(co)003:3846: sha chen ri ltar spungs pa /
NK125(co)003:3847: khrag gi rgya mtsho bskyil ba'i dbus na 'dug pa der slebs /
NK125(co)003:3848: de na khro bo dpag tu med pa'i gtso bo
NK125(co)003:3849: rdo rje thod phreng rtsal rigs lnga 'dus pa'i rgyal
NK125(co)003:3850: po las sku gsung thugs kyi 'od zer gyi sgo
NK125(co)003:3852: ha ha zhes pa'i gad mo chen po zhig byung ste /
NK125(co)003:3853: khro bo'i sprin phung ri rab las kyang che ba
NK125(co)003:3854: mgar gyi tsha tsha ltar du 'phros bas khong gnyis
NK125(co)003:3856: de las brgyal ba sangs tsa na brag dkar na 'gyel nas 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3858: khyed gnyis pos dag snang rgyun chad med pa de ma byung ngo //
NK125(co)003:3859: chos nyid don dam pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK125(co)003:3861: bdud nag po bkrag med gnyis mi phyed /
NK125(co)003:3863: ye shes kyi rol par ro gcig par shes pas /
NK125(co)003:3864: ye shes lha la zhen chags mi skye /
NK125(co)003:3865: bdud la 'jigs skrag mi skye ba zhig byung ba'i
NK125(co)003:3866: dus na 'khor 'das gnyis med ye shes brdal ba
NK125(co)003:3867: chen po zhes bya ba'i dag snang shar ba yin
NK125(co)003:3868: / khyed gnyis nga la 'jigs pa de ni dag
NK125(co)003:3869: snang rgyun mi chad pa ga la yin gsungs te
NK125(co)003:3870: / / don tig 'gro ba kun grol bya ba'i gdams pa gnang /
NK125(co)003:3871: de'i rjes zhig tu jo mos kong po'i sa phyogs
NK125(co)003:3872: su sbas pa chos rgyal dri med lhun pos gter
NK125(co)003:3873: nas bton te 'gro don che la /
NK125(co)003:3874: khong gnyis sangs rgyas gling pa'i gter g.yog tu byed /
NK125(co)003:3875: dri med kun dga' yang dus der byon par snang /
NK125(co)003:3876: thugs rje chen po ye shes 'od mchog ces pa'i zab chos yod do //
NK125(co)003:3877: de nas gter ston rnams lung bstan pa'i tshul ni /
NK125(co)003:3878: rgyal po'i gdung rabs brgyad dam bcu 'das nas //
NK125(co)003:3879: la stod mtsho bar gyang nag zhes bya bar //
NK125(co)003:3880: mu ge nad yams mi thog bud ba 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3881: glo bo dge dkar sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3882: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3883: gter ston sangs rgyas bla ma zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3884: zhes pa 'di ni snga mo zhig byon pa 'dra ste chos gter 'di yod kyang ma thos so //
NK125(co)003:3885: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3886: bal bod mtshams su me shor mi mang 'tshig /
NK125(co)003:3887: g.yung sna rdza rir sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3888: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3889: gter ston rgya lo ts+aa zhes bya ba 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3890: 'di rje mar pa lo ts+aa dang dus mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:3894: man ngag lam rim la sogs pa'i chos gter dang /
NK125(co)003:3896: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3897: khams kyi rme mdor bya khyi lha khang 'khrug /
NK125(co)003:3898: klong thang sgrol mar sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3899: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3900: gter ston sna nam pa zhes bya ba 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3901: 'di la rje sna nam pa zhes grags te /
NK125(co)003:3904: rtsis sogs mang po bton zer /
NK125(co)003:3905: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3906: la stod cung par gri len chu ltar 'khrug /
NK125(co)003:3907: g.yu phu rdza lhur sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3908: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3909: gter ston dum rgya zhang khrom zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3910: rgya zhang khrom 'di lho brag rnga mong chu shul
NK125(co)003:3911: du 'khrungs zer ba o rgyan gling pa'i gter 'byung
NK125(co)003:3912: na 'dug / g.yung mda' na yang gzim khang gi
NK125(co)003:3913: shul yin zer ba'i khang ro chung du gcig yod
NK125(co)003:3914: pas brtag /'di gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyi skye
NK125(co)003:3915: na 'dug / ba yin zer / gter kha phal cher yang gnubs kyi yin /
NK125(co)003:3917: ma mgon sogs drag sngags bsam gyis mi khyab pa thon /
NK125(co)003:3918: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3919: mang yul nam mkha' khrag mdog sngo dmar 'gro //
NK125(co)003:3920: khrag gi char ba zla ba bco brgyad 'bab //
NK125(co)003:3921: byams pa sprin du sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3922: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3923: gter ston nyi ma seng ge zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3924: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3925: shod gsum sa la ro 'dren 'jag skya 'phyo //
NK125(co)003:3926: mi re'i lag na phub re mda' gzhu re //
NK125(co)003:3927: byang gi gter phran 'ga' zhig sbas pa 'di //
NK125(co)003:3928: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3929: gter ston g.yo ru ston shag zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3930: 'dis byang pra dun rtse sogs nas rlung 'khor dmar nag dang /
NK125(co)003:3932: dregs pa nyi shu la sogs pa mang po bton no //
NK125(co)003:3933: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3934: spa gro gnam thang dkar por sog dmag 'dzom //
NK125(co)003:3935: las su dme 'khrug gos su lcags cha gyon //
NK125(co)003:3936: bum thang rtsis lung sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3937: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3938: gter ston bon po drag rtsal zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3939: bum thang rtsis lung ni dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi
NK125(co)003:3940: sku li ma bzhugs pas mon pa rnams kyi dkon
NK125(co)003:3941: mchog gsum gyi lha khang zer ba de yin /
NK125(co)003:3942: de nas rdzogs chen gu ru bzhi pa /
NK125(co)003:3944: sh+r+ai seng ha'i rdzogs rim bla ma dmar khrid zer ba'i po ti chen mo de bton /
NK125(co)003:3946: bsgom ma myong dang 'bral ma myong //
NK125(co)003:3947: mi bsgom don dang mi 'bral ba //
NK125(co)003:3948: zer ba'i man ngag de yang yod /
NK125(co)003:3949: phur pa la sogs pa'i chos skor gzhan yang bton no //
NK125(co)003:3950: spa gro gnam thang gi sog dmag ni rgya gar
NK125(co)003:3951: ga ta nas gar log gi dmag de byung ba
NK125(co)003:3952: yin / byang gi hor sog yong rgyur 'dod pa yang ma nges pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:3953: gter ston chos dang bcas pa sngar byon zin pas so //
NK125(co)003:3954: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3955: gtsang gi yug gdong nya ri 'ug pa lung //
NK125(co)003:3956: bstan pa gnyis 'khrug chos kyi byin rlabs yal //
NK125(co)003:3957: chos dang gang zag ya bral chom pos khyer //
NK125(co)003:3958: snyi drung shel brag sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3959: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3960: gter ston snye mo zhu yas zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3961: 'di la gter gyi kha byang bon po drag rtsal gyis phyung ste /
NK125(co)003:3962: snyi drung shal ma brag phug nas rdzogs chen spyi ti la sogs pa mang po yod /
NK125(co)003:3963: 'di ni dus snga mo zhig tu byung 'dug pas
NK125(co)003:3964: gter rtags yu ba gdong gis mtshon te nya ri
NK125(co)003:3966: der 'ug pa lung du zhal ngo nang ma mthun pas /
NK125(co)003:3967: zur thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aakya 'byung gnas la sgro phug phog /
NK125(co)003:3968: de rjes yangs pa'i gsang sngags gling btab nas yod pa 'di yin cing /
NK125(co)003:3969: sa skya pa dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i sku tshe'i smad la byung 'dug pas /
NK125(co)003:3970: dus snga phyi khyad ches pas dkrugs te gsungs pa yin nam /
NK125(co)003:3971: thang yig tshigs bcad lhug phal cher la 'dug kyang /
NK125(co)003:3972: bar skabs nas gter ston mang po lung bstan pa zhig chad pa 'dra'o //
NK125(co)003:3973: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3974: 'jim gyi byar 'dab b+ha dra dkon mchog mtshan //
NK125(co)003:3975: sde dgon za 'og kha phye 'dra ba 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3976: gtsang gi ri bo cher sbas gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:3977: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3978: gter ston grub thob dngos grub zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3979: grub thob dngos grub ni snga mo zhig tu byon nas mi yul du lo drug brgya bzhugs te /
NK125(co)003:3980: drug brgya lon pa'i lo der gter bton pa yin /
NK125(co)003:3981: lha sa nas chos rgyal srong btsan sgam po'i bka' 'bum dang /
NK125(co)003:3982: ri bo che nas kyang mang du thon /
NK125(co)003:3983: mnga' bdag nyang gi bla ma yin /
NK125(co)003:3984: rje btsun grags pa dang dus mtshungs su ra sa 'jim gyi sde dgon byung ba'o //
NK125(co)003:3985: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3986: rgya nag rgyal po'i rgyal sa rta rdzis 'phrog /
NK125(co)003:3987: bstan pa dar rgyas mnga' thang je cher 'gro //
NK125(co)003:3988: bal yul e yi lha khang sbas pa'i gter //
NK125(co)003:3989: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3990: gter ston gtsug lag dpal dge zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:3991: 'di ni bal po'i slob dpon gtsug lag dpal dge yin nam brtag /
NK125(co)003:3992: lha bla ma ye shes 'od kyi dus su slob
NK125(co)003:3993: dpon des gter bton zhes o rgyan gling pas 'chad
NK125(co)003:3994: / de ltar na dus rtags 'chol bar 'dug /
NK125(co)003:3995: snga dus su byon par snang /
NK125(co)003:3996: gter chos gang yin ma nges so //
NK125(co)003:3997: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:3998: la stod gtsang yul mtshon la so nams byed //
NK125(co)003:3999: 'dzam gling rgyal po'i dpon rgyud 'bangs mis gnon //
NK125(co)003:4000: lho brag gter phran 'ga' zhig sbas pa 'di //
NK125(co)003:4001: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4002: gter ston ku sa sman pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4003: 'dis sba gro bcal la sogs pa'i gter gnas nas /
NK125(co)003:4006: bon gyi sems phyogs mang po bton /
NK125(co)003:4007: bon skor rnams ni ma 'ongs pa na bod dar bar mkhyen nas /
NK125(co)003:4008: chos bon du bsgyur ba yin /
NK125(co)003:4009: 'di'i gter kha nas byung ba sems phyogs bon la shin tu dar ba byung /
NK125(co)003:4010: sman dpyad mdzad pas chos la phrin las ma byung /
NK125(co)003:4011: shog ser shing sgrom gang thon pas rgya nan ltar che'o //
NK125(co)003:4012: 'di rje mi la dang dus mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:4013: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4014: byang gi phyi gong ru ba 'tshubs mas khyer //
NK125(co)003:4015: bod 'dir dam chos bstan pa gsum du gyes //
NK125(co)003:4016: bka' gter gnyis kyis sangs rgyas bstan pa skyong //
NK125(co)003:4017: gtsang gi ru mtshams sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4018: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4019: gter ston bon po lha 'bum zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4021: sman rtsis chos bon bzhi ka thon te mang po yod /
NK125(co)003:4022: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4023: dbus gtsang khams su dug lnga'i chos shig 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4024: lta log spyod log bstan pa thabs kyis bsnub //
NK125(co)003:4025: zhabs tog yin zer bstan zhabs thag pa 'dogs //
NK125(co)003:4026: mon kha bum thang sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4027: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4028: gter ston khyung po bu dpal zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4029: 'di dus ma nges kyang snga mo zhig 'dra ste /
NK125(co)003:4030: par snams su ar tshoms ban d+he mi brgyad kyis
NK125(co)003:4031: grub chen o rgyan pa'i yang mes byang chub rgya
NK125(co)003:4032: mtsho dang chos kyi rgya mtsho gnyis kyis g.yog kun
NK125(co)003:4033: thub bya ba khrid de la stod la byon pa
NK125(co)003:4034: na / ar tsho rnams kyis khong gsum po yan lag phur bzhi la brgyangs nas /
NK125(co)003:4035: mkha' 'gro mchod pa'i tshogs sha byed zer /
NK125(co)003:4037: khyed gnyis la grub rtags 'dra med dam /
NK125(co)003:4038: da ni zug gis 'chi bar 'dug byas pas /
NK125(co)003:4039: gcung gis ngas phur pa'i 'khrab zhon cig bya'am zer /
NK125(co)003:4040: der gcen gyis skrag mi dgos /
NK125(co)003:4041: ngas 'di ltar bya yi gsung ste /
NK125(co)003:4042: rta mgrin du bstan nas spyi gtsug gi rta skad bton pas /
NK125(co)003:4043: ar tsho mi bco brgyad skrag nas slar dad cing
NK125(co)003:4044: gus pa byas pas rjes su bzung zer ba'i dus
NK125(co)003:4046: sbyor sgrol la sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa'i dus su byung bas so //
NK125(co)003:4047: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4048: bod kyi gnas dgon kun la 'thab ra 'cha' //
NK125(co)003:4049: lha sa dmar po'i ri la rdzong gcig 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4050: ngang ngur mtsho skam ne'u sing bye mas gnon //
NK125(co)003:4051: dge rgyas has po ri yi gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4052: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4053: gter ston sha mi rdo rgyal zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4054: 'di ni yul sha mi bra ru bya bar byung ste gter mang ngo zer ro //
NK125(co)003:4055: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4056: nga sprul yin zer gter min gter 'dra tshogs //
NK125(co)003:4057: dam nyams gar ma brin pa thams cad 'dus //
NK125(co)003:4058: nya ma mgo bskor 'brel med chos bshad byed //
NK125(co)003:4059: bstan pa'i chom po gter chos dkrug cing spel //
NK125(co)003:4060: bka' log mang po ra khyu tsam pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4061: pad+ma bdag kyang yi mug ga chad de //
NK125(co)003:4062: zhwa yi lha khang bi ma la yi gter //
NK125(co)003:4063: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4064: gter ston ldang ma lhun rgyal zhes bya ba //
NK125(co)003:4065: bi ma la yi sprul pa 'byung bar 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:4066: 'dis rdzogs chen rgyud bcu bdun rtsa 'grel /
NK125(co)003:4067: snying thig man ngag brgya bcu dgu rnams bton /
NK125(co)003:4068: bstan pa'i snying po nges pa don gyi 'gro don rgya che'o //
NK125(co)003:4069: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4070: skabs su gcig las gcig nyid sdug pa 'ong /
NK125(co)003:4071: jing gir rgya rnams grog ma tshang zhig 'dra //
NK125(co)003:4072: jo mo gling gsum sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4073: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4074: gter ston grwa pa mngon shes zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4075: 'dis zhang blon rdo rje bdud 'dul gyi skor dang /
NK125(co)003:4076: gter gyi kha byang la sogs pa mang du thon /
NK125(co)003:4077: sa steng gnas gzhi brgya dang rtsa brgyad bzhengs so //
NK125(co)003:4078: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4079: o rgyan nga nyid gnyal smad lha rjer sprul //
NK125(co)003:4080: dwags lha sgam por don sgom khyu zhig 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4081: mchims phu thang dben sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4082: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4083: ra shaka gter ston mdos la mkhas pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4085: ma mo sgang shar la sogs pa slob dpon pad+ma'i shog ser gter sgrom gang yang zer /
NK125(co)003:4087: da lta brgyud pa yang gnyan na yod /
NK125(co)003:4088: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4089: yul po che sar 'khrug pa'i bskal pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4090: sngags pas mthu sgrub skye bos bzlog pa slob //
NK125(co)003:4091: mi bsad stong la sku dang gsung rab 'jal //
NK125(co)003:4092: grong stod grong smad 'gro la skyel ma 'tshol //
NK125(co)003:4093: srin mo sbar rjes mkho mthing gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4094: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4095: mnga' bdag sprul pa nyang ral zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4096: 'dis lho brag gtam shul gyi brag srin mo sbar
NK125(co)003:4097: rjes can la sogs pa nas gter kha mang du
NK125(co)003:4098: bton te / rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi phyag dpe phal che ba thon /
NK125(co)003:4099: skabs shig tu ne'u seng yod pa'i lam kha zhig tu mnal du song ba na /
NK125(co)003:4100: bud med rta pa mo gcig byung ste /
NK125(co)003:4101: mnga' bdag la thod phreng gi lcags cig rgyab pa dang dran med du brgyal /
NK125(co)003:4102: bud med de'i rta pang na dom sgro nag po
NK125(co)003:4103: chen po zhig 'dug pa de bor 'dug pa brgyal
NK125(co)003:4104: ba sangs pa dang bsnams nas byon te khyim du
NK125(co)003:4105: gzigs pas / slob dpon pad+ma'i shog dril kho na 'dug ste /
NK125(co)003:4106: chos kyi rnam grangs bgrangs pa las 'das pa zhig byon te /
NK125(co)003:4107: shin tu zab pa thugs kyi dom sgro nag po'i skor zhes grags /
NK125(co)003:4108: gu ru drag po dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa'i
NK125(co)003:4109: chos skor bde gshegs 'dus chen du grags pa de
NK125(co)003:4111: mkha' 'gro ma ye shes mtsho rgyal gyis dngos su chos gtad pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:4112: gter gyi kha byang ra shag dang grwa pa las byung bar bshad /
NK125(co)003:4113: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4114: pu hrang rgyal pos bod la gser sdud 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4115: sde ba gyes shing gnas gzhi thob sha byed //
NK125(co)003:4116: gram pa rgyang la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4117: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4118: gter ston dbon gses khyung thog zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4119: 'di ni lha btsun byang chub 'od kyis bod btsun
NK125(co)003:4120: la sham thabs khral bsdus nas jo bo rje la
NK125(co)003:4121: gser mang po phul ba'i dus de yin /
NK125(co)003:4122: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4123: rgya gar ma phyin kun kyang lo ts+aa byed //
NK125(co)003:4124: bod kyi mkhas btsun thams cad sa mthar 'khyar //
NK125(co)003:4125: hor dang yon mchod khrims sar 'brel ba yong //
NK125(co)003:4126: nang nag phyi dkar dung dkar gnyer ma bzhin //
NK125(co)003:4127: bod kyi bsod nams mar mar 'grib pa'i dus //
NK125(co)003:4128: pad+ma shel phug sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4129: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4130: gter ston ra mo shel sman zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4132: rtsis dang sman dang chos gsum ka byung /
NK125(co)003:4133: 'bam nad la phug gi bcos thabs yang 'di'i gter kha yin /
NK125(co)003:4134: hor dang yon mchod sa pan gyi dus yin la /
NK125(co)003:4135: nang nag phyi dkar sa skya pa'i dpon chen rnams la zer par 'dug /
NK125(co)003:4136: kun snying lo ts+aa sa pan la 'dod pa ni yi ge ma dag pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:4137: sa pan gyi mtshan la kun snying mi zer /
NK125(co)003:4138: bod kyi mkhas btsun sa mthar 'khyar bas bod kyi 'chad nyan la gnod /
NK125(co)003:4139: hor khrims 'ja' mo gser yig pas bod 'bangs shin tu mnar ba dang /
NK125(co)003:4140: dus der rgya gar la ma phyin bar /
NK125(co)003:4141: dbyar tshad pas 'jigs nas mang yul du bsdad /
NK125(co)003:4142: dgun bal por phyin nas lo ts+aa bar grags pa
NK125(co)003:4143: mang po 'byung ba de lung bstan pa yin no
NK125(co)003:4144: // de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4145: sna thag sas byas hor dmag bod du 'ong //
NK125(co)003:4146: ngan song zer yang de 'dra'i sdug bsngal med //
NK125(co)003:4147: mi la srog bcad yul bud mang du yong //
NK125(co)003:4148: gnam skas mkhar chur sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4149: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas byung //
NK125(co)003:4150: gter ston gu ru chos dbang zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4151: 'di 'phags pa rin po che dang dus mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:4154: bka' brgyad sogs gter kha mang /
NK125(co)003:4156: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4157: bya rog tshang du dmag gi khrims rnga brdung //
NK125(co)003:4158: snying med po tsho gser phye chu la 'pho //
NK125(co)003:4159: zangs yag brag la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4160: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
