NK125(co)003:4161: gter ston gu ru jo tse zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4162: zhes pa 'phags pa rin po che gshegs /
NK125(co)003:4163: bla ma bdag nyid pa'i dus rgya nag tu yon mchod la zhu log phul nas /
NK125(co)003:4164: hor dmag gis bya rog tshang du dpon chen kun dga' bzang po nyes med du bsad pas /
NK125(co)003:4165: gser phye chu la 'pho ni de yin la /
NK125(co)003:4166: gu ru jo tse snye mdar byon /
NK125(co)003:4167: pu ti sum cu lhag tsam gyi chos gter dang /
NK125(co)003:4168: sangs rgyas kyi ring bsrel dang /
NK125(co)003:4169: slob dpon pad+ma'i sku la sogs pa mang du thon kyang /
NK125(co)003:4170: phyag rdzas zhan pas 'tsho ba lug rdzi la brten /
NK125(co)003:4171: gye re lha pa'i zhal ngo lha rin chen dbang
NK125(co)003:4172: gi rgyal po la gter gyi rdzas dang bka' rnams
NK125(co)003:4173: gtad do // de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4174: lha khang nang du 'bri la rta chu blud //
NK125(co)003:4175: gzho klung nang du me yi 'jigs pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4176: dpal mo dpal thang mtshon gyi char pa 'bab //
NK125(co)003:4177: gangs bar phug mor sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4178: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4179: gter ston pad+ma dbang phyug zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4181: g.ye'i gangs bar phug nas gter mang po thon /
NK125(co)003:4183: pu tra ming sring gi sgrub skor man ngag zab pa shin tu mang /
NK125(co)003:4184: bdag chen rgya gar pas mdzad pa'i chos skyong gi
NK125(co)003:4185: yig cha me 'bar ma zhes grags pa de yang
NK125(co)003:4186: / gter kha 'di'i khrod nas btus pa'i man ngag kho na yin /
NK125(co)003:4187: lha khang nang du 'bri la rta chu blud dang /
NK125(co)003:4188: gzho klung gi me ni dpon chen ag len gyis
NK125(co)003:4189: dmag rgyab nas 'bri gung gling log tu grags pa
NK125(co)003:4190: de'o // de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4191: smon mda' la mkhar shel gyi pha bong rdol //
NK125(co)003:4192: sing ma la khar 'jag ma'i mi chung skye //
NK125(co)003:4193: g.ya' ma spang gong sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4194: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4195: gter ston do ban rgya mtsho zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4196: 'di gter gnas 'brog smad mu tig spa ma gong yin pa 'dra ste /
NK125(co)003:4197: gter ston yar 'brog do'i do ban rgya mtsho yin la /
NK125(co)003:4198: sgrags yang rdzong nas kyang gter mang po thon pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:4199: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4200: rgyal po'i mngar tshud bod kyi mi rnams kun //
NK125(co)003:4201: rang gi lto gos bsran nas sa hor gso //
NK125(co)003:4202: gnas brtan hor las dmag dpon byed pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4203: rdo bod mtshams su sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4204: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4205: gter ston rag shi ston pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4206: 'di ni gnyal du byon pa yin la /
NK125(co)003:4207: rdo bod mtshams zhes pa'ang gnyal yin pas lho bod zhes pa yi ge ma dag pa'o //
NK125(co)003:4208: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4209: sa yi ya swo rdzing gi ma swo can //
NK125(co)003:4210: gros 'thor mang zhing yul stong mang du 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4211: lho bod phyogs su sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4212: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung /
NK125(co)003:4213: rdza rong b+hi yi sman pa nyi 'od gsal //
NK125(co)003:4214: da lta shi yang srog 'thud shes pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4215: 'di ni yar 'brog rdza rong b+hi ru 'khrungs pa'i sman pa mkhas pa zhig ste /
NK125(co)003:4217: rong b+hi'i rdza la sman gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4218: zhes pa 'di yang bton nam snyam mo //
NK125(co)003:4219: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4220: dus ni lo re bzhin du ngan du 'gro //
NK125(co)003:4221: mkhan po byas nas grong du tshogs dbang bskur //
NK125(co)003:4222: lkog tu bud med khyi phag tsam pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4223: sde 'khrug nang dme rgyab brten dug la re //
NK125(co)003:4224: bu tshal gser khang sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4225: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4226: gter ston grwa sgom chos kyi rdo rje 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4228: bsam yas bu tshal nas rgyal po las rgyud dang /
NK125(co)003:4229: pe har ar gtad la sogs pa mang po thon no //
NK125(co)003:4230: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4231: sangs rgyas bka' la res gcod 'dra min byed //
NK125(co)003:4232: rdzogs chen rde'u zhes bya'i chos log 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4233: ri bong 'dzin zhes bswe sbyor sman log 'ong //
NK125(co)003:4234: bod rtsis drug cu bskor zhing gsal sgron zhes //
NK125(co)003:4235: rtsis rgyud kun dang mi mthun dar ba 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4236: gter mar grags pa'i bslu chos mang zhig 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4237: 'o yug g.yag lcer sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4238: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4239: gter ston g.yag phyar sngon mor grags pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4240: 'di la dpe mang por 'o yug g.yag sde zhes 'byung /
NK125(co)003:4241: o rgyan gling pas kyang g.yag sder dgongs 'dug ste dpe ma dag pa yin /
NK125(co)003:4242: 'o yug g.yag lce ni stang ngur zhes pa'i lung
NK125(co)003:4243: lag da lta khra chung zer te de yin par
NK125(co)003:4244: snang / bee ro tsa na'i chos gter yin te
NK125(co)003:4245: ding sang ni de'i skor sgra yang mi grag go
NK125(co)003:4246: snang / // 'di yang dus snga mo zhig ste
NK125(co)003:4247: rdzogs chen rde'u ni bla ma sro pas byas pa
NK125(co)003:4248: ste rde'u skor bdun pa zhes pa yod /
NK125(co)003:4249: de ni tshe snga phyi med /
NK125(co)003:4254: pha tshe rog po'i nang du lag pa bcug pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4255: ra rog po'i khong par lag pa bcug pa khyad par med /
NK125(co)003:4256: thugs rje chen po bsgom pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4257: gangs ri dkar po bsgom pa la khyad med /
NK125(co)003:4259: bong bu'i wong sgra 'don pa la khyad par med zer te /
NK125(co)003:4260: mu stegs chad lta ba dang mtshungs pa'i rdzogs chen sems phyogs de yin /
NK125(co)003:4261: rong zom gyi slob ma shangs pa lce ston zer ba gcig byung ste /
NK125(co)003:4262: de yang de ltar du smra /
NK125(co)003:4263: 'di ni lta spyod ya bral bas sangs rgyas pa'i chos su ma rung /
NK125(co)003:4265: rdzogs pa chen po pa la yar gyi gol sa brgyad bshad pa'i gcig yin te /
NK125(co)003:4266: lta ba mtho drag pas gong brgal te rtse mor bsnyegs pas phar rgyab la lhung ba lta bu /
NK125(co)003:4267: spyod pa khyad du gsod pas lam bgrod pa la
NK125(co)003:4268: rkang pa ya gcig med pa lta bur gsungs shing
NK125(co)003:4269: / lta ba'i mthar thug ka dag ste dge sdig
NK125(co)003:4270: las 'das pa'i steng du nyams len byas pa ni
NK125(co)003:4271: la zla ba'i tshul yin te mnyam bzhag gi dus
NK125(co)003:4272: / yin / rjes thob kyi dus su ni dge
NK125(co)003:4273: sdig blang dor byed dgos te shan 'byed pa'i dus
NK125(co)003:4274: / yin / yin / des na sro dang lce ston la sogs pas la zla ba dang /
NK125(co)003:4275: shan 'byed pa'i rnam dbye ma phyed pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:4276: ri bong 'dzin zhes pa'i gso dpyad ni bdag gis ma mthong /
NK125(co)003:4277: gsal sgron zhes dang drug cu'i skor ni /
NK125(co)003:4278: srog lus dbang gsum gyi sme ba mtshungs ldan du mi bskor bar /
NK125(co)003:4280: srog gi shing pho byi ba gcig /
NK125(co)003:4281: lus kyi shing pho byi ba bzhi //
NK125(co)003:4282: dbang thang shing pho byi ba bdun //
NK125(co)003:4283: mi gsum gnyer pa re mos bzhin //
NK125(co)003:4284: zer ba de yin par snang ngo //
NK125(co)003:4285: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4286: bod khams yongs kyi chos lugs dgod re bro //
NK125(co)003:4287: 'jig rten khyim pa'i kha nas chos skad re //
NK125(co)003:4288: ra rog phag rog khyad par med ces zer //
NK125(co)003:4289: chos med po rnams nad pa'i sngas bsrung byed //
NK125(co)003:4290: mi re'i lag na rtsis kyi shog khra re //
NK125(co)003:4291: rmongs pa khyu 'dril mkhas pa bskyar la 'don //
NK125(co)003:4292: mon kha spa gror sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4293: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4294: gter ston grum dang mkhar nag zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4296: dpe rnams su grub thob mkhar nag ces 'byung ba yang ma dag pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:4298: spa gro'i yon bdag nag po mkhar bya ba /
NK125(co)003:4299: yon mchod gnyis bsdebs te 'don par gsungs pa de yin /
NK125(co)003:4300: gza' bdud kyi gsang sgrub la sogs pa drag sngags mang ngo //
NK125(co)003:4301: rig 'dzin chen po ku m+aa ra dza'i gza' mthu 'jigs po de yang 'di'i sgrub skor du 'dug /
NK125(co)003:4302: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4303: mi thub lnga 'byung rang la yid mi ches //
NK125(co)003:4304: de 'dra'i dus na 'dre nad gdug pa dang //
NK125(co)003:4305: nad du mi 'ong bya ba gcig kyang med //
NK125(co)003:4306: bod kyi chos spyod sum cha nyams nas 'gro //
NK125(co)003:4307: 'on cang rdo la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4308: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4309: gter ston lha btsun sngon mo zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4310: 'di lha btsun byang chub 'od yin zhes o rgyan gling pas gsungs /
NK125(co)003:4311: bsam yas bu tshal ba'i zhal ngo lha btsun sngon
NK125(co)003:4312: mo zhes pas 'o yug nang khong gi brgya grong
NK125(co)003:4313: rdzong pa yul phud nas gling mkhar rdzong btab ste
NK125(co)003:4314: lha gling mkhar pa zhes grags /
NK125(co)003:4315: de rjes dpal ldan bla ma dam pa dang dus
NK125(co)003:4316: mtshungs par bsam yas su lha btsun sngon mo zhes
NK125(co)003:4317: pa gcig kyang byung bas su yin ma shes pas
NK125(co)003:4319: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4320: mi la lus chas ya ma zung du yong //
NK125(co)003:4321: bstan pa'i chos kyang ya ma zung du yong //
NK125(co)003:4322: dge rgyas bris pa'i ri mo shul rjes med //
NK125(co)003:4323: khams kyi srin mo rdzong gsum gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4324: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4325: gter ston khams pa nyi ma grags zhes 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4327: spre'u rlag can la sogs pa chos skor mang po bton par grags so //
NK125(co)003:4328: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4329: sa nang 'jigs brgyad sha ba'i rwa co 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4330: bsod nams zad pas dbus su mi rgod sdigs //
NK125(co)003:4331: dwags po ldang lhar sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4332: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4333: mnga' bdag sras mo rin chen tshul rdor 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4334: zhes pa sa skya pa la nang zhig sha ba'i
NK125(co)003:4335: ru ltar zing zing ba byung nas bsod nams zad
NK125(co)003:4336: khar / dpon chen rgyal bzang gis ta si byang
NK125(co)003:4337: rgyal ba btson du bzung ba de la dbus su
NK125(co)003:4338: mi rgod sdigs zer bar snang /
NK125(co)003:4339: mkha' 'gro snying thig la sogs pa zab chos mang po dang /
NK125(co)003:4346: gtad rgyud gsal sgron la sogs pa drag sngags bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK125(co)003:4347: de'i dus rgya hor gyi dmag dang gser yig pa 'dul ba la yang dgongs pa 'dra'o //
NK125(co)003:4348: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4349: dam sel brgyud pas slob ma gri ru 'chi //
NK125(co)003:4350: rdo yi mchod rten gdugs tog chos 'khor nyams //
NK125(co)003:4351: mon kha chu phug sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4352: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4353: gter ston tshe brtan rgyal mtshan zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4354: 'di mon la mo stod pa yin /
NK125(co)003:4355: snar thang pa yin yang zer /
NK125(co)003:4356: spa gro chu mo phug nas bla ma zhi drag /
NK125(co)003:4357: rdzogs chen mnyam nyid rang grol /
NK125(co)003:4362: lung bstan bka' rgya ma sogs rgya cher bton /
NK125(co)003:4363: dam sel brgyud pa ni slob mas 'phags pa rin po che bkrong pa yin par snang /
NK125(co)003:4364: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4365: bsgrub pa ma byas grub thob yin zhes zer //
NK125(co)003:4366: rang nyid ma smin gzhan la dbang bskur byed //
NK125(co)003:4367: pu ri rdza la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4368: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4369: gter ston sangs rgyas gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4370: zhes pa long po gyim zhes bya bar 'khrungs /
NK125(co)003:4372: gter phran skor la yang pod long dgu tsam bton no //
NK125(co)003:4373: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4374: dbus pa'i 'dun ma gcig dril sa hor skrag /
NK125(co)003:4375: sdig spyod bdud sprul bstan pa rgyas yun ring //
NK125(co)003:4376: 'bri thang ko ro brag gi gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4377: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4378: gter ston rin chen gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4380: rgya gar gyi pha bong rus sbal nag po dang /
NK125(co)003:4381: 'bri thang ko ro nas gter mang po thon /
NK125(co)003:4382: kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer las cung zhig bgres /
NK125(co)003:4383: ta si byang rgyal dang yang dus mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:4384: o rgyan gling pa dang yang ngo //
NK125(co)003:4385: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4386: yar lung mthil nas rnam smin bskyed pa'i rgyal po 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4387: phag gis sa slog dbus khams sa hor za //
NK125(co)003:4388: btsan rdzong brgya dang rtsa brgyad phyogs su 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4389: shel gyi brag phug sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4390: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4391: gter ston o rgyan gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4393: yar lung shel brag nas bka' 'dus chos kyi rgya mtsho la po ti sum cu so bdun /
NK125(co)003:4394: grwa g.yu sgong brag /'on phu stag tshang la sogs
NK125(co)003:4395: nas bton pa'i gter phran la yang po ti sum
NK125(co)003:4396: cu so bdun tsam pa'i chos gter dang /
NK125(co)003:4398: chos rgyal gyi dbon rgyal sras lha rje skye ba
NK125(co)003:4399: bdun pa de'i sku gdung sogs gter smyon yin pas
NK125(co)003:4401: gdung brgyud da lta yang e na yod do //
NK125(co)003:4402: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4403: sa hor dur sa dbus gtsang kun la 'debs //
NK125(co)003:4404: mchod rten 'og nas thod pa khyi yis g.yengs //
NK125(co)003:4405: bsam yas mchims phur sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4406: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4407: gter ston dri med 'od zer zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4408: 'dis mchims phu nas shog ril gsum tsam thon /
NK125(co)003:4409: gzhan ma bzhes kyang dgongs gter bstan bcos mang po mdzad /
NK125(co)003:4410: de dus mkhan po'i sku gdung has po ri'i rgyab
NK125(co)003:4411: tu mchod rten na bzhugs pa dbu thod thon pa
NK125(co)003:4413: mkhan po'i dbu thod byung ngo zer nas rtsed mo'i rol cha byas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4414: thang po che ba'i tshong btsun zhig dang 'phrad pas /
NK125(co)003:4415: khos mdzo khal dang bcas pa byin nas bslus te khyer /
NK125(co)003:4416: bsam yas pa rnams kyis rjes bsnyegs pas zin te
NK125(co)003:4417: dbu thod blangs pa da lta bsam yas kyi 'di
NK125(co)003:4418: yin la / dbu mal thang po che na yod /
NK125(co)003:4419: ta si byang rgyal gshegs pa'i lo de yin no //
NK125(co)003:4420: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4421: gtsang gi sgyer bur do ya gnyis su 'thab //
NK125(co)003:4422: rang thag khyung lung phag pa khyu gcig 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4423: kong po mchims yul sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4424: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4425: gter ston rat+na gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4426: 'di'i gter rtags la stod sgyer bu ba nang 'thab dus dang /
NK125(co)003:4427: gong ma grags 'byung ba'i dus yin /
NK125(co)003:4428: rat+na gling pas kong por byon skad ma thos kyang
NK125(co)003:4429: lho mon dbus gtsang rnams nas gter mang po bzhes
NK125(co)003:4430: / rgyud bcu bdun gyi bka' srung nag mo khros
NK125(co)003:4431: ma'i rgyud de ha cang rno drag pas mang po
NK125(co)003:4433: rig 'dzin chen po ku ma r+aa dzas ldang lha
NK125(co)003:4434: ru sbas pa de sngags srung rang gis lung bstan
NK125(co)003:4435: nas bton pa sogs ches mang ngo //
NK125(co)003:4436: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4437: mdza' bo nang 'khrugs tsher mas mtha' mi 'gugs //
NK125(co)003:4438: sa steng g.yo ba'i bdud kyi sprul pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4439: yum bu bla sgang sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4440: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4441: gter ston chos rje gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4442: 'di la 'ga' zhig na dpon rje gling pa zhes dang /
NK125(co)003:4443: rog rje gling pa zhes kyang snang /
NK125(co)003:4444: sngar byon pa'i lo rgyus ma thos so //
NK125(co)003:4445: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4446: bka' log khrims ral dam nyams lung pa gang //
NK125(co)003:4447: lha mi'i gnas su gtam ngan grags pas khyab //
NK125(co)003:4448: sha 'ug stag sgor sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4449: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4450: gter ston gter bdag gling pa zhes kyang 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4453: mi 'byon pa ni ga la srid snyam mo //
NK125(co)003:4454: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4455: sna bo la khar so pa res mos byed //
NK125(co)003:4456: mchod rten dkar por sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4457: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4458: gter ston kun skyong gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4459: 'di rdo rje gling pa'i skye ba yin /
NK125(co)003:4460: yang gter dang shog ser ma phyi 'theb sbas pa thon /
NK125(co)003:4461: rdo rje gling pa la gang yod kyi chos skor de yod /
NK125(co)003:4463: bo dong phyogs las rnam rgyal /
NK125(co)003:4464: rin spungs nor bzang rnams dang dus mtshungs so //
NK125(co)003:4465: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4466: nyang smad nyi ma mdo ru rdzong zhing 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4467: dmag dpon brgya rtsa lung stong phyi rtags 'jog /
NK125(co)003:4468: g.yas ru gtsang 'gram sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4469: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4470: o rgyan mdo sngags gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4471: 'di mchog ldan mgon po yin par grags te /
NK125(co)003:4472: sku skye snga ma kun skyong gling pa'i dus bdud
NK125(co)003:4473: mo zhig gis bskul nas dbang med du slob dpon
NK125(co)003:4474: pad+ma'i lung bstan ngan pa yod pa gcig la bzang
NK125(co)003:4475: por bcos pas rten 'brel 'phyugs te gter yang ma
NK125(co)003:4477: nyang smad nyi ma mdo ni pa nam lhun grub rtse yin /
NK125(co)003:4478: mchog ldan mgon po dus phyis byung bas dkrugs par mngon /
NK125(co)003:4479: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4480: yar 'brog mtsho gling dgu la dmag sgar 'cha' //
NK125(co)003:4481: stag 'thab nang du gtsang pa sum gnyis 'chi //
NK125(co)003:4482: rtsis kyi lha khang sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4483: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4484: o rgyan bstan gnyis gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4485: 'di dus rtags dbus gtsang 'thab pa'i skabs te /
NK125(co)003:4487: dbus kyi sne'u la sogs pa rnams su gtsang pa'i rdzong dpon dgon pa ba dpal bkras /
NK125(co)003:4488: shangs g.yang ldan rtse pa la sogs pa stag shar mang pos 'thab gral du bsad pa de yin /
NK125(co)003:4489: deng sang stag gru kha dang /
NK125(co)003:4490: thabs lud pa'i nang du yong par sems pa ni ma go ba'o //
NK125(co)003:4491: rin spungs ngag dbang rnam rgyal ba'i dus yar 'brog
NK125(co)003:4492: tu dmag sgar btab sogs sngar byung zin pa yin
NK125(co)003:4493: / gter ni sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'dus pa /
NK125(co)003:4503: bka' srung rnam sras gza' la sogs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4504: gter phran yang thig ye shes mthong grol /
NK125(co)003:4506: tshe sgrub tsit+ta'i rgya can la sogs pa byung ngo //
NK125(co)003:4507: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4508: stod lung yul du phag tshang khyu gcig 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4509: sa btsan ri bo re la rdzong chung re //
NK125(co)003:4510: la rtsub 'phrang rtsub gnyer med khyu yis 'tsho //
NK125(co)003:4511: kong po bu chur sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4512: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4513: gter ston o rgyan rdo rje gling pa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4514: zhes dus de ni gong ma zhabs drung skyor mo lung pas shun la rdzong btab /
NK125(co)003:4515: yar lung du sde gzar lo skor gcig tu langs pa'i skabs de yin par 'dug ste /
NK125(co)003:4516: dgongs te gsungs pa zhig gam /
NK125(co)003:4517: yi ge pas ma dag pa zhig yin /
NK125(co)003:4518: rdo rje gling pa ni kun skyong gling pa'i sku skye gong ma yin /
NK125(co)003:4519: karma pa rol pa'i rdo rje las lo drug gis bgres zhes pas de gong du byon par gsal /
NK125(co)003:4520: gter chos ni snying thig bcu gsum /
NK125(co)003:4521: bon rdzogs chen gser gyi yang zhun /
NK125(co)003:4522: rdzogs pa chen po lta ba klong yangs /
NK125(co)003:4525: brtan ma las rgya mtsho sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK125(co)003:4526: gter gnas kyang gnam lcags brag /
NK125(co)003:4529: mchims phu la sogs pa phal cher dbus gtsang lho mon nas byung bas /
NK125(co)003:4530: kong po bu chu ni gter ston gzhan zhig dang nor ba 'dra snyam mo //
NK125(co)003:4531: nyang po ru bde chen gling pa zhes pa'i gter
NK125(co)003:4532: ston gcig byung bas de dang dus 'grigs par 'dug
NK125(co)003:4533: / bde chen dang rdo rje yi ge nor ba 'dra'o //
NK125(co)003:4534: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4535: 'gos kyi phag rir gnas gzhi rdzong la 'gegs //
NK125(co)003:4536: la stod stag grur dug gi tshong 'dus 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4537: me 'bar mtsho la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4538: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4539: o rgyan pad+ma gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4540: 'di ni mon bum thang du chos 'khor ba dpon po thub pas khrom bsags te /
NK125(co)003:4541: gter thon na bya dga' chen po ster /
NK125(co)003:4542: ma thon na nga'i lung pa 'di zog pos 'gebs pas khrims las sgrol lo zhes byas pas /
NK125(co)003:4543: gter ston nyams 'ur te phyag tu sgron shing gcig
NK125(co)003:4544: la me sbar te zam pa'i kha nas mtsho nang
NK125(co)003:4545: du mchong / der khrom pa kun ku co dir gyis byung /
NK125(co)003:4547: dpon po thub pa yang skyengs te /
NK125(co)003:4548: pha ma la bu tshab ngas bya yis ma ngu zer skabs //
NK125(co)003:4549: da ci'i me de ma shi bar phyag g.yas su bsnams /
NK125(co)003:4550: mchan khung du la bswe'i gter sgrom chen po rdza ma tsam re bcug nas /
NK125(co)003:4551: sku lus chu'i zil ba phrom me gang nas byon cha med par byung /
NK125(co)003:4552: khrom mi mang thams cad la gter zhal phyes te byin rlabs byas pas /
NK125(co)003:4553: thams cad yid ches te snyan pas sa steng thams cad du khyab /
NK125(co)003:4556: chos gter bla rdzogs thugs gsum la sogs pa nyi zla ltar yongs la khyab /
NK125(co)003:4557: sngon gyi smon lam gyi mthus gter gyi bstan pa
NK125(co)003:4558: yang tshe lo sum cu'i bar du gnas par gsungs
NK125(co)003:4559: so // de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4560: rgya gar g+hu ta wa dang b+hi sa na //
NK125(co)003:4561: pan+di ta ni gnyis gsum bod du 'ong //
NK125(co)003:4562: lha sa'i jo shaka 'di la mchod pa byed //
NK125(co)003:4563: lho kong byang kong sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4564: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4565: o rgyan las 'phro gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4566: o rgyan las 'phro gling pa zhes sam 'ja' tshon snying po yang zer /
NK125(co)003:4567: kong yul nyang kha stod kyi mgon khang du 'khrungs /
NK125(co)003:4568: gter gnas kyang rngod hom 'phrang lcags kyi sgo mo nas yang zab dkon mchog spyi 'dus dang /
NK125(co)003:4569: rta phag yid bzhin nor bu /
NK125(co)003:4570: bu chu nas thugs rje chen po ngan song rang grol /
NK125(co)003:4572: sgam po zangs lung nas sgam po'i phyag rjes sogs gdan drangs pa'o //
NK125(co)003:4573: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4574: bod 'dir rgyal po'i ming btags brgya rtsa 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4575: gangs dang seng ge las kyis 'brel ba yis //
NK125(co)003:4576: 'jig rten pa la bde ba skad cig med //
NK125(co)003:4577: byar gyi brag la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4578: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4579: gter ston bsam gtan gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4582: mgon po zhal bzhi pa'i po ti rgyas pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4583: gzhan yang 'ga' re yod par grags so //
NK125(co)003:4584: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4585: sle ma mtshal gyi ri la bros shing yib //
NK125(co)003:4586: gnubs kyi sreg pa lung du mu ge 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4587: khyung tshang brag la sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4588: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4589: o rgyan zhig po gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4590: de la sle ma mtshal ni sa rtags bstan pa ste /
NK125(co)003:4591: de'i ri mo mtshal gyis bris pa ni bskyil 'phrang gi bum pa brag yin la /
NK125(co)003:4592: de'i byang bye thang gi ri la sbas lung sreg
NK125(co)003:4593: pa lung bya ba them chung bdun pa gcig yod
NK125(co)003:4594: pa de rnyi brdol gyis zhing rnams khyer te brlag
NK125(co)003:4595: pas de'i mi rnams la mu ge byung ba de
NK125(co)003:4596: yin par snang / yul chung de sngon skor thung
NK125(co)003:4597: shes rab ye shes bya ba rdzogs chen sems sde'i
NK125(co)003:4598: bla ma zhig byung ba de'i yul yin /
NK125(co)003:4602: bsam yas sogs nas gter bzhes /
NK125(co)003:4603: slob ma mang bas 'gro don che /
NK125(co)003:4604: gter ston 'di la bla ma dgongs 'dus kyi cha
NK125(co)003:4605: lag gter zhabs rgyal ba 'dus pa la sogs pa
NK125(co)003:4608: phal cher bka' gter gong ma rnams la thugs gtsigs su mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:4609: gsang sngags rnying ma'i bstan pa srog mthud pa lta bur gyur to //
NK125(co)003:4610: de nyid mi gnas mya ngan 'das 'og tu //
NK125(co)003:4611: rta rgod thang la dbus pa'i tshong 'dus 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4612: has po ri'i rgyud me 'bar rdzong zhes 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4613: kha rag phug tu sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4614: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4615: o rgyan bde chen gling pa zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4616: zhes lho brag tu byon pa des /
NK125(co)003:4618: tshe sgrub yid bzhin me long /
NK125(co)003:4620: dam rdzas myong grol sogs mang du thon /
NK125(co)003:4621: thugs spyod rtsings pas gzhan gyis bkrongs /
NK125(co)003:4622: de rjes sprul sku rim pa gnyis byon te gter ma bzhes so //
NK125(co)003:4623: de nas mi thog re la gter ston re byon pa ni dgongs pa can te /
NK125(co)003:4624: sngar mi thog re la gter ston 'ga' re 'dzom pa yang mang du 'byung /
NK125(co)003:4629: rang byung ye shes kyis lho brag mkhar chu nas thun mong gi skor mang po dang /
NK125(co)003:4630: zur mkhar gyi a jo dpal po dang /
NK125(co)003:4631: byang chub gling pa dpal rgyal mtshan dang /
NK125(co)003:4633: bswe ban nyi ma'i snying po /
NK125(co)003:4637: karma gling pa sogs gling pa brgyad /
NK125(co)003:4639: ye shes khyung brag /'jam dbyangs bla ma /
NK125(co)003:4642: kong po rags kha gter ston dang /
NK125(co)003:4646: lho brag byang chub gling pa /
NK125(co)003:4647: yar 'brog gi jo sras rtsing po /
NK125(co)003:4653: jo gdan dkon mchog grags la sogs pa gter 'don
NK125(co)003:4654: pa po bgrang par mi spyod pa dag byung bas
NK125(co)003:4655: / da rang mi 'byon pa 'dra snyam du yid skyo la /
NK125(co)003:4656: yang chos rje gling ba dang /
NK125(co)003:4657: gter bdag gling pa gnyis ni da phyis 'byon nges
NK125(co)003:4658: su bdag gi bla ma zhig po gling bas gsungs
NK125(co)003:4659: / rnal 'byor pa nus ldan rdo rje bya bas
NK125(co)003:4660: mdo khams su gter 'don bya ba'ang thang yig gcig
NK125(co)003:4661: na 'dug pa sngar ma byung ba 'dra zhing /
NK125(co)003:4662: deng sang dus ngan pa de lta bu'i skabs su
NK125(co)003:4663: 'gro don mdzad pa'i gter ston 'byon thang ba la
NK125(co)003:4664: / 'gro ba rnams kyi bsod nams la ma 'tshams
NK125(co)003:4665: sam ci zhig snyam du yid gdung bar gyur to
NK125(co)003:4666: / // nor gter rnams ni rgyal brgyud kyi don
NK125(co)003:4667: dang lha khang gso ba'i cha rkyen la dgongs pa
NK125(co)003:4669: dus phal cher bton nas brlag /'ga' zhig yod par
NK125(co)003:4670: / // yin te / grags / bsam yas rkyang
NK125(co)003:4671: pa'i dkor mdzod nas kha byang mang po yod pas
NK125(co)003:4673: lo ts+aa bas khong rang gi 'bul ba phyir bslog
NK125(co)003:4674: nas kha byang 'ga' zhig blang dgos /
NK125(co)003:4675: nga byams chen bzhengs pa'i cha rkyen ma ldang ba yin gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:4677: sems can gyi bsod nams dman pas /
NK125(co)003:4679: byi bas phad pa sogs mang po byung bas chud zos te 'dug /
NK125(co)003:4680: brul btub pa 'dra 'bul lo zer ba la /
NK125(co)003:4683: khyed rang 'di sgrub gsungs nas dzam nag gi gdams pa gnang ba ltar yin /
NK125(co)003:4684: deng sang chos gter thams cad slob dpon pad+ma'i dang /
NK125(co)003:4685: gter yig thams cad mtsho rgyal gyi phyag bris su byed de cung ma dgongs /
NK125(co)003:4686: chos gter ni slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK125(co)003:4693: sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms sogs rje 'bangs mang pos sbas pa yin la /
NK125(co)003:4694: spyir na rgya bod kha che li bal la sogs
NK125(co)003:4695: yul chen po rnams su bka' bsdu ba po rigs
NK125(co)003:4697: 'phags pa klu sgrub la sogs pas sbas pa'i gter yang bsam las 'das pa yod /
NK125(co)003:4698: rje 'bangs nyer lnga'i khrod kyi lo ts+aa ba mang pos phyis mnga' bdag dpal 'khor btsan dang /
NK125(co)003:4699: sras srong btsan 'bar gyi bar yun ring du bzhugs pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:4700: 'bre rgyal ba'i blo gros rong zom chos bzang gi bla ma yin /
NK125(co)003:4701: de mnga' bdag srong btsan 'bar dang dus mtshungs /
NK125(co)003:4702: rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyis mnga' bdag dpal 'khor btsan bsnyung dus rgyal po rtse mdos mdzad /
NK125(co)003:4703: blon po bka'i thang yig 'di yang dus phyi mo zhig la bsgrigs pa 'dra ste /
NK125(co)003:4704: sems sde'i bka' bab brgyad bgrang nas /
NK125(co)003:4705: zur chung pa'i slob ma rma thog byang 'bar dang /
NK125(co)003:4706: sgro phug pa'i slob ma bya sgom dang /
NK125(co)003:4707: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyi slob ma so ye shes dbang phyug dang /
NK125(co)003:4708: gnubs kyi slob ma dan yon tan mchog /
NK125(co)003:4709: de'i sras gu ma de ba zin tsam byung ba
NK125(co)003:4710: skor thung shes rab ye shes sogs byas 'dug pa
NK125(co)003:4711: / mi 'dod bzhin du khab len rdos nyul bzhin /
NK125(co)003:4712: gtad rgya 'don pa'i gter ston mang 'byung phyir //
NK125(co)003:4713: zhes gter ston chen po rnams kyis rang gi gter
NK125(co)003:4714: skal ma yin pa yang mang po blang chog pas
NK125(co)003:4716: btsun mo bka' thang sogs phyis zhig rnying ma ba 'dras sbas pa de /
NK125(co)003:4718: rjes 'jug rnams kyis slob dpon pad+ma'i gsung mtsho rgyal gyi phyag bris su bsam pa 'dra snyam mo //
NK125(co)003:4719: rgyal po bka' thang ni gu ru jo tse la yang yod /
NK125(co)003:4720: dpe phyi ma'i deb yod pa sbas pa o rgyan
NK125(co)003:4721: gling pa la'ang babs zhes bdag gi bla mas gsungs
NK125(co)003:4722: / dpal 'khor btsan gyi dus rma ban byang chub
NK125(co)003:4723: blo gros stod du 'bro rnams kyis mi sha la
NK125(co)003:4724: bkums pa rgyal por skyes te mnga' bdag la gnod
NK125(co)003:4725: / pa la / rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyis mdzad
NK125(co)003:4726: pa'i mdos kyi smreng yang yod de rgyal po rtse
NK125(co)003:4727: mdos kyi cha lag tu bkod nas lho brag mkhar
NK125(co)003:4729: dus phyis khams pa dar ber can gyis bton pa la sogs pa rgyu mtshan mang ngo //
NK125(co)003:4730: de lta bas na bod kyi rig 'dzin mang pos
NK125(co)003:4731: sbas pa phyis kyi gter ston rnams kyis thon pa
NK125(co)003:4732: la slob dpon pad+ma'i gter zhes ma zer cig /
NK125(co)003:4733: rgyu mtshan gzhan yang yod de /
NK125(co)003:4734: thang yig yi ge ma dag pa dang lhad zhugs
NK125(co)003:4735: pa rnams 'don pa'i tho byang phyis 'byon pa rnams
NK125(co)003:4737: de ltar gong du bshad pa'i gter ston dus rtags go rim nges pa las /
NK125(co)003:4738: ma nges pa kho na mang ba de ni dgongs
NK125(co)003:4739: pa can gyis bzung ste go rim 'chol ba yin
NK125(co)003:4740: nam / de ltar ma yin na yi ger 'god pa pos go rim nor ba yin pas /
NK125(co)003:4741: phyis kyi gang zag blo dang ldan pa rnams kyis snga phyi'i go rim bsdebs par rigs la /
NK125(co)003:4742: gal te rnying ma ba blun po dag ni tshul de lta bu la mi mgu mod kyi /
NK125(co)003:4743: de ni shes rab brgya ba las /
NK125(co)003:4744: gang zhig rang la shes rab med //
NK125(co)003:4745: de la bstan bcos ci byar yod //
NK125(co)003:4746: mig gnyis dag dang bral ba la //
NK125(co)003:4747: me long gis ni ci zhig bya //
NK125(co)003:4748: sbrul la 'o ma blud pa na //
NK125(co)003:4749: dug 'phel ba ni kho nar zad //
NK125(co)003:4751: 'on kyang o rgyan gling pas bal yul e'i gter
NK125(co)003:4752: ston gtsug lag dpal dge lha bla ma ye shes
NK125(co)003:4753: 'od dang dus mtshungs so zhes gsungs pa ltar /
NK125(co)003:4754: bstan pa la dad pa rnams kyis chos rgyus la 'dris par bya'o //
NK125(co)003:4756: mtha' dmag dbus rdib 'bri dang phag pa 'thab //
NK125(co)003:4757: dbus gtsang sil bu phag khyu tshal par 'gro //
NK125(co)003:4758: stag tshang zab lung sbas pa'i gter kha 'di //
NK125(co)003:4759: mi bzhag 'don pa'i rtags de bstan nas 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4760: gter ston rdo rje gro lod zhes bya 'byung //
NK125(co)003:4761: zhes pa 'di phal cher na mi snang yang rnying
NK125(co)003:4762: ma gcig gnyis na snang ba 'di ni da lta'i
NK125(co)003:4763: dus yin pa snyam mo zhes lho brag sprul sku
NK125(co)003:4764: gtsug lag phreng ba'i chos 'byung du bshad na /
NK125(co)003:4765: gter ston de sngar byon zin nam /
NK125(co)003:4766: phyis byon yang ma nges so //
NK125(co)003:4768: rgyal po'i bla gter dbu rtse rim gsum du //
NK125(co)003:4769: rje yi bla gter gter mdzod re re sbas //
NK125(co)003:4770: khams gsum zangs khang bu tshal gser khang gling //
NK125(co)003:4771: dge rgyas bye ma jo mo gling gsum du //
NK125(co)003:4772: rgyal po'i bla gter gter kha re re sbas //
NK125(co)003:4773: yak+sha ltag 'og gling bzhi gling phran brgyad //
NK125(co)003:4774: khrus khang gling dang tshang mang ke ru gling //
NK125(co)003:4775: mthu rtsal gling dang phyogs bzhi'i mgon khang bzhir //
NK125(co)003:4776: slob dpon pad+ma'i thugs gter re re sbas //
NK125(co)003:4777: mchod rten dkar por chos gter re re sbas //
NK125(co)003:4778: mchod rten dmar por rtsis sman mdos chog sbas //
NK125(co)003:4779: mchod rten nag por ngan sngags drag sngags sbas //
NK125(co)003:4780: mchod rten sngon por bzo gter rig gnas sbas //
NK125(co)003:4781: spyir na gtsug lag khang gi skor 'di la //
NK125(co)003:4782: 'dzam gling spyi la dgos pa'i gter kha lnga //
NK125(co)003:4783: bod khams spyi la dgos pa'i gter kha lnga //
NK125(co)003:4784: 'don du mi btub bcud la dgos pa lnga //
NK125(co)003:4785: bton nas gter tshab dgos pa'i gter kha lnga //
NK125(co)003:4786: ma bton dngos grub yal ba'i gter kha lnga //
NK125(co)003:4787: ming can nyer lnga ming med mang du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4788: mchims phu yang dben slob dpon thugs gter lnga //
NK125(co)003:4789: g.ya' ma lung du tshe sgrub tshe chu sbas //
NK125(co)003:4790: rdo yi mchod rten gsang gter re re sbas //
NK125(co)003:4791: dbus pad can la skor chu tshe chu sbas //
NK125(co)003:4792: rnam snang rgyab tu bka' gtad rab 'byams sbas //
NK125(co)003:4793: lho yi skyer chu lha khang zab gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4794: bum thang rtsis lung rje gter sems phyogs sbas //
NK125(co)003:4795: bum thang dge gnas yum gter ma mo sbas //
NK125(co)003:4796: glo bo dge dkar dgongs gter bstan 'gyur dang //
NK125(co)003:4798: g.yas ru gtsang 'gram yab gter gshin rje sbas //
NK125(co)003:4799: g.yon ru gtsang 'gram rdzas gter sna tshogs sbas //
NK125(co)003:4800: rtsis kyi lha khang phyi gter mdo sngags sbas //
NK125(co)003:4801: byang gi pra dun tse yi lha khang du //
NK125(co)003:4802: nang gter sman gter ngan sngags brgya rtsa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4803: khams kyi glang thang sgrol ma'i lha khang du //
NK125(co)003:4804: bar gter mi 'dra rgyud lung bcu gsum sbas //
NK125(co)003:4805: shar kong bu chu ngar legs lha khang du //
NK125(co)003:4806: rgya gter rdzu 'phrul sgyu ma sna tshogs sbas //
NK125(co)003:4807: rgyal rtse du ma gshin rje gdong kha dang //
NK125(co)003:4808: srin mo phung lung brag gsum myos thang dang //
NK125(co)003:4809: mdor na lho kong byang kong shar nub kong //
NK125(co)003:4810: kong po'i yul 'di pad 'byung 'dul zhing ste //
NK125(co)003:4811: bod gter chen po brgya dang rtsa brgyad sbas //
NK125(co)003:4812: gter phran stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis sbas //
NK125(co)003:4813: sbas pa'i yul dgu dben gnas brgyad kyang sbas //
NK125(co)003:4814: de rnams re rer bod gter brgya rtsa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4815: gter phran bye ba dgu khri gter du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4816: g.yo ru khra 'brug rdzas gter bub gcig sbas //
NK125(co)003:4817: shel gyi brag phug gsang gter bka' 'dus sbas //
NK125(co)003:4818: lho brag mkho mthing bde gshegs 'dus pa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4819: mkhar chu gnam skas brag la yongs rdzogs sbas //
NK125(co)003:4820: gtam shul srin mo sbar rjes gsang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4821: stag tshang seng phug thugs gter skor dgu sbas //
NK125(co)003:4822: mon kha ne ring seng ge rdzong gsum du //
NK125(co)003:4823: ma ning gter kha phran gter bco lnga sbas //
NK125(co)003:4824: spa gro gnam thang dkar nas 'bri mtshams bar //
NK125(co)003:4825: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i nor gter mang du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4826: pho ma rdzing phug gsang gter ngan sngags sbas //
NK125(co)003:4827: gtsang gi phug mo che ru tshe bdag sbas //
NK125(co)003:4828: yang phug ring mor klu bdud spu gri sbas //
NK125(co)003:4829: sgrags kyi yang rdzong phur pa thams cad sbas //
NK125(co)003:4830: grwa yi g.yu sgong brag la gter smyon sbas //
NK125(co)003:4831: mu tig sba ma gong la gsang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4832: zar po zangs mtsho brag la gter phran sbas //
NK125(co)003:4833: 'phyong rgyal bang sor nor gter chos gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4834: phying bar stag rtser dgongs gter zung zhig sbas //
NK125(co)003:4835: shams po gangs la gsang gter gter smyon sbas //
NK125(co)003:4836: gnyal gyi gdong kha brag nag mda' sgro la //
NK125(co)003:4837: sman dpyad gtsug lag bstan srung du ma sbas //
NK125(co)003:4838: gnyal smad dge ri nag po'i brag logs la //
NK125(co)003:4839: nor dang gter gyi kha byang mang du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4840: gsal rje gangs la phra men spu gri sbas //
NK125(co)003:4841: chos bgro thod dkar dpe srol lung pa la //
NK125(co)003:4842: dngul dpyad gser bre sil ma mang po sbas //
NK125(co)003:4843: za chu 'dus par gshin rje'i ngan sngags sbas //
NK125(co)003:4844: gnyal rong 'dom khar g.yu dang byi ru sogs //
NK125(co)003:4845: pho gyong bza' yi lus chas gos rgyan sbas //
NK125(co)003:4846: lug stod brag dkar gdong la nor g.yu sbas //
NK125(co)003:4847: sko ro ngam grog thugs gter brgya rtsa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4848: khal kha lha yul phug par gter phran sbas //
NK125(co)003:4849: byar gyi ltag chung gter phran gter smyon sbas //
NK125(co)003:4850: khra mo ldang lhar zab gter nges don sbas //
NK125(co)003:4851: byar dwags kong gsum slob dpon dgongs gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4852: rdo mon lo gnyal slob dpon gsang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4853: tsa ri'i gnas la gsang gter mang du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4854: 'ol kha'i mgar phug yum gter skor bzhi sbas //
NK125(co)003:4855: 'on gyi stag tshang gnyis par rgya mtsho sbas //
NK125(co)003:4856: bya pho ze ba brang gi brag rnams la //
NK125(co)003:4857: lha bzang klu dpal pho chas cha gcig sbas //
NK125(co)003:4858: zangs spyad lcags spyad sder cha brgya rtsa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4859: khrab sogs nor dang chos gter mang po sbas //
NK125(co)003:4860: phug pa'i nang du thun mong gter kha sbas //
NK125(co)003:4861: lo mo lo chur nor gter rkyang pa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4862: yar lung khra 'brug mchod rten mgo lnga la //
NK125(co)003:4863: zab gter rdzas gter dam rdzas mang du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4864: dgon thang gtsug lag khang gi brag ri la //
NK125(co)003:4865: nor gter chos gter dam rdzas 'ga' zhig sbas //
NK125(co)003:4866: 'phang thang gtsug lag khang gi rgyab ri la //
NK125(co)003:4867: rnam sras yon tan 'byung ba'i sgrub skor sbas //
NK125(co)003:4868: yum bu gla sgang skor la gsang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4869: btsan thang g.yu yi lha khang brag ri la //
NK125(co)003:4870: gter chen lnga dang gter chung dgu sbas so //
NK125(co)003:4871: mon mkhar mgon po gdong la thugs gter lnga //
NK125(co)003:4872: nor g.yu gser khrab dbul dang bral ba sbas //
NK125(co)003:4873: grwa phyi brag po che la bod gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4874: grwa yi zur gdong zur la ral gri sbas //
NK125(co)003:4875: dol gyi lce bde'i shar zur khrab rmog sbas //
NK125(co)003:4876: gzhung gi ra gong rgyab la gser grwa sbas //
NK125(co)003:4877: gtsang gi sil ma brag phug rdzogs chen spyi tig sbas //
NK125(co)003:4878: gtsang gi mang mkhar gangs la mthu 'bum sbas //
NK125(co)003:4879: mang yul dpal mo thang gi 'dre phug tu //
NK125(co)003:4880: bka' srung 'dus pa ngan sngags skor gsum sbas //
NK125(co)003:4881: byams pa sprin du sgrub thabs nyi shu sbas //
NK125(co)003:4882: gtsang gzhung snye mor mdo gcod rgyud gcod sbas //
NK125(co)003:4883: la stod srin po rdzong la zhi byed sbas //
NK125(co)003:4884: la stod ding ri ding chur yo ga sbas //
NK125(co)003:4885: lha rtse brag la a nu yo ga sbas //
NK125(co)003:4886: rgyang po lung la o rgyan rnam thar sbas //
NK125(co)003:4887: ra so klu dgug lung bstan mang du sbas //
NK125(co)003:4888: rdo rje gangs kyi dngul phug gsang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4889: grom pa rgyang du phyi gter nang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4890: zab bu lung du gsang gter dgongs gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4891: thugs gter gter kha brgya dang rtsa brgyad sbas //
NK125(co)003:4892: 'o yug g.yag lcer gter gyi yan lag sbas //
NK125(co)003:4893: spa gro chu mo phug tu thugs gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4894: g.yung phu rdza lhung gter phran rdzas gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4895: yer ba zla ba phug tu zab gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4896: zangs yag brag la thang yig gsang gter sbas //
NK125(co)003:4897: gzho stod ti sgror mkha' 'gro'i skor rnams sbas //
NK125(co)003:4898: stod lung 'phar ba tshang du phyag chen sbas //
NK125(co)003:4899: sha 'ug ltag sgor ma ning gter bcu sbas //
NK125(co)003:4900: dom tshang rong du gter phran 'dres ma sbas //
NK125(co)003:4901: lha sar gsang gter gter phran zur gcig sbas //
NK125(co)003:4902: mchims phu blon po mgul du bcud len sbas //
NK125(co)003:4904: mnga' bdag nyang gi thang yig le'u brgya dang rtsa bzhi par /
NK125(co)003:4905: lhan gyi za 'og brag la zhi byed sbas //
NK125(co)003:4906: rdur ru'i brag la o rgyan zhabs rjes sbas //
NK125(co)003:4908: de ltar bkod pa de dag kyang mdo tsam yin na de dag sngar thon zin pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4909: da 'don rgyu 'di dag yin zhes brjod par 'os mod kyang /
NK125(co)003:4910: rang re rnying ma pa spus dag rnams la zur tsam yang brjod rgyu med do //
NK125(co)003:4911: de ltar bstan zhabs gter gyis skyong ba'i tshul yang rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pas lung bstan te /
NK125(co)003:4912: mngon du zhugs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo las /
NK125(co)003:4913: nga mya ngan las 'das nas ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK125(co)003:4914: mdo sde 'di lo bzhi stong du 'dzam bu'i gling
NK125(co)003:4917: de'i 'og tu sa'i khung du song bar 'gyur ro //
NK125(co)003:4918: yang lo lnga brgya pa tha ma'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:4919: lnga brgya'i tha mar gyur ba /
NK125(co)003:4920: dam pa'i chos dang dge sbyong 'jig par 'gyur ba /
NK125(co)003:4922: tshul khrims dang ldan pa'i phyogs grum par 'gyur ba'i dus la babs pa /
NK125(co)003:4923: chos ma yin pa dar ba'i dus der /
NK125(co)003:4924: sngon gyi rgyal ba la bya ba byed pa /
NK125(co)003:4925: dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed pa /
NK125(co)003:4926: dge ba'i sa bon smin pa nyung zad cig 'byung ste /
NK125(co)003:4927: de lta bu dag gi don du ting nge 'dzin
NK125(co)003:4928: gyi mdo sde 'di sa'i khung nas phyungs te spyod
NK125(co)003:4930: bsgom pa dang rnal 'byor la brtson par 'gyur ro //
NK125(co)003:4933: nga ni phyi dus mya ngan 'das byas nas //
NK125(co)003:4934: sku gdung thams cad rgyas par byas gyur te //
NK125(co)003:4935: sangs rgyas byang chub 'di dag legs bzung ste //
NK125(co)003:4936: bris nas sgrom gyi nang du bcug byas nas //
NK125(co)003:4937: mchod rten sa dang brag dang ri dag dang //
NK125(co)003:4938: lha dang de bzhin klu yi lag dag tu //
NK125(co)003:4939: mdo sde bzhag par byas nas 'di dag rnams //
NK125(co)003:4940: lha yi brtul zhugs 'dra bar bya phyir 'gro //
NK125(co)003:4941: de dag phyi ma'i dus na so so'i rigs //
NK125(co)003:4942: thams cad bor te slad du babs gyur nas //
NK125(co)003:4943: sangs rgyas byang chub 'di dag legs bzung ste //
NK125(co)003:4944: bsam pa ji bzhin du ni byed par 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:4946: bris te sgrom gyi nang du bcug byas nas //
NK125(co)003:4947: zhes gter snod dang gter chos bstan /
NK125(co)003:4948: mchod rten sa dang phrag dang sogs kyis gter gnas /
NK125(co)003:4949: lha dang de bzhin klu yi lag tu bzhag gis gter srung dang /
NK125(co)003:4950: so so'i rigs thams cad bor te slad du babs gyur nas /
NK125(co)003:4952: bsam pa ji bzhin byed par 'gyur ni 'gro ba'i don chen po byed pa'o //
NK125(co)003:4953: gzhan yang gter ma 'byung ba'i tshul /
NK125(co)003:4954: bsod nams thams cad sdud pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mdo la sogs pa dang /
NK125(co)003:4955: mdo sde gzhan dag tu'ang 'byung bas de dag tu blta'o //
NK125(co)003:4957: gter ston tshad ma la zhal bgo //
NK125(co)003:4959: sgrub gnas kyi yon tan la sogs pa gsungs /
NK125(co)003:4960: ma 'ong lung bstan mang po gnang /
NK125(co)003:4961: dus kyi tha ma la bod la 'bros sa dgos /
NK125(co)003:4962: ma bros na hor dmag gis bod dmyal thag gcod pa gsungs /
NK125(co)003:4963: 'bras mo gshongs la sogs pa'i sbas yul rnams su //
NK125(co)003:4964: mnga' bdag rje 'bangs rnams slob dpon nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul la brten nas byon te /
NK125(co)003:4965: yon mchod bka' bgros nas gter kha mang du sbas /
NK125(co)003:4966: sbas yul rnams su 'gro ba'i lam yig mang po
NK125(co)003:4967: bris te gter ston chen po rnams kyi gter kha'i
NK125(co)003:4968: khrod du sbas / lha sa'i gtsug lag khang 'di khong gi snying lta bu yin /
NK125(co)003:4969: 'di ma stong na bod kyi bstan pa mi stong /
NK125(co)003:4970: de bas na 'di chus mi 'jig pa'i thabs la brtson pa bskyed dgos gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:4972: klu'i gdan 'dren bzlog pa'i thabs kyang mang po gsungs te yi ger bris /
NK125(co)003:4973: de nas glang lo bsam yas su lo gsar ma byed gsungs par blon pos ma nyan /
NK125(co)003:4974: 'o na rta ma rgyug gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:4975: ci zer rta los rgyug zer te blon pos ma nyan /
NK125(co)003:4976: der rta brgyugs pas khrom gseb nas rgyal po la 'jab mda' phog ste su yin ma shes /
NK125(co)003:4977: rgyal po bsnyung nas sku gshegs /
NK125(co)003:4978: sku 'das la sogs pa'i bya ba tshar nas /
NK125(co)003:4979: stag lo de la slob dpon srin yul du gshegs zhes bka' ma dag gi lo rgyus la yod /
NK125(co)003:4980: gter ma pa ni de rjes kyang lo gsum bzhugs par 'dod /
NK125(co)003:4981: gang ltar yang so so'i snang ngo la de ltar 'byung ba yin pas mi 'gal lo //
NK125(co)003:4982: de la gter ma ltar na 'das tshar nas mu ne btsan po rgyal sar bton pas /
NK125(co)003:4983: yum gyis dug btang ste rgyal sa zla ba drug las ma byung /
NK125(co)003:4984: der mu khri btsan po rgyal sar bton pas /
NK125(co)003:4985: slob dpon lho nub la gshegs pa la mu khri
NK125(co)003:4986: btsan po yab kyi mya ngan ma sangs pas bzhugs
NK125(co)003:4987: / has po ri la khrid de 'dus byas mi
NK125(co)003:4988: rtag pa'i chos gsungs rdzogs chen pad+ma snying thig gnang
NK125(co)003:4989: / / 'di rgyal po'i sdug bsngal sel byed nyon
NK125(co)003:4990: mongs rang grol bya ba de yin zhes mnga' ris
NK125(co)003:4991: / / pan chen gsungs / rgyal bus rdzogs pa chen po'i don mngon du gyur /
NK125(co)003:4992: der mkhan po bo d+hi sat+wa yang dre'usa phra shad rgyab te gshegs zer /
NK125(co)003:4993: lo rgyus la la na de'i sngon du gshegs kyang zer /
NK125(co)003:4994: gang ltar gdung dar zab kyis dril /
NK125(co)003:4995: tsan dan gyi sgrom bu rin chen sna tshogs kyis
NK125(co)003:4996: brgyan pa'i nang du bzhugs su gsol te has po
NK125(co)003:4999: slob dpon bo d+hi sat+wa'i gdung /
NK125(co)003:5000: has po ri yi rtsa ba ru //
NK125(co)003:5001: tsan dan sgrom du bzhugs su gsol //
NK125(co)003:5002: de yi rgyu mtshan 'di yin te //
NK125(co)003:5003: bod 'dir khrims ldan ches nyung yang //
NK125(co)003:5004: ser lpags gyon pas ri klung 'gengs //
NK125(co)003:5005: de ltar de dag thams cad kyang //
NK125(co)003:5006: bskal bzang 'di yi tha ma la //
NK125(co)003:5007: sangs rgyas mos pa'i nyan thos su //
NK125(co)003:5008: phyir mi ldog par 'gyur bar gsungs //
NK125(co)003:5010: yab gshegs nas slob dpon gyis lo gsum bzhugs par byed /
NK125(co)003:5011: de nas srin yul du gshegs par chas pas /
NK125(co)003:5012: rje 'bangs mchog dman bar ma thams cad mya ngan gyis non /
NK125(co)003:5015: der lha sras kyis 'jig rten gyi zas nor ri ltar spungs nas phul /
NK125(co)003:5016: srin po 'dul ba'i dus la babs pa la zhu bar mi spobs kyang /
NK125(co)003:5018: tha ma'ang lo gcig bzhugs par zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:5019: lo gcig bsdad kyang 'bral mi phod mod gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:5020: lha sras dran med du brgyal /
NK125(co)003:5022: slob dpon gyis lha sras thugs gso ba'i zhal gdams dang chos mang du gsungs /
NK125(co)003:5023: nga lus srog bral nas 'gro ba ltar ma yin mod /
NK125(co)003:5024: gzhan du song yang myur du mjal yod /
NK125(co)003:5025: dus bzang po la rmi lam du'ang mjal 'ong /
NK125(co)003:5026: 'di nas skyes rabs bco brgyad song ba'i tshe /
NK125(co)003:5027: nges par mjal te 'du 'bral med do //
NK125(co)003:5028: zhes gsungs 'bul ba rnams phyir slog /
NK125(co)003:5029: rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs pa yon
NK125(co)003:5030: mchod rnams khra 'brug tu byon te bka' 'dus chos
NK125(co)003:5032: dus der lha lcam man+d+hara dngos su byon nas dkyil
NK125(co)003:5033: 'khor la bskor ba byas nas slob dpon la brda
NK125(co)003:5034: don rtags kyi bstod pa mdzad /
NK125(co)003:5035: slob dpon la mos gus byas pa'i phan yon rgya cher gsungs te mkha' spyod du bzhud /
NK125(co)003:5036: slob dpon gyi rgyal sras lha rje khrid shog gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:5037: lta ba rdzogs chen pad+ma snying thig /
NK125(co)003:5038: yi dam bka' 'dus chos kyi rgya mtsho /
NK125(co)003:5039: bla ma bstan gnyis skor gsum gyi chos bdag tu
NK125(co)003:5040: dbang bskur te gter ston o rgyan gling par lung
NK125(co)003:5041: bstan / rgyal sras 'di skye bdun yin pas sku
NK125(co)003:5042: gdung gter du sbos gsungs te dgung lo bco lnga
NK125(co)003:5043: la gshegs pa gter du sbas par gsungs /
NK125(co)003:5045: mon mo bkra shis khye'u 'dren gnyis kyis shel brag tu spyan drangs /
NK125(co)003:5047: thang yig na skabs 'dir pe har 'khor bcas kyis glag btsal ba dang btul ba'i tshul bshad do //
NK125(co)003:5049: klu rigs lnga byung ba sogs kyang dam la btags /
NK125(co)003:5050: gza' klu rgyal po gsum gyi bcos ka dang bsrung ba sogs kyi yig sna mang du mdzad /
NK125(co)003:5051: lha 'dre thams cad byung ste dam la bzhag go //
NK125(co)003:5052: de nas lha sras rje 'bangs la zhal ta gsungs te bsam yas dbu rtser 'di skad gdams pa /
NK125(co)003:5053: kho thag ma chod bar dung la dris //
NK125(co)003:5054: nan tan zhu ba da lta'i dus 'di yin //
NK125(co)003:5055: nan chags mdzad na kho thag chod de mchi //
NK125(co)003:5056: blo snying brang gsum pad+ma la gtod //
NK125(co)003:5057: bslus na pad 'byung zhan no rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5058: drang por smras na yid ches mi skye zhing //
NK125(co)003:5059: tshig gron bcug na chos min las ngan gsog /
NK125(co)003:5060: bla ma bsten yun srings shig rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5061: na so gzhon dus dam chos rem la gyis //
NK125(co)003:5062: rgas nas byed dus 'byung bas 'chun por dka' //
NK125(co)003:5063: tshe 'di skad cig yin no rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5064: rtog pa rags dus nang du mkhan po tshol //
NK125(co)003:5065: ched du spang blang mi dgos rang sar zhog /
NK125(co)003:5066: lta bas thag chod dgos so rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5067: nyon mongs zad nas chos la bya ru med //
NK125(co)003:5068: snying rje med na chos kyi rtsa ba rul //
NK125(co)003:5069: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal yang nas yang du soms //
NK125(co)003:5070: chos la phyi bshol ma byed rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5071: mos gus can gyi rang don 'grub pa yin //
NK125(co)003:5072: gzhan la chos yus drin bzhag bya ru med //
NK125(co)003:5073: snying rus ma chung bsgrub pa rem du gyis //
NK125(co)003:5074: tshe gang dus brgya'i za ma lan gcig yin //
NK125(co)003:5075: dri gos mdun du chos bshad ci la phan //
NK125(co)003:5076: ma shi dus na chos la nan cher nyon //
NK125(co)003:5077: mtshan byang mgo la dbang bskur byed tshe 'phyis //
NK125(co)003:5078: lo re bzhin du dbang bskur byin rlabs zhus //
NK125(co)003:5079: rnam shes bar do khyi glen bzhin du 'khyams //
NK125(co)003:5080: mtho ris 'dren ste de la dka' las yod //
NK125(co)003:5081: gzugs med bag chags lus de rkyen khar yangs //
NK125(co)003:5082: gar 'khyog mi shes wal le bsam zhig thong //
NK125(co)003:5083: bsgrub pa lo ru bsags na dngos grub 'byung //
NK125(co)003:5084: dam chos gyis la 'bad pa chos phyogs thon //
NK125(co)003:5085: bod yul chos kyi nyi ma zer la khad //
NK125(co)003:5086: brda de go bar mdzod cig rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5087: gdung sems can la pad 'byung gshegs pa med //
NK125(co)003:5088: gsol ba 'debs la pad 'byung sgo nyal yod //
NK125(co)003:5089: tshe zad nad la sman gyis phan pa dka' //
NK125(co)003:5090: zhag tu gcig song gnyis song mi tshe zad //
NK125(co)003:5091: long yod po tsho 'chi khar khres khres byed //
NK125(co)003:5092: a re 'gyod de bag tsam 'phyis pa 'dra //
NK125(co)003:5093: sdig pa'i bsu ma sngon la 'ong nyen che //
NK125(co)003:5094: ngus pas mi phan sems la snying rus bskyed //
NK125(co)003:5095: 'khor ba'i skyon mthong dam chos mi byed na //
NK125(co)003:5096: don snying nang khrol rul lo rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5097: lam 'grul lus pas zla bo bsnyegs pa bzhin //
NK125(co)003:5098: pad 'byung 'gro sa lho nub rnga yab gling //
NK125(co)003:5099: gos zad dug po gsar par mi 'gyur bzhin //
NK125(co)003:5100: da ni pad 'byung bshol yang bshol mi thebs //
NK125(co)003:5101: 'chi kha'i nad pa snum zad mar me bzhin //
NK125(co)003:5102: tshe yi 'phel rkyen zad pas bsdad dbang med //
NK125(co)003:5103: de bzhin sdong po skam pa'i yal 'dab bzhin //
NK125(co)003:5104: bod du mi sdod pad 'byung srin yul 'gro //
NK125(co)003:5105: ljong shing kha nas bya tshogs 'phur pa bzhin //
NK125(co)003:5106: skad cig mi sdod pad 'byung skyas gcig 'degs //
NK125(co)003:5107: yon mchod gyes so lha sras rje 'bangs rnams //
NK125(co)003:5109: lha sras rje 'bangs rnams kyis grab byas te mang yul gung thang la khar thab btegs /
NK125(co)003:5110: yon mchod rnams chas te zur mkhar rdo'i mchod rten du chibs gzhol /
NK125(co)003:5111: 'bul ba bsnyen bkur phul te chos dang gdams pa mang du gsungs /
NK125(co)003:5112: zab lam bla ma'i rnal 'byor gnang /
NK125(co)003:5113: de nas lha sar phebs te rab gnas bskyar /
NK125(co)003:5114: nor bu dgos 'dod kun 'byung gter du sbas /
NK125(co)003:5115: der rje 'bangs nyer lngas thog drangs /
NK125(co)003:5116: mkhan po sh+aakya bla ma la sogs pa btsun pa thams cad dang /
NK125(co)003:5117: bee ro ts+aa na dang ska cog la sogs pa lo ts+aa ba thams cad dang /
NK125(co)003:5118: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes dang rdo rje bdud 'joms la sogs pa sngags pa thams cad dang /
NK125(co)003:5119: bla sman nyang tsha sh+r+ai la sogs pa sman pa thams cad dang /
NK125(co)003:5120: bla mkhyen byang ston khu lu la sogs pa rtsis pa thams cad dang /
NK125(co)003:5121: mkha' 'gro ye shes mtsho rgyal dang /
NK125(co)003:5122: ngang btsun dpal gyi rgyal mo la sogs pa mo btsun thams cad dang /
NK125(co)003:5123: yon bdag mkhar chen rgyal ba la sogs pa thams
NK125(co)003:5124: cad kyis mgrin gcig tu bzhugs par zhus kyang ma
NK125(co)003:5125: gnang bas / thams cad mig mchi mas gang ste yus kyis brnangs /
NK125(co)003:5126: de nas byon te bshol ma thebs pa'i phyi bzhin
NK125(co)003:5127: du rje 'bangs rnams bsnyegs te de nub bzhugs sar
NK125(co)003:5128: / da slob dpon ni srin yul la gshegs /
NK125(co)003:5129: yab rgyal po ni dgung la gshegs /
NK125(co)003:5130: bod mun khung ltar gyur pa la thugs brtse bar dgongs nas gdams pa gcig zhu zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:5131: thugs rje chen po'i gdams pa gnang /
NK125(co)003:5132: de nas yar gshegs te ri glang ru'i thang du phebs /
NK125(co)003:5133: 'dir ma 'ongs pa na sa zhes bya ba'i gtsug lag khang dang dge 'dun gyi sde 'byung zhing /
NK125(co)003:5134: 'jam dbyangs kyi sprul pa bdun brgyud 'byon pas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gsal bar byed de /
NK125(co)003:5135: phung byed hor gyi sna 'dren bas bod la drin du che ba rang mi 'ong gsungs /
NK125(co)003:5136: rje 'bangs thams cad la so sor zhal gdams gnang /
NK125(co)003:5137: der thams cad slob dpon gyi zhal la blta zhing kyi hud kyi smre sngags 'byin /
NK125(co)003:5138: gnam shin tu dwangs pa la lha 'dre rnams ngus
NK125(co)003:5139: pa'i mchi mas mi kun gyi gos slag bang ba
NK125(co)003:5140: byung / der yang zhal gdams mang du gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:5141: gung thang la thog nas nga 'gro gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:5142: thams cad khong gi snying bton pa ltar gyur te /
NK125(co)003:5151: kun gyi mig mchi mas gang bas lam ma mthong zhing skad ma thon no //
NK125(co)003:5152: der yud cig nas mgur mang po gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:5154: khyed rnams zo mdog bde dus 'dir //
NK125(co)003:5156: da lta srin po ma btul na //
NK125(co)003:5157: 'dzam gling srin gyis stong par byed //
NK125(co)003:5159: bod rnams sku khams ci bder bzhugs //
NK125(co)003:5160: zhes gsungs pas sprin gyi gseb nas rta mchog rin po che byung ste slob dpon de la chibs /
NK125(co)003:5161: lha mang pos mchod pa'i sprin phung bsam gyis mi
NK125(co)003:5162: khyab pas mchod cing lha'i rol mo glu dbyangs du
NK125(co)003:5163: mas bstod pa dang bcas te bar snang la gshegs
NK125(co)003:5164: zer / seng ge chibs te gshegs yang zer te so so'i snang ba la shar ba'o //
NK125(co)003:5165: der rje 'bangs rnams nya bye tshan la bor ba ltar gyur te /
NK125(co)003:5169: rkang pa sa la btsugs pas 'gyel te sdug bsngal lo //
NK125(co)003:5170: de nas mchi ma phyis te bltas pas /
NK125(co)003:5171: nyi zer gyi dbus na bya rog tsam /
NK125(co)003:5172: de nas bltas pas je chung la song ste /
NK125(co)003:5173: re zhig song ba na cang ma mthong /
NK125(co)003:5174: de nas mnyam par bzhag ste bltas pas /
NK125(co)003:5175: rgya gar dang o rgyan gyi sa mtshams zangs ri kha bya ba zhig na bzhugs par mthong /
NK125(co)003:5177: bdag cag gi rje lha sras da ji ltar bgyi /
NK125(co)003:5178: zhes yid kyis gsol ba btab pas /
NK125(co)003:5180: khams gsum 'khor bar skyes pa sdug bsngal btson dong yin //
NK125(co)003:5181: chos skyong rgyal por skyes kyang 'du 'dzi g.yeng ba'i gnas //
NK125(co)003:5182: rgyal po chen po sems nyid klong gsal ltos //
NK125(co)003:5183: phyi ma rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur //
NK125(co)003:5184: zhes gdams pa de lha sras kyi snyan du gsol /
NK125(co)003:5185: de nas rje 'bangs rnams tshur log byon /
NK125(co)003:5186: lha sras zab bu la 'byon par bzhed kyang /
NK125(co)003:5187: blon po rnams kyis bsam yas la spyan drangs nas /
NK125(co)003:5188: yab mes kyi mdzad srol bzang pos mnga' 'bangs chos
NK125(co)003:5189: bzhin du bskyangs te bod khams bde ba la bkod
NK125(co)003:5190: / sangs rgyas bstan pa'i zhabs tog rgya cher mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:5191: de ltar slob dpon chen po 'dis rgya bod du
NK125(co)003:5192: lo ji ltar bzhugs pa'i lo grangs thang yig tu
NK125(co)003:5193: bshad pa ni / in+d+ra bo d+hi'i khab tu lo lnga /
NK125(co)003:5194: bsil ba'i tshal du lo lnga /
NK125(co)003:5195: chos la sbyangs pa lo bcu /
NK125(co)003:5206: yul bcu po re rer nyis brgya re bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:5217: de ltar yul bcu po de re rer dgu bcu go brgyad go brgyad re bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:5218: bal yul du lo bzhi bcu ste /
NK125(co)003:5219: de dag bsdoms pas sum stong drug bargya'o //
NK125(co)003:5224: klu yul rnams rgya gar la mi gtogs te /
NK125(co)003:5225: slob dpon sku 'khrungs pa nas bod du byon pa
NK125(co)003:5226: phan chad kyi lo grangs phyogs gcig tu bsdoms pa
NK125(co)003:5227: yin / stag gzig ni stod hor dang /
NK125(co)003:5228: ge sar hor yin pa dang /
NK125(co)003:5229: rgyal po byi je mer gan du mdzad pa de yin par snang /
NK125(co)003:5230: bsam yas dbu rtser lo drug cu /
NK125(co)003:5232: de ltar byas na brgya dang bcu gcig gi grangs mi 'grigs par 'dug /
NK125(co)003:5234: sgrags yang rdzong du lo gsum /
NK125(co)003:5235: g.ya' ma lung du lo bzhi /
NK125(co)003:5237: mu tig spa ma gong du lo gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5238: sham po gangs su lo gsum /
NK125(co)003:5239: g.yu sgong brag la zla ba gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5240: lho brag mkhar chur lo bdun /
NK125(co)003:5241: 'brin thang gsal rjes brag la zla ba bcu /
NK125(co)003:5242: zab bu lung du lo gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5243: zangs yag dpal phug tu zla ba gsum /
NK125(co)003:5244: gzho stod ti sgror lo bdun /
NK125(co)003:5245: 'phar ba tshang du lo gcig /'ol kha mgar phug tu zla ba gcig /
NK125(co)003:5247: kha rag dang chu bo rir lo gcig /
NK125(co)003:5248: o dkar brag phug tu zla ba gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5249: tsa ri ru zla ba drug /
NK125(co)003:5250: khyung tshang brag tu zla ba drug /
NK125(co)003:5251: snye mo snying drung du zla ba drug /
NK125(co)003:5252: blon po mgul du zla ba drug /
NK125(co)003:5253: snying po rdzong du zla ba gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5254: mon kha ne ring du zla ba gsum /
NK125(co)003:5255: spa gro stag tshang du zla ba bzhi /
NK125(co)003:5256: spa gro chu mo phug tu zla ba gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5257: brag mtha' khra mor zla ba gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5259: mkhar chen brag la lo gcig /
NK125(co)003:5260: spa gro cal gyi brag la lo gcig /
NK125(co)003:5261: lha ri gangs la lo gcig /
NK125(co)003:5262: g.yung rdza lhung du zla ba gsum /
NK125(co)003:5263: mon bon brag la zla ba gsum /
NK125(co)003:5264: 'on phu stag tshang du zla ba gsum /
NK125(co)003:5265: zar mo ri la zla ba gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5266: dwags rdzong phug par lo gcig /
NK125(co)003:5267: byar gyi stag chung brag tu zhag gsum /
NK125(co)003:5268: dom tshang rong du zhag lnga /
NK125(co)003:5269: stag tshang rong du zhag lnga /
NK125(co)003:5270: gzig tshang rong du zhag dgu /
NK125(co)003:5271: spyang tshang rong du zhag drug /
NK125(co)003:5272: mkha' 'gro brag phug tu zla ba bzhi /
NK125(co)003:5273: lha rtse brag la zla ba bzhi /
NK125(co)003:5274: rong b+hi'i rdza la zla ba gcig /
NK125(co)003:5275: mchims kyi sngog lung du zla ba gcig /
NK125(co)003:5276: gong chung lung du zla ba phyed /
NK125(co)003:5277: mgrin bzang du zla ba phyed dang gnyis /
NK125(co)003:5278: lha sa dang khra 'brug tu zla ba phyed dang gnyis re /
NK125(co)003:5279: gtsang phung po ri bo che ru zla ba gsum ste /
NK125(co)003:5280: 'di la lo brgya dang bcu gcig /
NK125(co)003:5281: zhag nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'ong bar snang la /
NK125(co)003:5282: bsam yas dbu rtser lo drug bzhugs pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK125(co)003:5283: lo lnga bcu nga drug dang zhag nyer brgyad 'ong bas /
NK125(co)003:5284: de ltar na bod du lo hril po yin pa 'dra /
NK125(co)003:5285: bla ma rnams ni bgrod pa re la lo re ru byas pa'i phyed lo yin zhes gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:5286: blo dang ldan pa rnams kyis dpyad par bya'o //
NK125(co)003:5288: bum thag rdo rje brtsegs pa'i brag dang /
NK125(co)003:5289: sba gro brag dkar la sogs pa bzhi ru sku rjes bzhag /
NK125(co)003:5290: kong po brag gsum gyi mtsho la sogs pa bzhi la phyag rjes bzhag ste /
NK125(co)003:5291: gnam mtsho phyug mo'i phyag rjes de ni mda' rgyang las ring ba tsam zhig yod la /
NK125(co)003:5292: gzhan yang rjes 'jug gdul bya mos pa'i rten du
NK125(co)003:5293: sgrub gnas rnams su slob dpon yab yum gyi phyag
NK125(co)003:5294: zhabs kyi rjes ngo mtshar can mang du bzhag par
NK125(co)003:5295: mdzad do // bod yul du slob ma grub pa thob pa'ang snga thog la rje 'bangs nyer gcig /
NK125(co)003:5296: phyi thog la rje 'bangs nyer lnga /
NK125(co)003:5297: thugs sras snying gi bu dgu la sogs ni gter ma ba la grags pa 'di dang /
NK125(co)003:5298: bka' ma rong zom gyis mdzad pa'i chos 'byung du /
NK125(co)003:5300: yer ba'i grub thob 'od lus grub pa brgyad cu /
NK125(co)003:5301: chu bo ri'i sgom chen brgya dang brgyad yod pa las /
NK125(co)003:5302: lha lung dpal rdor gyis rgyal po bsad pas khams phyogs la bros te 'od lus ma 'grub /
NK125(co)003:5303: gzhan brgya dang bdun po 'od lus la gshegs so zhes bshad snang yang /
NK125(co)003:5304: de dag gi mtshan gyi rnam grangs ma smos pas 'adi'o zhes bgrang bar ma nus /
NK125(co)003:5305: yi ge gzhan du mchims phu na grub chen nyer lnga /
NK125(co)003:5307: mar gong bza' la sogs pa rnal 'byor ma bcu bdun /
NK125(co)003:5308: chu bo ri na dpal gyi ye shes la sogs pa grub chen sum cu so lnga /
NK125(co)003:5309: nyang ting 'dzin bzang po sogs yer pa na grub chen brgya dang bdun /
NK125(co)003:5310: de thams cad 'ja' lus su gshegs /
NK125(co)003:5311: lha lung dpal rdor gong ltar du 'chad /
NK125(co)003:5312: de dag tu ma zad slob dpon gyi dngos slob ni mtha' yas pa zhig byon par snang ste /
NK125(co)003:5313: phag mo grub pa'i yang mes a mes byang chub
NK125(co)003:5314: 'dre bkol bya ba de yang slob dpon 'di'i dngos
NK125(co)003:5315: slob grub pa thob pa zhig yin /
NK125(co)003:5316: grub chen o rgyan ba'i yang mes rgyus byang chub
NK125(co)003:5317: gzhon nu zhes mdo khams dbyar mo thang du byon
NK125(co)003:5318: pa de yang slob dpon gyi dngos slob yin /
NK125(co)003:5319: rog ban nam mkha' ye shes zhes rog shes rab 'od kyi yang mes de yang yin la /
NK125(co)003:5320: rog ban nam ye nas gdung rabs nyer bzhi 'das pa na rog shes rab 'od byon te /
NK125(co)003:5321: de yan chad du grub thob kyi brgyud pa bar ma chad par byon zhes 'byung /
NK125(co)003:5322: mnga' bdag nyang gi yang mes nyang de bzhin gshegs pa rta mgrin gyi grub thob de dang /
NK125(co)003:5323: yang nyang mchog rab gzhon nu bya ba sngags 'chang
NK125(co)003:5324: grub thob gcig byung ste khong la slob dpon pad+mas
NK125(co)003:5325: gnang ba'i 'khrul 'khor rtsa 'grel la sogs pa man
NK125(co)003:5326: ngag zab mo mang zhig kyang yod la /
NK125(co)003:5327: gu ru chos dbang gi yang mes dbang rje btsan khrom bya ba de yang yin te /
NK125(co)003:5328: de ni snyegs bon sna rings bya bas da rgyal po la thog phab kyi sgug sdod byas par /
NK125(co)003:5330: nga'i gdan pho brang thog tu thing /
NK125(co)003:5332: de'i gnang nyin thog mda' bdun phab byung ba la /
NK125(co)003:5333: sdig mdzub la dkris te slar bon po la 'phangs bas /
NK125(co)003:5334: bon po 'khor dang bcas pa shi'o zhes 'byung ba de yin /
NK125(co)003:5335: sha mi rnams kyi yang mes sha mi go cha bya ba nam mkha' la 'phur pa de dang /
NK125(co)003:5336: glang bu se po zhes pa rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston pa de dang /
NK125(co)003:5337: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug dang /
NK125(co)003:5338: shug sdong rtsa ba nas bton te khyer nas btsan
NK125(co)003:5339: thang lha khang ka ba btsugs pa'i dge bsnyen ngom
NK125(co)003:5341: ngab mi byang chub rgyal mtshan /
NK125(co)003:5343: yar lung smon spro'i ngab mi can tsong bya ba dang /
NK125(co)003:5346: dpal ldan sa skya pa'i yang mes mkhon klu dbang
NK125(co)003:5347: srung la sogs pa bod kyi che rgu phal che
NK125(co)003:5348: ba'i yang mes rnams kyang dngos slob tu byung 'dug
NK125(co)003:5349: pas / slob dpon pad+ma bod du yun ring du bzhugs pa'i gtan tshigs de lta bu yin no //
NK125(co)003:5350: gong du bshad pa ltar sba bzhed las yun ring
NK125(co)003:5351: ma bzhugs par bshad pa de yang kha cig gi
NK125(co)003:5352: snang ngo la bden pa yin te /
NK125(co)003:5353: slob dpon khyad par can de sdig blon rnams kyis
NK125(co)003:5354: mtha' mi ngan sngags mkhan gser 'dod can gcig tu
NK125(co)003:5356: 'ga' zhig gis ni slob dpon gyi sku mthong thos ma byung bar yang bshad pa'i phyir te /
NK125(co)003:5357: de dag ni sngon drang srong skar ma la dga'
NK125(co)003:5358: bas bcom ldan 'das phyi rol pa'i drang srong rang
NK125(co)003:5359: 'dra ba gcig tu mthong ba dang tshul mtshungs so
NK125(co)003:5360: // sba bzhed dang mthun par rta mgrin yang gsang
NK125(co)003:5361: gi lo rgyus su yang rgyal po la rta mgrin
NK125(co)003:5363: slob dpon gshegs par bzhed pa la /
NK125(co)003:5364: rgyal pos bzhugs par zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:5365: bdag bod yul du sdod na /
NK125(co)003:5366: rgyal po sku tshe nyi zla dang mnyam par bya /
NK125(co)003:5368: byis phrug la gzi'i rna cha 'dogs pa yin pas /
NK125(co)003:5369: khyed rang blon po rnams tshogs la gros gyis gsungs pas /
NK125(co)003:5370: blon po rnams gros byas pas /
NK125(co)003:5371: rgyal po sku tshe nyi zla dang mnyam na blon po la gros kyi dbang mi yong /
NK125(co)003:5372: gtsang po sbubs su bcug na khas drag zhan dang yul bzang ngan gyi shan mi phyed /
NK125(co)003:5373: byis phrug la gzi'i rna cha btags na byis pa
NK125(co)003:5374: de la yengs nas bza' btung dang gos mi dran
NK125(co)003:5376: matha'i mon phrug kho rang phar slog zer kha dan /
NK125(co)003:5377: rgyal pos kyang khrims la 'gal ma nus par slob dpon gshegs /
NK125(co)003:5379: bdag rjes su 'dzin par zhu zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:5381: lho nub na srin po kha gnon pa dang gdul bya yod pas der 'gro zhing /
NK125(co)003:5382: rgyal po khyed dang lhan cig 'og min gnas su mjal lo gsungs nas /
NK125(co)003:5383: ru lag gi phyogs la yar byon pas /
NK125(co)003:5384: ru lag gi lha 'dre rnams kyis ma bzod par g.yas rur bros pas /
NK125(co)003:5385: da lta yang g.yas ru ba rnams mdze can dang
NK125(co)003:5386: mi'u thung mang ba'i rgyu mtshan de yin zhes bshad
NK125(co)003:5387: la / yang yun ring bar bzhugs tshul gcig kyang byung ste /
NK125(co)003:5389: de dus o rgyan pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK125(co)003:5390: za hor mkhan po bo d+hi sat+wa /
NK125(co)003:5391: kha che'i slob dpon bi ma la mi tra /
NK125(co)003:5392: sing ha'i slob dpon d+ha na ta la /
NK125(co)003:5393: rgya gar gyi ka ma la sh+ai la dang /
NK125(co)003:5394: de lnga'ang skad mi mthun te /
NK125(co)003:5395: lo ts+aa ba ska ba dpal brtsegs /
NK125(co)003:5398: ba gor bee ro tsa na /
NK125(co)003:5399: 'og g+hom 'phrul 'byed dang lnga ni sgra bsgyur gyi lo ts+aa bar bzhag go //
NK125(co)003:5400: mchan bu'i lo ts+aa ba ni /
NK125(co)003:5405: shud bu a ba dang lnga'o //
NK125(co)003:5406: de rnams +aar+ya pa lo'i gling du spyan drangs nas /
NK125(co)003:5407: byams pa gling du lung bstan /
NK125(co)003:5408: zla ba'i gling du yo ga bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:5409: nyi ma'i gling du rgyud lung bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:5410: yak+sha ltag 'og gling du sngags bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:5411: brda sbyor tshang mang gling du brda sprad /
NK125(co)003:5412: dag pa khrus khang gling du khrims bcas /
NK125(co)003:5413: byang chub gling du sems bskyed /
NK125(co)003:5414: sgra bsgyur gling du sgra bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:5416: snang ba'i gling du mdo bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:5417: bsam gtan gling du sgom grwa btsugs /
NK125(co)003:5418: pe har gling du rten btsugs /
NK125(co)003:5420: bee ro tsa na'i gling du slob ma'i grwa btsugs /
NK125(co)003:5421: de ltar dam pa'i chos mang po dar zhing rgyas par mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:5423: sba bzhed pa bsam yas lo bcu gsum la tshar bar bzhed /
NK125(co)003:5424: thang yig pa lo lnga la 'byongs zer bas /
NK125(co)003:5425: yun de tsam bzhugs pa yang shugs las shes pa yin no //
NK125(co)003:5426: tshul gzhan yang phur pa man ngag drug pa'i lo rgyus las /
NK125(co)003:5427: slob dpon gshegs pa la mnga' bdag gis bshol lan gnyis su btab pas ma gnang /
NK125(co)003:5428: yang slob dpon chen po lags /
NK125(co)003:5429: bdag gi mnga' thang 'di thams cad 'bul bas bzhugs par zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK125(co)003:5432: khyed kyi rgya gru gu hor gsum btul ba'i mnga'
NK125(co)003:5433: thang longs spyod 'di kun rtsed mo tsam skyo sangs
NK125(co)003:5434: yin mod / khyod kyi yang dbon gyi ring la rgyal khrims 'jig /
NK125(co)003:5435: rgyal po la 'khur ba'i mi mi 'byung /
NK125(co)003:5436: mdzad pa la bya dga' gnang ba mi 'byung /
NK125(co)003:5437: ngan pa la chad pa mi gcod /
NK125(co)003:5438: gdug pa sbrul lta bu khrims la gnod pa yong bas /
NK125(co)003:5439: de la phan pa'i man ngag mang du bzhag go gsungs /
NK125(co)003:5440: yang nan gyis bzhugs par zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK125(co)003:5441: 'o na nga nan ltar sdod dgos na rgyal po'i sku tshe la 'gyur ldog med pa zhig byed /
NK125(co)003:5442: bye ma'i gling khams ne'u sing du bsgyur /
NK125(co)003:5443: ri la bug pa gtod de lam bya /
NK125(co)003:5446: ya gi mang yul byams sprin nas /
NK125(co)003:5447: ma gi kong yul bres sna yan chod kyi gtsang po sbubs su 'jug /
NK125(co)003:5448: rgyal khams la 'gyur ldog med pa zhig bya'o gsungs /
NK125(co)003:5449: der blon po kun gros byas pas /
NK125(co)003:5450: matha'i mon bu 'dis ni gang byas thams cad 'ong par 'dug pas /
NK125(co)003:5451: rgyal khams 'gyur ldog med pa de bzang ste /
NK125(co)003:5453: rgyal po'i sku tshe la 'gyur ldog med pa bzang ste /
NK125(co)003:5454: 'o cag la jo bo 'di lta bu mi 'ong /
NK125(co)003:5455: bye ma'i gling khams ne'u sing du gtong ba yang bzang ste /
NK125(co)003:5457: ri la bug pa phug na dus lan gcig tsa na yul la btsan pa mi 'ong /
NK125(co)003:5458: rkun ma'i mgo la 'brug btags na dus lan cig tsa na mi phongs pas btsal bas mi rnyed /
NK125(co)003:5459: byis phrug la gzi btags na gzhon pa rtse mo la chags nas tshar bskyed mi 'ong /
NK125(co)003:5460: gtsang po sbubs su bcug na yul gyi stangs mi phyed /
NK125(co)003:5461: 'dir phar thong zer nas blon po rnams kyis sdod du ma ster ro //
NK125(co)003:5462: de nas slob dpon gshegs pas /
NK125(co)003:5464: bdag gi thugs dam bsam yas 'di ma 'ongs pa'i
NK125(co)003:5465: dus lan gcig tsa na gso ba'i cha rkyen ji
NK125(co)003:5467: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas mkha' 'gro ma rnams bskul te /
NK125(co)003:5468: de rnams kyis nor sna mang po bsdus nas byung
NK125(co)003:5469: ba mnga' bdag la gnang nas gso ba'i cha rkyen
NK125(co)003:5471: bdag gi gtsug lag khang 'di dus lan gcig tsa
NK125(co)003:5472: na bye mas mnan te mi mchi lags sam zhus
NK125(co)003:5473: pas / slob dpon gyis dgongs pa skad cig ma
NK125(co)003:5474: zhig mdzad pas lha khang gi mtha' thams cad thang
NK125(co)003:5477: bdag ma shi ba'i gong du 'khor gcig cis kyang phebs par zhu zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:5479: 'phrul gyi rgyal po dad pa'i dgongs pa yin //
NK125(co)003:5480: bdag la lan gcig slar la byon cig pa //
NK125(co)003:5481: bdag kyang de ltar mchi bar dga' lags te //
NK125(co)003:5482: rgyal khams mang po chos kyis skyong ba dang //
NK125(co)003:5483: lha ma yin gyi yul du bstan pa'i sgron me bya ba dang //
NK125(co)003:5484: lho nub srin po'i kha gnon bya ba dang //
NK125(co)003:5485: thugs rjes 'dul skal du ma mchis lags pas //
NK125(co)003:5486: gal te bdag gis lan gcig ma brtol nas //
NK125(co)003:5487: bla med 'og min gnas su mjal ba dang //
NK125(co)003:5488: sngon yang mchod rten khri 'phangs brtsigs bzhin smon //
NK125(co)003:5490: yang mnga' bdag gis lan gcig cis nas kyang 'byon 'tshal zhus pas /
NK125(co)003:5492: dus lan gcig na rgyab na gangs yod pa /
NK125(co)003:5493: mdun sa yi lte bar 'dug pa zhig tu sprul ba'i rgyal blon 'byung bas /
NK125(co)003:5494: dus de tsa na khor cig 'ong ste mjal lo gsungs nas bzhud do zhes bshad de /
NK125(co)003:5495: de ltar bka' ma'i lo rgyus khungs ma mang po zhig tu byung ba dang /
NK125(co)003:5496: sba bzhed pa'i lugs de dag 'dra min ma gtogs khungs gcig par 'dug ste /
NK125(co)003:5497: yab rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi skabs yin /
NK125(co)003:5498: khri srong gshegs nas slob dpon dang lha sras mu khri btsan pos zab lung du byon /
NK125(co)003:5499: lha sras kyi sku tshe bskyab pa la rnam rgyal mchod rten bzhengs /
NK125(co)003:5500: shog bswe la slob dpon gyi sku 'dra byas pa da lta yang yod /
NK125(co)003:5501: srin yul du thegs dus gung thang la thog tu lha sras kyis bskyal /
NK125(co)003:5502: dus kyi tha ma la lha sras kyi gdung brgyud gung thang du 'ong bar lung bstan /
NK125(co)003:5503: de nas dus ring zhig na mnga' ris rdzong kha pa byung /
NK125(co)003:5504: da lta yang yod bzhin du slob dpon gyis bod
NK125(co)003:5505: du yun ring bzhugs pa'i gtan tshigs kyang gsar rnying
NK125(co)003:5506: gnyis ka'i gang zag lo rgyus la 'dris pa dag
NK125(co)003:5508: de lta bu'i slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa de
NK125(co)003:5509: shing pho spre'u'i lo la srin po 'dul du gshegs
NK125(co)003:5510: pa nas / da lta'i me pho rta lo 'di
NK125(co)003:5511: yan la lo brgyad brgya dang drug cu rtsa gnyis
NK125(co)003:5512: pa nas / 'das la / dge slong chos kyi
NK125(co)003:5513: seng ges mnga' ris rdzong khar sprul sku mchog ldan
NK125(co)003:5514: mgon po'i drung du brtsis pa ltar na /
NK125(co)003:5515: slob dpon bod du phebs pa nas /
NK125(co)003:5516: me rta 'di yan la lo brgyad brgya dang gnyis 'das zer te /
NK125(co)003:5517: drug cu skor gcig gis nyung bas /
NK125(co)003:5518: 'di gnyis gang dag pa'ang blo gros dang ldan pa rnams kyis dpyod par mdzod cig /
NK125(co)003:5519: bstan pa'i gnas tshad la mi mthun pa mang bas gzhan du shes par bya la /
NK125(co)003:5520: o rgyan gling pa ni bstan pa lnga brgya phrag
NK125(co)003:5521: bcu gnas pa la khong gi gter 'byung brtsams pa'i
NK125(co)003:5522: sa mo yos de yan lag lnga brgya phrag bdun
NK125(co)003:5523: rdzogs / da lta lnga brgya phrag gsum yod de /
NK125(co)003:5525: bstan zhabs lnga brgya phrag bdun nye ba na //
NK125(co)003:5526: o rgyan ngas kyang thugs rjes skyobs sam lta //
NK125(co)003:5527: zhes gsungs pas so gsungs te /
NK125(co)003:5529: lnga brgya phrag bdun nye ba na //
NK125(co)003:5530: zhes pa lnga brgya phrag drug pa rdzogs su nye ba de yin /
NK125(co)003:5531: de tshun la lnga brgya phrag bzhi yod dam snyam /
NK125(co)003:5532: gang ltar khong ba'i sa mo yos de ta si
NK125(co)003:5533: byang rgyal gyi dgung lo sum cu so brgyad pa
NK125(co)003:5534: / karma pa rang byung rdo rje gshegs pa'i lo de yin /
NK125(co)003:5535: de nas me rta 'di yan la lo nyis brgya dang bdun cu rtsa drug 'das so //
NK125(co)003:5536: lhag ma stong dang bdun brgya bdun cu don bzhir nges la /
NK125(co)003:5537: lnga brgya phrag bdun rdzogs mtshams su nye ba nas
NK125(co)003:5538: yin na stong dang nyis brgya don bzhi gnas pa'o
NK125(co)003:5539: // sa skya ba'i lugs kyi sum stong bdun brgya so dgu 'das /
NK125(co)003:5540: lhag ma bdun brgya re gcig /
NK125(co)003:5541: rtags tsam 'dzin pa lnga brgya dang bcas pa gnas par bzhed do //
NK125(co)003:5542: de ltar thang yig rnams grong tshig mi mdzes pa
NK125(co)003:5543: dag gis mog mog por byas snang ngo gsungs pa
NK125(co)003:5544: yang bden mod / 'on kyang 'phags pa rnams ni
NK125(co)003:5545: sems can gyi blo dang 'tshams pa'i chos ston pa
NK125(co)003:5546: yang bden mod / po yin pas / gdul bya
NK125(co)003:5547: khyim pa rnams kyis go bde bar gyur na dad
NK125(co)003:5548: pa skye ba'i rgyur 'gro ba la dgongs sam snyam
NK125(co)003:5549: yang bden mod / po yin pas / / de
NK125(co)003:5550: bzhin du bdag gis kyang mi shes bzhin du bri
NK125(co)003:5551: ba 'di la dgos pa med pa ma yin te
NK125(co)003:5552: yang bden mod / po yin pas / / / ji skad du /
NK125(co)003:5553: pad+ma 'byung gnas bdag ni da 'gro bas //
NK125(co)003:5554: nga dang ma mjal mos gus byed pa rnams //
NK125(co)003:5555: gser dngul snag tshas pad 'byung rnam thar bris //
NK125(co)003:5556: nyan dang klog dang 'dzin dang gus byed rnams //
NK125(co)003:5557: 'gal rkyen bar chad gzhan gyis 'tshe las skyob //
NK125(co)003:5558: bar do med cing bde ba can du 'gro //
NK125(co)003:5559: de sogs yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK125(co)003:5560: zhes gsungs pa ltar bris pa lags /
NK125(co)003:5561: mtha' rtogs pa po zhig ni gang na yang med pa 'dra ste /
NK125(co)003:5562: ding sang gi gsar ma pa mkhas pa dag grub
NK125(co)003:5563: thob 'dar phyar gyi gter ma rta mgrin yang gsang
NK125(co)003:5564: zhes mgrin gcig tu sgrogs mod /
NK125(co)003:5568: rgyang po grags pa dbang phyug dang gsum gyis /
NK125(co)003:5569: brag dmar lha sa'i yer pa rdzong gi brag pho bo rta'i rna ba can nas bton pas /
NK125(co)003:5573: rgyang po la mdze byung bas /
