NK125(co)003:5574: po ti zhu ston bya ba rta mgrin gyi grub thob tu grags pa zhig la gtad de /
NK125(co)003:5575: dbang bka' lung bka' med pa la yun ring po 'byams /
NK125(co)003:5576: dus phyis grub thob 'dar phyar nags rgyal na bzhugs dus /
NK125(co)003:5577: zhang tshes zla grags zer ba'i sngags pa zhig tu
NK125(co)003:5578: slob dpon pad+mas sprul te rta bod kyi dbang lung
NK125(co)003:5579: sbyin / sngags kyi de h+r+aihru bsgyur la sgrubs shig
NK125(co)003:5580: gsungs pa ltar byas pas grub pa thob pa der
NK125(co)003:5581: sbyin / gda'/ de bas na lhad med pa zhig
NK125(co)003:5582: gsar ma ba dag la'ang dka' ba 'dra snyam ste
NK125(co)003:5584: de nas srin yul rnga yab gling sog kha yu ba nang du bstan pa de na /
NK125(co)003:5585: gling bzhi gling phran dang gling chung bsdoms pas gling nyi shu rtsa gnyis yod pa las /
NK125(co)003:5586: dbus na sha khrag za byed kyi gling na grong
NK125(co)003:5587: bye ba dgu yod pa'i dbus byang shar dang nye
NK125(co)003:5588: ba / mtsho mu le 'phrul gyi me long bya ba'i rgya mtsho /
NK125(co)003:5589: de las chu rnga phyogs bzhir 'bab pa zhig yod /
NK125(co)003:5590: de'i dbus na zangs mdog dpal ri chu nas dpangs su rgyang grags nyi shu dang /
NK125(co)003:5591: khor yug tu rgyang grags drug cu yod pa /
NK125(co)003:5592: ri de'i rtse na srin po'i rgyal po de bsgral te dad nas sbar /
NK125(co)003:5593: slob dpon nyid sngar gyi rgyal po ji lta bar sprul pas /
NK125(co)003:5595: 'o cag gi rgyal po ni sngar bas kya gzi mdangs che'o zhes sgrog go //
NK125(co)003:5596: der srin po rnams dang lha ma srin sde brgyad
NK125(co)003:5597: thams cad bsdus te sngar bas ches 'phags pa'i pho
NK125(co)003:5598: brang gi bkod pa chen po /
NK125(co)003:5599: rgya srang thams cad mig mang ris su yod pa /
NK125(co)003:5600: lcags ri rim pa bdun gyis bskor ba'i nang ma
NK125(co)003:5601: gsum la rta babs phyogs re la rim pa gsum
NK125(co)003:5602: gsum byas te bcu gnyis bcu gnyis dang ldan pa
NK125(co)003:5604: lcog brgyad brgyad po thams cad kyang srin po'i thod pa 'ba' zhig gis brtsigs pa /
NK125(co)003:5605: de la rgya sgo chen po sum cu rtsa gnyis btsug pa /
NK125(co)003:5606: pho brang chen po de'i mtha' bskor la srin po'i
NK125(co)003:5607: grong khyer yod pa'i phyogs mtshams brgyad du tshogs khang
NK125(co)003:5608: chen po bzhi ru sprul pa re mdzad de /
NK125(co)003:5609: shar zhi ba chos kyi tshogs khang du slob dpon
NK125(co)003:5610: pan+di ta'i chas kyis sde snod gsum gyi chos 'chad
NK125(co)003:5611: / lho rgyas pa longs spyod kyi tshogs khang du
NK125(co)003:5612: slob dpon mgon po tshe dpag med du bzhengs te
NK125(co)003:5613: rgyud sde rgya mtsho las rab 'byams kyi chos ston
NK125(co)003:5614: / / nub pad+ma dbang gi tshogs khang na slob
NK125(co)003:5615: dpon dpal rta mgrin du bzhengs nas thams cad dbang
NK125(co)003:5616: du sdud cing gsang sngags ma rgyud gtso bor ston
NK125(co)003:5617: / / / byang sbyor sgrol phrin las kyi tshogs
NK125(co)003:5618: khang na slob dpon gu ru drag por bzhengs te
NK125(co)003:5619: khrims gnyis las 'gal bar byed pa'i srin po rnams
NK125(co)003:5620: tshar gcod cing sbyor sgrol gyi chos ston /
NK125(co)003:5621: dbus na pho brang pad+ma 'od kyi gzhal yas khang
NK125(co)003:5622: na thog rim pa gsum dang ldan pa'i 'og khang
NK125(co)003:5623: na rin po che'i khri dang srin po bsgyel ba'i
NK125(co)003:5624: steng na / slob dpon khro bo chen po sku tshad srin po sum 'gyur las che ba /
NK125(co)003:5625: zab ber dmar smug khra bo gsol ba la /
NK125(co)003:5626: men dri dmar pos thod bcings ba /
NK125(co)003:5627: seng ge'i g.yang gzhi gsol ba /
NK125(co)003:5628: sku las me 'bar ba 'jigs su rung ba gcig bzhugs /
NK125(co)003:5629: yum ye shes mtsho rgyal yang khro mo'i rnam pa
NK125(co)003:5630: can du bzhugs pa'i 'khor du rig 'dzin 'bum phrag
NK125(co)003:5631: lnga dang / phyi 'khor mkha' 'gro chos skyong /
NK125(co)003:5632: bran g.yog lha srin sde brgyad kyis bskor ba yod de /
NK125(co)003:5635: 'khor gyi bkod pa rig 'dzin 'bum phrag lnga dang /
NK125(co)003:5636: ye shes mkha' 'gro chos skyong dpag tu med pas bskor ba yod do //
NK125(co)003:5637: de la bar khang na gu ru mtshan brgyad dang /
NK125(co)003:5638: steng khang na thod phreng rtsal rigs lnga'o //
NK125(co)003:5639: grong khyer de'i shar na rdo'i thang la yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i chu bo 'bab pa /
NK125(co)003:5640: lho na tsan+dana gyi nags dang 'bras bu can gyi shing gi tshal yod pa /
NK125(co)003:5641: nub na nyams su dga' ba'i skyed mos tshal dang /
NK125(co)003:5642: byang na rin po che'i brag ri mchod rten rang byung mang pos gtams pa /
NK125(co)003:5643: sa phyogs thams cad pad+ma dang me tog sna tshogs pas yongs su gang ba zhig go //
NK125(co)003:5644: de nas rnga yab kyi shar stod dz+aa ti'i nags gling bya ba na /
NK125(co)003:5645: srin po'i grong khyer 'bum tsho nyi shu rtsa gcig yod la /
NK125(co)003:5646: srin po lha las babs pa'i rigs can bya ba nam mkha' la 'phur nus pa /
NK125(co)003:5647: gcan gzan gyi sha dang dz+aa ti'i 'bras bu la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5648: der slob dpon gyi rnam sprul bde ba r+aa dza
NK125(co)003:5649: bya bas rgyal po mdzad de sgyu 'phrul gyi chos
NK125(co)003:5651: rnga yab kyi shar smad na bun 'thib pa bya
NK125(co)003:5652: ba'i gling na grong khyer bye ba phrag gsum yod
NK125(co)003:5653: / srin po dri 'dzin kun tu rgyu zhes pa'i rigs can /
NK125(co)003:5654: khrag gi dri tshor na skad cig la rgyang grags bco brgyad du sleb pa /
NK125(co)003:5655: sha chen dang khrag chen la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5656: de na smra ba'i seng ge zhes bya ba'i rgyal
NK125(co)003:5657: por sku sprul nas 'jam dpal sku'i chos ston cing
NK125(co)003:5658: don mdzad do // rnga yab kyi lho phyogs zang
NK125(co)003:5659: thal ke ri brtsegs pa'i gling bya ba grong khyer
NK125(co)003:5661: srin po grul bum pho nya'i rigs can bya ba
NK125(co)003:5662: yod de lag pa brgya stong gi mtshon cha 'debs
NK125(co)003:5663: / ri dwags dang shi sha la longs spyod do //
NK125(co)003:5664: de na rgyal po thod pa'i phreng ba can zhes
NK125(co)003:5665: bya ba'i rnam 'phrul gyi ma mo dang gshin rje'i
NK125(co)003:5666: chos ston cing don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:5667: rnga yab kyi nub stod sha mkhar can bya ba'i
NK125(co)003:5668: gling na grong khyer 'bum tsho nyi shu rtsa dgu
NK125(co)003:5669: / srin po thams cad kyang nad nyung la dug gis mi tshugs pa sha stag yod /
NK125(co)003:5670: zas su sa 'og gi sa bdag klu gnyan gyi phrug gu rnams brkus te longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5671: der khyung chen 'bar ba zhes bya ba'i rgyal por
NK125(co)003:5672: sprul nas chos phyag rgya chen po gsungs te don
NK125(co)003:5673: mdzad do // rnga yab kyi nub smad khrag mtsho
NK125(co)003:5674: khol ma zhes bya ba'i gling na grong khyer bye
NK125(co)003:5675: mdzad do // ba gnyis yod / me tog dang chu la gnas pa'i srog chags la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5676: srin po'i tshogs de dag kyang chu la mi bying ba'i rdzu 'phrul dang ldan /
NK125(co)003:5677: de na gtum po me dbal bya ba'i rgyal por
NK125(co)003:5678: sprul nas spyan ras gzigs kyi chos gsungs nas don
NK125(co)003:5679: mdzad do // rnga yab byang na nor bu'i gling bya ba grong khyer bye ba gcig yod /
NK125(co)003:5680: nor bu dang sha khrag sna tshogs la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5682: der lag na rdo rje bya ba'i rgyal por sprul
NK125(co)003:5683: nas chos drag sngags bstan srung gi don mdzad do
NK125(co)003:5684: // shar lho na 'bar ba'i gling bya ba yod /
NK125(co)003:5685: de na srin po glog phreng gi rigs 'bri g.yag dang ra lug la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5688: de na zil gnon me 'od zhes bya ba'i sprul pas rgyal po mdzad cing /
NK125(co)003:5689: ma mo'i rgyud lung gi chos kyis don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:5690: lho nub rak+sha 'khrug pa'i gling bya bar /
NK125(co)003:5691: srin po lang ka mgrin bcu'i rigs lus gcig las sprul pa bcu phrag 'gyed /
NK125(co)003:5692: zas su mi rta khyi gsum brku zhing za /
NK125(co)003:5694: de na rak+sha thod phreng bya ba'i rgyal por sprul te /
NK125(co)003:5695: khyab 'jug gi 'jug pa bcu las brtsams te /
NK125(co)003:5696: khyad par gsang chen bla na med pa dus kyi 'khor lo chos ston cing don mdzad do //
NK125(co)003:5697: nub byang rlung nag 'khrug pa'i gling na grong khyer 'bum tsho gsum /
NK125(co)003:5698: srin po karti ka'i rigs g.yang sar lhung bas mi skyon pa'i rigs yod /
NK125(co)003:5699: sems can sna tshogs pa'i sha khrag la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5700: de na seng ge sgra sgrog bya bar sku sprul
NK125(co)003:5701: pa'i rgyal pos 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi chos bstan
NK125(co)003:5703: byang shar mun nag 'khrug pa'i gling na grong khyer 'bum tsho nyi shu rtsa gcig yod /
NK125(co)003:5704: gling de phal che ba srin po pho mo mi bsrun pas gang /
NK125(co)003:5705: 'gro ba'i bla dang tshe srog la longs spyod /
NK125(co)003:5706: mi snang ba'i rdzu 'phrul dang ldan /
NK125(co)003:5707: de na slob dpon gyi sprul pa gtsug na me
NK125(co)003:5708: 'bar bya bas rgyal po mdzad cing chos spyi dang
NK125(co)003:5709: khyad par du dmod pa drag sngags kyi sgo nas
NK125(co)003:5710: don mdzad do // de rnams kyi dbus sha khrag
NK125(co)003:5711: za byed kyi gling bya ba la grong khyer bye
NK125(co)003:5713: slob dpon gyi sku dngos kyis rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs pas 'dul zhing /
NK125(co)003:5714: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos sgor bcug nas /
NK125(co)003:5715: phyin chad 'dzam bu'i gling gi skye 'gro rnams la
NK125(co)003:5716: srin po dag gis gnod cing 'tshe ba mi 'byung
NK125(co)003:5717: bar mdzad de / mdor na khams gsum 'khor ba
NK125(co)003:5718: ma stong gi bar du bzhugs te 'gro ba'i don
NK125(co)003:5719: yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar mdzad pa yin la
NK125(co)003:5720: bar mdzad de / / bod 'dir mtha' dmag lhags nas 'dul ba'i bstan pa nub par byed /
NK125(co)003:5721: de rjes sngags kyi bstan pa gos dkar gyon pa mang po 'byung zhing /
NK125(co)003:5722: de dag gi nang du'ang sprul pa re 'byon par gsungs shing /
NK125(co)003:5723: skal ba dang ldan pa'i gang zag 'od lus su grol ba yang mang du 'byung la /
NK125(co)003:5724: tshe lo bcu pa'i bar du gsang sngags ston /
NK125(co)003:5725: de nas yar 'phel gyi dus su byams snying rje
NK125(co)003:5726: la sogs pa tshad med bzhi dang dge ba bcu'i
NK125(co)003:5727: chos bstan pas / mi rnams bsod nams yar 'phel
NK125(co)003:5728: te rigs gzugs 'byor pa che dang bsod nams gong
NK125(co)003:5729: chos bstan pas / 'phel du 'gro / tshe lo
NK125(co)003:5730: brgyad khri ba'i dus su byams pa 'jig rten du
NK125(co)003:5732: de dus slob dpon nyid rgyal sras 'gro ba kun
NK125(co)003:5734: gdul bya mchog gi skal ba can mang po la
NK125(co)003:5735: gsang sngags kyi chos 'khor bskor ba nyid gsungs so
NK125(co)003:5736: // gzhan du na longs spyod rdzogs sku spyan ras
NK125(co)003:5737: gzigs tshul mi 'dra ba brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs
NK125(co)003:5738: pa sgrub thabs brgya rtsa ru 'byung ba 'di dag
NK125(co)003:5739: // dang / sprul pa'i sku bskal bzang gi sangs rgyas stong dang /
NK125(co)003:5740: de dag gi yon bdag 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK125(co)003:5741: po stong la sogs pa yang slob dpon chen po
NK125(co)003:5742: 'di'i rnam par 'phrul pa kho na yin te /
NK125(co)003:5743: su zhig gis bsam par nus /
NK125(co)003:5744: brjod pa'i mtha' nam yang rdzogs pa'i skabs med do //
NK125(co)003:5745: rgyal ba mchog de'i rnam par thar ba'i rabs //
NK125(co)003:5746: ngo mtshar yid kyi dga' ston dbyar gyi rnga //
NK125(co)003:5747: skal bzang thar 'dod yongs kyi rna ba'i rgyan //
NK125(co)003:5748: las rab skal bar ldan pa'i dpal du gyur //
NK125(co)003:5749: bya rog 'gros kyis gling bzhi'i mtha' 'jal dang //
NK125(co)003:5750: rgya mtsho'i gting mtha' mdzub mos 'tshol ba bzhin //
NK125(co)003:5751: rgyal ba'i yon tan phrin las nam mkha'i khyon //
NK125(co)003:5752: sus kyang tshad bzung nus pa'i go skabs ci //
NK125(co)003:5753: 'on kyang 'gro 'dis mthong ngam thos kyang rung //
NK125(co)003:5754: gang zhig mos pas sangs rgyas sar sbyor la //
NK125(co)003:5755: log par lta ba'ang 'khor ba mtha' can du //
NK125(co)003:5756: don chen thob par 'gyur phyir bdag gis bkod //
NK125(co)003:5757: rmongs zhen rdzun lung gtam gyis ma bslad cing //
NK125(co)003:5758: sngon chad ma grags pa yang 'dir brjod med //
NK125(co)003:5759: mkhas pa gong ma'i bzhed tshul gung bsgrigs pa //
NK125(co)003:5760: tshul 'dir nongs na mthol bshags tshangs par stsol //
NK125(co)003:5761: mdzo khal khur du longs pa'i po ti la //
NK125(co)003:5762: mi mkhas grong tshig 'khrul pas ma sbags par //
NK125(co)003:5763: 'di bas lhag pa'i gsal dag 'dus pa zhig /
NK125(co)003:5764: byed po yod na lan brgyar phyag bgyir 'os //
NK125(co)003:5765: grags dang mkhas 'dod lugs gzhan sun 'byin phyir //
NK125(co)003:5766: 'khyog po'i ngag gis bshad pa 'di na med //
NK125(co)003:5767: ji bzhin smras pa'i bsod nams mchog des bdag /
NK125(co)003:5768: skyob pa pad+ma rgyal po de mtshungs shog /
NK125(co)003:5769: mkha' dbyings bde chen rol pa'i cho 'phrul kun tu 'phro ba'i rtsal g.yos pas //
NK125(co)003:5770: 'dod rgu'i 'byung gnas ye shes rgya mtsho rgyal ba rgyal sras sprin 'phro ba //
NK125(co)003:5771: zab cing rgya che rab tu zhi ba dmigs med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK125(co)003:5772: rgyal ba kun gyi yum mchog de yi bka' drin dran pas rtag tu 'dud //
NK125(co)003:5773: 'di sbyar bsod nams dge ba'i char rgyun gyis //
NK125(co)003:5774: thub bstan phan bde 'byung ba'i sa gzhi'i khyon //
NK125(co)003:5775: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i lo thog rab rgyas te //
NK125(co)003:5776: 'gro kun nyer 'tsho'i dpal la spyod par shog /
NK125(co)003:5777: gser gyi rnga yab ji lta'i byang phyogs ljongs //
NK125(co)003:5778: phun tshogs 'dod rgu'i bkod pa rnam bkra ba //
NK125(co)003:5779: gtsug lag khang bzang chags pa'i ri ngogs su //
NK125(co)003:5780: zil gnon zhes bya'i lo la 'di sbyar ro ////
NK125(co)003:5783: rgyal kun 'dus zhal snyigs 'gro'i skyabs gcig pu //
NK125(co)003:5784: dus gsum mkhyen pa o rgyan rdo rje 'chang //
NK125(co)003:5785: gang gi rnam thar mdzad pa bsam yas las //
NK125(co)003:5786: tshur mthong snang ngor cha tsam nyer mtshon pa //
NK125(co)003:5787: khungs ldan bka' gter lo rgyus rgya mtsho che'i //
NK125(co)003:5788: snying po'i yang snying bcud du phyungs 'di ko //
NK125(co)003:5789: mkhas grub bye ba'i ded dpon sog zlog pa //
NK125(co)003:5790: blo gros rgyal mtshan bzang po'i legs bshad do //
NK125(co)003:5791: tshul 'di 'gro mang dad pa 'phel slad dang //
NK125(co)003:5792: mgon de'i bka' drin dran pas yid bskul te //
NK125(co)003:5793: bdag nyid lhag bsam 'bad brtson du ma yis //
NK125(co)003:5794: phyi mo btsal zhus spar du bsgrub la phyogs //
NK125(co)003:5795: de tshe sprin dgon o rgyan tshe ring gis //
NK125(co)003:5796: gtong ba'i mdzod sgo gtan pa med phyes te //
NK125(co)003:5797: chos kyi ring bsrel ci dgar rab 'jo ba'i //
NK125(co)003:5798: ngo mtshar 'phrul chen shing rta 'di drangs so //
NK125(co)003:5799: legs byas las byung rnam dkar cha ci mchis //
NK125(co)003:5800: bstan dang 'gro ba'i phan bde'i btsas su bsngo //
NK125(co)003:5801: mchog gsang ring lugs nub med 'phel rgyas shing //
NK125(co)003:5802: rnam mang gdul bya smin grol bkra shis shog /
